%%%Chapter-4
4th chapter typed with modifications as suggested (19.11.2019)
caturtho'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

tathā tau balasampannau vajrakālau mahābalau |
pṛṣṭavān graharājendraṃ bhārgavaṃ bhṛgunandanam [004:001]
bhagavannasmattāttena preṣitā vinayaṃ prati |
diśo gatāstathā deśāḥ saptadvīpā vasundharā [004:002]
[vijayaṃ ka ga]
nirjitāḥ saptapātālā vaśe kṛtvā ca tatprajāḥ |
nṛpānuśāsane sthāpya tava pārśvamihāgatāḥ [004:003]
[nṛpāḥ svaśāsane ka ga]
kenopāyena indrādīn jitvā svarga jayāmahe |
| etadeva mamācakṣva sarvavidyākṛtaśrama [004:004]|
śukra uvāca
jambūdvīpaṃ samastantu saptadvīpā vasundharā |
pātālāḥ sukhasādhyāstu divaṃ duḥkhena sidhyati [004:005]
yasmiṃstiṣṭhati deveśaḥ sarvadevanuto hariḥ |
viṣṇuḥsarvātmako devo brahmā vedaviśāradaḥ [004:006]
[devamūlo hariḥ khapustakasya pāṭhāntare]
bṛhaspatirmahāprājño arthaśāstrakṛtaśramaḥ |
indro mahābalaścaiva dhanado vahrirniṛtī [004:007]
marūdvāyuryamo yatra yatra candradivākarau |
viśvedevā vasurudrā graha nakṣatra tārakāḥ [004:008]
[marudvādyayayau ka||
na jetuṃ śakyate kāla divaṃ dharmeṇa rakṣitam |
rājadharmopadeśena bhūpātālāni bhuñjatha [004:009]
[bhuñjata ka ga]
anyathā dharmataḥ prāptaṃ rājyaṃ nāśamupaiti hi |
mārjāramūṣikaṃ yad vadyuddhaṃ dhvāṅkṣolūkaṃ yathā [004:010]
[mahan ka ga]
mahiṣāśvaṃ yathā yuddhaṃ yathā dantimṛgādhipam |
evaṃ yuṣmatsuraiḥ sārdha yuddhamekāṅgamucyate |
yuddhabhogaṃ tathā kālaṃ deśañcaiva na jānatā |
[004:011]
[yuddhamekaṃ samucyate kha pustakasya pāṭhāntare; yuddhabhāgaṃ ka ga |
samuddhigaṃ tathā kālaṃ deśañcaivamajāna tām-iti kha pustakasya pāṭhāntare]
asmadripubalāśaktiṃ ye yudhyanti narādhipāḥ |
ātmanāśaṃ vrajantyete nṛpā nayaparāṅmukhāḥ [004:012]
[ ātma0 ka ga; āśu ka ga]
nayo hi balavān yuddhe daivasampatsamanvitaḥ |
tathā puruṣakārantu buddhvā yudhyanti ye nṛpāḥ [004:013]
te jayaṃ śatru nāśantu labhante avicāraṇāt |
pṛthvī puravarairyuktā saśailavanakānanā [004:014]
yāvajjīvaṃ sthirā teṣāṃ yeṣāṃ nīti kramāgatā |
dharmeṇa prāpya rājyaṃ te dharmādevajayo bhavet [004:015]
[na kramā0 ka; dharmo devejyayā ka]
devāśca-rudra-brahmendra-keśavā-ravi-candramāḥ |
teṣāṃ yo yodhamiccheta sa kathaṃ jāyate sukhī [004:016]
[eteṣāṃ yo dhanaṃ icchet ka |
eteṣāṃ yo vadhamicchet-ga]
na yuddhena vinā devāḥ sidhyanti hi kvacit dviṣāḥ |
yuddhe ghātaṃ bhaved vatsa bandhu vargaparikṣayaḥ [004:017]
kṣayaṃ yāti dhanaṃ yuddhe aśvadantimahābalāḥ |
same'pi punarviṣame yatra śaṅkarakeśavau [004:018]
[ kiṃ puna0 ka ga; keśavaśaṅkarā ka]
kāla uvāca
dṛṣṭīviṣā mahāghorā anantādyā mahoraghāḥ |
nirjitā asurā rakṣāḥ pātālatalavāsinaḥ [004:019]
na hi me śakyate jetuṃ śaṅkareṇa mahātmanā |
kimpunardevarājena brāhmaṇena varākiṇā [004:020]
[me kha; brahmaṇā ca ka ga]
vajradaṇḍasahāyasya mama khaḍgakarasya ca |
saṅgare ko bhavecchaktaḥ kālapāśena karṣitaḥ [004:021]
brahmā vā yadi vā rudraḥ sarvadevanamaskṛtaḥ |
asmākaṃ nirjitā pṛthvī tathā pātālagocarā [004:022]
[pātālagoragāḥ ka]
svāmino darśanādeva divaṃ prāptaṃ tato yadā |
jayastathā bhavet kīrtiḥ parājayaḥ parāgatiḥ [004:023]
[prārabhato ka]
prasthitā grahaśārdūṃla anujñāṃ dātumarhasi |
evaṃ śukraṃ samāpṛcchaya nabho māse tu cottare [004:024]
[madhe tu cottarām kha]
diśañcottaraṛkṣe ca dvitīyāyāṃ tato gatau |
nandanaṃ tau vanaṃ gatvā sarvasainyena tiṣṭhataḥ [004:025]
[á¹kṣeṇa ka]
yamāntakaḥ pūrvadiśi merau ghorastu cottare |
paścime vajradaṇḍastu kālo dakṣiṇataḥ svayam [004:026]
[merorthī0 ka]
evaṃ te veṣṭayitvā tu koṭikoṭiguṇena tu |
āruruhuḥ purīṃ yāmyāṃ merorurdhvamadhiṣṭhitām [004:027]
[ārūroha purīṃ yāmāṃ kha]
aneka parikhopetāṃ vaivasvatīṃ mahojjavalām |
tatra te kṛṣṇaghorāsyā daṇḍapāṇimahābalāḥ |
yamaścāruhya mahiṣaṃ kālapāśakarodyataḥ [004:028]
[yamaśca rurūhe ka ga]
tataḥ sā dānavī senā yuddhamānā mahāhave |
dāritā yamarājena svabalena mahātmanā [004:029]
tāṃ bhagnāṃ sahasā dṛṣṭvā krodhena tu sudīpitaḥ |
uttthan hālāhalaḥ śakra mahābalaparākramaḥ [004:030]
parśunā tu satejena sūryāyutaprameṇa ca |
jighāṃsan yamajāṃ senāṃ padminīmiva dantinaḥ [004:031]
yamāntakastathā cakre mahāmāyātmakaṃ balī |
mahiṣaṃ yamabhaṅgāya mahiṣasya mahābalam [004:032]
kāle caiva kṛtānte ca daṇḍinā vinipātite |
ekadhā daśadhā cāpi śatadhā ca sahasradhā [004:033]
[kālaṃ ka ga; kṛtāntaṃ ka ga; vinipātitaṃ ka; vāpi ka; śatadhāpi ka]
ayutāṃ lakṣakoṭīni māyāvī vai vinirmame |
tairdṛṣṭvā dharmarājastu cātmānaṃ śatadhāvṛtam [004:034]
[mi. ka]
vāhanāstrāṇi santyajya gatavān pāvakīṃ purīm |
durnirīkṣyāṃ ripu rghorastasya dṛṣṭvā tu vāhinīm [004:035]
[durnirīkṣaṃ vibhu ka]
ajāruḍhāṃ samastāste vahninā saha saṅgaram |
taṃ vahniṃ jvālālakṣeṇa kālānalamivotthitam [004:036]
[vahinarjvālākṣepena ka]
dadāha sahasā śakra vajradaṇḍasya vāhinīm |
purī tejasvatī tasya tāmra prākāra toraṇā [004:037]
[tejovatī ka]
struvahastāstathā viprā utthitā bahulakṣadhā |
dhyānena te'dahan sarvāṃ vāhinīṃ vibhughorajām [004:038]
[śruvahastā tathā ka]
evaṃ dṛṣṭvā tathā kālo daṇḍinā sarvagena ca |
māyā megha samutthena vāriṇā tūpaśāmayet [004:039
[sarvageṇa ka]
cetasāmṛtadāvānyaiḥ sarvān krūrān prarohayet |
evaṃ tacchamitaṃ tejo vahnikrodhasamudbhavam [004:040]
[cenamāmṛtasvādākṣaḥ sarvān krūrān prarohayat ka]
vavarṣa paṅkaśaivāla kadalīndīvarāṇi ca |
evaṃ tat pāvako dṛṣṭavā svasainyaṃ daṇḍanirjitam [004:041
tyaktvā tejo'bhimānantu gata indrāmarāvatīm |
indreṇa tau samāyātau dṛṣṭvā yamahutāśanau [004:042]
[samāyāntau ka ga]
mahākṣobhaṃ samāsthāya gajarājaṃ ruroha saḥ |
udāyacalasaṅkāśaṃ sindūrāruṇavigraham [004:043
ghaṇṭākiṅkiṇīśabdāḍhyaṃ cāmarairupaśobhitam |
caturdantaṃ mahānāgaṃ suraśatrubhayāvaham [004:044]
āruroha surādhyakṣo vajrapāṇirmahābalaḥ |
mātaliñca puraskṛtya viśvedevāstathāpare [004:045]
[puraskṛtvā ka]
vaiṣṇavā vāruṇā saumyā aindrāścāndrāstathaiva ca |
kubero dhanadaścandro vāyurvaruṇa eva ca [004:046]
[te bhaṭā ka |
bhallāṭāḥ kha-pustakasya pāṭhāntare]
śrutvā devendrasaṅgrāmaṃ sarve tatra yuyutsavaḥ |
āgatāḥ kṣaṇamātreṇa svāyudhodyatapāṇayaḥ [004:047]
evaṃ te tridaśāḥ śakkra saśakrāḥ saṅgarotsukāḥ |
śrutvā devaḥ svayaṃ tatra hyāgato garuḍadhvajaḥ [004:048]
indrastu paramaṃ deva śaṅkha cakra gadā dharam |
dṛṣṭavā papāta caraṇe bhaktyā stotreṇa pūjayet [004:049]
[caraṇau ka]
indra uvāca
namaste devadeveśa sarvadevamaya prabho |
śaṅkha cakra gadā hasta vanamālā vibhūṣaṇa [004:050]
[sarvadeveśa ka]
śrīvatsāṅka mahākāya kaustubhoraskamaṇḍita |
devārināśa deveśa vedagarbha namostu te [004:051]
devamūrtira mūtiśca veda yajña phalaprada |
trimūrtistrigatirdeva bhaktānāṃ bhayanāśana [004:052]
[vedamūrti-ka]
sama mitrāryudāsīna ripuṇāṃ kulanāśana |
trāhi māṃ devadeveśa pītavāso jagatpate [004:053]
[samamitrārimadhyastha devāri0 kha ga; pītavāsā ka]
dānavairbādhitā devāstvāmeva śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ |
nirjito yamayajñeśo bahnirdīptisamanvitaḥ [004:054]
evaṃ tvaṃ bhagavan prāptaḥ kiṃ karomi tadādiśa |
tathā śrutvā vaco viṣṇuḥ kṛpayā śakrabhāṣitam [004:055]
provāca vihasan devo mā bhaiṣīrmama sannidhau |
yadyapi devadeveśa umā dehārdha hāriṇaḥ [004:056]
[ghāriṇā ka]
āgatastasya devendra tathāpi arirhanyatām |
kintu kāraṇasadbhāvaṃ kathayāmi śṛṇuṣva tat [004:057]
[parihanyatām kha]
viṣṇuruvāca
āsīd dundubhirnāmā'sāvasurāṇāṃ prabhūttamaḥ |
tena jitāḥ surā sarve brahmavaraprabhāvataḥ [004:058]
ajeyo brahmasūryāṇāṃ yamasyāsmākameva ca |
tadā nirjitya devāṃstu svarṇāccayāvayate kila [004:059]
[ajayo ka ga; tathā ka]
tāvat tasya mahābāho īśaḥ śailaṅgamo'bhavat |
tadā paśyati deveśīṃ śaṅkarasya tanusthitām [004:060]
[devasya ka ga]
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā kṣobhamāpannaḥ kāmavihvalacetanaḥ |
devīṃ samudyato vaktuṃ devena ca sa īkṣitaḥ [004:061]
[devī samudyato dharttu ka ga]
tataḥ sa sahasā dagdho netrajenānalena tu |
devadevasya kopena dānavo bhasmatāṃ gataḥ [004:062]
sāyudhaḥ sarathaḥ krūraḥ sapadātiḥ savāhanaḥ |
sahasā bhasmībhūtaṃ taṃ daṣṭavā devastrilocanaḥ [004:063]
[taṃ sahasā ka]
raktapītāsitaśyāmā bhaṣmāddhūritameva ca |
gṛhītvā sitabhasmena devīñcāpyavadhūnayat [004:064]
[bhasmāllavitameva ca ka]
tasya hastakarāsphālād bandhūnanāvasānataḥ |
uddhṛtā mahati vartiḥ sarvavarṇakabhūṣitā [004:065]
[udghṛtā ka; sarvatantukabhūṣitā ka]
tāṃ tapantīṃ samālokya umāṃ devanamaskṛtām tasmin samudbhavācchāyā sarvalakṣaṇalakṣitā [004:066]
[umā devanamaskṛtā ka]
dvitīyaṃ devabhāgantu yācamānā mahābalā |
tadā umā dadau śāpaṃ smṛtvā ghoraṃ mahāsuram [004:067]
gaccha pāpa durācāra bhūtalaṃ tvaṃ mahābala |
tathārūpo bhavedghoro nīla megha sama prabhaḥ [004:068]
[svaṃ ka; paṃktitrayaṃ ga pustake nāsti]
mahārūpo bhayaṃ dattvā sasurāsurarakṣasām |
devena taṃ tadā dṛṣṭvā kimetadbhavatīkṛtam [004:069]||
[dadyāt ka; tu ka]
sa eva nirjitaḥ śatrurasmākaṃ vadhamudyataḥ |
na yuktaṃ śatrupakṣasya vṛddhiṃ dātuṃ kadācana |
[004:070]
yaśca kāraṇadravyāṇāṃ saviśeṣaṃ kṛta mudā |
mocate kṛpayā mūḍhaḥ sa eva nidhanaṃ vrajet [004:071]
[sāvaśeṣaṃ ka]
nipātya sākhilaṃ sarvaṃ mūlaṃ yasya na khanyate |
sa eva syād balī bhūyo badarī iva śobhate [004:072]
[śākhinaṃ ka ga; sādvalo bhūyaḥ badarīriva ka]
tathā tvamapi durbuddhe rmayāyaṃ vinipātitaḥ |
devānāṃ vidhnakartā ca ṛṣi-brāhmaṇa trāsakaḥ [004:073]
na yuktaṃ dvijadevānāṃ śatruvargasya vardhanam |
mandabuddhe sadā bāle srīsvabhāvena varttase [004:074]
ityuktā śambhunā devī kruddhā tamavalokya sā |
madbhaktiparamo bhūtvā sarvadevān jayiṣyati [004:075]
[tāmavalokya ka]
viṣṇubhāvaḥ paro hyeṣa avadhyo'yaṃ bhaviṣyati |
kuśadvīpapuravāsī candraśobhāṃ bhaviṣyati [004:076]
[viṣṇubhāvaparo ka; kuśadvīpapure'rccāsīccaṃdra0 śobhāṃ ramiṣyati]
saptadvīpāḥ sapātālāḥ sapta lokāḥ savāsavāḥ |
etadājñākaro bhūtvā ajeyo'yaṃ bhaviṣyati [004:077]
niśamya vacanaṃ devyā unmārgagatibhāṣitam |
śaśāpa roṣamāviśya tvañca marttyaṃ gamiṣyasi |
tatra caiṣa durācāraḥ patitvaṃ yācayiṣyati [004:078]
[tava hyeṣa ka]
tathā krodhānalādīptā sā śapetāsurādhipam |
nīla megha nibhākāraṃ yama mahiṣa mivāparam |
krīḍamānā haniṣyāmi pañcānana vyavasthitā [004:079]
[krodhānaloddīptā ka]
uvāca kūpitā devī devo'pi ca tathaiva tām |
evaṃ pūrvaṃ surādhyakṣa śambhunā vajranirmitaḥ [004:080]
[evaṃ ca kopitā ka ga; rajanirmita ga]
dundubherdehajo bhūtvā mama bhaktiparāyaṇaḥ |
candraśobhāpurāvāsī madīyārcāsadodyataḥ [004:081]
[sadejyakaḥ ka ga ]
tasyedaṃ śāsanaṃ prāptaṃ brāhmaṇairapi duḥsaham |
kimpunaḥ sarvayatnena sabalo yadi dānavaḥ |
āgato ghoranāmā'sau rudrādīnapi saṃharet [004:082]
[brahmaṇo'pi ka]
tacchutvā tathāśrutvā ka tu harervākyaṃ kiṃ karomi prabho vada |
tvayā dattaṃ mama svargaṃ yajñā sarvāśca rakṣitā [004:083]
[tathāśrutvā ka ga; yajñān kurvaścarakṣitaḥ ka ga]
indrāṇāmÌ tvaṃ prabhuḥ svāmī devānāṃ tvañca pālakaḥ |
ityukte vadate viṣṇuḥ śṛṇu śakra samāhitaḥ |
tatrāgato mahābuddhi rvācaspati rbṛhaspatiḥ [004:084]
[ityukto ka ga]
bṛhaspatiruvāca
yasya śāsanamātreṇa sarve devāḥ sabhāskarāḥ |
śamitā vasuyuktāśca vāriṇā iva pāvakaḥ [004:085]
[balayuktāpi ka ga]
tasya kaḥ śakyate yuddhe sabalasya nipātitam |
brahmā vā yadi vā rudraḥ sāma naya vivarjitaḥ [004:086]
[nipātanam ka]
ajeyaḥ sarvadevānāmetad dattaṃ tvayā prabho |
umayā tacca pūrve ca sarva devāri kaṇṭakaḥ [004:087]
[ajayaḥ ka ga; sacca ka]
sarvāṃstra-tattva-vettā ca sarva-dharma-parāyaṇaḥ |
tathā bhaktiparā deva tathā bhāryā pativratā [004:088]
[tava bhaktiparo ka]
lokapālaḥ prajāpālo dharmavartmanyavasthitaḥ |
tathā prabhūtabhūpālāḥ koṭi koṭi guṇāhatāḥ [004:089]
[guṇānvitāḥ ka ga]
dantināṃ yasya mattānāmaśvānāñca caturguṇāḥ |
airāvatasamāḥ sarve sacalā iva bhūdharāḥ [004:090]
[airāvataguṇāḥ ka ga]
nārāyaṇāstra brahmāstra śivāścānye'tha vāruṇāḥ |
tasya evaṃvidhaḥ śatrorvināśaḥ kena kriyatām |
deśakālakramañcāpi ekāṅgaṃ pratibhāṣate [004:091]
[sanārāyaṇa brahmāstrāḥ śaivāścānye'tha ka]
muktastrāsakṛtairdoṣaiḥ krodhajaiśca tathaiva ca |
ekādīn sapta yo vetti sa guṇī guṇināṃ varaḥ [004:092]
[muktā ka ga]
aśva mahiṣa mārjāra-ākhu kākolukaṃ yathā |
na yuddhaṃ śreyase deva uragā nakulaiḥ saha [004:093]
[ākhukākolakamiva ka]
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe (brahmopadeśe) bṛhaspativākyāni nāma caturtho'dhyāyaḥ [004:004]
[ityādye devīpurāṇe ka]
