%%%chapter 005
pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ |

bhagavānuvāca |

satyameva mahāprājña bṛhaspati vacaspate |
tvameva vedituṃ yogyaḥ sarva nyāya vivecakaḥ ||005:001||
[racituṃ ka; sa ca ka]
śambhugītā nayā yasya auśanāśca tathā nijāḥ |
madīyā brahmagītāśca vetti yaḥ sa vacaspati||005:002||
[vācāṃ patiḥ ka ga]
tvayā indrasya nāthena sacivena mahātmanā |
ko na bādhayituṃ śakya śūlapāṇirapīhayā ||005:003||
sarvaguṇapradhānā ye durvijñeyā mahātmabhiḥ |
yogibhiḥ ṣaḍguṇā eva mantribhiḥ sandhivādibhiḥ ||005:004||
[sandhivādinaḥ ka |
paṃktitrayaṃ gapustake nāsti]
vibhinnāḥ sandhisandhāne samadoṣāśca bādhayaḥ |
sandhatte samatejastu saciraṃ bhiṣajau varau ||005:005||
[vyādhayaḥ ka ga; samatejastu ka]
tvaṃ trikālanayaṃ vettā sarvavidyāviśāradaḥ |
vadāsya yadbhavedyuktaṃ surarājasya sattama ||005:006||
[tvaṃ hi ka]
vṛhaspatiruvāca
devadeva surādhyakṣa śaṃkha cakra gadā dhara |
tvadīyā me matirbhadrā na nijāsuranāśana ||005:007||
madānubhāvo deveśa tava pratyakṣato vayam |
yad vadāmo mahātmānaṃ dhṛṣṭā kulavadhūriva ||005:008||
[mahātmāno ka ga]
tava vāco guṇāviṣṭā niṣkrāmantisma manmukhāt |
tathāpi kiñciddeveśaṃ hitāhitakaraṃ prabho ||005:009||
[tanmukhāt-kha; kiñciduddeśaṃ ka]
tavājñākāriṇo bhūtvā sukhamicchanti divaukasaḥ |
tiṣṭhantu tasya vācāyāṃ yāvaddevaṃ trilocanam ||005:010||
toṣayitvā jayāṃ devīṃ vindhayācalanivāsinīm |
evaṃ te mantrayitvā tu śakro viṣṇurbṛhaspatiḥ ||005:011a-d||
nāradaṃ preṣayāmāsu rvajradaṇḍasya śāsane ||005:011ef||
[bhavān kha; vācaspatiḥ ga]
viṣṇuruvāca
tvaṃ devarṣe viprendra brahmaputra mahātapaḥ |
gatvā vadasva taṃ pāpaṃ ghoraputraṃ surāriṇam ||005:012||
gatavān viṣṇorādeśānnārado yatra so'suraḥ |
tamāyāntamṛrṣi dṛṣṭvā kālo vajraśca pūjya tau ||005:013||
[vajrasya ka]
nārada uvāca
tava ghorasuto vajra sakālasya mahābala |
śāsane saṃsthitā devā devī kāntatarā ca te ||005:014||
[cāntakarā ka]

kiṃ punaḥ śatayaṣṭā vā brahmaṇo viṣṇutatparaḥ |
bhuñja svargaṃ mahīṃ yāvaddevadevī tavāntakau ||005:015||
[kiṃ ka; śatayaṣṭāro brahmaṇo ka]
ṣaṣṭayā mindrāgni devasya śāsanaṃ ghorajaṃ divi |
kṛtvā bṛhaspati rviṣṇu rjagmu ryatra pitāmahaḥ ||005:016||
[devādyā-ka]
(iti śrīdevīpurāṇe devyavatāre haribṛhaspatyo)
(rbrahmasadana prāptirnāma pañcamodhyāyaḥ ) |
|
[ityādye devyavatāre brahmasadanaprāptirhari vṛhaspatisaṃvādaḥ]
