%%% Chapter 006
ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ |
in pdf page 34
brahmovāca |

namaste viśvarūpeśa viśvabhāva namo'stu te |
sarvadevamaya śrīman vāsudeva namo'stu te ||006:001||
[viśvadeveśa ka]
bhūta-bhavya-bhaviṣyāṇāṃ kāraṇākāraṇau namaḥ |
anādirādi-madhyānta-parakāraṇa-kāraṇa ||006:002a-d||
bhaviṣyarūpa sadbhāvaṃ matsyarūpaṃ namo'stu te ||006:002ef||
dhātrī-dharaṇa kūrmeśa varāha narasiṃharāṭ |
sarvavedapate vedya vedāntānta namo namaḥ ||006:003||
[sarvadevapateâga; namo'stute ka]
vāmanāya namastubhyaṃ rāmarāma namo namaḥ |
vāsudeva namastubhyaṃ kṛṣṇadeva namo namaḥ ||006:004||
[rāmāya ca ka; rāmadeva ka ga]
śuddha-sadbhāva-bhāvāya śuddha-buddha-tanūdbhava |
rāgadveṣavinirmukto raktavāso namostu te ||006:005||
[raktavāsa ga]
aśvārūḍha mahobāho kalidharma-pravartaka |
digambaradharo deva śūdradharmapravartaka ||006:006||
mlecchavargaṃkuloccheda namaste kalkirūpiṇe |
yugānta yuga-utpatti-yugadharma-pravartaka ||006:007||
[kapilatanu ga]
namaste devadeveśa ! īpsitārtha-pradāyaka |
yadicchāmi bhavet tvatto mama deva tathaiva ca ||006:008||
[bhavanta te ka ga]
mama kāryeṣu kāryāṇāmīpsitānāṃ surottama |
bhaviṣyāṇāñca vastūnāṃ sāhāyyaṃ kuru keśava ||006:009||
tatastuṣṭo mama viṣṇuḥ purā āsīt surādhipa |
varado'bhūd yathākāmaṃ sāhāyyamīpsiteṣu ca ||006:010||
evaṃ yo vaiṣṇavaṃ stotraṃ prātarutthāya bhāvayet| madhyāhne sandhyākāle ca tasyecchā kāmasiddhidā ||006:011||
[itaḥ paramadhyāyānteâviṣṇustavaḥ ityeva pāṭhaḥ ka]
putrārthī labhate putraṃ dhanārthī labhate dhanam |
vidyārthī labhate vidyāṃ sukhārthī sukhabhāg bhavet ||006:012||
ita śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre viṣṇustavaḥ samāptaḥ |

[viṣṇustavaḥâityeva ga pustake]
brahmovāca |

mayā pūrvai ca tvaṃ deva uktamāsījjanārdana |
asurāṇāṃ varaḥ śreṣṭho na deyo madhusūdana ||006:013||
[pūrveva ka ga]
labdhavarā madodrekādasurāḥ sura-bādhakāḥ |
bhavanti devadevānāṃ dvija-yajña-vināśakāḥ ||006:014||
tathāpyevaṃ mahāvāho ! vināśāyāsurasya ca |
cintyatāṃ brahman govindo vācaspatirbṛhaspatiḥ ||006:015||
[brahmagovindau ga]
brahmovāca |

tvameva sarvavettāsi tathāpi surasattama |
kāryāgatantu vaktavyaṃ nahi doṣastrivikramam ||006:016||
[puruṣottama ka ga; kāryagataṃ ka]
tadbhavet tatpurā kalpe bhautye manvantare hare |
devadevo mahādevo yo'sau paramakāraṇaḥ ||006:017||
[uttare tu ka]
svargaḥ sarvavyāpī ca anādi-nidhanaḥ śivaḥ |
tasyecchārthaṃ surādhyakṣa sthitaḥ pālayitā prabhuḥ ||006:018||
[prajāḥ ka |
kruddhag krodhena dīpitaḥ |
tapase sthitau pālayitā prajā ga pustake]
sutaḥ kālāgnirudrasya rudrapāṣāṇa mūrdhani |
tasmin hālāhalo nāpa mahābala-parākramaḥ ||006:019||
[gataḥ ka ga; vajrapāṣāṇa ka ga]
upanetātmajaṃ ghoraṃ dvitīyamiva pāvakam |
taṃ samprekṣya tadā deva mudgareṇa hataṃ tvayā ||006:020||
prabuddho'sau tadā bahniḥ śuddhakrodhena dīpitaḥ |
tasya niśvāsajā jvālā nirgatāstu diśo daśa ||006:021||
tadā tvaṃ mohasampanno mama śaṅkā tadābhavat mayā sañcintito rudraḥ khaṭvāṅga-karabhāskaraḥ ||006:022||
[mahā ka mahā bhavet ga; bhāsuraḥ ka ga]
sa ca karaṇasadbhāvo dhyāna-siddhi-varapradaḥ |
preṣayāmāsa cāmuṇḍāṃ kālānalasamaprabhām ||006:023||
rakṣaṇāya tavāsmākaṃ hutāśanaśamāya ca |
tasyāḥ prekṣaṇamātreṇa sā ca jvālā śamaṃ gatā ||006:024||
[sātrāya kha]
tadāsau vadate devaṃ hālāhala hutāśanaḥ |
kathyatāṃ kāraṇaṃ viṣṇo yenāhaṃ tāḍitastvayā ||006:025||
tvayā ca yācito deva jagāma taṃ hutāvaham |
pūrṇaḥ saṃvarttate kālo māṃ brahmasya ca pāvakaḥ ||006:026||
[tvayā ca ka; jayame'stu tadāvaha iti khapustake |
jagadekaṃ tadāvaha ka ga]
tena vodhitavān rudro yo'sau kālāgni-viśrutaḥ |
vadato kāraṇaṃ brūhi yena tvaṃ mama kṣobhakaḥ ||006:027||
[rocitavān ka]
viṣṇutvamāgato deva jagato dahanāya ca |
uttthitastāvat kālāgnirmahājvālaughabhāsvaraḥ ||006:028||
[bhāsuraḥ ka]
śamitastasya devyā yaḥ pratāpaḥ punareva saḥ |
tadā tvayā mahādeva jñātvā śaktiṃ mahābalām ||006:029||
[māyādeva kha]
jagadutpattipālāya nidhanāya vayaṃ purā |
tutoṣa parayā bhaktyā stavenānena mādhavaḥ ||006:030||
viṣṇupitāmahāvūcatuḥ |

namaste kālajālaugha-ghoradīpti-praśāmati |
nīlasyanda mahākāla navamegha prabhāvati ||006:031||
[dīpti praśāmaki ka]
rakta sindūra kiñjalka vidrumākāra bhāvati |
pīta padmāruṇā hemasarvākāra vibhāvati ||006:032||
śveta-śaṅkhābdhikṣīrābhra-hima-kunda-vibhāvati |
sṛṣṭi-saṃhāra-karttāri-rudramūrti-prabhāvati ||006:033||
brahma-viṣṇu-yama-śakra-candra-sūrya-virodhaki |
īśa rakṣo'nila toyāmanalātmanamaskṛte ||006:034||
[īśarakṣā ... namaskṛti ka]
ekadhā bahudhā tvañca daśadhā śatadhā śivā |
punarukta-padārthārtha-bahukāraṇa-kāraki ||006:035||
kālapāśo mahāmāyo vadha-bandhana-mocaki |
surāsura-narasiddha-nānābhāva-pravartaki ||006:036||
[siddhi bhāvābhāva...ka]
paśu-mṛga-pakṣi-tiryak-tṛṇa-mānuṣa-varttaki |
brahma-prajeśa-somaśca yakṣarakṣaḥ piśācaki ||006:037||
[kapustake nāsti; rakṣaśatru piśācasu ka ga]
gandharvabhāvabhāveṣu tvañca devi parāpare |
lava-syanda-truṭi-nimeṣa muhūrtta atha kāṣṭhasu ||006:038||
kalāyāmardhayāmeṣu sandhyā-vāsara-rātriṣu |
pakṣa-māsa-ṛtu-dvitri-ayaneṣu sameṣu ca ||006:039||
mānavān devaśatrūṇāṃ brahmādyasmākaṃ jantuṣu |
kalpa kalpa mahākalpa-utpatti sthiti hetuṣu ||006:040||
[bhadrakāli bhahākāli tañca devi yareṣu ca ityadhikaḥ pāṭhaḥ ka pustake ]
daiva puruṣa sadbhāva mantraśaktibhaveṣu ca |
vidyā-vadana-vettāri veda-vedānta - vādiṣu ||006:041||
[vettāraṃ ka vettāsi ga]
mantra-tantra-jvara-ghora-kūṣmāṇḍa-bhūta-jātiṣu |
śabda-pramāṇa-siddhānta sāṅ ravya-yogāgameṣu ca ||006:042||
jyotirvedyādiśāstreṣu kāla gāruḍādiṣu |
rasa anya kriyāvādasaritsāgaramadhyasu ||006:043||
[bāla ka; khanya ka ga]
sarvagā sarvakāryeṣu sarvabhāvapravartaki |
na hi śakyā guṇā devī tava vaktuṃ samādiṣu ||006:044||
[sarvakartā ca ka ga; mamādiṣu ka]
nityaiva bhāvyate sarvā kṛtakṛtyasya kīrttanā |
stotā tvañca stutistvañca vettā tvaṃ vedanī ca tvam ||006:045||
ko'yaṃ stotā stavaḥ kasya kriyate vākpralāpanam |
evambhūtārthabhavyaistu bhaviṣyaiḥ pauruṣaistathā ||006:046||
tutoṣa paramā devī varadā ca abhūdubhau |
||006:047ab|| in pdf page 36
devyuvāca |

kṛṣṇa brahman varaṃ yāca tuṣṭā'hamubhayorapi ||006:047cd|| in the middle devyuvāca comes. Is it o.k.?
tadā tvahañca sañcintya sahāya bhava suvrate |
yeṣu yeṣu ca kalpeṣu manvantarayugeṣu ca ||006:048||
[tadātmabhūśca ka]
teṣu teṣu pathādevi yad yasmāt ko bhaviṣyati |
kartṛtve sthāpane nāśe tattu niṣpadyate yathā ||006:049||
[jayo'smākaṃ ka ga; taṃ tvaṃ kha ]
tattatheti ca sā uktvā parevoparatā hyabhūt |
kālena stavamākarṇya phalañca stavate kṛtam ||006:050||
[puraivopatāvabhūt ka]
idaṃ yaścarccikāstotraṃ brahmaviṣṇu vinirmitam |
devagandharvayakṣo vā ṛṣirvipro'tha kṣatriyaḥ ||006:051||
[viṣṇurbrahma ka ga]
vaiśyaḥ śūdro'balā vā'pi bhaktitaḥ sampaṭhiṣyati |
śṛṇuyāccintayedvā'pi sarvārthān prāpayiṣyate ||006:052||
[trarairvāpi ka]
na grahā na ca kūṣmāṇḍā na bhūtā na ca rākṣasāḥ |
piśācāḥ pūtanānandā nāgāḥ sarpāśca gonasāḥ ||006:053||
[navagrahaḥ navakuṣmāṇḍā ga ]
bālajā bhūtajā ye ca grahā duṣṭā mahābalāḥ |
śamaṃ yāsyanti rogāśca vātapittakaphodbhavāḥ ||006:054||
sthāvarāḥ kṛtrimā bhaumā viṣā dantanakhodbhavāḥ |
aupasargikarogāśca praṇaśyantyavicāraṇāt ||006:055||
[ghorā ka ga]
pātakāśca śamaṃ yānti brahmaghātādayaḥ kṛtāḥ |
gurupitṛsuhṛdvandhumātābālābalāvadham ||006:056||
[brahmahatyādayaḥ ka]
pātakaṃ śamate bhaktyā śravaṇāllabhate phalam daśānāṃ rājasūyānāmagniṣṭomaśatasya ca ||006:057||
[pātakaṃ śameta śravaṇāllabheta yatphalaṃ śruṇu ga]
śravaṇāt phalamāpnoti sarvadānavratādikam |
mucyate sarvaṃpāpebhyo devyāste līyate naraḥ ||006:058||
iti śrīdevipurāṇe brahmaviṣṇukṛtaḥ stavo nāma ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devyavatāre brahmaviṣṇukṛtaḥ stavaḥ ka ga]
