%%% Chapter 007
saptamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

evaṃ pūrva tvayā devī toṣitā surasattama |
sā sarvakāryākāryeṣu śaṅkarād yadavāpsyasi ||007:001||
tatra gatvā mahādevaṃ parāparatanūdbhavam |
toṣayāmāsa govindo ghoradaṇḍavadhakṣamam ||007:002||
evaṃ pūrvastadā viṣṇu sa ca brahmā surottamaḥ |
gatavān yatra devo'sau yogināṃ dhyānagocaraḥ ||007:003||
[pūrva tadā ka]
tadā hyaṅghriyugasyādhaḥ petaturdvijamādhavau |
mūrttibhūtaṃ śivaṃ sākṣācchaktivāmāṅga bhūṣaṇam ||007:004||
[kāmāṅga ka ga]
trinetraṃ paśyate viṣṇurbrahmā viṣṇuṃ prapaśyati |
evaṃ vicitratāṃ tasya matvā dhyānena śūlinaḥ ||007:005||
[evaṃ vircityatāmÌ tasya sadā dhyānena śūline ga]
bhūta-bhavya-bhaviṣyārthaiḥ prabhūreṣa parākramaiḥ |
nāma saṅkīrttanādyaistu stavenainaṃ tutoṣa ca ||007:006||
jaya sūkṣma parānanta kāraṇatrayatave |
dhyānagabhya parādhyakṣa sākṣibhūta guṇatraye ||007:007||
jaya vijita sadbhāva hyasmākaṃ surasattama |
jaya hyākāśa-vāyvagni-toya-dhātrī ca mūrttaye ||007:008||
jaya tanmātra-karmākhya-buddhīndriya-vidhātave |
jaya buddhi-mano-garva-pradhānapuruṣātmane ||007:009||
jaya mālā-kalā-rāga-kāya-vidyā-vivodhana |
jaya niyāmakaśakti jaya vidye samudbhave ||007:010||
[vidyāvirodhine ka; sarvavidyeśasambhave ka ga ]
jaya kālāgnisādanta vyāptivyāpaka śūline |
jaya ghora mahāghora kāladaṇḍa yamāntaka ||007:011a-d||
jaya andha pṛthuskandha khaṭvā rurujighāṃsaka ||007:011ef||
[itaḥ pūrvaṃ jaya khaṭvāṅgaâitvādyārabhya mahātmaneâityataḥ pāṭho bidyate ka; aṇu pṛthusyūya ka]
jaya kāla mahākūṭa viṣakaṇṭhasthajīrṇave |
jaya dānava-vidhvasaṃ gaṅgā-jala-jaṭā-dhara ||007:012a-d||
jaya tripuradāheśa kāmadāheśa śambhave ||007:012ef||
jaya khaṭvāṅgamālāhi bhūṣaṇānāṃ sadāpriya |
jaya digvāsa bhūteśa jaya śmaśānavāsine ||007:013||
jaya sārdragajacarmaprāvṛtāya mahātmane |
jaya triśūlahastāya karṇāpūrita iṣave ||007:014a-d||
jaya vāsukiśaṅkhābja-anantakṛtamekhala ||007:014ef||
jaya gaurīstanasparśaṃromaromāñcadhūsara |
jaya gamya mahīkampa devadeva bhavodbhava ||007:015||
jaya ḍiṇḍi mahākāla śambhuśaṅkara īśvara |
jaya rudra hara ghora satyavāsa sadāśiva ||007:016||
[daṇḍi ka ga; satyaṃ dhāma ka ga]
jaya puruṣa vaktreśa parameṣṭhibhavāya ca |
jaya paśupate sarveśa bhīma ugra namo namaḥ ||007:017||
[brajeśa kha; śaveṃśa ka ga ]
evaṃ stutastadā devo brahmā viṣṇuśca tuṣṭavān |
varaṃ vara hare brahman yatte manasi vāñchitam ||007:018||
yathāvṛttakathāṃ jñāpya ghoradaṇḍaṃ nivarhaya |
evamuktastadā tena īśaḥ sañcintya abravīt ||007:019||
[tebhya ka]
yā sā ādyā parā śaktiryoganidrā mahātmanām |
sā tu rsihaṃ samāruhya vindhye krīḍanatāṃ yayau ||007:020||
[mahātmanā ka; brīḍā ka; brajet ka]
tatrasthā hyasmadaṃśena parāśaktibalena ca |
brahmamÌstavaṃ kiṅkaro bhūtvā viṣṇuśca nayarūpiṇā ||007:021||
[brahma tvaṃ ka; jayarūpiṇā ka ga]
pratihāryo mahātejāścatvāro'nyā mahābalāḥ |
ṛgyajuḥsāmātharvāṇāṃ yaddhāma yatparaṃ balam ||007:022||
te ca vedāstanusteṣāṃ mūrtimanto bhavanti ca |
sarvā vīṇākarā devyaḥ sarvāḥ pāśāṅkuśodyatāḥ ||007:023||
sitaraktapītakṛṣṇā bahuvaktrāstrilocanāḥ |
divyapaṭṭāṃśukacchannā divyābharaṇabhūṣitāḥ ||007:024||
[bhūṣaṇāḥ ka ga]
kāmarūpā mahārūpā aṇimādiguṇairyutāḥ |
hāra-nūpura-nirghoṣa-maṇi-vaidūrya-carccitāḥ ||007:025||
keśai rmṛga-madā-moda-ghana-nīla-samaprabhaiḥ |
veṇībandha mahīcchadma uragairiva pṛṣṭhagaiḥ ||007:026||
ardhenduriva lalāṭanimnonnatavirājitaiḥ |
niṣpāvasadṛśaghrāṇā karṇayūgme samāṃsale ||007:027||
[vivarjitaiḥ ka ga; yugmeṣu sāsena ga]
nīlotpala-dala-prakhyairhariṇīriva locaneḥ |
vidrumākāraśobhāḍhyaiḥ pakvavimbopamādharaiḥ ||007:028||
[sārīṇairiva ka]
kunda-kuḍmala-ābhāṣa-danta paṃktiḥ suśobhanā |
hanu-gaṇḍasthala- cibukānaupamya-manoramāḥ ||007:029||
kamburekhasamagrīvaiḥ sarvāḥ sarvaistu māṃsalaiḥ |
pīnonnata-kucāvṛtta-hāravalita-madhyagaiḥ ||007:030||
[samaigrāvaiḥ ka]
madhya-deśa-tanu-kṣāma-trivalī-roma-varjitaiḥ |
dakṣiṇāvartta-gambhīra-nābhi-maṇḍala-maṇḍitaiḥ ||007:031||
guru-vistīrṇa-nitamba-māṃsopacita-śobhitaiḥ |
aśvattha-patra-sākāra-nigūḍha-maṇi-bandhanaiḥ ||007:032||
[saṃskāra ka; sūnutaiḥ ka]
kūrmaṃpṛṣṭha iva śroṇigaguhyadeśaistu śobhanaiḥ |
nigūḍhagulphadeśaiśca samaiḥ pādaiḥ sumāṃsalaiḥ ||007:033||
ūrū karirākāvilomai viṃśiraiḥ śubhaiḥ |
jānunī samasuśliṣṭajaṅghairvṛttaiḥ suśobhanaiḥ ||007:034||
aṅgulīnāṃ kramānyūnā madhyamādi yathāsthitaḥ |
vicitralāñchanairbhaṃdraiḥ pānahastaiśca lāñchitāḥ ||007:035||
mṛṇālakomalairvṛttairdoṃrdaṇḍaiḥ sudṛḍhaiḥ samaiḥ |
tāḥ sarvā mohanā devyo darśanāt sparśanādapi ||007:036||
kāmārttā vihvalā yābhiḥ kriyante dānavā budhāḥ |
śāntidā dītarāgāṇāṃ tā devyo ṛṣimānavāḥ ||007:037||
[muktidā ka ga]
trātāstāḥ sarvadevānāmāpatsu sumahatsu ca |
cintitāryapradāḥ puṇyā dhyātā japtātha pūjitāḥ ||007:038||
kanyārūpā mahābhāgā mahadādinamaskṛtāḥ ||007:039|| only half a sloka comes, is it o.k.?
tāsāmapi mahādevī yā sā śaktiranaupamā |
parāparavirmiśrā ca sarvadiga mṛtatmikā ||007:040||
[sarvadikkāmṛtātmikā ka ga]
vastumātrāsthitā brahman rviṣṇave prabhaviṣṇave |
śāntirūpā surūpā yā ghorarūpā surārihā ||007:041||
[bahu ka; śāntarūpā sā ghorarūpā ka ga]
ekānekavibhāgena koṭibhedairvyavasthitā |
sadāsmākaṃ bhavasyaiva svāmibhūtā mahātmikā ||007:042||
[bhavāmÌśceva ka ga]
tāsāṃ caturṇāṃ devīnāṃ nāyikā suranāyikā |
yuga-manvantara-kalpa-utpatti-sthiti-nāśinī ||007:043||
