bhaviṣyati samastānāmīpsitārtha phalapradā ||007:044a-d||
tasyāpi vāhanaṃ brahman harinārtha vinirmitam ||007:044ef||
brahmovāca |

sarvadevā sagandharvāḥ sarvadevāstayā saha |
sarvadevamayaḥ kṛtvā vāhano hyaridarpahā ||007:045||
[tvayā ka ga]
tathā tvaṃ keśavo deva vayaṃ keśavamūlataḥ |
viṣṇuḥ sthāsyati grīvāyāṃ sarvalokāśca tadvapuḥ ||007:046||
śiromadhye mahādevo dvitīyaḥ kālarūpiṇaḥ |
lalāṭāgre mahādevī nāsāvaṃśe sarasvatī ||007:047||
[umādevī ka]
ṣaṇmukho maṇibandheṣu nāgāśca pārśvataḥ sthitāḥ |
karṇayoraśivanau devau cakṣuṣoḥ śaśibhāskarau ||007:048||
danteṣu vasavaḥ sarve jihvāyāṃ varuṇaḥ sthitaḥ |
hūṅkāre caccircakā devī yamayakṣau ca gaṇḍayoḥ ||007:049||
sandhyādvayaṃ tathauṣṭhābhyāṃ grīvāyamindra āśritaḥ| grīvāsandhiṣu ṛkṣāṇi sādhyāścorasi saṃsthitā ||007:050a-d||
nirghṛṇatve tamastasya kraurye sarvāṃstu pūtanāḥ ||007:050ef||
pālane mātaro devyaḥ apāne pitaraḥ sthitāḥ |
śriyā rūpe sthitā tasya bāle cādityaraśmayaḥ ||007:051||
vṛṣaṇe merurvinyastaḥ sāgarā vasane sthitāḥ |
saritastasya svedasthā sthāpitāḥ parameśvara ||007:052||
[rasane kha; vedasthāḥ ka; sthīyatāṃ ka ga]
yajñāḥ sadevatāḥ sarve cāṅgule cābhavad ya saḥ |
balaṃ vīryañca deveśa tvadīyaṃ yasya sarvataḥ ||007:053||
[lāṅgale ka; bhavatonyasaṃ ka ga]
khādakādīni rakṣāṃsi nyastavyāni sureśvara |
sarveṣāṃ vāhanādeva ye ca yasya niyojitāḥ ||007:054||
ātmanaḥ pararakṣāsu pathi saṃgrāmasāgare |
bhūtarākṣasavetālādyarīṇāṃ saṅkaṭeṣu ca ||007:055||
[yathā ka]
grahaduṣṭeṣu sarveṣu upasargamayeṣu ca |
surakinnarakanyāsu hyapsarāsbalāsu ca ||007:056||
[aupasargabhayeṣu ka ]
garbharakṣā mātṛrakṣā putrārthe gurviṇīṣu ca |
evaṃ saṃpṛṣṭavān deva druhiṇaḥ keśavena ca ||007:057||
[mahārakṣā ka ga]
vihasya kathyeta śakra yathāvadanupūrvaśaḥ |
namaḥ piṅgalanetrāya koṭarākṣāya bhairava ||007:058||
namaste ghorarūpāya surāsurabhayaṅkara |
namaḥ khaṭvāṅgahastāya rurucarmārdravāsase ||007:059||
[khaḍgapaṭṭiśadhāriṇe ka]
namaḥ kapālamālāya brahmakṛṣṇasabhājane| namaḥ karāla-mālāya nārāyaṇa-tanūruhe ||007:060||
[namaḥ kapāla.....ṃudgarahastāya iti nāsti ka; brahmaśiravibhājane ga]
namo mudgara- hastāya khaḍgapaṭṭiśadhāriṇe |
namaḥ parāśuhastāya pinākavarapāṇine ||007:061||
namaḥ śaṅ khagadā-hasta kratu-ḍamarū-vādine |
namaḥśaila mahāveśa mahāveganinādite ||007:062||
[kunta ka danta ga; mahābega mahāveganinādine iti nāsti ka ga ]
namaḥ śailamahāghora vajrahastāya cakriṇe |
ūrdhvakeśa mahāveṣa mahāmeghaninādine ||007:063||
mahāvidyujjihvāya mahā-ulkānibhāya ca |
somasūryāgninetrāya nānākrīḍāratāya ca ||007:064||
nānā-bhakṣya-kriyā-bhojya-nānāhāra-priyāya ca |
māṃsāsavarasāmetha pūtanādi-ratāya ca ||007:065a-d||
kṛnta kṛnta surādhyakṣaṃ śatruvarga mahāvala ||007:065ef||
khāda khāda mahāghora khaḍgakhaṭvāṅgadhāriṇe |
bandha bandha mahāpāśa mahāśatrupramarddana ||007:066||
hāhā huṅkāranādena daityān hi vinikṛntaya |
mahārūpa mahīkāya samadevāriśaṅkara ||007:067||
ugra bhairava cāmuṇḍa ḍiṇḍimuṇḍi jaṭādhara |
chinda chinda mahācakra iṣuhastāya śaṅkara ||007:068||
[bhinda ka ga]
jambhakādyātha cāmuṇḍā ḍākinyo bhūtamātaraḥ |
ye ye dānavapakṣasya te te khāda māntaka ||007:069||
[mantike kha |
paṃktidvayaṃ gapustake nāsti ]
vajraśaktimahādaṇḍa khaḍgapāśāṅkuśodyataḥ |
gadātriśūlahastāya savāṃ bādhāṃ vināśaya ||007:070||
jvara bhūta grahonmāda śakulī nandarevatī |
nāga kinnara gandharva sarvarogodbhavā samā ||007:071||
[śakulī ka ]
kālapīḍā kriyāpīḍā pāpapīḍātha dhātujā |
vātapittakaphodbhūtāṃ śamayet bhairavaḥ sadā ||007:072||
[vātajā ka ga]
vidveṣoccāṭanādīni māraṇastambhakarṣaṇāḥ |
mantrayantrakṛtāṃ bādhāṃ śamaya surasattama ||007:073||
atharvavihitāṃ pīḍāṃ tathā śāpāditāpasaiḥ |
duṣṭavākyakṛtāṃ sarvāṃ nāśayed vṛṣavāhana ||007:074||
khaḍgakuntabhuśuṇḍyādi ghātāścakrāsijāśca ye |
vajramuṣṭikṛtā deva stambha stambhaśubhāmbara ||007:075||
[subhāsvara ka ga]
iṣujopalavārkṣo'tha ye cānye vairiṇaḥ kṛtāḥ |
āhaveṣu mahābāho te śamaṃ yāntu bhairavaḥ ||007:076||
[vairibhiḥ ka; āhareṣu mahāghoraṃ kha]
daṃṣṭrāviṣaṃ mahāghoraṃ nakhajaṃ rudra nāśaya |
parasainyavighātantu kālavajrakarānala ||007:077||
kurva kurva mahākrodha parasya vadhamāhave |
nakravyāghravarāheṣu siṃhakhaḍgabhayeṣu ca ||007:078||
trāya māṃ devadeveśa taskareṣu patheṣu ca |
sarit sāgaranadyeṣu dīrghikopavaneṣu ca ||007:079
parvateṣu taḍāgeṣu vanavindhyāṭavīṣu ca |
agrato rakṣate śambhuḥ śūlapāṇirmahābalaḥ ||007:080||
pṛṣṭhato bāṇahastastu pinākī vṛṣaketanaḥ |
pārśvatastu mahārudraḥ khaḍgakheṭakadhāriṇaḥ ||007:081||
[tathā rudraḥ ka; paṃktitrayaṃ nāsti gapustake]
ākāśe ca mahādevo ghaṇṭāḍamarūśabditaḥ |
pātālasthaḥ svayamīśo vāsukīkṛtabhūṣaṇaḥ ||007:082||
sarvataḥ śivanāmā ca bhayebhyaḥ pātu śaṅkaraḥ |
evaṃ stutvā mahādevaṃ praśnoktāṃllabhate guṇān ||007:083||
ya idaṃ paṭhate brahman mamāpi tava sannidhau |
viṣṇavāgāre tvadīye vā tīrthe goṣṭhe catuṣpathe ||007:084||
ekaliṅge taḍāge vā parvate vā vane'pi vā |
nadīsaṅgamapuṇye vā gṛhe vā hutapāvake ||007:085a-d||
na tasya vyādhayaḥ śoko na hānirna ca śatravaḥ ||007:085ef||
[ekaliṅgaikavṛkṣe ka]
na jvarārtibhayodvegā nāpi mitreṣṭanāśanam |
nākāle maraṇaṃ tasya na cāpāyo'sya sambhavet ||007:086||
[jarārti0 ka ]
mocate sarvapāpāni śravaṇāt paṭhanādapi |
dhāraṇāt patrabhūrjeṣu tāmrapātreṣu pūjayet ||007:087||
[paṭhane'pivā ka; paṭṭeṣu pūjanāt ka]
yantrapustakamantreṣu sarvakāmān prayacchati |
brahmahatyā surāpānaṃ hanyāt pātakaduṣkṛtam ||007:088||
sakṛduccāraṇād brahman sarvakarmaphala labhet |
sarvatīrthatapodānaṃ sarvavratapradāyikā ||007:089||
[sarvayajñaphalaṃ ka ga]
śaṅkareṇa kṛtā rakṣā sarvakāmārthasādhikā |
gṛhe'pi tiṣṭhate yasya sa sukhaṃ yaśa āpnuyāt ||007:090||
[lekhe'pi ka]
iti śaṅkaragītārakṣā samāptā|
[devīpurāṇe devyavatāre ityadhikaḥ pāṭhaḥ]
brahmovāca |

siṃhaṃ niṣpāditaṃ deva devyāyā vinivedaya |
tadaṅgatejaḥ sabhbhūtā jayādyā yāśca mātaraḥ ||007:091||
[tadaṃśa0 ka| tvadaṃ śateja ga; bhūtayaḥ ka ga]
tā devyājñākarā bhūtvā martye gatvā rarāma ca |
jambūdvīpe mahādvīpe sarvabhogaphalaprade ||007:092||
[varapradāḥ ka]
vindhye parvatarājendre narmadājalaphenite |
nirddhūtapāvakalile ṛṣisiddhaniṣevite ||007:093||
[rāje ca ka ga; sphālite ka ga; pāvakāsatva0 kha]
vadhāya suraśatrūṇāṃ narāṇāñca hitāya ca |
paritrāṇāya bhaktānāṃ sarvavarṇāśrameṣu ca ||007:094||
antyajānāṃ mahābhāga bhaktānāṃ samadarśanāḥ |
pūjitāḥ saṃstutā devyaḥ karmabhāvaphalapradāḥ ||007:095||
evaṃ tāḥ sammatīḥkṛtvā nāyikā mātarārtihāḥ |
niyuktāḥ śambhunā martye vindhaye śailavarottame ||007:096||
[natavartikāḥ iti kha-pustakasya pāṭhāntare, ga]
tadā tāḥ sarvagā bhūtvā saptadvīpāñca medinīm |
vyāpāyitvā sthitāstasmin vindhye bhūdharasattame ||007:097||
[tatastāḥ ka]
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe devīvindhyāvataraṇaṃ nāma saptamo'dhyāyaḥ |
