aṣṭamo'dhyāyaḥ |

vajradaṇḍa uvāca |

asmākaṃ marttyapātālāḥ śakradyāśca tathāmarāḥ |
sādhitāḥ kāladevasya prasādena mahābalāḥ ||008:001||
[kālaveṣasya ka]
dūtā nyavedayan gatvā devasthānamanuttamam |
evaṃ śrutvā tadālāpaṃ vajrakālacikīrṣitam ||008:002||
[tasya ka ga]
bṛhaspatinā cākhyātaṃ brahmaṇo vāsavasya ca ||008:003||
bṛhaspatiruvāca |

kālena saha vajreṇa ghoraḥ svarganivāsinām |
ānayanāya kṛto yatno bhavatāṃ tanniveditam ||008:004||
brahmovāca |

nāradaṃ preṣaya viṣṇo asurasya vimohanam |
karoti yena sa gatvā adharmeṣu niyojanam ||008:005||
veda brāhmaṇa devānāṃ bhaktiṃ kṛtvā upāgataḥ |
tasya patnī hyadharmeṣu yāti dharmabahiṣkṛtā ||008:006||
[deva ka ga; vedānāṃ ka ga; kṣamāyataḥ ka ga |
kṛtvājñayāyataḥ kha; patidharma ka ga ]
adharmaniratāḥ sarvāḥ prajāstasya na śāntidāḥ |
yena kenacidupāyena tenedaṃ kuru mādhava ||008:007||
evaṃ pṛṣṭastadā viṣṇurnāradaṃ sa samādiśat |
tvaṃ brahmaja mahāprājña sarvaśāstra-viśāradaḥ ||008:008||
kuśadvīpaṃ vraja brahmaṃstvamadharmavighātakaḥ |
tatheti taiḥ samādiṣṭo devārthe kṛṣṇavigrahaḥ ||008:009||
[brahma danudharmavighātakaṃ ka ga; devārthadṛṣṭaṃ ka]
āgamadhyānayogena svatantra ṛṣipuṅgavaḥ |
kuśadvīpaṃ aṇāt prāpto yatra rājā mahāsuraḥ ||008:010||
dvāḥsthena taṃ samāyāntaṃ dṛṣṭvā brahmasutottamam |
praviṣṭo yatra vai rājā ghoro ghoraparākramaḥ ||008:011||
dvāḥstha uvāca |

rājarāja mahābāho dvāre brahmasutottamaḥ |
nāradastiṣṭhate deva sthāpyatāṃ ki praveśyatām ||008:012||
tacchrutvā danurājendro nāradaṃ dvāramāgatam |
dvāsthaṃ samādiśat tūrṇaṃ kūpajo hṛṣṭamānasaḥ ||008:013||
praveśato pratīhāra dvijarūpo janārdanaḥ |
labdhādeśastadā dvāḥstho nāradamānayata tataḥ ||008:014||
ta trāsau viṣṇubhaktātmā ghoro devadvija priyaḥ |
taṃ prekṣya utthito rājā bhūbhyāṃ jānugataḥ śiraḥ ||008:015||
[diśacchakra kuśapo ddhārivigirahaḥ; yatrā0 ka ga ]
praṇamya bhaktibhāvena prapūryārghodakāsanaiḥ |
sukhaṃ saṃviśa devarṣe ityukto nārado'vadat ||008:016||
[prapūjyārdhyodakāśanaiḥ ka ga]
atha rājan mahābāho viṣayān mānayan sukham |
mānayasva priyān kāmān strīṇāṃ krīḍāvatī sadā ||008:017||
[krīḍārataḥ ka ga]
etadeva phalaṃ rājan devatārādhanodbhavam |
bhūpatitvaṃ sadā bhogyāḥ striyo vā navayauvanāḥ ||008:018||
[bhojyāḥ ka ga]
ātmānaṃ paramaṃ devaṃ toṣaṇīyaṃ budhaiḥ |
śrūyate ca mahārāja devadevastrilocanaḥ ||008:019||
ṛṣikanyāprakīḍāya gato dāruvanaṃ kila |
sa ca devo mahādevaḥ paratattvārthavedakaḥ ||008:020||
[bādakaḥ ka ga]
sevate viṣayān rājan yathā sarveṣu saḥ paraḥ |
tathā ca bhagavān viṣṇuḥ śriyaṃ vakṣaḥsthale varam ||008:021||
[striyaṃ rakṣasthaledharat ka]
candra indra surā brahma sarve ca sukhamarthinaḥ |
tadarthaṃ tapyate dharmaphalo'yaṃ viṣayo nṛpaḥ ||008:022||
[ tadānu ka; viṣayānnṛpa ka |
tadarthe tapyate dharmāphalo'yaṃ viṣayā nṛpa ga]
evamuktastataḥ śakra ghoraḥ pratyavavoca tam |
nahi ânāradaâ dharmasya âviṣayānmokṣaṇaṃâ śubham ||008:023||
[evamuktvā ga; pratyabhyarocayat ka ga]
ghora uvāca |

saṃyatāste âśubhā brahman visṛṣṭāâ ânarakāya te |
indriyavijayīâ pumān vinayenopapadyate ||008:024||
vinītaḥ sevate lokaṃ tadā sampamāpnuyāt |
sampadā âgharma bhogāâ hi svavṛtti-paripālanam ||008:025||
[sampado dhamaṃbhogāya ka ga]
tacca sampālanaṃ brahman dṛṣṭādṛṣṭaphalapradam |
vyādhi-bheṣaja-sevāyāṃ kṣayaṃ gacchedasaṃśayam ||008:026||
[sabhpālayan kha]
sevyamānendriyā brahman pravṛddhimupayānti hi |
jvālāmālākulaṃ gehaṃ mahāpāvaka-dūpitam ||008:027||
anenopaśamaṃ yāti viṣayāṇāñca dīpakam |
dāhajvaramahātāpo vahnipittasamudbhavam ||008:028||
[viṣayānnātmadīpakam kha; vahniḥ pittasamudbhavam ka samudbhavaḥ ga ]
hima-candana-saṃyogācchamenna viṣayānmune |
kadalī-dala-kahlāra-mṛṇāla-kamalotpalaiḥ ||008:029||
hima-candana-karpūrai kāmāgnirjvalate tu taiḥ |
ṛṇaṃ dānena śamate dahanobhyudakena ca ||008:030||
śatravo ghātamānā hi kṣīyante hyavicāraṇāt |
eteṣāṃ ghātanaṃ brahmaṃstannibodha sukhāvaham ||008:031||
[tannirodhaḥ sukhāvaha ka ga]
śabda-sparśa-rasarūpa-gandha-vāgindriyāstathā |
pāṇi-pādapā yūpasthāḥ saṃyatāstu sukhāvahāḥ ||008:032||
[pādapadmarūpasthaśca ka ga]
pataṅga-mṛga-matsyebha-kīṭādyāśca patatriṇaḥ |
ekaikaviṣayāsaktāḥ sarve mṛtyuvaśaṃ gatāḥ ||008:033||
yaḥ punaḥ saṃhatān seved viṣayān viṣayī naraḥ |
sa patenmahadaiśvaryācchinnamūla iva drūmaḥ ||008:034||
[pumān kha]
striyaḥ pānaṃ divāsvapnaṃ tathā vāditranartanam |
dyūtāṭanamṛgā geyaṃ kāmajāṃ nindanaṃ pare ||008:035||
[kāmajāni dṛśā param ka]
daṇḍairvācā īrṣāsūyākrodhapaiśunyasāhasam |
arthānāṃ dūṣaṇaṃ vyādhi aṣṭako'yaṃ vināśakṛt ||008:036||
[daṇḍabādhā īrṣyā0 ka ga; ātmabhūṣaṇakrodho'rtho ka |
arthadūṣaṇa krodho'rtha iti kha pustakasya pāṭhāntare ]
devā vidyādharā yakṣāḥ kinnaroragamānuṣāḥ |
paśavaḥ pakṣiṇaḥ sarve viṣaye nidhanaṃ gatāḥ ||008:037||
evaṃ vivekamāsaktaṃ buddhvā ghoraṃ narādhipa |
dharmavyājaṃ samāsthāya viṣayaiḥ saṃnniveśyatām ||008:038||
[surādhipa ka ga]
nārada uvāca |

nirjitya śatrusainyāni kṣitiṃ dharmeṇa pālayet |
anāthāmudvahet kanyāṃ vaṃśajāṃ na ca doṣabhāk ||008:039||
[doṣataḥ ka ga]
dharmasya sādhanaṃ rājyaṃ rājyādaiśvaryamuttamam |
bhuñjayan punaranyāśca striyo ratnavibhūṣitāḥ ||008:040||
[bhuñjayat suraramyāśca ka ga]
madyamaithunamāṃsasya na doṣaḥ svapravṛttitaḥ |
mitrāgamasukhālāpāḥ strīṇāṃ sambhogahetavaḥ ||008:041||
[svapravṛttiṣu ka ga; nidrāgama0 ka]
nityaṃ ceṣṭā mano'bhīṣṭāḥ kathā geyāḥ sukhapradāḥ ||008:042||
[citrā ka]
saudhapṛṣṭhamṛdunnātha raśmayaḥ sukhahetavaḥ |
uṣṇodakasukhasnānaṃ payaḥpānaṃ varastriyaḥ |
||008:043||
[saudhapṛṣṭha durādharṣa ka; parastriyaḥ khapustaka pāṭhāntare]
vājīkaraṇayogāṃśca nandikeśvara uktavān |
bhuktvā nārīśataṃ puṃsaḥ saubhāgyaṃ paramāpnuyāt ||008:044||
sahastreṇa mahābhogī hyayutena dhaneśvaraḥ |
lakṣeṇa kāmadevatvaṃ koṭinā paramaṃ padam ||008:045||
evaṃ pūrvopadeśantu nandinā paripṛcchataḥ |
viṣṇutattvaṃ kāmatattvaṃ śivatattvaṃ tathāparam ||008:046||
[pūrvāpare śambhuṃ nandinā paripṛcchitaḥ ka ga; viṣatattvaṃ ka ga]
ityevaṃ kapilaḥ prāha munīnāṃ pravaro muniḥ |
dviraṣṭavarṣāṃ kanyāñca pīnonnatapayodharām ||008:047||
yaḥ sadā kāmayate pumānamaratvaṃ sa gacchati ||008:048||
sthūlāṃ śithiladurgandhāṃ kekarāṃ vā kaṭāṃ śaṭhīm |
rogiṇīṃ vyādhitāṃ mūkāmayogyāṃ mandagāminīm ||008:049||
[śaṭhām ka ga]
gatvā pumānavāpnoti vyādhiṃ puṃstvavināśanam |
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena striyo'nveṣyā mahāmate ||008:050||
tadāyattā ime prāṇāḥ śukraujobalameva ca |
balañca paramaṃ śukraṃ tañca jīvaṃ mataṃ budhaiḥ ||008:051||
tacca śubhābalāyogād vardhate asurādhipa |
sa hṛṣṭaḥ sphītaḥ puruṣastasmāt sarvakṣayo bhavet ||008:052||
[sadvá¹tta vitaraḥ ka sadvapuvirataḥ puruṣaḥ ga]
evaṃ dharmārthakāmānāṃ na hānirbhavate'sura |
jambudvīpe mahābāho vindhye bhūdharaputrikā ||008:053||
dviraṣṭavarṣakanyā sā sarvalakṣaṇasaṃyutā |
yogyā rājaṃstvadīyasya vibhavāntaḥpurasya ca ||008:054||
tāmānaya yathā śaktyā trailokasya vibhūtaye |
pātālaṃ mūlabhūtantu sāraṃ pṛthvī sasāgarā ||008:055||
śākhāśailavanopetā divaṃ puṣpaṃ vinirddiśet |
apsarastatphalaṃ viddhi tāḥ kanyāḥ phalabījagāḥ ||008:056||
evaṃ sa nāradādeśāt vyāja-dharma-pravartitaḥ |
cakāra sammatiṃ śakra kanyāmudvahanopari ||008:057||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe devyavatāre ghorapralobhanaṃ nāmāṣṭamo'dhyāyaḥ |
|8|| here for this |
|8|| shall I put ||008||?
