nāradakathanācchakra vyājadharmarato'suraḥ |
na sa pūjayet viprān na vedān na vā acyutam ||009:001||
[sampūjayate ka; na ca devān ka ga]
na mantridvāḥstha vākyāni na ca patnīsamaṃ vaset |
sarva dharmapathaṃ tyaktvā balavāhana sañcayam ||009:002||
[mantrīśasya ka; balaṃ ka; kalaṃ vāhanameṣa ca ka ]
pānasaṅgamageyādimicchan dyūtaniṣevaṇam |
utkaṇṭhitamanā jātaḥ parapatnīrataḥ sadā ||009:003||
svakāntāṃ viṣavanmene na ca dharma pratīkṣate |
eka eva suhṛd vipro nārada ṛá¹ṣisattamaḥ ||009:004||
yena me viṣayāsaktirdattā kāmasukhapradā |
katareṇa vidhānena ānayāmi mudā tvaham ||009:005||
[sadā ka]
parapatnyaḥ śubhā bhadrāḥ pīnontapayodharāḥ |
satyameva hi dharmasya phalaṃ rājyaṃ mahodayam ||009:006||
tathā ca puragrāmāṇi gṛhāḥ patnyaḥ suśobhanāḥ |
devavidyādharā yakṣā brahmaviṣṇumaheśvarāḥ ||009:007||
sadākāmamudāsaktāḥ striyaḥ pānamano'nugāḥ |
tathā vayañca kurvāmo yathā bhūdharaputrikām ||009:008||
[kāmamanāsaktāḥ ka; kurvām ka |
kuryāṇaḥ iti kha pustaka pāṭhāntare]
nāradakathanāt satyaṃ bhuñjāmi suradurlabhām |
what to do with this line ? there is no number.
brahmovāca |

vijñāya nāradācchakra ghora tanmativartmagām |
amātyasahito vāgmī candrabuddhiramantrayat ||009:009||
[ghoraṃ tanmativartamaṇam iti kha; rājñī ka ga; asaṃdravan ga ]
candramatiruvāca |

yathā tāta mama svāmī candraśobhamahātmanaḥ |
tathaiva tvaṃ mahāmātyo mama bharttānupālakaḥ ||009:010||
tava sarvāṇi śāstrāṇi vidyā-ānvikṣikādayaḥ |
vasanti udare yasya sa kathaṃ mucyate pathaḥ ||009:011||
[cyavate ka ga]
amātyavaśagaṃ rājyaṃ vaśo rājā sumantriṣu |
tanmate bhuñjate pṛthvīmanyathā tu viparyayaḥ ||009:012||
tvayā tāta samasteyaṃ pṛthvīpātāladevarāṭ |
nāthena bhavatā prāptā sa kathaṃ na vaśastava ||009:013||
[sa kathaṃ no vaśo bhavet ka]
yadā hi vyasanāsaktaṃ nṛpaṃ buddhiviparyaye |
vijñāya sa tadāmātyaḥ prākṛtaṃ darśayedbhayam ||009:014||
[yathā ka; satatāmādyaḥ ka]
tava bhinnāḥ sutā bhāryāḥ sāmāntāḥ pravarā nṛpāḥ |
madīye tvaṃ mate varttan svayaṃ tannahi vetsyasi ||009:015||
[vartta svayaṃ tvaṃ na hi vatsyase kha]
tvaṃ punaḥ sarvabhāvena tasyājñāmanuvarttakaḥ |
na hi iṣṭaṃ sadāmātyaṃ rājño rājyaṃ kathaṃ bhavet ||009:016||
[tadā rājño vākyaṃ vākyakaraṃ bhavet ka |
na hi dṛṣṭaṃ sadāmātyaṃ rājño vākyakaraṃ bhavet kha |
na hi iṣṭaṃ sadā vākyaṃ rājño vākyakaraṃ bhavet ga ]
yasya samutsavā vaidyā amātyā nṛpavākkarāḥ |
na hi rājyaṃ sthiraṃ tasya kapimālevamūrddhagā ||009:017||
[sāṃvatsarāḥ ka. ga; mūrddhani ka]
amātyapravaraṃ rājyaṃ bhūtā dvāḥsthā avekṣakāḥ |
mahānasaḥ striyaḥ śayyāpānatāmbūladāyakāḥ ||009:018||
[amātyāḥ pravarā ka; lekhakāḥ ka ga]
ete hi yasya sadūvṛttāḥ sa rājā-sukhabhuk sadā |
vibhinnairbhidyate tāta sikatā iva setuṣu ||009:019||
dharmādharmasya saṃsiddhiḥ svāminaḥ sukhamicchatām |
bhṛtyānāṃ bhavata tāta anyathā nirayāstava ||009:020||
[niva yāntuḥ vaḥ ka ga]
ṛjuvraṇatvaksāramahāvaṃśā yathā gṛham |
dhārayanti sadā rājyaṃ mantriṇo daṇḍapālakāḥ ||009:021||
[vá¹hatvaśāṃ ka ga]
rājñāñca śabdamātraiva abhimānaṃ yathā mama |
rājyañcāmātyalekhyānāṃ bhogyaṃ tāta na cānyathā ||009:022||
strīsvarūpā yadā kiñcinmayā vāṇī na saṃskṛtā |
tathāpi mama kṣantavyaṃ bālānāṃ na hi ruṣṭatām ||009:023||
[rūpyatāṃ ka ga| rūpyatāṃ kha]
evaṃ sabāndhavaṃ mantraṃ candrabuddhiḥ prahṛṣṭavān provāca saṃstutaṃ vākyaṃ devī tvaṃ devatāsvapi ||009:024||
[savāsavaṃ ka ga; candravṛddhiḥ ka ga; prapṛṣṭavān ka ga; deva tvaṃ devatā api ka]
suṣeṇa uvāca |

[susena]
tvameva sarvavākyānāṃ nayānāmupadeśinī |
tathāpi kiñcid vaktavyaṃ na tveva tacca manyase ||009:025||
[vaktṛṇāṃ ga; yatdhevaṃ ka]
sarvanītigataḥ pāro devadvijanadejyakaḥ |
śuddhamatiśca matimān kathaṃ sa vipathe vrajet ||009:026||
[buddhiśca ka ga]
akasmādadya rātrau ca nāradādvākyacoditaḥ |
tasya icchākaro bhūtvā asmākañca nahīcchati ||009:027||
yathāmātyena mattena vibhūtirviphalā tava |
yena vṛddhāstriyaḥ sevī kṛtovaidyāḥ purohitāḥ ||009:028||
[kuto0 ka ga]
evaṃ tasya matirbhūttvā nāradapathagā śubhe |
vayaṃ tvañca tathāgaccha pratyakṣamanuśāsyatām ||009:029||
[nāradaḥ pathagaḥ ka]
avamanya tathā dvāḥsthaṃ devī mantrī gatau hi tam |
saṃkruddhalocano'paśyat na ca vācābhyabhāṣata ||009:030||
[jyaśyan ka]
candramatiruvāca |

yadāpi bhavato nāsmān vācāyāmapi bhāṣate |
tathāpi kiñcid vaktavyaṃ na sapatnībhayaṃ mama ||009:031||
[nayatau hyasmānvācamānāpi bhāṣayet ga]
na cāvijñātaśīlāsu strīṣu bhogyāgamaḥ kvacit |
viṣakanyābhayaṃ ghoraṃ pāpajaṃ śrūyate param ||009:032||
[śāpajaṃ ka ga]
tapasvivyañjakaṃ nagnacaṇḍabhīrūcarānugān |
yajñavipravidāṃ rājā viśvastaḥ sīdate'cirāt ||009:033||
[nagnacaṇḍībhīrūvanāntagāt ka]
rajakī tāntrikī cakrī varuṭhī puṣpagranthinī |
kaivartī īkṣaṇī vṛddhā na hi sthāpyā gṛhe ciram ||009:034||
[kandukī ka kha ga]
sūtikā vadhirā yantrī kulālī strījane yathā |
vināśaṃ kurute'vaśyaṃ dharmarājo'pi tadvaśaḥ ||009:035||
[bandhikā ka; deśyan ka |
deśān ka]
pānaṃ kanyāsanaṃ śayyā vāhanantu vicāritam |
bhuñjāno mahadāpnoti mṛtyukṛcchraṃ tathā gadam ||009:036||
[kalpāsanaṃ ka ga]
na hi anicchatī bālā bhuñjanīyā kadācana |
na ca tāmudvahennātha śṛṇu pūrvakathāmimām ||009:037||
[nāhaṃ ka; tāmudvāhayennātha ka]
tvañca vetsi yathānyāyaṃ tathāpi cra śṛṇu lokataḥ ||009:038||
[spaṣṭaṃ ka ga; lokaya ka ga]
krauñcadvīpe purāvṛttaṃ rājā nāmnā sumedhasaḥ |
tasya patnīsahasrāṇi aṣṭāvaṣṭābhavat kila ||009:039||
sarvasampattisampannaḥ samastabalavāhanaḥ |
bhuñjan pṛthvīmimāṃ nātha sasamudrāṃ sakānanām ||009:040||
tāvat kālena mahatā parikrāman paraṃ kila |
dvīpaṃ śākāhvayaṃ nātha tasmin krīḍan yathāvidhi ||009:041||
[nāma ka ga]
so'śṛṇot puṣkare kāyāmṛṣe khpasamanvitām |
sarvalakṣaṇasampannāṃ sarvābharaṇabhūṣitām ||009:042||
[sa śṛṇvan ka ga]
tāvat sa tatrago nātha na paśyedṛṣitāpasām |
sā kanyā bhadranāmā ca tāmudvāhasamutsukaḥ ||009:043||
[mudvāhana ka ga]
kāmārtto vihvalībhūto na vindyādaparaṃ vavacit |
anicchamānāpi tathā gṛhītā pāṇinā kare ||009:044||
[na cintyādaparaṃ kvacit ga]
sā kanyā bhadranāmnī ca rudantīṃ na mumoca saḥ |
tathā sa tāṃ bhuñjayitvā gato dvīpaṃ narādhipaḥ ||009:045a-d||
[vāma ka |
rāmanāmnī ga]
śākāhvamāgatastāvat puṣkare munisattamaḥ ||009:045ef||
[sa kanyāṃ ramaṇārthī tu rudantīṃñca na mocate kha]
tena sā vimanā dṛṣṭā rudamānā tu kanyakā |
papraccha sarvamākhyātaṃ yathāvṛttaṃ sureśvara ||009:046||
[vimalā ka; dṛṣṭvā ka ga]
śrutvā krodhasamāviṣṭaḥ śaśāpa tamṛṣirnṛpam |
sumedhasastato yāto narakaṃ bhūtalādabhūt ||009:047||
[sumedhāḥ sa valo jāto narakaṃ ka ga]
evaṃ nātha na sāṃpatnyaśaṅkayā asureśvara |
vārayāmi ca tvāṃ svāmin tava rājyasukhārthinī ||009:048||
[sasureśvaraḥ ka; ca tvāṃ ka ga]
