bandha bandha kampaya kampaya cala cala cālaya cālaya rudhiramāṃsamadyapriye hana hana kuha kuha |

[raṃga raṃga kalpaya cala cala cālaya cālaya ka ]
chinda chinda māraya māraya vajraśarīramānaya ānaya |

[anubrūma ityadhikaḥ ka]
trailokyagatamapi duṣṭamaduṣṭaṃ vā gṛhītamagṛhītaṃ vā āviśaya āviśaya |

[śatamapi ka; dṛṣṭamadṛṣṭaṃ ka]
krāmaya krāmaya nṛtya nṛtya bandha bandha koṭarākṣi ūrdhvakeśi ulūkavadane |

[kāmaya kāmaya ka]
karaṅkiṇi karaṅkamālādhāriṇi daha daha paca paca gṛhna gṛhna maṇḍanamadhye |

[varāṅgamālā kha]
praveśaya praveśaya kiṃ vilambasi brahmasatyena viṣṇusatyena rudrasatyena ṛṣisatyena |

āviśaya āviśaya kili kili mili mili vikṛtarūpadhāriṇi kṛṣṇabhujaṅgamaveṣṭitaśarīre,
[daha.....ḍhāriṇi iti yāvat ka pratau nāsti]
sarvagṛhāveśini pralamboṇṭhi bhagnanāsike kapilajaṭe brāhmi bhuñja bhuñja jvala jvālāmukhi,
[bhaṅga ka; cipiṭamukhi ka pratāvadhikaḥ]
jvala jvala khala khala pātaya pātaya raktādi ghūrṇāpaya ghūrṇāpaya bhūrmi pātaya pātaya, śiro
gṛhṇa gṛhṇa cakṣurnimīlaya mīlaya hṛdayaṃ bhuñja bhuñja hastapādau gṛhṇa gṛhṇa mudrāḥ,
[bhajaṃ bhajaṃ ka]
sphoṭaya sphoṭaya hūṃ hūṃ phaṭ vidāraya vidāraya triśūlena bhedaya bhedaya vajreṇa,
hana hana daṇḍena tāḍaya tāḍaya cakreṇa chedaya chedaya śaktinā bhedaya bhedaya,
daṃṣṭrayā kīlaya kīlaya kartikayā pāṭaya pāṭaya aṅkuśena guhṇa guhṇa,
śirortijvaram ekāhikaṃ dvayāhikaṃ tryāhikaṃ cāturthikaṃ ḍākinī skanda,
[śirorogārtijvaraâekāhika-dvāhika-tryāhika-cāturthaka kha ]
grahāna muñcāpaya muñcāpaya tana tana utthāpaya utthāpaya bhūmiṃ pātaya pātaya,
[lala lala kha]
gṛhṇa gṛhṇa brahmāṇi trāhi māheśvarī ehi ehi kaumāri ehi ehi traiṣṇavi ehi ehi vārāhi
[brahmāṇi kha; ehi ehi kha]
ehi ehi aindri ehi ehi cāmuṇḍe ehi ehi kapālini ehi ehi mahākāli ehi ehi,
[mahākapālini kha]
revati ehi ehi mahārevati ehi ehi śuṣkarevati ehi ehi ākāśa revati ehi ehi,
himavantacāriṇi ehi ehi kailāśacāriṇī ehi ehi paramatantrān,
chinda chinda kili kili vicce aghore ghorarūpiṇi cāmuṇḍe rudrakodhādviniḥsṛte,
asurabhayaṅkari ākāśagāmini pāśena bandha bandha kartta kartta śamaya tiṣṭha tiṣṭha,
[samayaṃ kha]
maṅgalaṃ praveśaya praveśaya gṛhṇa gṛhṇa mukhaṃ bandha bandha cakṣurbandha bandha hṛdayaṃ bandha,
[maṇḍalaṃ praveśaya kha]
bandha hastapādau bandha bandha duṣṭagṛhān sarvān bandha bandha sā diśā bandha bandha,
vidiśā bandha bandha ūrdhvaṃ bandha bandha adhastāt bandha bandha bhasmanā pānīyena |
]||
[gṛhaṇa gṛhaṇa ityārabhya............bandha bandha ityantaḥ pāṭho nāsti kha; sarva bandha bandha ityadhikaḥ pāṭhaḥ ga]
mṛttikayā vā sarvairvā āviśaya āviśaya ghātaya ghātaya cāmuṇḍe kili kili vicce hūṃ phaṭ ||009:057||
[pātaya pātaya kha]
evaṃ sā padamālākhyā vidyā devanamaskṛtā |
yasyārthā udaraṃ jagmurmadīyaṃ bhārgavaḥ purā ||009:058||
[ eṣāsyāḥ kha; yasyārthe kha ]
sa ca varṣaśataṃ divyaṃ sthitvā śāpena śāpitaḥ |
| cakāra ca tadā devī kāruṇyād bhavatoṣitā ||009:059||
[carācara tadā ka; stabatoṣitā kha]
tava liṅgādviniṣkrāntaḥ śukro nāmnā bhaviṣyati |
suto'yaṃ tava deveśa sarva vidyādhipo varaḥ ||009:060||
[vidyādharo kha]
tvayāpi vatsa na deyā abhakte nājitendriye |
aṣṭottaraṃ śataṃ kuryāt karmaṇā gaṇanāyaka ||009:061||
[vatsanādeyā nā bhakte kha; aṣṭau kṛṣṭa kha; gaṇasattama kha ]
evaṃ pūrva mahāvidyāṃ śivānnandīśaḥ prāptavān |
samasta padauccārā aṣṭottaraśataṃ vibho ||009:062||
[nandīśa kha]
śakra uvāca |

karmaṇā kurute nātha rki vā pratyekaśabditā |
