sanatkumāraṃ varadaṃ koṭisūryasamaprabham |
merupṛṣṭhāśritaṃ dṛṣṭvā sarvabhūtanamaskṛtam ||010:010 p1||
praṇamya śirasā tasmai yogācāryāya nāradaḥ |
paripṛcchati yatnena susūkṣmaṃ yogamuttamam ||010:011 p1||
bhagavan ! śrotumicchāmi tanme kathaya suvrata ! |
kenopāyena tadyogaṃ prāpyate ṛṣisattama ! ||010:012 p1||
tasmai provāca bhagavān sarvaśāstraviśāradaḥ |
śṛṇu nārada vakṣyāmi yogaṃ saṃkṣepatastava ||010:013 p1||
puṣpabhūteṣu śāstreṣu madhuvat sāramuddhṛtam |
yogadharmaṃ pravakṣyāmi namaskṛtvā maheśvaram ||010:014 p1||
jñānād bhavati vairāgyaṃ vairāgyād dharmasañcayaḥ |
dharmācca yogo bhavati yogānmāheśvarā guṇāḥ ||010:015 p1||
pūrva jñānāgamaṃ kṛtvā virakto dharmamācaret |
atiprasaṅgo jñāneṣu na kāryaḥ siddhimicchadā ||010:016 p1||
[nirukto ka; abhiprasaṅgo kha]
dharmaḥ prayatnataḥ kāryo yogināntu viśeṣataḥ |
nāsti dharmādṛte yoga iti yogavido viduḥ ||010:017||
yathādeśaṃ yathākālaṃ yathādravyaṃ yathukramam |
yathopadiṣṭaḥ karttavyo dharmo dharmaphalārthibhiḥ ||010:018 p1||
na sukhāni ca dharmaśca nādharmaścāsukhāni ca |
sukhārthī vā tyajet dharma dharmārthī vā tyajetsukham ||010:019 p1||
varaṃ nopārjito dharmo na caivāparirakṣitaḥ |
tasmāt kṛstnasya dharmasya karttavyaṃ parirakṣaṇam ||010:020 p1||
[kṛtasya kha]
anyathā kriyate dharmo anyathā copadiśyate |
karttavyaścopadeṣṭavyo dharmo dharmaparāyaṇaiḥ ||010:021 p1||
sarvadharmān parityajya yatidharma samācaret |
