japyantu cintayennityaṃ na ca śūnyo bhaveddvijaḥ |
sthitvā kālāntaraṃ kiñicadomityetadanusmaret ||010:010||
oṃkāraṃ praṇavo brahma akṣaraṃ paramaṃ padam |
ityete dhyāyanopāyā ṛṣibhiḥ parikīrtitāḥ ||010:011||
[dhyāninopāyān kha]
yama-niyama-ratānāṃ bahu-vighna-bhayeṣu ca labdha dhairyāṇām |
bhavati jayo viduṣāṃ prāṇa-vāyu-dhāraṇa-labdha-lakṣaṇānām ||010:012||
