yamānāṃ niyamānāñca avāntarakriyāsu ca |
sarvadigdeśakāleṣu yogābhyāso viśiṣyate ||010:001||
yadi syāt pātakaṃ kiñcid yogī kuryāt pramādataḥ |
yogameva niṣedeta nānyaṃ mantraṃ kadācana ||010:002||
sarveṣāmeva mantrānāṃ yogamantraṃ viśiṣyate |
tasmād yogaḥ sadā sevyaḥ sarvāvasthāgatairapi ||010:003||
yastu kāyakṛtān bhogān dhyāyamānantu sevate |
alpavīryaṃ hi tadyogaṃ yogaśāstreṣu garhitam ||010:004||
[kāmakṛtān kha]
yo dhyātvā yuñjeta dhyānaṃ yajjñeyaṃ yatprayojanam |
sarvāṇyetāni yo vetti sa yogī yoktumarhati ||010:005||
[dhyātā kha0; yogamarhati kha]
ātmā dhyātā mano dhyānaṃ dhyeyaḥ sūkṣmo maheśvaraḥ |
yattat paramamaiśvaryametaddhyānaprayojanam ||010:006||
dve brahmanī veditavye śabdabrahmaparañca yat |
śabdabrahmaṇi niṣnātaḥ paraṃ brahmādhigacchati ||010:007||
antaḥ śarīraprabhavamudānapreritañca yat |
vāguccārya śrotravṛtti śabdabrahma taducyate ||010:008||
śabda brahma paraṃ brahma tasmin kṣīṇe yadakṣaram |
sadā taṃ manasā dhyāyed yadīcchecchreyaḥ ātmanaḥ ||010:009||
vaktukāmo yadā vācyamartha samprati padyeta |
buddhyahaṅkārasaṃyukto tathā dhyānaṃ samācaret ||010:010||
upalabdhiḥ smṛtirdhyānaṃ saṅkalpaḥ praṇavaṃ prati |
kalpanā bhāvanā cintā dhyānamityabhidhīyate ||010:011||
pavanavirahito yathā pradīpaḥ sthita iva lakṣyate niścalasvabhāvaḥ |
viṣayavirahitaṃ tathā hi cittaṃ sthitamiva lakṣyate'mitapravṛtti ||010:012||
