dhyāyamānastamoṅkāraṃ prāṇairyadi viyujyate |
tasya tat paramaiśvaryaṃ bhinne dehe pravarttate ||010:001||
oṃkārād bhraśyate cittaṃ kṣiptaṃ kṣiptaṃ punaḥ punaḥ |
śabdādibhirasampṛktaṃ bhūyastasmin niyojayet ||010:002||
[kṣipraṃ kṣipraṃ kha; saṃyuktaṃ yogāya na nivartate kha]
anirviṇṇastu yuñjānaḥ śrāntaḥ śrāntaḥ punaḥ punaḥ |
kālena tadavāpnoti guhyādguhyataraṃ padam ||010:003||
deva-mānuṣa-tiryakṣu jantuḥ karma-vaśānugaḥ |
tāvad bhramati saṃsāre yāvadyogaṃ na vindati ||010:004||
nivṛttaṃ sarva saṅgeṣu buddhayā cādhiṣṭhitaṃ manaḥ |
cittamoṅkārasaṃyuktaṃ yogāya na nivarttate ||010:005||
anena kramayogeṇa yasyoṅkārādhivāsitam |
tasyoṅkāraṃ parityajya cittaṃ nānyatra gacchati ||010:006||
ekamātraṃ dvimātraṃ vā trimātraṃ kṛtsnameva ca |
hṛsvaṃ dīrghaṃ plutaṃ śāntaṃ śāntena manasodvahet ||010:007||
tailadhārāmivācchinnāṃ dīrghaghaṇṭāninādavat |
oṅkārasantatiṃ kuryād viśuddhenāntarātmanā ||010:008||
viśuddhamanasā yuktaḥ śāntātmā mohavarjitaḥ |
āsādya paramaṃ yogamakṣayaṃ labhate padam ||010:009||
[labhate paramaṃ padam kha]
oṅkāreṇa viśuddhātmā paraṃ brahmādhigacchati |
pare brahmaṇi sandhyāya saṃsārādvipramucyate ||010:010||
[sandhāya āsaṃsārād vimucyate kha]
yo jñātvā bahu-vidha-doṣa-duṣṭametat saṃsāra satatamabhipravarttamānam |
yogāya pravarttate yogamārgavettāsau bhuṅkte phalamatulaṃ śivaprasādāt ||010:011||
