ekāgrapraṇidhānañca apramādāt tathaiva ca |
yuñjānastu sadā yogaṃ yogadvāraṃ prapaśyati ||010:001||
yogadvāraṃ paraṃ guhyaṃ sarvatāpapraṇāśanam |
pavitramatulañcaiva durddarśamakṛtātmabhiḥ ||010:002||
na taṃ paśyanti vibudhā na tiryañco na mānuṣāḥ |
kāmabhogaparivyagrā bahūpakṛtakilviṣāḥ ||010:003||
[tridaśā kha]
yogadvāreṇa yatayo yuktātmāno dṛḍhabratāḥ |
oṅkārarathamāruhya gacchanti paramāṃ gatim ||010:004||
yogadvāramatītānāṃ nānyo loko vidhīyate |
yadgatvā na nivarttante prāsādācchaṃkarasya ca ||010:005||
