cittotpattau na cotpattirna ca cittakṣaye kṣayaḥ |
anādimadhyaparyantaḥ sarvavyāpī maheśvaraḥ ||010:001||
[bhāvotpattau......ityārabhya maheśvaraḥ iti yāvat pāṭho nāsti kha ]
bhāvotpattau tayoḥ saṅgamantaḥkaraṇapūrvakam |
bhāvābhāvau tayoreva niyoga ubhayorapi ||010:002||
na dīrgho na cāsau hrasvo na plutaśca maheśvaraḥ |
dhyānakāle nimittaṃ hi sarvathā hyupacaryate ||010:003a-d||
śabda-tattve ca bhāve ca saṃjñāyāmakṣareṣu ca ||010:003ef||
pañcasvartheṣu satatamoṅkāramiti nirddiśet |
tattvacintābhisaṃvaddhaṃ cintā manasi vartate ||010:004||
[sambandhaṃ kha]
manaḥ kṣetrajñasaṃyuktaṃ svaśarīre vyavasthitam |
śabda sparśastathā rūpaṃ raso gandhastathaiva ca |
||010:005a-d||
samprāpto nopalabhyeta etad yuktasya lakṣaṇam ||010:005ef||
[samprāptā nopalabhyante kha]
sukhaduḥkhañca mokṣañca svaśarīreṇa vindati |
śītoṣṇaṃ nābhi jānāti etad âyuktasya lakṣaṇamâ ||010:006||
