śaṅkha-dundubhi-rnirghoṣaivirvidhairgīta-vāditaiḥ |
kriyamānairna vudhyate etad yuktasya lakṣaṇam ||010:007||
yogakarmaṇi yuktasya viśeṣād vighnakārakāḥ |
upasargāḥpravarttante tān jitvā prāpyate sukham ||010:008||
upasarge'pi sṛṣṭasya naiva siddhirna sādhanam |
tasmād vighnāḥ sadā heyāḥ śāstradṛṣṭena karmaṇā ||010:009||
[upasargopasṛṣṭasya kha upasargāya iti ka pustakasya pāṭhāntare]
pratimā śravaṇañcaiva vedanaṃ sparśanaṃ tathā |
bhramo mohastathā vartta upasargāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||010:010||
vyapagata-kaluṣāṇāṃ nitya-snānodakānāṃ śivamatiparamārtho japyabhaikṣyendhanānām |
guruvacana-ratānāṃ nitya-dharmodyatānāṃ darśanamapi puṇyaṃ yogamārgasthitānām ||010:011||
