dhāraṇāṃ sampravakṣyāmi kartavyā yā prayatnataḥ |
manaso hṛdyavasthānaṃ dhāraṇetyabhidhīyate ||010:001||
yathā cakṣuḥ prakāśena dṛṣṭarūpāṇi paśyati |
tadvat sūkṣmayogena yuktastattvāni paśyati ||010:002||
nirmalatvād yathādarśe pratibimbāni paśyati |
tadvad viśuddhe manasi niṣkalaṃ brahma paśyati ||010:003||
yathā jñānaprakāśena susūkṣmārthān prapaśyati |
tadvat susūkṣmamoṅkāraṃ praṇidhānena paśyati ||010:004||
nirguṇaṃ manasā grāhyamanaupamyaṃ mahādyutim |
pradhānapuruṣeśānaṃ sarvabhūtapatiṃ śivam ||010:005||
sthitaṃ sthitena manasā śuddhaṃ śuddhena cetasā |
parāparasvarūpeṇa yatsūkṣmamupanayet punaḥ ||010:006||
taccittastanmayo yuktastanniṣṭhastatparāyaṇaḥ |
doṣairyogāgninirdagdhaiḥ |
śivaṃ paśyati śāśvatam ||010:007||
[tasmāttata ka]
anutpādyaṃ sarvagataṃ sarvajñaṃ sarvakāraṇam |
akṣataiśvarya-sampannaṃ devamekaṃ maheśvaram ||010:008||
[akṛtaiśvarya0 kha]
yaṃ dṛṣṭvā labhate siddhiṃ samānaguṇalakṣaṇam |
yaṃ dṛṣṭvā janma-mohābhyāṃ naiva saṃyujyate punaḥ ||010:009||
eṣa saṃkṣepato yogo vyākhyāne cāsya vistaraḥ |
maharṣīnāmanukampārthamuddhṛto mama sūnūnā ||010:010||
yatprāpya nāradaḥ siddho vidyāvidyārtha tattvataḥ |
idamamṛtapadaṃ śivaprasādāt pravacanamuktavān sanatkumāraḥ ||010:011a-d||
[yaṃ prāpya kha]
anadhigatamapi karoti siddhiṃ paramiha vindate sa rudratattvam ||010:011ef||
