[tena pūrvaṃ kha]
yathā na śaktāḥ samare daityān yoddhuṃ pitāmaha |
śatrūṇāṃ paribhūtānāṃ śaraṇaṃ tvāṃ gatā vayam ||011:046||
yathāhaṃ cintayāmāsa śakraviṣṇudivaukasām |
ketunā śambhudattena uditena asaṃśayam ||011:047||
[ucchritena kha]
tato mayāsurāḥ sendrā viṣṇumārādhayan purā |
sa dāsyati mahāketuṃ sarvadaityavimohanam ||011:048||
te gatā mama cādeśāt kṣīrode yatra keśavaḥ |
parāparasvarūpasthamajamavyayaṃ śāśvatam ||011:049||
śrī vatsāṅka mahāvāhuṃ kaustubhoraska bhūṣaṇam |
stuvantyete samahendrā devāḥ śatru bhayārditāḥ ||011:050||
[kaustubho vakṣabhūṣitam kha]
tutoṣa keśavasteṣāmÌ varaṃ brūhi purandaraḥ |
tadā tairyācito devaḥ ketuṃ dadau surārihā ||011:051||
[sahendrā vai kha]
tena tad bhūṣayitvā tu dattaṃ deva bhayāpaham |
śvetacchatra mahātejaḥ sragmālāpiṭakānvitam ||011:052||
sūryāyutasamaprakhyaṃ kiṅkiṇīvara-nāditam |
cāmaravyajanopetaṃ śambhulakṣaṇalakṣitam ||011:053||
taddṛṣṭvā saubalaṃ sainyaṃ magnaṃ sa ca nipātitam |
tadā prabhṛti he śakra ! ketustava kramāgataḥ ||011:054||
anyeṣāñcaiva rājñāñca ucchrayo vijayāvahaḥ |
mayā hareṇa devena viṣṇunā vāsavena ca ||011:055||
yaddattaṃ kaścidevedaṃ nṛpatirucchrayiṣyati |
sa samastādhipo bhūmāvajeyaśca bhaviṣyati ||011:056||
agastya uvāca |

[dadasva cārihā kha]
evaṃ śakrasya śabdena kathitaṃ ketumucchrayam |
