[samā vā kha]
vṛttā vā bhaṃgamādhatte rājñaḥ putra purohitān |
āvabhaṃge balaṃ bhindyāt nemyo nāśa kṣayaṃ tathā ||012:024||
[saṃkṣayam ga ka]
arthasya kṣayabhaṃgena śāṃtiṃ tatra tu kārayeta |
indraja-chatra-maṃtreṇa jātaveda samāpi vā ||012:025||
