dvāraśobhāṃ patharathyāṃ gṛhe haṭṭe ca kārayet ||012:026||
[tathā ga]
paṭu paṭaha ninādāṃśca veśyaśaṃkhaṃ dvijātayaḥ |
maṃgalairvedaśabdaiśca tānne yādyaṃtra ucchrayet ||012:027||
tatrasthaṃ-citrakarmāra-nirmitaistāṃ tu veṣṭayet |
