rasanāṃ vicitravarṇāṃ prathamāṃ dadyātsvayaṃbhuvaḥ ||012:031||
suraktāṃ caturasrāṃ ca viśvakarmā dvitīyataḥ |
aṣṭāṃ śrīṃ tu svayaṃ śakro nīlaraktāṃ pradāpayet ||012:032||
kṛtsnaṃ yamena vṛttaṃ ca varuṇena ṣaḍaśrakam |
