vahnīśa-ṛá¹ṣimaṃtraiśca hotavyaiḥ dadhicākṣataiḥ ||012:040||
śukra-skanda-guru-rudra apsarādi prapāṭhayet |
hutvā tu vidhivad vahniṃ jvālāṃ lakṣeta buddhimān ||012:041||
sutejāḥ sumanodīptaḥ saṃhato ravisaṃprabhaḥ |
raktāśokasamākāro rathabherīsvanaḥ śubhaḥ ||012:042||
śaṃkha-duṃdubhimeghānāṃ nādāḥ śastrāstu pāvake |
tataḥ kadalīkṣudaṃḍān patākāśca samucchrayet ||012:043||
anyāśca vividhāḥ śobhāḥ śakraketuṃ samucchrayet |
prauṣṭhapadetu aṣṭamyāṃ śuklāyāṃ śobhane dine ||012:044||
[proṣṭhapadyāṃ ga]
āśvine vātha śuklāyāṃ śravaṇenātha ucchraye |
paura-jana-nagna-vṛndaiḥ paṭṭa-bherī-nināditam ||012:045||
vitānadhvajaśobhāḍhyaṃ patākābhiḥ samujvalam |
viṣṇavīśa-śakramaṃtreṇa siṃha rakṣākṛtena ca ||012:046||
dṛḍhaṃ ca mātṛkarasthaṃ śubhato raṇamākulam |
avilaṃvitamutthānaṃ bhagnaṃ piṭakaṃ tathā ||012:047||
na drutaṃ vā samutthāpyaṃ ketuṃ vāsavajaṃ vibho |
utthitaṃ rakṣayetprājñaḥ kākolūkakapotayoḥ ||012:048||
nasadalīpanaṃ dadyādanyeṣāmapi pakṣiṇām |
yaṃtroddeśena taṃ kuryyānmukhaṃ ketoryathāvidhi ||012:049||
tathā susaṃsthitaṃ pūjyaṃ sukhayaṃtrasvayaṃtritas |
rātrau jāgaraṇaṃ kuryyādiṃdramaṃtrānukīrttanam ||012:050||
purohitaḥ sadaivajñaḥ śubhaśāṃtirataḥ sadā |
chatrapāto nṛpaṃ hanyātpatākā mahiṣīvadham ||012:051||
piṭake yuvarājasya sasacivamanukaṃpane |
rāṣṭraṃ toraṇapātena dhvajena annakṣayo bhavet ||012:052||
patite śakradaṃḍe tu nṛpamanyaṃ samādiśet |
kṛmijālakautthāne śalabhāttaskarādbhayam ||012:053||
[nṛpamantraṃ ga]
susame saṃsthite śāṃtirnṛpasya nagarasya ca |
yāvaducchritaṃ tiṣṭhanti tāvatpaurā hṛṣṭāḥ sadā ||012:054||
[lokāḥ ka]
ketorniratāyajane bhuṃjīyādviprakanyāśca |
pūjā yādṛśī utthāne kuryātpāte tathaiva ca ||012:055||
[ketoniratojane kha]
rātrau śubhakṛtpātanaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ kākakāpotaiḥ |
yāti nṛpaḥsaharāṣṭraṃ kertuṃyaścaiva kārayet ||012:056||
nagare vā pure kheṭe paurā yadyevaṃ kurvate |
puranagarasya dvāre vṛṣasiṃha-khagotthitam ||012:057||
ketuṃ samasta ghorāṇāṃ nāśanaṃ jayadaṃ matam |
evaṃ pūrvaṃ hariḥ ketuṃ prāptavān vṛṣavāhanāt ||012:058||
tathā brahmasya tenaiva brahmaṇaḥ śakramāgatam |
tena somasya tato dakṣe taṅgantuṃ samāgatam ||012:059||
tadā prabhṛti kurvanti nṛpā adyāpi ucchrayam |
evaṃ yaḥ kārayedrājā ketuṃ vijaya kārakam ||012:060||
tasya pṛthvī balopetā sadvīpā vaśagā bhavet ||012:061||
ityādye śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre dhvajalakṣaṇaṃ nāma dvādaśo'dhyāyaḥ
