%%% Chapter 013
trayodaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

etat te sarvamākhyātaṃ ketukhyāpanamāgatam |
bhūyaḥ kiṃ pṛcchase rājaṃstanno brūhi vadāmi te ||013:001||
[ketūtthāpana sāgaram ka ga]
nṛpavāhana uvāca |

kathitaṃ vidyāmāhātmyaṃ yogaṃ nārada-pṛcchitam |
ketoḥ samucchrayaḥ puṇyaḥ sarvakāma-sukhapradaḥ ||013:002||
bhūyastāta punaḥ pṛcchet kathaṃ ghoro mahābalaḥ |
nāradena sapatnīkaḥ sahamaṃtrī vimohitaḥ ||013:003||
[ahaṃ ga]
agastya uvāca |

yathā sa pṛṣṭavānvatsa śakrastvasurasattamaḥ |
evaṃ pitāmahaṃ pūrvaṃ vidyāyogasya kautukam ||013:004||
[devaṃ ga]
devaṃ bhūyo'pi saṃpṛṣṭo ghora-buddhi-vighātanam |
kathaṃ kuryyānmahābāho nārado munisattamaḥ ||013:005||
[vighātakam ga]
brahmovāca |

tasya japanaśīlasya pratāpāt surasattamaḥ |
devānāṃ mahatī vṛṣṭiḥ sarvvā sukhapradā bhavet ||013:006||
vanaspatiḥ samastāśca phalapuṣpaiḥ suśobhitāḥ |
mohitā ghorasenā tu sahamaṃtripurohitā ||013:007||
[suśobhitaiḥ ka ga]
vidharmapathagā sarvvā bhartturanveṣaṇe ratā |
vaṃcane tasya dārāderdhanasya vibhavasya ca ||013:008||
sanmārga satpathaṃ tyaktvā tena te mohitāsurāḥ |
vikarmaniratā vatsa vidharmamatiśīlinaḥ ||013:009||
tāñca śīlamatīṃ rājñīṃ digambaraparāyaṇām |
aneka vrata-bhūyiṣṭhāṃ hetuvāda-manonugām ||013:010||
[śaśīmatīm ga]
pāṣaṃḍa-sarva-dharmasthāṃ śiva-viṣṇu-jugupsitām |
na cāgniharaṇe bhaktirnātithau gṛhapūjane ||013:011||
[pāpaṃ tu sattvadharmasthāṃ ga]
na mātaro mahābhāgā na gāvo na ca brāhmaṇāḥ |
evaṃ sā nāradocchiṣṭān dharmān kuryyāt sadā satī ||013:012||
evaṃ vidharmmamādhāya tasya ghorasya vai sabhāḥ |
supathamujjhayitvā tu unmārgena pravarttire ||013:013||
[vai satām ga]
ghora uvāca |

brahmaputra mahābāho śailaputryā naye mama |
ko yogyo hyatra yodhānāṃ drutakāryyasya brūhi naḥ ||013:014||
[nayanaṃ mama ga]
nārada uvāca |

yataḥ śaśāṅka-sampūrṇā bilāñchana ivānanāḥ |
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā munayaḥ kṣobhaṃ kiṃ punarasurādhipāḥ ||013:015||
[vilāñjana ka ga]
tathā tvaṃ sarvva-sainyena eko vā vigatāyudhaḥ |
vrajasva yatra tāḥ kanyāḥ śailarāja-sutottamāḥ ||013:016||
dakṣiṇā sārvadaivatyai paurṇamāsyāṃ samāyayau |
savāhana-balāmātyaḥ sapurohitaḥ sāyudhaḥ ||013:017||
[dakṣiṇādhīśadaivatye kha; savāhana balomaitri ka ga]
suṣeṇa kuru huṅkāraṃ devala-vibhu-dāruṇaiḥ |
vāṇa-keśava-cāmuṇḍa-anuhrāda mahābalaiḥ ||013:018||
[mahāravai ka ga]
sāmantapravarairyyodhairmmaṅgalairāśibhistathā |
muhūrte abhijinnāmni madhyāhne tyajate puram ||013:019||
[vāśibhiḥ ga]
tasya nirgacchato vegāt śvāno vāsthimukho'bhavat |
dhvaje ruroha kāpotaḥ śivā śyāmā ca dakṣiṇā ||013:020||
piṅgalā rūrūgodhā ca śūkarī  kabalāstathā |
gaja-bānara-senāja-śikhicchivā ca vāmataḥ ||013:021||
panthānaṃ bhindate sarpaḥ kumbhodakaṃ vyaśīryyata |
rūrāva vānaro ṛkṣo mārjjāro hyatibhairavam ||013:022||
[kumbhodakaṃ viśīryata ga]
taila-takra-tṛṇa-keśa muṇḍābhyaktādi darśanam |
vāntonmatta-jaḍa-mūka kṣutkṣābha-nakrajaṃ varam ||013:023||
tuṣa kārpāśalavaṇaṃ ninditānāñca darśanam |
raktāmbaradharaṃ muṇḍaṃ paṅkāmiṣaṃ tathā vasām ||013:024||
[vasā ga]
lalāṭaṃ śakrajaṃ cāpamulkāpātā dhvajānanāḥ |
diśāṃ dāho mahīkampa sarajaḥ kaluṣaṃnabhaḥ ||013:025||
[athadāruṇāḥ ka ga]
nistejāstapate bhānurnadyaḥ pratimukhāvahan |
uṣṇodakaṃ mahākūpaṃ dāruṇaṃ dīrghakāsu ca ||013:026a-d||
[pratimukhāvahan ga]
akālavikṛtiḥ puṣpaphalānāmabhavat tadā ||013:026ef||
śīta uṣṇa virpayyāsā meghanādāśca dāruṇāḥ |
āraṇya-sattvā grāmeṣu grāmajāraṇyavāsinaḥ ||013:027||
kṛṣṇa sarpa samūhāśca śaśaścala pipīlikāḥ |
dhvāṃkṣāṇāṃ mahatī senā mṛgāṇāñca tathaiva ca ||013:028||
