dhvajacchatra patākānāṃ sphuṭanaṃ daṇḍa bhedanam ||013:030||
[aśvaḥ kha; dhvajachatra ga; bhiṃdanā kha]
kalaṅkamasi-cakreṣu nāhaitād dundubhe ravaḥ |
jyātala truṭanaṃ cāpe nārācānāñca kuṇṭatā ||013:031||
[na hatā duṃdubhīkhān ka, na |
hṛtāyuḥ bhīrarvāt ga; jātanākṛyta ka ga]
gadānāṃ mudgarāṇāñca śīrṇatādāya bhinnatā |
śuṣkaprarohaṇañcārkaḥ sārdrapātastathaiva ca ||013:032||
[tādyatha ga ka]
pratimārudat prasvedaṃ mṛtakānāñca jalpanam |
gavāṃ rāsabhamārohaḥ strīṇāñca bahvapatyatā ||013:033||
[rodana ka ga; sūtakānāṃ ka; rāṃsamārohaḥ ka ]
strī sute aviddāgādi ajamṛta suśobhanam |
bālānāṃ ghātanaṃ yuddho nistriṃśaḥ sakalāḥ prajā ||013:034||
[sūtehyavidyāṃgādi ajāviśruṇojanam ka; ghātagā yuddhānistriṃśāḥ ka ga]
makṣikādaṃśamuḍukā bahuśo nāśa darśanam |
nistejā dahane vahniḥ sadhūmaḥ sphuṭate muhuḥ ||013:035||
[mayūka ka; nistejā na dahedvanhiḥ ka ga]
evaṃvidhāstathotpātā dṛṣṭā ghoreṇa vāsava |
prapṛccha nāradaṃ so'pi kimetacca kṛtaṃ dvija ||013:036||
[na devyā ka ga; papraccha nāradaṃ sautaṃ kimetaddhita ka]
nārada uvāca |

śailarājaḥ kṣitidhārīḥ vāsavāṃśaḥ śivātmakaḥ |
devānāṃ tā striyaḥ kanyāḥ hiyatāmasurādhipa ||013:037||
[vāsavāṃsaḥ ka; śivātmajaḥ ka ga; śriyaḥ ka ga]
sāgnidevagaṇāstatra tenedamākulaṃ jagat |
prayāhi mātraṃ tvaṃ tiṣṭha kālo hi bahudoṣakṛt ||013:038||
[sā śrīrdeva gatā tanna tenedamā kulaṃ jagat ka ga]
tadā sa nāradenoktaḥ prayayau śīghragāmibhiḥ |
vindhyācalasya rasanā narmmadā yatra nimnagā ||013:039||
[narmadā ka ga]
yatra sā vīcikallola-kala gīta -mahotsukā |
matta mātaṃga saṃghṛṣṭa taru-parvvata-saṅkulā ||013:040||
[vīcikallolaka ga]
yatra kurarakāraṃḍa cakravākopaśobhitā |
yatra varhiṇa pārīndra kalahaṃsopanāditā ||013:041||
[vaikuravakāraṃḍa ka ga; pārendra ka ga]
rājahaṃsa mahāvāta kāla kelīvaddiddibhaiḥ |
pārāvāta śuka siddhi sārikai rūpapāṭibhiḥ ||013:042||
[śuki, sārikai, pāṭhibhiḥ ka]
nakraṃ matsya mahāgrāha makarākula codakā |
bhramarī sari carmmāra kala sairandhri vallikā ||013:043||
[matasya matsya ka; kuli todakā ka ga; bhramarāṃ śavi carmārakaṇa śairaṃdhri vallikā ka ga]
kāpaṭṭa mahāsena pāṭhina jhaṣarohitāḥ |
gahvarāḥ siṃha tuṇḍo jīvā jalajātayaḥ ||013:044||
[gaddharāsiṃha tuṃḍauṣṭha rājīva jalajābhayaḥ ka ga]
tatra gatvā mahābāho ghorasenāvatiṣṭhata |
yatrāsau bhūdharendrāṇāṃ vindhyo nāma mahāgiriḥ ||013:045||
[vaitiṣṭhatāṃ ka ga]
yatra dārita-mātaṅga-keśarī-nakha-muktibhiḥ |
yatra śūkara saṃghasya śūkarāśca bhayapradāḥ ||013:046||
[śuktibhiḥ ka ga; śūkarāśvā bhayaṃ pradāḥ ka ga]
khaḍgi-dvīpi-mahāganḍaiḥ rurū-mahiṣa-śalyakaiḥ |
tarakṣu-ṛkṣaśārddhūlaiḥ śākhāmṛga-mahāmṛgaiḥ ||013:047||
[rururohitaśallakaiḥ ka ga; rikṣu ka ga]
kṛṣnasāraiḥ sadācāraiśvavaradbhiḥ svecchayānvitaiḥ |
munidārakasaṃśaktaṃ satataṃ samidhānane ||013:048||
[saktā saktaṃ samidhānane ka]
puṣpapatra-phalāhārā kandamūla-phalāśanāḥ |
vādyamvukaṇaśākānna pakvamāṃsasamāśanāḥ ||013:049||
[puṣpapatra phalāhārāḥ skaṃdamūlaphalāśanāḥ ka ga]
veda-vedāṅga-tattvajñāstatkriyā dhyānatatparāḥ |
yogābhyāsaratā nityaṃ śiva-viṣṇu-parāyaṇāḥ ||013:050||
[parā ka]
aneka śākhaśākhāntā nivasanti tapo'rthinaḥ |
veṇu sambhava santāna sambhūtā barbbarā varāḥ ||013:051||
[śākhāntāt ka; reṇu kha; ghargharāravāḥ ga]
pulīṃdāḥ śavarātaṅkāḥ kapāli mleccha jātayaḥ |
kandamūla phalāhārāḥ yatra valkala-dhāriṇaḥ ||013:052||
[puliṃdāḥ ka ga; kapāṭā ka]
guñjābharaṇa kuṣmāḍgā mālā hārāvalamvinaḥ |
śatapatra-kṛtā voḍhā śuka-picchavibhūṣaṇāḥ ||013:053||
[kṛṣṇāṃga ka; voṭaśukapiñjavibhūṣaṇāḥ ka]
dhātu-maṇḍita-sarvāṅgā nityaṃ-mudita-mānasāḥ |
kāntāṅga krīḍanasaktāḥ karikumbha karacchidaḥ ||013:054||
[kāṃtāṃka ka ga]
nistriṃśaprasāśatṛṣṭi daṇḍamudgaradhāriṇaḥ |
vasanti yatra mātaṅgāḥ saṃghaśo dantadhāriṇaḥ ||013:055||
[sajyakodaṃḍadhāriṇaḥ ka ga]
gṛheṣu kṛta-saṃskārāḥ śākhicchāyā kṛteṣu ca |
aśoka cūta bakulamādhavī dhanabeṇuṣu ||013:056||
[nija ka ga; vakulā cūta mādhavī ka ga]
ariṣṭa biṣṭa kapālu tamālārjjuna pādapaiḥ |
praṇaṣṭa sūryyasantāpāḥ śālatālai nabhaspṛśaiḥ ||013:057||
[riṣṭa ga; kampillatmālārjuna ka; pranaṣṭa ka; saṃtāpa ka ]
iṅgudodumbara kharjjūraiḥ mātuluṅgaiḥ sadāḍimaiḥ |
phalaistṛptiṃ prapadyante bālā mātaṅga jātayaḥ ||013:058||
[kharjura ka; mālatuṅga ka ga]
pataṅgakara saṃghāta chāditāśca supūjitāḥ vasanti yatra nīraugha-mucaḥ saṃvarttakādayaḥ ||013:059||
[pataṃga kara saṃhāta grīṣmatāpa supīḍitā ka]
atha tasmin mahāśaile ghorāṇīkāvatasthire |
hayena rathapādātaṃ bahudhā samāvasata ||013:060||
[cāvakrīḍate ka; samavāsata ka]
vādyacinhakhodghuṣṭā nagnabṛnda-prapīḍibhiḥ |
ajāyata mahānādaḥ sahasā giri-pūrakaḥ ||013:061||
[dyuṣṭanagnavṛnda prapāṭhibhiḥ ka]
kandareṣu vicitreṣu nādāḥ pratīmukhāhatāḥ |
mṛgendratoṣajanakāḥ kapisainyānuvartinī ||013:062||
[prati mukhāgatāḥ ka ga; taṃ śrutvā vijayā devyācchaṃdānuvartinī ka ga]
praṇirgatā prahṛṣṭātmā vāsavāya varapradā |
vicitradāma-śobhāḍhyā bālā-bharaṇa-bhūṣitā ||013:063||
akrīḍata sā bālābhiḥ kanyakābhiḥ samāgatā |
mārkaṇḍaṛá¹ṣayāvāsaṃ pāpaughatamanāśanam ||013:064||
[kapisainyamayāpaṭṭā ga; saṃ coghatamanāśanam ka]
tatra tāmāgatāṃ dṛṣṭvā munīnāṃ sarvvasiddhidām |
ghorāharapravṛtyartha devyā hetoḥ samāgatā ||013:065||
[devī ka ga; haṃtuṃ ka]
dānavāpi tadā kṛṣṭāḥ kālapāśena vāsava |
śailendraṃ bodhayāmāsuḥ bhāsvarādyā mahābhaṭāḥ ||013:066||
[bhāsurādyāmahābhaṭāḥ ka ga]
aja pāde tathā ṛá¹kṣe dānavasya baruthinī |
sa cāśvina-prathamāhe girindramavarohayeta ||013:067||
[tadā ka; sā cākhiṇāḥ prathamāhegirīndramavabodhayet ka ga]
tadā durmmukha nāmānaṃ mahābala-parākramam |
agragaḥ sarvva sainyasya pradadau sa tu dānavaḥ ||013:068||
[agrataḥ ka ga]
tatraiva vijayā devī krīḍanāya samāgatā |
sa ca tāṃ prekṣya daityendraḥ kāmavihvalacetanaḥ ||013:069||
karaṃ prasārayed devyā devī tamavalokya ca |
gatāsuśca sa duṣṭātmā papāta dharaṇītale ||013:070||
[devyai ka ga; dhāraṇī tate ka ]
saṃdhyāyāṃ vijayā gatvā kāraṇāya nivedavet |
āgato dānavo devi mayā sa dharaṇotsukaḥ ||013:071||
[kāraṇāyāṃ kha]
yāvat kraddhvā prapaśyāmi tāvat sa vigatāsavaḥ |
tat śrutvā cintayed devī ghoro hyatra samāgataḥ ||013:072||
[taṃ smṛtvā ka]
ghātanīyo mayā duṣṭaḥ pūrva śāyena śāpitaḥ |
ghoro'pi svapnān paśyet niśānte śṛṇu vāsava ||013:073||
[svapnāt prāpaśyan]
abhyaṅgā kaṭutailena raktāmbaravibhūṣitaḥ |
kurūṃḍakusumāmoda puṣpamālābhimālitaḥ ||013:074||
[abhyaktaḥ ka ga; māliptaḥ kha]
udvāhakaraṇaṃ prekṣya pakvamatsyāmiṣāṇi ca |
nṛtyante dānavāḥ sarvve kṛṣṇavastravibhūṣaṇāḥ ||013:075||
[prekṣya pakva ka; nṛtyate ka]
kṛṣṇāyasāḥ sālaṅkārāḥ kṛṣṇa-srag-gandhya-carccitāḥ |
kṛṣṇāmvaradhara-strībhiḥ sarva-daityā vagūhitāḥ||013:076||
[sarve tehya ka ga]
ūṣṭrāruḍhaistathā pumbhiḥ pāśadaṇḍodyatairmahān |
nīyate hyavaśāḥ sarvve tuṣakeśāsthisaṅkulaiḥ ||013:077||
tamondhakāre kāntāre paṅkakūpagatāḥ pare |
śṛgālaiḥ śvabhirbhakṣyante hyapare vigatāsavaḥ ||013:078||
[tamoṃdhakāre kāṃtāre ka]
apare vāyasairgṛdhraistarakṣairvānaraiḥ paraiḥ |
evaṃvidhairmahāsattvaiḥ mahāsainyānupādrutāna ||013:079||
[sarvasainyānupādrutān kha]
dṛṣṭvā kṣubhito ghoraścharddhi mūrcchādi vihvalaḥ |
papāta śikharārūḍhastato bhairavarūpiṇī ||013:080||
[kṣubhite ghora śrūrdi mūrchrādi vihvalaḥ ka ga]
jayāpuṣpakṛtā śobhā gardabhārūḍhavāhanaḥ |
asthimālā lasadgrīvā mahāśukarānanā ||013:081||
[rāsabhārūḍha ka ga; laladgrīvā mahāśūla karānanā ka ga]
nirmāṃsā kekarākṣī kuddhakeśā bhayaṃṅkarī |
āgatya sahasā nārī pāśāṅkuśakarodyatā ||013:082||
[mayaṃkarā ka ga]
dhūmrāyamāṇā ca tathā gṛhīto'yaṃ nirāyudhaḥ |
yāmyāya tathā nītaḥ ananta patha devalaḥ |

[cābhyāna ka yāmyānanaṃ ga]
evaṃ dṛṣṭvā tadā ghoraḥ prabuddhaḥ śarvarīkṣaye |
||013:083||
ityādye śrīdevīpurāṇe ghoravadhe svapnadarśano nāma trayodaśo'dhyāyaḥ ||013:084||
[devyavatāre ka]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 014
caturdaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

indra uvāca |

evaṃvidhaistathā svapnaiḥ dṛṣṭai ghoreṇa padmaja |
prabhāte kimabhavat tasya śubhaṃ vāpyathavāśubham ||014:001||
kiṃ vā sā vāhinī tasya tathā mantri purohitau |
cakāra tat samākhyāhi kautūhalaparā vayam ||014:002||
brahmovāca |

śṛṇu vāsava tatvena vadato hyakhilaṃ mama |
utthāya sa tadā vīro devamantramanusmaran ||014:003||
tāvannaṣṭāḥ smṛtistasya mahāmohavimohitaḥ |
pratīkṣya vāsarāt paṃca tāvat-kālaḥ samāgataḥ ||014:004||
tena śrutvā hataṃ vīraṃ durmukhamarisūdanam |
śailarājendra-kanyāyā vinā kopānnirāyudhaḥ ||014:005||
tataḥ sa kālakālena prerito vadate'surān ||014:006||
kāla uvāca |

tayā nipātito vīro durmukho hyarimarddanaḥ |
tāṃ kanyāṃ kutra paśyāmi tanno vadata suvratāḥ ||014:007a-d|| yadi parvatarājendro rakṣate saha śaṃbhunā ||014:007ef||
tathāpi pratyanighnāmi yadi vā keśavo bhavet |
ityuktvā tadā kālaḥ pūrṇakālo mahābalaḥ ||014:008||
nivāritaḥ suṣeṇena mantriṇā na ca saṃsthitaḥ |
kāla-bhairava-cāmuṃḍā piṅgalākṣā mahāsurāḥ ||014:009||
[cāmuṃḍapiṃgalākhyā ka ga]
āruhya parvataṃ vīrāstarjjayaṃstāṃ ca kanyakām |
tān dṛṣṭvā uṣṭrāruḍhān kecit syandana-saṃsthitāḥ ||014:010||
jayā ca aśvamārohat gajamiva mahābalam |
kṛpāṇa pāṇinī tarjya tadā kālaṃ mahābalam ||014:011||
māyārūpaṃ surāstrajñaṃ yuddhaśāstra-viśāradam |
māyotthaṃ nirmmame siṃhaṃ gajarājabhayaṅkaram ||014:012||
[nirma ka]
mahiṣaṃ ca mahāghoraṃ yamasya iva vāhanaṃ |
bhairavaṃ taṃ samāsthāya vijayāmabhimardayet ||014:013||
yamāntakastathā raudraṃ vibhuṃ prahlāda-dundubhiḥ |
ajitāṃ mṛgamārūḍhāṃ mardayet sahasā tadā ||014:014||
vāmanairduṣṭa-lobhākṣairhālāhala-bhayaṅkaraiḥ |
daśadhā veṣṭitā devī yā sā nāmnāparājitā ||014:015||
daśadhā śatadhā caiva tathāyutāthalakṣadhā |
nigūḍhajaṃtavaḥ śakra devāḥ paśyanti śaṅkitāḥ ||014:016||
[saṃkitā ka]
tataḥkarṇika-nārāca-bhuṣuṇḍi mudgaraistathā |
vavarṣa dānavī senā devīnāṃ sahasopari ||014:017||
tadā jayā tu saṃkruddhā śarapātena pīḍitā |
prāsaṃ prakṣepayet kāle tasyāḥ siṃha nipātanam ||014:018||
taṃ prāsaghātāhata-chinnabandhaṃ nistriṃ śamādāya tadā tu kālaḥ |
carmmeṇa vāmaṃ bhuja pūrayitvā jayāmukho'dhāvata kruddha kopāt ||014:019||
dṛṣṭvā tu kālaṃ sahasā patantaṃ kṛpāṇapāṇiṃ suvivṛddha-manyum |
jayā mumocopari tasya śaktiṃ kṛpāṇa-ghātādapi tāṃ jaghāna ||014:020||
śaktiṃ hatāṃ paśya tadā jayā tu nārāca-dhārā jala vāri vāhaiḥ |
kālasya senopari sā vavarṣa kālo'pi bhinnaḥ śatavāraṇaghātaiḥ ||014:021||
[kātarāṇāṃ ghātaiḥ ga]
sa devighātāhata bhū-niṣaṇṇo labdhvā tu ceṣṭāṃ suvisrabdha cetā |
ādāya vajrāśani vajrakopaḥ khuraṃ pramumoca sutīkṣṇadhāram ||014:022||
tamāpatantaṃ tu devī śarebhyaściccheda yānyānyapi tasya moca |
ekena yānamapareṇa aśvānanyena chatraṃ sapatākadaṇḍam ||014:023||
[tu māpatam ka; tasya kha; aśvām ka]
ciccheda sā kāla mahābalasya devīṃ śaraistasya vivṛddhamanyuḥ |
tathāpi kālo gadatāṃ mumoca devīmukho dhāvituṃ sampravṛttaḥ ||014:024||
[yā ka; gadayā ka ga; dhāvati kha]
cakreṇa taṃ kāla bhaṭasya taṃtaṃ devī vimuktena gatā svabhūmau |
kālaṃ hataṃ bhairava sannirīkṣya niṣaṇṇamṛtyuḥ sa vivṛddhamanyuḥ ||014:025||
[gadā sva bhūmau kha]
gadāṃ samādāya jayāṃ pravṛttaḥ kharapraghātādapi so gatāyuḥ |
evaṃ sa kālo hata-bhairavañca cāmuṇḍapiṃgākṣa mahābalaśca ||014:026||
[ kaurava ka ga; sukhadaprabhātāvapi kha; bhairavasya ga ]
māyāvino mattamataṅgarūpā devyā samāsādya jvalantakopāḥ |
te devi vāṇāśani bhinnarakṣā gatāsavaḥ pretapathaṃ prayātāḥ ||014:027||
[bhinnarūpā ga; prayāti ga]
evaṃ hate kālabale aśeṣe devā mumocopari puṣpavṛṣṭim |
meghāśca śītojvalavārivindūn vātā vavāhāpi divyagandhāḥ ||014:028||
nṛtyanti vidyādhara-siddha-saṃghā mahāpsarā-kinnara-cāraṇāśca |
||014:029||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe devyavatāre kālavadhonāma caturdaśo'dhyāyaḥ
[iti devyavatāre kālavadhaḥ ga]
%%%
caturdaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

