śaktiṃ hatāṃ paśya tadā jayā tu nārāca-dhārā jala vāri vāhaiḥ |
kālasya senopari sā vavarṣa kālo'pi bhinnaḥ śatavāraṇaghātaiḥ ||014:021||
[kātarāṇāṃ ghātaiḥ ga]
sa devighātāhata bhū-niṣaṇṇo labdhvā tu ceṣṭāṃ suvisrabdha cetā |
ādāya vajrāśani vajrakopaḥ khuraṃ pramumoca sutīkṣṇadhāram ||014:022||
tamāpatantaṃ tu devī śarebhyaściccheda yānyānyapi tasya moca |
ekena yānamapareṇa aśvānanyena chatraṃ sapatākadaṇḍam ||014:023||
[tu māpatam ka; tasya kha; aśvām ka]
ciccheda sā kāla mahābalasya devīṃ śaraistasya vivṛddhamanyuḥ |
tathāpi kālo gadatāṃ mumoca devīmukho dhāvituṃ sampravṛttaḥ ||014:024||
[yā ka; gadayā ka ga; dhāvati kha]
cakreṇa taṃ kāla bhaṭasya taṃtaṃ devī vimuktena gatā svabhūmau |
kālaṃ hataṃ bhairava sannirīkṣya niṣaṇṇamṛtyuḥ sa vivṛddhamanyuḥ ||014:025||
[gadā sva bhūmau kha]
gadāṃ samādāya jayāṃ pravṛttaḥ kharapraghātādapi so gatāyuḥ |
evaṃ sa kālo hata-bhairavañca cāmuṇḍapiṃgākṣa mahābalaśca ||014:026||
[ kaurava ka ga; sukhadaprabhātāvapi kha; bhairavasya ga ]
māyāvino mattamataṅgarūpā devyā samāsādya jvalantakopāḥ |
te devi vāṇāśani bhinnarakṣā gatāsavaḥ pretapathaṃ prayātāḥ ||014:027||
[bhinnarūpā ga; prayāti ga]
evaṃ hate kālabale aśeṣe devā mumocopari puṣpavṛṣṭim |
meghāśca śītojvalavārivindūn vātā vavāhāpi divyagandhāḥ ||014:028||
nṛtyanti vidyādhara-siddha-saṃghā mahāpsarā-kinnara-cāraṇāśca |
||014:029||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe devyavatāre kālavadhonāma caturdaśo'dhyāyaḥ
%%%[iti devyavatāre kālavadhaḥ ga]
%%%%
Chapter 015
pañcadaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

hate kāle kālabala prabhāve suhṛṣṭa devāḥ saha vāsavena |
ghorasya patnī vimanā viṣaṇṇā dṛṣṭvā tu śakra stuvate tu devīm ||015:001||
[kāle hate ka ga; prabhave ka; sureṇa kha; vimānāṃ ka; tanuvate tudevyāṃ kha]
śakra uvāca |

jaya jaya surāṇāṃ paritrāṇabhūte mahāhare saṅgarasupratāpe |
samasta bhītān parirakṣaṇāya tvāṃ devīṃ muktvā aparo na cāsti ||015:002||
[paritrāṇa bhṛt ka ga; mahāhara saṃga vastu prabhāte ka |
mahodara saṃgarasuprabhāte ga]
mahābalaṃ ghorabalaṃ pradhānaṃ yamasya vahnera'pi saṃcitāram |
vayaṃ sabrāhmaṇāḥ savāyuyakṣāstvayā punardevi divaṃ niviṣṭāḥ ||015:003||
sarve'pi bhītā bhavatīṃ praṇamya bhayebhya muñcantyavicāraṇena |
mahārṇave siṃha-gajābhi bhūtāstvāmāśritā vītabhayā bhavanti ||015:004||
jvālaughakālānala-sampravṛddhaṃ yaṃ brahmaviṣṇorapi mohakarttā |
taṃ prekṣya devī sahasā mahāntaṃ samaṃ gataṃ prāvṛṣiṇeva pāṃśu ||015:005||
yaṃ dundubhiḥ brahmajanārddanaiśca na nirjjitaṃ bhāskara-vāyu-yakṣaiḥ |
jalesarakṣaiḥ sahasā vibheti taṃ devī dṛṣṭvā bhasmīprayātam ||015:006||
[kṣeja ka]
tvaṃ bhūmi vāyu kha jalaṃ hutāśaṃ diśo divaṃ sāgara ṛkṣacakram |
yāṃ sarvvadevāḥ satataṃ namanti tāṃ devadevīṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi ||015:007||
yāṃ dhyānayogairapi yogaśavatyā dhyāyanti nityaṃ paratattva devīm |
vedānta vādī satataṃ ca kṛtsnāṃ yāṃ yājino nityamaśveṣu yajvāḥ ||015:008||
[saktā ga; devīṃ kha; vedī ga; vadanti kha]
yāṃ sāṃkhyayogaiḥ sapatañjalākhyaiḥ siddhānta-mantrairapi mantravādī |
yā ḍākinī bhūtagrahaiḥ praśastān sattvān samastānapi mocayeti ||015:009||
[sāṃkhyayogaurapi yoga saktādhyāyaṃti sapataṃ jākhyaiḥ ka]
na cādirasya na ca madhyamantaṃ na rūpakāntirna ca stotramanyat |
yāṃ śaṃṅkaraḥ sarvvagato'pi satauti tāṃ devadevīṃ śaraṇaṃ prapadye ||015:010||
evaṃ tāṃ toṣayāñcakre jayāṃ kālanivarhaṇām |
pradadau sā varaṃ tasya devarājasya vāsava ||015:011||
[nivarhaṇīṃ ka ga; ca ka ga]
idaṃ ghorabalaṃ hatvā bhūyo'pi surasattamaḥ |
tava puṣṭiṃ kariṣyāmi sarvvakālaṃ purandara ||015:012||
[iṣṭa ga]
yo hyetadvijayā stotraṃ bhaktitaḥ sampaṭhiṣyati |
praṇaṣṭa-rājyadravyāṇi punareva labhiṣyati ||015:013||
brahmovāca |

śrutvā hataṃ tadā kālaṃ bhairavaṃ piṅgalam |
vajradaṇḍastadā kruddho devyā yoddhuṃ vyadhāvata ||015:014||
[saha bhairavapigaṃlāṃ ga]
pāśa-mudgaradaṇḍābja kunta-bāṇa-kṛpāṇabhṛt |
vavarṣa sahasā bajraḥ prāvṛṇmegha ivāmvubhiḥ ||015:015||
na diśo na tadākāśaṃ na ca bhūvāyugocaram |
lakṣyate bāṇadhārodhairvajradaṇḍamahādhvanaiḥ ||015:016||
[yamauvaram ga]
devyā dhanuṣi vajreṇa śarāḥ pañcāśat preritāḥ |
tairvividhya dhanurdevyā kopānala-sudīpitā ||015:017||
vimokṣe vāruṇaṃ śastraṃ mahāmegha-samaprabham |
taṃ nadantaṃ mahāghoraṃ vidyutpūrvvāṃ diśo daśa ||015:018||
[vāruṇamastraṃ ga]
vavarṣa plavate sarbvā dānavīṃ vāhinīṃ tadā |
taṃ dṛṣṭvā vajradaṇḍedaṃ mahāmāyā-samudbhavam |
vāyuṃ mumoca meghānāṃ tena te śamitā ghanāḥ ||015:019||
dṛṣṭvā ghanān vajrānilena śāntān devī tadā krodhavivṛddhamanyuḥ |
meghādrimālā iva droṇatulyān sabhūdharān sarvvadiśo vicikṣipe ||015:020||
taṃ vāyuśastraṃ sahasā nirudhya vajrāśaniṃ rvāṇa-śilā vavarṣaiḥ |
hatvā tadaśvān yadarakṣarakṣam saṃsārathiṃ chatra dharaṃ ca daṇḍam ||015:021||
jighāṃsa vajraṃ vala-vajra-vīryyam śareṇa hemadala patritena |
hatantu vajraṃ sahasā ca dṛṣṭvā yamāntako yatra jayā jayantam ||015:022||
mumoca vāṇān sahasā sakopāt devyāhataḥ so'pi paraṃ prayāti yamāntakaḥ pretapathaṃ mahāntam ||015:023||
[prayātaḥ ka]
iti devyavatāre śrīdevīpurāṇe vajravadhonāma pañcadaśo'dhyāya
[ityādye devyavatāre vajradaṇḍavadhaḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 016
ṣoḍaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

hate vajre mahāvīre hate cāpi yamāntake |
ghorasenārdditā bhūtā hatavīryyaparākramā ||016:001||
tān dṛṣṭvā nihatān vīrān suṣeṇaḥ pratyabhāṣata |
mayā tvaṃ deva-devānāṃ buddhimadbhyoṣiko mataḥ |
yena pūrvva suraḥ svāmī acyutaḥ paritoṣitaḥ ||016:002||
yaḥ samaḥ sarvvabhūteṣu sthāvareṣu careṣu ca |
rājya-madotsekānna vikāraḥ pravarddhitaḥ ||016:003||
yasya mātṛsamāḥ sarvvāḥ paradārāḥ snuṣā iva |
yasya kāñcanaloṣṭānāṃ viśeṣo nopalabhyate ||016:004||
yasya śabdādayo bhāvā na bādhante manāgapi |
yasya kāmajakrodhādirna gaṇo viśate tanum ||016:005||
yasya durgāṣṭakārambhe nityañca karuṇodayam(FN) |
yasya vyūha-kriyāṃ bhāvamaṇḍalaṃ tattvaveditā ||016:006||
[ga pustake nāsti śloko'yaṃ]
pratyakṣaṃ varttate nityaṃ karasyamapidhātrijam |
yasya kari mahāgandhā madamattā na rāṣṭrajāḥ ||016:007||
yasya hārakadaṇḍāni chatreṣu na jane kvacit |
yasya ghātā aśvoṣṭreṣu na pure na ca kheṭake ||016:008||
yasya bhūtāḥ priyākope kārmmukāṇāmÌ na vigrahe |
yasya cādhvarayajñeṣu cāśrupāto na śokajaḥ ||016:009||
yasya śakti kṛpāṇeṣu kalaṅko na ca bhīkṛtaḥ |
yasya svapna prabhā mithyā na ca vaktavyayājane ||016:010||
yasya vāle mukhābhaṅgī na ca krodhāt bhayātkvacit |
evaṃ vidhasya te deva sarvvaśāstravidasya ca ||016:011||
[vāṇeṣu jyābhaṃgo ga]
āpado yā viśantīgāstanmahadadbhutaṃ ripuḥ |
yāvadyāvat samādhāya ghoro mantrī pracakrame ||016:012||
[viśaṃtye hatamahatpadbhutaṃviduḥ ka; samavāya ka; pracamet ka]
tāvannārada āyāto viṣṇubrahmeśapreṣitaḥ |
yatra sā paramā devī trayāṇāmapi kāraṇā ||016:013||
niṣkalā śāntidānantā munīnāṃ trāṇadharmiṇī |
sthitā sā vastrarūpeṇa jayā dyau śambhurājñayā ||016:014||
[dāśāṃtāmanana ka]
tāñca kṛtsnāṃ tadā dhyātvā nāradastattvavinmahān |
durvvijñeyāṃ mahādevīṃ mantranāmaistutoṣa saḥ ||016:015||
|| nārada uvāca |
|
jaya śambhunute devī jaya rudratanūdbhave |
jaya keśava brahmeśa utpattisthiti kāraki ||016:016||
jaya-saṃhāra kārāya rudradehabhavāya ca |
jaya parārtha bhāveśi jaya vāgeśi maṅgale ||016:017||
[parārddha ka]
jaye sarvva mate māte jaya nāmavarapreda |
sarvvage sarvvanāmebhyaḥ prasīda mama śaṅkarī ||016:018||
nāmānyudīrayiṣyāmi yāni te prathitaṃ triṣu |
yaistu nāmaiḥ sadā loke atraivamanugīyase ||016:019||
durgā śākambharī gaurī varadā vindhyavāsinī |
kātyāyanī suprasādā kauśikī kaiṭabheśvarī ||016:020||
mahādevī mahābhāgā mahāśvetā maheśvarī |
tridaśā vandinīśānī bhavānī bhūtabhāvinī ||016:021||
jyeṣṭhā ṣaṣṭhī tamoniṣṭhā brahmiṣṭhā brahmavādinī |
aparṇā caikapāpā ca suparṇā caikapāṭalā ||016:022||
[brahmane brahma cāriṇī ka ga]
trilokadhātrī sāvitrī gāyatrī tridaśārccitā |
triśūlinī trinayanā tripadā triguṇātmikā ||016:023||
śraddhā svāhā svadhā medhā lakṣmīḥ kānti kṣamāvatī |
vṛddhi samṛddhi rbuddhiśca śuddhi saṃśuddhireva ca ||016:024||
[śāntiḥ ka ga; siddhi ka]
sarvvajñā sarvvatobhadrā sarvvatokṣi śiromukhī |
sarvvabhūtādimadhyāntā sarvvalokeśvareśvarī ||016:025||
mānavī yādavī devī yoganidrātha vaiṣṇavī |
arupā bahurūpā ca surupā kāmarupiṇī ||016:026||
śailarājasutā sādhvī skandamātācyutasvasā |
jayā ca vijayā devī ajitā aparājitā ||016:027||
[cyutambarā kha]
śrutiḥ smṛtiḥ dhṛtiḥ kṣāntiḥ śaktiḥ śāntirathonnatiḥ |
prakṛtiḥ vikṛtiḥ kīrtiḥ sthitiḥ santatireva ca ||016:028||
kālarātri mahārātri bhadrakālī kapālinī |
cāmuṇḍā caṇḍinī caṇḍī cāmuṇḍavināśinī ||016:029||
[caṃḍā śikhaṃḍinī ka ga]
rudrāṇī pārvvatīndrāṇī śaṃkarārddhaśarīriṇī |
dīkṣā dākṣāyaṇī caiva nārī nārāyaṇī tathā ||016:030||
niśumbha-śumbhadamanī mahiṣāsuraghātinī |
sahasranayanā dhorā revatī siṃhavāhinī ||016:031||
[yudhinī ka; vīrā ka ga]
viśvāvatī vīryyavatī vedamātā sarasvatī |
māyāvatī bhogavatī satī satyavatī tathā ||016:032||
[devamātā ka ga; bhagavatī ka ga]
samasta kāryakaraṇī īpsitārtha-prasādhako |
vrajāmi śaraṇaṃ devīṃ śaraṇāgatavatsalām ||016:033||
bhīmāmugrāṃ tathā dhūmrāmambikāṃ tryambaka-priyām |
tvaṃ hī bhāvaprapannānāṃ hṛdisthā pāpanāśinī ||016:034||
[pādaśanī ka]
jayañca samare nityaṃ vidyālābhañca durlabham |
dīrghamāyurayotsāhaṃ pārthivānāñca icchatām ||016:035||
putrāśca guṇasampannāḥ parāpara parāgatiḥ |
tvayā hyetāni prārthyante mamāpi varadā bhava ||016:036||
evaṃ stutā tato devī nāradena mahātmanā |
dadarśa sahasā śakra siṃhārūḍhāṃ mahāvalām ||016:037||
carmmāsi-dhanu-nārāca-śūla-khaṭvāṅgadhāriṇīm |
vajra-śakti-gadādaṇḍa-paśu-mudgara-vibhratī ||016:038||
pāśāṅkuśa-dhvaja-vīṇā-ghaṇṭā-ḍamarū-dhāriṇī |
citra daṇḍā tathā muṇḍa kanakābhedīnī tathā ||016:039||
dvipārdra carmma sā raudra śailakṛtaścāriṇī |
akṣa sūtra karā devī varadodyata-pāṇinī ||016:040||
[hutabhugdhāriṇī ka ga]
bhaktānāṃ bhakti-jananī pāvanī jananī tathā |
yāca yācetī vācantī varaṃ bruhya manogatam ||016:041||
[manonugāṃ ka]
tataḥ sa praṇataṃ uce ghoraṃ deva-ripuṃ vadha |
tathetī nāradamuktvā tāvad ghoraḥ samāgataḥ ||016:042||
|| iti śrī devyavatāre devīpurāṇe devyānāradadarśanaṃ nāma ṣoḍaśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
%%%%
%%% Chapter 017
saptadaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

indra uvāca |

nāradasya varaṃ datte ghore tatra samāgate |
kimakurvvad bhagavatī kiṃ vā ghoro mahāvalaḥ ||017:001||
[kiṃ kurvadbhavatī tatrakiṃ vā ghoro mahāvalaḥ ka]
kiñca loka pramāṇantu hataśeṣasya no vada |
evaṃ pṛṣṭastadā brahmā aśeṣaṃ vāsavena tu ||017:002||
[kiṃ balaṃ ka ga]
vimṛṣya kathyate sarva devyā ghoraṃ mahāraṇam |
yadidaṃ pṛcchase śakra devyā ghorasya saṅgaram ||017:003||
[kiṃ balaṃ ka ga]
brahmovāca |

taṃ bravīmi yathāvṛttaṃ pratyekaṃ na tu vāhinī |
varṇituṃ śakyate śakra samairgranthibhiḥ koṭibhiḥ ||017:004||
tathāpi kiñcit saṃkṣepāt kathayāmi surādhipaḥ |
rathānāṃ koṭayastriṃśat saptalakṣāstathāyutam ||017:005||
koṭiśatāni pañcāśad gajānāṃ saptatistathā |
lakṣāyuta sahasrāṇi ṣaṣṭiḥ pañcādhikā vibho ||017:006||
koṭi lakṣāṇi cāśvānāṃ paṃca paṃcāśad vāsava |
lakṣā dvātriṃśat pañcāśat sahasraparisaṃkhyayā ||017:007||
[koṭi lakṣāṇi cāśvānāṃ paṃca paṃcāśadvāsava ka ga]
lakṣā dvāsaptatiḥ śakra tathāyutatrayaṃ trayam |
hataśeṣantu ghorasya tiṣṭhate'marapuṅgavaḥ ||017:008||
ghātitaṃ dviguṇametajjayā vijayāsaṅgare ||017:009||
yamāntakastathā kāla durmukhaâvajraâbhairavaiḥ |
svayante ghātitaṃ devyā mahākālyā hyanekaśaḥ ||017:010||
śakra uvāca |

hataśeṣabalo brahman ghoro ghoraâparākramaḥ |
bhīto vā prāṇarakṣārthaṃ kiṃ vā yuddhamanonugaḥ ||017:011||
brahmovāca |

hataśeṣabalaḥ śakra ghoraḥ krodhāgni-dīpitaḥ |
cakāra māyayā senāṃ hatāhatasahasradhā ||017:012||
tāṃ ghoraâmāyāmanubhūtabhūtāṃ senā yayau vāsava sapta lokān |
bhūmyantarīkṣān sahasapta dvīpān pātāla lokāntaravyāpta mārgān ||017:013||
[sadvīpa ka ga]
viṣṇuṃ samasteśaâsureśaâvandyaṃ śakraṃ mahāmattaâmataṅgaâyānam |
rakṣo'nalaṃ vāyuṃ tathā kuberamīśañca rudraṃ jagadīśitāram ||017:014||
somaṃ raviṃ dīptavatāṃ variṣṭhaṃ rudrān samastān hyatha viśvadevān |
ṛkṣān grahān nāgaâsusiddhaâsaṅghān vidyādharān kinnarabhūta-pitṛn ||017:015||
sarvān samastānapi pīḍayitvā devyastathā ghātayituṃ pravṛttaḥ |
tāṃ ghoraâmāyāâmatiâmugdhaâcetāḥ śambhustathā rsasmarate parāṃ tām ||017:016||
[mabhi ka; dugdha ka]
īśvara uvāca |

jayaâjaya harihara kamalāsanābhyarccite namo devī śive śambhu vaktrodbhave |
caṇḍa rūpe suvaktre sunetre sugātre suveśe suvimvādharoṣṭhi mahāyogini barhiṇīva ||017:017||
[arccite devimāte; rūpe svarūpe ka ga; suveśe sukeśe ka ga]
piṃcchadhvaje tuhinakaraâkumudakundenduâsavarṇābhiratyantatīkṣṇābhirdaṃṣṭrābhiḥ saṃdṛśyate |
bhairavī bhīṣaṇī vīrabhadre subhadre śmaśānapriye padmapatrekṣaṇe ghora rūpe ||017:018||
[padmavaktre ka]
jayantī jaye mānasi mānavi martyamāte mṛgendradhvaje sarvvasiddhiprade |
jalanidhi varadundurbhi rmeghanirghoṣa hāsasvane ||017:019||
[nirghoṣa mahāsure ka ga]
brāhmi kaumāri māhendri māheśvari vaiṣṇavi vārāhi vāyuragnyātmaje |
hemakūṭe mahendre himādrau mahīdhāriṇi vindhyasahyālaye śrī girau saṃsthite ||017:020||
hrasva dīrghaiḥ kṛśaiḥ sthūlalambodaraistālajaṅghai rmahābhairavaiḥ pramathalakṣaṇairvṛte |
dinakaraâkoṭi kalpāntara vahniprabhe hemavarṇe suvarṇe ratiâprīti dakṣe ||017:021||
[jaṅghaiḥ ka ga; rakṣe ka]
matiâśāntiâlakṣmīâdhṛtiâṛddhiâdyutiâsiddhiâbuddhiâkṛtiâtuṣṭiâpuṣṭiâsthiti |
sṛṣṭiâvṛṣṭiâpriye vedaâmāte kṛtajñe kumāri dhruve śāśvati tāpasi sāṃkhyayogodbhave ||017:022||
[gati ka]
viṣadharahala-mūsala-paraśu-pāṣāsi-cakrāvja-khaṭavāṅga-daṇḍāṃkuśānekaśastrodyate |
śūlākṣasūtradhanurddhāriṇī daityavidrāvaṇi hāriṇī dhāriṇī bandhani mokṣaṇi ||017:023||
duritāni(FN) māraṇi kīrtivistāriṇī dīpti sañjīvanī bhedanī tāpani |
śuṣkamūrdhe ume caṇḍike bhīma vaktrāmbuje tripuradahane harasyārddha sthite ||017:024||
[sādhakāṃstaraṇī kha pustake nāsti; saṃjīvanī chedanī ka; deha ka]
vidyudulkāmukhi kṛṣṇamūrdhe navamyaṣṭamī pañcamī paurṇamāsi caturthī tathaikādaśī kṛṣṇapakṣotsave |
indranīlai rmahānīla-muktā phalaiḥ padmarāgaiḥ sphaṭikairmaṇi-marakatairvajravaiḍūryyacāmīkarālaṅkṛte ||017:025||
nūpuraiḥ kuṇḍalairmukuṭa-keyūra-hāra-dyuti-vibhūṣite hemaratnojjavale valkala nīla kauśeya pītāmbare |
kanaka-kalaśa tulyena pīnonnatenātiramyeṇa hemāṃśu jālograniṣpīḍitena stanenorasā madhye ||017:026||
[cīrāmbare ka]
tanvaḍgayaṣṭā nitambasthale nābhiṃ samavarddhanenāmbike tryambake nṛtyamānāsadā śobhase |
vara-vṛṣabha-haṃsa-mātaṅga-nīla-gati-gāmini-meru sañcārinisāgarān śoṣaṇi parvatān pūrvān ||017:027||
[sadvarttulenāvike ka ga; netramānā ka]
kadru sāvitrīṃ gāyatrīṃ dhātrīṃ vidhātrīṃ ditimvīkṣya māyā jitendriyasya vidrāvaṇī brāhmi vetāli |
kaṅkālikā kapālini bhadrakāli mahākāli kālānale kalikāle kale niṣkale ||017:028||
jaya jaya maṅgalodghuṣṭarāve dhāriṇibhirmahī siddhasaṅghaiḥ suśabdaiḥ sahāyaiḥ susannaddha tvaṅgaiḥ |
vimānaiśca divyairgajendrai sunīlaisturaṅgaiḥ suvegaiḥ sitaiścātapatraiśca saṃchādite ambare ||017:029||
[mahā ka; ghuṣṭarāradhva nimirmahāsiddha saṃṅkhaiḥsusaṅghai suśabdaiḥ ka; svasamvaddha ka ga; vardvaiḥ ka; taraṃgaiḥ ka]
raktamaule gaṇairdeva daityendra yakṣāpsarairvandibhiḥ stūyase lolajihvairlaladugra keśaiḥ śaraṇye varaṇye |

[amūrevalgamānairgaṇai dervi ka]
mahārukṣa ghaṇṭā ravodgīta karṇotsave veṇū-vīṇā-dhvani-stotra-vāditra-gandharva-nityapriye ||017:030||
[mahārukta; ghaṃṭāvarod gīta ka; cārukarṇotsa ve ka ga; nityapriye kha]
kṛtabhujagavara kuṇḍaloddhṛṣṭa gaṇḍadvaye sarvvabhūtālaye sarvvabhūtottame (FN)| gauri gāndhāri mātaṅgi dhūmeśvari dharmmaketū dakṣavidhvaṃsini mahiṣa mṛtyuprade ||017:031||
[kṛtya bhujaṃgavara ka; ka pustake nāsti; pade ka]
śumbha niśumbhanī mohinī dīpani varṣaṇi revati kālakarṇī sukīrṇi jagat sṛṣṭi saṃsārakartrī |
yogeśvari sarvvalokeśvari khecari gocari caṇḍi mātaṅgi dhūmre śaśāṅkānale girivaratanaye ||017:032||
[viyogeśvarī ka ga]
vare mantra mūrti mahāmūrtye digvyāpini suprasanne prasannārcite suvrate |
gotami kauśaki pārvvati bhūtavetāli kātyāyani ṛgyajuḥ sāmātharvvapriye devī nitye ||017:033||
[mahāmūrti ka ga; bhūtāni kha; ṛá¹gyajuḥ ka]
śubhe bhīṃmanāde mahāvāyuvege sarasvatyarundhatyamoghe asaṃkhyāta bāhūdare'nekavaktrai |
vividhaâmṛtyuâmārīti śākambharī śailaśṛṅgeṣu śailaśṛṅgeṣu tuṅgeṣu nityam vata kandaravāsini bhīmasaṅge nityaṃ tvamevocyase ||017:034||
[mārīca ka ga; rate ka ga; bhīmasaṃjñoti ka]
kuvalayādala nīla lolā lasaiḥ locanaiḥ snehayukte, śatākṣepavaktrā mbujodbhāsibhiḥ kālanirṇāśini |
ma sandīpani sādhakālokāni svargaâpātāla-mokṣa-prade, cakravartiprade śrīdhare putravat paśya mām ||017:035||
[lola līlā ka ga; sneha digdhaiḥ ka; sitaisūlatākṣe ka]
darbharomāgni jihve triguṇe prameye tvamevodadhivīci bhānauḥsuṣumnā īḍā piṅgalā saumanāḍī tu sautrāmanīṃ kiṅkiṇī caṇḍī nirghoṣajuṣṭā ||017:036||
tvamevoṣadhī kālanirṇāśanī jāhṇavī tvaṃ jaṭābhirbhayā dhāriṇī gambhīraghorasvane |
sarṣva śastrodyate sarvvadevairvṛte rakṣa rakṣasva māṃ divyamālyāmbare divyagandhānulipte ||017:037||
dhārya tārāha mṛtā satyavādityajātā jitā krodhanāvameva krodhaniṣṭhā |
vibhutyāhūtī kālarātrī śacī kāmarūpī svadhāveśinī vidhna nirṇāśanī khyātirnārāyaṇī ||017:038||
[tvamevāryya bhāvā ka; krodhaniṣṭhā ka ga; sudhāveśanī ka]
kṛṣṇa piṅga pragalbhānilabhrāmaṇī devadaityendrarakṣoragaiḥ kinnaraiḥ |
yakṣa gandharvva vidyādharai rvandite munivaraiḥ saṃstute bhagavatī tava kīrti nāmucyate ||017:039||
kālapāśe rnivaddhaṃ surendraiśca nīṃtamṛṣīndraiśca śaptaṃ mṛgendraigṛhītaṃ gajendrai rvibhinnaṃ grahendrābhibhūtam |
khagendrairviluptaṃ bhujaṅgaiśca daṣṭaṃ jale vāpi magnaṃ sthale vāpi khinnaṃ vane vāpi mūḍhaṃ raṇe śarairbhinnadeham ||017:040||
paraiḥ samsukhasya vivāde nirastaṃ mahāgrāhagrastaṃ tathārādhyamānantu māteva saṃrakṣase putravannityaśaḥ |
vidhakalikaluṣapāpādhiye mānavāste'pi sañcintya devī tvadīyaṃ mukhaṃ pūrṇacandraprabham ||017:041||
[saṃpratasthaṃ ka; siṃcitva]
soma sūryāgninetra pradyotita kuṇḍalairlolasaṃghṛṣṭagaṃḍadvaye te'pi pāpān prabhuñcati |
saṃsāraghorārṇave majjamānāṃstathā śatrumadhyagatān yānapātrasthitān śṛṃṅkhalairveṣṭitān taskarairāvṛtān ||017:042||
[saṃsāra ghorāṃtare ka ga; kṣutpipāsārditān vṛkṣasāyāgatān yaṃtrasaṃpītān ka]
trāsi sarvvān sadevān sarakṣān sagandharvaṃ nāgān savidyādharān sāśvinān |
sagrahān sapta pātālabhūrloka divyāntarīkṣasthitān nātra kuryyād vikalpaṃ mahadevī sañcintya tvām ||017:043||
[sarākṣan ka]
caṇḍike śivapuravaramārga sopānametanmahādaṇḍakaṃ śivakṛtaṃ ghoranikṛntaṃ pāpanirṇāśanaṃ sarvvakāmapradam |
nāmabhiśchāndasaiḥ sādhakānāṃ hitārthāya saṃkṣepataḥ kīrtitaṃ sāramuddhṛtya daghnājyamiva sarvadā ||017:044||
[saṃyogataḥ ka]
ye paṭhanti sadā bhaktyā teṣu vakṣāmyahaṃ śṛṇu (FN)| vājapeyāśvamedhāgniṣṭoma godānādikaṃ tathā ||017:045||
[paṭhante ka; ga pustake nāsti; medhānala ka]
ṛk sopānādikaṃ yajña puṇyaṃ labhyate tathā(FN) bhūtale yāni tīrthāni cānyāni vā |
teṣu tīrtheṣu devārccana-snāna-homopavāsa-stuti-dānaṃ puṇyaṃ vrataṃ sarvvametat phalam ||017:046||
[labhante ka ga; ka pustake nāsti; purā yāni ka]
yaḥ paṭhet daṇḍakai rdaṇḍakenāpi siddho divi krīḍate brahmāviṣṇvindra lokotta maiḥ |
divyayānairmahākalpakoṭi sahasrāṇi siddhairvṛtaḥ sādhakaḥ ||017:047||
taru vinipātakāle vrajatyagni kālāgni rudraṃ śataṃ nārakaṃ viṃśatiścāṣṭa koṭi sametam |
tathā bhūrbhūvaḥ svamaharjanastapaḥ satyaṃ lokāntikaṃ brahmaṇoṃ'ḍaṃ vinirmadya rudrān ||017:048||
[ruddhā ka]
dvi pañcāśat saṃkhyāstathā toya-tejo-nīlākāśa guhyāṣṭakam |
aṣṭaṣaṣṭhimatikramyat prākṛtaṃ pauruṣaṃ niyatikālaṃ samagraṃ savidadeśvaḥ ||017:049||
cakrarti śaktikalāṃ vāpi sūkṣmāṃ tyajitvā brajante paraṃ yatra nityam |
padaṃ sarvvabhūtottamaṃ sarvvagaṃ niṣphalaṃ dhyānahīnaṃ viśante sadā ||017:050||
[samāpaṃ savidyarevaraṃ cakravartti sva śakti ka ga]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe ghoravadhe śivakṛto devīstavo nāma saptadaśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye devyavatāre ghoravadhe devyāstavaḥ ka ga]
