%%% Chapter 018
aṣṭadaśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

stutā hyevaṃ purā devī devadevena śambhunā |
hitāya viṣṇuśakrāṇāmanyeṣāmapi devatām ||018:001||
[raktatā ka]
tanmāyā tamasācchannamaśeṣaṃ sacarācaram |
udyotitaṃ kṣaṇenaiva bhānunā tadyathā divam ||018:002||
[udyotayan ka; tu ka]
pravṛddhi śakti saṃrambhāḥ sarvve devāḥ savāsavāḥ |
vavarṣu puṣpamālābhirbhavānyāścaraṇāmbuje ||018:003||
[pravuddha ka ga]
atha taṃ danupatiṃ ghora prāvṛṭkāla ghanopamam |
mardayan vihasan devī sutīkṣṇairniśitaiḥ śarai ||018:004||
[taṃ tattu rārti ka; arddayan visahaṃ ka; sva ka]
ardditā śaravarṣeṇa dānavasya tu vāhinī |
devī-kara-vimuktena lāghavena balena ca ||018:005||
niśceṣṭaṃ dānavaṃ sainyaṃ tadā hyāsīt purandara |
evaṃ kātyāyanīṃ vāṇairniṣprabhaṃ ghorajaṃ balam ||018:006||
cakrāviddhaṃ na lakṣyet dānavairvigataujasaiḥ |
suṣeṇastu tadā kruddho manyumāsthāya vāsava ||018:007||
māyāgajaâsamūhantu cakāra madavihvalam |
tānnāgānmadagandhyādairbalivṛndairniṣevitām ||018:008||
[madagaṃdhādaiḥ kha]
codayāmāsa divyāyā jayāyāmasurottamaḥ |
jayāpi dānavaṃ vīkṣya siṃhamāroha bhāsvaram ||018:009||
[bhāsuram ga]
gajān vimarddayet sarvvān viśīrṇā iva diggajāḥ |
gajasainye hate śakra dānavaḥ suradarpahā ||018:010||
ādāya tarasā khaṅgaṃ jayāyāḥ siṃhaghātakam |
atha siṃhe hate devī kauśikoparisaṃsthitā ||018:011||
suṣeṇasya śiraśchedaṃ rathāṅgena tu vāsava ||018:012||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe suṣeṇavadho nāmāṣṭādaśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye devyavatāre suṣeṇavadhaḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 019
ekonaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

hate tasmin mahādaitye dānavasya varūthinī |
nalinī himapātena śamiteva vibhāvyate ||019:001||
[mahāmāye ka mahāmātye ga]
suṣeṇe nihate śakra daiteyaḥ suramarddakaḥ |
suṣeṇa-sadṛśān yodhān māyotthāṃ cakrire bahūn ||019:002||
ajāâvivadanān ghorān siṃha-śūkara ānanān |
gajāśvarathamārūḍhān carmmakhaḍgakarodyatān ||019:003||
te sarvve ajitāṃ yoddhuṃ mahābalaâparākramāḥ |
makarasthāṃ pāśahastāṃ danḍāṃkuśakarodyatām ||019:004||
te dṛṣṭvā ajitāṃ sarvve na vibhyathu manāgapi |
atha taiḥ kalakalārāvaṃ kṛtvā devī viceṣṭitām ||019:005||
[tathā ga]
daśadhā śatadhā śakra tathā hmayutaâkoṭidhā |
devyā śarāsanaṃ cakaṃ cicchedurdanusattamāḥ ||019:006||
vimoca śara jālāni devī sarve hmuṃ padrutā |
sampīḍitavalān dṛṣṭvā tṛtīyāñcāparājitām ||019:007||
[mumoca ka ga]
śamituṃ śaravarṣeṇa dānavānāṃ bhayaṅkarīm |
ghoramāyāsamutthānāṃ vāhinī yamapanthagā ||019:008||
[śametum ka ga]
prayātā dānavī śakraâgajāśvaâbhaṭa pattiṣu |
nahi saṃkhyā tadā hyāsīt dvividhāsu balāsu ca ||019:009||
hatasenastadā ghoro bahumāyi purandaraḥ |
indraâcandrārkaṃâviṣṇūnāṃ rūpāṇi bahudhāsṛjat ||019:010||
candraṃ cakreṇa sampīḍya viṣṇumindraṃ tathaiva ca |
devīnāṃ samsukho devyā dvandvayuddhena preṣayet ||019:011||
[preṣitāṃ ka ga]
tā māyāṃ ghorajāṃ devyā jayāpāśena pāśitāḥ |
nikṛṃtyāśiva padmāni gajairiva lamahāhṛde ||019:012||
[śara ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe māyāsainyavadho nāma ekonaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye devyavatāre māyāsainyavadhaḥ ka ga]
