%%% Chapter 020
viṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

yāṃ yāṃ cakāra daityendro māyāṃ māyāvidāṃ varaḥ |
tāṃ tāṃ nikṛntate devī nayaṃ devo yathā guṇaḥ ||020:001||
śakti-traya-samopetaḥ pauruṣeṇa samanvitaḥ |
bala-vāhanayukto'pi daivenaikena pīḍitaḥ ||020:002||
[pātitaḥ ka ga]
śakra uvāca |

yadā hi balavān daiva ekaḥ śatruvalaṃ jayet |
tadā gajāśvayodhānāṃ vyarthatā hyanumīyate ||020:003||
[dhyanumīyapto kha]
na dharmmo nāpi cādharmmo na mantrī na purohitaḥ |
daiva eva hi karttā tu śubhāśubhaphalapravaḥ ||020:004||
aśvamedhādi yajñā ye brahmahatyādi pātakāḥ |
daiva eva hi karttā ca na puṇyaṃ na ca dīṣabhāk ||020:005||
bhiṣak samvat sarāmādyai rna hi kiñcit prayojanam |
kṛṣi karmmānu vārtā ca daivaṃ sarvvaṃ karoti hi ||020:006||
[saṃvatsarā ka]
yadetat kathanārambhe devyā ādyavatāraṇam |
tata karoti vidhirbrahman kimetad bhavatā kṛtam ||020:007||
anenaivānumānena śuśrūṣā vinayena hi |

agastya uvāca |

evaṃ pūrvvaṃ bhavānāsīt cakra brahmasya daivike ||020:008||
pauruṣasyānusandhāya yatate kamalodbhavaḥ |

brahmovāca |

daivo hi sarvva-śaktīnāṃ balānāṃ paramaṃ balam ||020:009||
cintyāḥ anya padārthāḥ syurdaivaṃ kenāpi cintyatām |
daivānukūlatā śakra śakti pauruṣa ceṣṭitam ||020:010||
[sarvve ka ga]
phalate sarvvalokānāṃ kṛṣervṛṣṭiriva dvayam |
tathāpi pauruṣaṃ śakra yatitavyaṃ jigīṣuṇā ||020:011||
[jatitavyaṃ yaḥ ka]
nahi śayyāgatāṃ kāntāṃ daivamevāvagūhate |
tasmāt puruṣakāro'pi sidhyatyeva niyāmitaḥ ||020:012||
tathāpi śakti yuktena balāyato samanvitaiḥ |
paraṃ puruṣakārasya yatitavyaṃ sadā vibho ||020:013||
[ukteva ka; balāyati ka ga; vudhaiḥ ka ga]
deva dānava gandharvvā ṛṣayo mānavāḥ surāḥ sarvve daivavaśāḥ śakra daivo'pi hi śivā matā ||020:014||
[mānaveśvarā ka ga; daivopiddhi ka]
sa ca dānava rūpeṇa deva rūpeṇa vāsava |
sthityutpatti vināśāya brahma-viṣṇu-śivā tanuḥ ||020:015||
nānā rūpadharā bhūtvā sarvvaṃ haṃti karoti ca |
tenemāṃ dānavīṃ māyāṃ ghoro ghorāṃ pracakrame ||020:016||
[māyāvīṃ ka]
evaṃ brahmā purā śakra śakreṇa samabhāṣata |
yāvat sā vāhinī devyā dānavena vimardditā ||020:017||
tathāstaṃ prāpite sūrye sandhyāyāṃ samupasthitā |
ajitā sarvvaṃdevānāmabhayāya ca preṣitā ||020:018||
[tathātvaṃ ka; samupasthito kha]
brahma viṣṇivandrarudrāṇāṃ yoganidrā ca sā smṛtā |
sā rakṣā paramā bhūtā kāla-vandhana-kārikā ||020:019||
tathāgatā mahādevī devatā rakṣaṇe niśi |
kālo'pi sārddhayāme tu yāmini vigate vibho ||020:020||
anekākāriṇo bhūtvā bahumāyo mahābalaḥ |
prāvṛṭkāle samārambhe kālanīlānilaprabhuḥ ||020:021||
[mahārabhbhī ka]
raktākṣo bhairavākāraḥ surāsurabhayaṅkaraḥ |
yamavāhanakoṭīnāṃ sahyaiveko vinirmitaḥ ||020:022||
tasya sañcaramānasya kampate ca vasundharā |
nimnonnatāni kurute bhayaṃ jagmuḥ surāsurāḥ ||020:023||
ghoro mahāghora tanuṃ vidhāya devyā samaṃ jagmurmahāhavāya |
saṃkruddhakālā naladīptatatejāṃ tāṃ paśyate siṃhavare niviṣṭām ||020:024||
bhayāni kurvvan danijādhipasya surādhipe cābhayarūparūpām |
daityāntakīṃ sṛṣṭikarīṃ surāṇāmālokya devīṃ sahasā tu ghoraḥ ||020:025||
pādānta randhreṣu girīn sa kṛtvā candrārkatārāṇiśire dhvanitvā |
siṃhena yoddhuṃ sahasā pravṛttaḥ siṃhe'pi tañjāṅghranaravaiviṃvidhya ||020:026||
[pādāṃtakavahinaṣu kha; dhunitvā ka; siṃhopi taṃ aṃghrinakhaiḥ vividhya ka ga]
nakhaprahārairmahiṣasya kāye asṛk pravāhaugha-vinirgatā ye |
divaukasaistaiḥ sahasā pradiṣṭāṃ kuruṇḍa mālā iva vadhya-kāye ||020:027||
[kūruṇṭa ka ga]
tad ghora-śṛṅgāgra-prahāra-bhinno harirnanāda sahasā ca rivannaḥ |
saṃkopitaṃ daitya-nipāta-ghātairhariḥ prajaghne narava-daṃṣṭra-ghātaiḥ ||020:028||
[taṃ ka; sahasa ca khinnaḥ ka ga]
devyāḥ śire mudgarapāśaghātāt vahūn mumoca śara-daṇḍa-ghātān |
tathāpi no vādhayituṃ sa śaktaḥ pañcānanaḥ śṛṅgahataḥ papāta ||020:029||
[kraṃtacakrān ka]
taṃ ghoraghātāhata-siṃha-rājaṃ bhūmau gataṃ ghora bhaṭaiḥ pradṛṭṣvā |
te dānavāḥ krodhavaśaṃ prapannā devītanāvastravarāṇi cikṣipuḥ ||020:030||
[asurāṇi cikṣiyuḥ ka ga]
dṛṣṭvā tu devīṃ taiḥ pīḍitāṅgī nivārayetām vijayā jayā ca |
nivārite ghorabale samaste māyāsamutthe tamapāyarupe ||020:031||
[niṣpīḍitāṃgī ka ga]
devī kṛpāṇena tamāpatantaṃ ciccheda grīvāṃ dharaṇīṃ nipātya |
dṛṣṭvā surāstaṃ nihataṃ surāriṃ puṣpāṇi devī caraṇeṣu cikṣipuḥ ||020:032||
tasya śiraścheda-samudbhavantaṃ raktānanaṃ raktavilocanāntam |
kruddhānanaṃ mukta-kacaṃ sughoraṃ kṛpāṇapāṇiṃ śata-ghora-kāram ||020:033||
devyānanaṃ tarjjana garjjamānaṃ śaṅkāvahaṃ nirbhaya devatānām |
taṃ dṛṣṭamātraṃ sahasā tu devīṃ pāśena saṃpāśya mumoca nainaṃ ||020:034||
śūlena mūrdhni sahasā vibhinnaṃ taṃ muktavīra mapatad gṛhītam |
ṛkṣādhipe cāstagate'sureśe daityādhipāḥ pretapathaṃ prajagmuḥ ||020:035||
[jīvaṃ ka ga]
iti śrī devī purāṇe devyavatāre ghokavadho nāma viṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye devyavatāre ghoravadhaḥ samāptaḥ ka ga]
