%%% Chapter 023
trayoviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

kṣīrāśī nandikārabhya devyā bhaktirato nṛpaḥ |
śāka yāvaka ekāśī prātaḥ snāyī śivārataḥ ||023:001||
[kāttikā ka ga]
pūjayet tilahomaistu dadhi kṣīraghṛtādibhiḥ |
kāryyantu devīmantreṇa śrṛṇu pūjā phalaṃ hare ||023:002||
mahāpātakasaṃyukto yukto vā sarvvapātakaiḥ |
mucyate nātra sandeho yasmāt sarvvagatā śivā ||023:003||
[upapātakaiḥ ka ga]
anyo vā bhāvanāyukto anena vidhinā śivām |
svayaṃ vā anyato vāpi pūjayet pūjāpayeta vā ||023:004||
na tasya bhavati vyādhirna ca śatrukṛtaṃ bhayam |
notpātagrahaduḥkhaṃ vā na ca rāṣṭraṃ vinaśyati ||023:005||
sadā subhāva sampannā ṛtavaḥ śubhadā ghanāḥ |
niṣpattiḥ śasyajātānāṃ taskarā na bhavanti ca ||023:006||
[svabhāva ka ga]
prabhūtapayaso gāvo brāhmaṇāḥ svakriyāparāḥ |
striyaḥ pativratāḥ sarvvā nivṛtta-vairiṇo nṛpāḥ ||023:007||
phala-puṣpavatī devī vanaspatiḥ mahāmatiḥ |
bhavate nātra sandehaścarccikāvidhipūjanāt ||023:008||
[dhātrī śasyāni rasavaṃti ca]
jayantī maṅgalā kālī bhadrakālī kapālinī |
durgā śivā kṣamā dhātrī svāhā svadhā namostute ||023:009||
anenaiva tu mantreṇa japahomantu kārayeta |
prātaḥ saṃsmaritā vatsa mahiṣadhnī prapūjitā ||023:010||
aghaṃ nāśayate kṣiṃpraṃ yathā sūryyodaye tamaḥ ||023:011||
siṃhārūḍhā dhvaje yasya nṛpasya ripuhā umā |
dvārasthā pūjyate vatsa na tasya ripujaṃ bhayam ||023:012||
kapisaṃsthā mahāmāyā sarvvaśatru vināśinī |
vṛṣe yathepsitaṃ dadyātkalaśe śreyamuttamam ||023:013||
haṃse vidyārtha kāmāṃstu varhiṇe sutamiṣṭadā |
garutmagā mahāmāyā sarvvarogavināśinī ||023:014||
mahiṣasthā mahāmārī śamate dhvajasaṃsthitā |
karisthā sarvvakāryyeṣu nṛpaiḥ kāryyā triśūlinī ||023:015||
padmasthā carccikā ropyā dharmakāmārtha mokṣadā |
pretasthā sarvvabhayadā nityaṃ paśu-nipātanāt ||023:016||
pūjitā devarājendra nīlotpalakarā varā |
bhavate siddhikāmasya cittāgre saṃvyavasthitā ||023:017||
[dharā ka ga]
gandha puṣpācciṃtaṃ kṛtvā vastra homa sucarccitam |
phalaśāliyava śuci varddhamānā vibhūṣitam ||023:018||
śobhane ucchraye lagne patākāṃ vā manoramām |
cāmaraṃ kalaśe śaṅkhamā tapatra vitānakam(FN) ||023:019||
[śloko'yaṃ nāsti ka ga pustake]
bhavate siddhikāmasya nṛpasya śubhadāyakam |
ūmÌ namo viśveśvari durge cāmuṇḍe caṇḍa hāriṇī ||023:020||
dhvajaṃ samucchrayiṣyāmi vasordhārāṃ sukhāvahām ||023:021||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre citraṇa vidhināma trayoviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye devīpurāṇe cinhavidhiḥ ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 024
caturviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

samayena ṛtumāsa pakṣāhādi kramena tu |
sūkṣma-sthūla-vibhāgena devī sarvvagatā vibho ||024:001||
dvādaśaiva samākhyātā samā saṃkrāntikalpanāḥ |
saptadhā sā tu boddhavyā ekekaiva yathā śṛṇu ||024:002||
mandā mandākinī dhvāṃkṣī ghorā caiva mahodarī |
rākṣasī miśritā proktā saṃkrāntiḥ saptadhā nṛpa ||024:003||
[kṣobha ka ga]
mandā dhruveṣu vijñeyā mṛdau mandākinī tathā |
kṣipre dhvāṅkṣīṃ vijānīyādugrairghorā prakīrtitā ||024:004||
carairmahodarī jñeyā krūrairṛkṣaistu rākṣasī |
miśritā caiva nirdiṣṭā miśritākṣaistu saṃkrame ||024:005||
tricatuḥ pañca saptāṣṭa nava dvādaśameva ca |
krameṇa ghaṭitā hyetāstatpuṇyaṃ pāramārthikam ||024:006||
atītānāgatān bhogān ādyaḥ paṃcadaśa smṛtāḥ |
sānnidhyaṃ bhavate tatra grahāṇāṃ saṃkrame ravau ||024:007||
[grahāṇāṃ pātumeva vai ga]
vyavahāro bhavelloke candrasūryopalakṣitaḥ |
kālo'pi kalate sarvva brahmādya sacarācaram ||024:008||
puṇya-pāpa-vibhāgena phalaṃ devī prayacchati |
ekadhāpi kṛtaṃ tasmin koṭi koṭi guṇaṃ bhavet ||024:009||
dharmmo vivarddhate hyāyū rājyaṃ putra sukhāni ca |
adharmma vyādhi śokādi viṣuvāyana sannidhau ||024:010||
[sukhādayaḥ ka ga; hyādhri ka]
viṣuveṣu ca yajjaptaṃ dattaṃ bhavati cākṣayam |
evaṃ viṣṇu pade caiva ṣaḍaśīti mukheṣu ca ||024:011||
ayaneṣu vikalpo yastanme nigadataḥ śṛṇu |
yāvadviṃśakalā bhuṃkte tat puṇyamuttarāyaṇe ||024:012||
[kalpo ka; yuktā ka ga]
niraṃśe bhāskare dṛṣṭe dinānte dakṣiṇāyane |
arddharātre tu sampūrṇe divā puṇyamanāgatam ||024:013||
sampūrṇe cārddharātre tu udayāstamane'pi ca |
mānārddha bhāskaraṃ puṇyamapūrṇe śarvvarīdine ||024:014||
[dale ka]
sampūrṇa ubhayorjñeyamaviveke'parehani(FN) |
ṣaḍaśītimukhe'tīte vṛtte ca viṣuvad vaye ||024:015||
[ga puske nāsti ]
bhaviṣyatyayate puṇyamatīte cottarāyaṇe (FN)| ādau puṇyaṃ vijānīyād yadā bhinnātithirbhavet ||024:016||
[ga pustake nāsti]
arddharātre vyatīte tu vijñeyā cāpare'hani |
mandā viprajane śastā mandākinyastu rājani ||024:017||
dhvāṃkṣī vaiśyeṣu vijñeyā ghoraśūdre śubhāvahā |
mahodarī tu caurāṇāṃ śoṇḍikānāṃ jayāvahā ||024:018||
[śubhapradā ka ga]
cāṇḍāla-pukvaśānāntu ye cānye krūrakarmiṇaḥ |
sarveṣāṃ kārukāṇāñca miśritā dhṛtivarddhinī ||024:019||
nṛpān pīḍati pūrvvāhṇe madhyāhṇe ca dvijottamān |
aparāhṇe tu sā vaiśyāñchūdrānastamane raveḥ ||024:020||
[pīḍayanti ka]
piśācāṃśca pradoṣe tu arddharātre tu rākṣasān |
arddharātre vyatīte tu pīḍyante naṭanartakīḥ ||024:021||
[nantakā ka ga]
uṣaḥkāle tu saṃkrāntau hanti go svāmino janān |
hanti pravrajitān sarvvān sandhyākāle na saṃśayaḥ ||024:022||
etat sthūla vibhāgantu bhakti kāmasya kīrtitam |
paramārthena yā saṃkhyā kathayāmi nṛpottama ||024:023||
susthe nare sukhāsīne yāvat spandati locanam |
tasya triṃśattamaṃ bhāgaṃ tatparaṃ parikīrtitam ||024:024||
tat parācchatabhāgaṃ tu truṭirityabhidhīyate |
truṭyāḥ sahasrabhāgārddhaṃ tatkālaṃ ravi-saṃkrame ||024:025||
tat kāleṣu dravībhūtaṃ trailokyaṃ sacarācaram |
vyatīpāte'pi syād bhavet puṇyaṃ samādhikam ||024:026||
tatra brahmāpi sandigdhamuvāca surasattama |
dānādhyayanajāpādi viśiṣṭaṃ ghora homataḥ ||024:027||
[atra ka; hotra kha]
vasorddhārāsu labhyeta anyathā na kathañcana |
devīkālagatā vatsa yathā sūkṣmaṃ prakīrtitā ||024:028||
sādhakī sarvvakāmāṇāṃ mahābhaya vināśinī |
kathitā te matā sā tu kiṃ bhūyaḥ paripṛcchasi ||024:029||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe saṃkrāntividhirnāma caturvviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye devīpurāṇe saṃkrāntividhi ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 025
pañcaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

vidyādhara uvāca |

yathā sā sarvagā devī sarvveṣāñca phalapradā |
tathāhaṃ śrotumicchāmi vasorddhārāṃ suvistarām ||025:001||
agastya uvāca |

brahmaṇā yā samākhyātā devarājasya pṛcchataḥ |
vidhiśca pāpahā śrotuḥ śṛṇuṣvāvahito mama ||025:002||
vasorddhārā sthitā devī sarvvakāma pradāyikā |
tathā te kathayiṣyāmi śṛṇu puṇyavivṛddhaye ||025:003||
sarveṣāmeva devānāṃ kathitā devī cottamā |
viśeṣeṇa tu vahṇisthā āyurārogyadā matā ||025:004||
[sarveṣāṃ kha; kathite yaṃ ka]
vijayaṃ bhūmilābhantu priyatvaṃ sarvvamānavān |
vidyā-saubhāgya putrādi kuṇḍasthā saṃprayacchati ||025:005||
tasmān nṛpeṇa bhūrtyarthe vasorddhārāśritā śivā |
pūjanīyā yathā śaktyā caṇḍī kāmaphalapradā ||025:006||
[cāśru ga]
rudrādityā grahā viṣṇurvayaṃ yakṣāḥ sakinnarāḥ |
hutāśanamukhāḥ sarvve dṛṣṭādṛṣṭa-phala-pradāḥ ||025:007||
godānaṃ bhūdānañca ratnaṃ sarpistalāni ca |
dānāni mahatānyāhusteṣāṃ dhārā viśiṣyate ||025:008||
viprāṇāṃ koṭikoṭīnāṃ bhojayitvā tu yat phalat |
tadvṛtta-nirataiḥ śāntairekenāpi ca tadbhavet ||025:009||
vyatīpāte na sandehaḥ sa ca sūkṣmaḥ prakīrtitaḥ |
ayane viṣuvaccaiva dinacchidraṃ tathaiva ca ||025:010||
[ayanaṃ ka ga]
duṣprāpaṃ dānaṃ homānāṃ dhārāyāṃ labhate nṛpaḥ |
tasmān nṛpeṇa vṛddhyartha dṛṣṭvādṛṣṭa jigīṣuṇā ||025:011||
[labhyate ka ga]
vasorddhārā prakarttavyā sarvakāmaṃ jayāvahā |
samaṃ vā athavārddha vā ṛtumāsārddhavāsaram ||025:012||
[samaṃ ka]
kṛtvā vibhavarūpeṇa śāśvataṃ labhate phalam |
ekāhamapi yo devīṃ kalpayitvā hutāśane ||025:013||
pātayet sarpiṣo dhārāṃ sa labhatepsitaṃ phalam |
devī-mātṛ-samīpasthaṃ śiva-viṣṇu-samīpagam ||025:014||
[abhedīpsitaṃ ka ga]
bhānoḥ prajāpatervāpi vasorddhārā gṛhe bhavet |
cirantaneṣu(FN) siddheṣu svayaṃ vā saṃskṛteṣu ca ||025:015a-d|| parvvateṣu ca divyeṣu nadīnāṃ saṅgameṣu ca ||025:015ef||
[paṃktiriyaṃ nāsti ka ga pustake; ciraṃtaniṣū ka ]
guhāsu ca vicitrāsu gṛhagarbheṣu bhūmiṣu |
dattvā samīhitān kāmān vidhinā labhate nṛpaḥ ||025:016||
[sarveṣu ka]
atha sāmānyato gehaṃ samasūtraṃ janonmukham |
vāstusaṃśuddhi-vinyāptamekādaśakaraṃ param ||025:017||
[labhyate ka]
trīṇi pañcātha saptā vā daśa vā nava kārayet |
viṃśaikaṃ vā vahunāṃ vātriṃśadūrdhvaṃ na kārayet ||025:018||
[vaskta saṃśuddha ka; bhāvanyūnaṃ ka ]
pakveṣṭaṃ śailadārvva vā saliṅgaṃ sahatoraṇam |
pañca sapta navāsyaṃ vā gavākṣaka vibhūṣitam ||025:019||
[paṃcātha vā sapta daśavā nava kārayeta ka]
sarvvato bhadravinyastaṃ krama vṛddhayāvivakṣitam |
ūrdhvadhūmasya niṣkāsaṃ saprakāśaṃ viśeṣataḥ ||025:020||
[ṣaṣṭhāṅka kha]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe toraṇavidhirnāma pañcaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[nava vā ka ga     ādye devyavatāre śaraṇavidhiḥ ka ga]     Please check the footnotes.
%%%%
%%% Chapter 026
ṣaḍviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

sadaivaṃ sagrahaṃ kāryyamathavā deva toraṇam |
tasya madhye bhavet kuṇḍaṃ hastādilakṣaṇānvitam ||026:001||
[devataiḥ samaṃ ka ga]
catuṣkamatha vṛttaṃ vā paṅkajākṛti cātha vā |
pṛthivī jayadaṃ śakra vṛttaṃ kāmaphalapradam ||026:002||
[daṃśākaṃ kuḍaṃ varo śāstraṃ ga; śākraṃ ka ga ]
paṅkaje jayamārogyaṃ yoga-jñāna-pradāyakam |
śeṣāḥ kāryavibhāgena kuṇḍāḥ kāryyā vijānatā ||026:003||
sāmānyaṃ sarvvahomeṣu śakra kuṇḍaṃ varottamam |
vistāraṃ khātatulyantu mekhalaistribhirbhūṣitam ||026:004||
[śākraṃ ka ga]
catvāri trīṇi dve kuryyādaṅgula kuṇḍamānataḥ |
dviguṇān dviguṇe kuṇḍe homa mātreṇa kārayet ||026:005||
[sāreṇa ga]
evaṃ saṃsādhayedvipra stutaḥ pātraṃ saśṛṃkhalam |
haimaṃ vā rājataṃ vāpi tāmraṃ vā lakṣaṇānvitam ||026:006||
catvāri kaṭakopetamayaḥ śṛṃkhala saṃgraham |
tasya madhye bhavedrandhraṃ karṇārddhasya śalākayā ||026:007||
[caturbhi ka ga; ratnam ga]
homotthayā pramāṇena caturaṅgulamānayā |
dhṛtaniṣkramaṇārthāya kuryyāt samyak vipaścitaḥ ||026:008||
palairdaśabhirarddhonyairnānyekāntu mayā brajeta |
pañcabhistu śatairhomaḥ saptatyā ca ṣaḍasrayā ||026:009||
yathā pūrṇā brajed vatsa tathā kuryyānna cānyathā |
hastamātraṃ bhaved haimaṃ śṛṃkhalaṃ bhujagākṛti ||026:010||
[śṛṃkhalaṃ ca bhujā kṛti ga]
randhre sūtranibaddhañca avalambya adhastanam |
maṇiṃ vā paṅkajaṃ pātramāśvatthaṃ kārayet tale ||026:011||
evaṃ kāryyānurūpeṇa dviguṇaṃ triguṇaṃ pivā |
kuryyāt pātraṃ dhṛtaṃ vedhaṃ pratiṣṭhā-vidhivoditama ||026:012||
[devi ka; sarvakāla prado yadā ka]
uddeśaṃ kiñcidatrāpi kathayāmi nṛpotama |
samāyana ṛturmāsa pakṣāhorātra pūrvvavat ||026:013||
lagnādi viśodhayed vatsa sarvvakāma pradā yathā |
kṣaṇikeṣu ca kāryyeṣu bharktiyuktaṃ kṣaṇe śubhe ||026:014||
[bhaktiyukta ya]
kṣaṇaṃ devī ca draṣṭavyā yathā sarvvagatā śivā |
tattvabhūtā grahā nāgāstriguṇāpi śivā guṇāḥ ||026:015||
[tadbhūtā grahā nāgā ka ga]
nitye naimittike home mantrayogena dāpayet |
yī yasya bhaktimāsaktastasya kuryyāt tu sannidhim ||026:016||
sagrahān lokapālāmÌstu mātarā bhujagaṃ pivā |
kalpayet sarvvahomeṣu devī etairvyavasthitā ||026:017||
sthūlarūpā tu taistuṣṭaistuṣṭā devī mahāphalā |
kālādibali gandhādi pratiṣṭhāvacca kārayet ||026:018||
[kālādivani ka ga]
yadā sampatti sampannaḥ sarvakāle pradāpayet |
tadā mantra-graha-bhūtān lokapālān niveśayet ||026:019||
[tadā ka ga; saṃpara ka]
haima rājata tāmrā vā sunive śopalakṣitā |
vastra puṣpavalirgandhadakṣiṇādi yathākramam ||026:020||
[imā ka ga; bāla ka; varṇa ka]
mātaraṃ lokapālānāṃ grahāṇāñca yathāvidhi |
hṛdayena pradeyantu mūlamantraiḥ purātanaiḥ ||026:021||
athavā sarvvasāmānyāṃ vaidikāmapi kārayet |
atharvva vidhinā vatsa pūrvoktā vā yathā purā ||026:022||
prabhūta-mantra-naivedyai rbhūri-dakṣiṇa-saṃyutaiḥ |
kuryyānmahāprayatnena anyathā na kathañcana ||026:023||
chede bhayaṃ vijānīyāt tadartha tanna kārayet |
sahasrāhuti homena yatra tatra niveśayet ||026:024||
[vijāyāt ka]
mūla mantreṇa devyāyāḥ śṛṃkhalā hṛdayena tu |
ghṛtañca śiromantreṇa śikhāyāṃ tatra pātayet(FN) ||026:025||
[ka pustake nāsti]
kavacena tathā vahṇiṃ rakṣayitvā pradāpayet |
aśvamedhena mantreṇa sarvva sarvvāsu nikṣipet ||026:026||
[sarva sarvvāstra nikṣipet ka]
lokapālān grahān-nāgān dvādaśārddhena pūjayet |
śivādyān sanakādyāṃśca devādyānapi pūjayet ||026:027||
[līlākapāla ka]
nityeṣu ca mahā prājña naimitteṣu viśeṣataḥ |
pañcakāni ca saptādi navakāni kriyādikaiḥ ||026:028||
[va pathā ka]
agre varṇāśca gandhaśca śabdāścākṛtayastathā |
vikārāśca tathā vatsa boddhavyāḥ siddhyasiddhidāḥ ||026:029||
[tathā rāścatathā ka]
tadante ca stavaṃ kārya sarvvakāmapradāyakam |
yena sānnidhyamāyārti sarvvahomeṣu maṅgalā ||026:030||
sahasrārcci mahātejā namaste bahurūpiṇe |
nīlakaṇṭha śitikaṇṭha pītavāsāya pāvane ||026:031||
[nīla ka]
sruvamekhaladhārāya brahmaṇe dahane namaḥ |
sarvvāśine sarvvabhartre pāvakāya namo namaḥ ||026:032||
durgāya umārūpāya strīliṅgāya sutejase |
vasu aśvinarūpāya sarvāhārāya vai namaḥ ||026:033||
tvaṃ rudra ghorakarmāsi ghorahā parameśvaraḥ |
viṣṇustavaṃ jagatāṃ pālo brahmā sṛṣṭikaraḥ smṛtaḥ ||026:034||
[jagatpālosi ka ga]
tvañca sarvārthako deva yamāya piśitāśine |
varuṇānilāya somāya īśadevāya vai namaḥ ||026:035||
[deva lokapāla tatsthita ka indrā pavahye ka]
sūryyāya cātriputrāya bhūsutāya budhāya ca |
bṛhaspataye śukrāya śani rāho'tha ketave ||026:036||
sarvvage graharūpāya vyāla mātaṅga rūpiṇe |
vṛṣṭi sṛṣṭi sthitirbhūti karttāya varadāya ca ||026:037||
[vālya kha]
namaste skanda mātastvaṃ pitre cāpi namo namaḥ |
kuṇḍe vā maṇḍale vāpi sthaṃḍile vāpi tvaṃ vibho ||026:038||
mahānase vā tvāṃ deva hutvā iṣṭaṃ labhennaraḥ |
ghṛta-kṣīra-rasa-dhānya-tila-brīhi-yavān kuśān||026:039||
[yavaṃ ka ga]
bhāvādabhāvato vāpi satataṃ homayedanale |
evaṃ vidhivihīno'pi naro vigatakilviṣaḥ ||026:040||
[bhāvāya bhāvato vāpi kha]
rki punarnityahomaṃ tu vasorddhārā hutāśane |
sarvva maṅgala mantreṇa pūrṇāhutiṃ pradāpayet ||026:041||
lokapāla grahāṇāṃ tu oṃkāreṇa namo'tiṃkaiḥ |
svaiḥ svairmantraistu śeṣāṇāṃ homaṃ kāryyaṃ nṛpottama ||026:042||
annaṃ vicitraṃ śuṣkañca saṃskṛtaṃ ghṛtapāyasaiḥ |
homayedvidhivad vipro baliñcāpi pradāpayeta ||026:043||
sitavastradharo bhūpaḥ sabalaḥ sahavāhanaḥ |
pūjayet śambhuṃ rudrādīn mātaraṃ pitaraṃ dvijīn ||026:044||
[pūjayecchatra ratnā dāna mātaraṃ dvijāt ka]
ācāryyān brāhmaṇāṃ llokān sarvvāśramaratāśca ye |
naṭa-narttaka-veśyāśca kanyakā vidhavāḥ striyaḥ ||026:045||
[bāṃdhavān ka ga; naranernaka ka]
dīnāndha-kṛpaṇāṃścaiva annadānena pūjayet |
evaṃ niveśanaṃ kṛtvā nityaṃ japyaṃ śataṃ śatam ||026:046||
prātarmadhyāhna saṃdhyāyāṃ stavaṃ śāntiṃ prakīrttanam |
bhavate nṛparāṣṭrasya pūrvoktaṃ phaladāyakam ||026:047||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe vasorddhārā-niveśanavidhiḥ nāma ṣaḍviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devyavatāre vasordhārāniveśanavidhiḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 027
saptaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

[śakra uvāca ga]
taptahāṭakavarṇena sūryya-sindūra-kānti kṛta |
śaṅkhakundendū-padbhābho ghṛta-kṣīra nibhaḥ śubhaḥ ||027:001||
[varṇābho ka ga]
javābho'śoka-puṣpābho lākṣādara samanvitaḥ |
śubhadaḥ sarvvakāryāṇāṃ viparīto hyasiddhidaḥ ||027:002||
meghadundubhi-śaṅkhānāṃ veṇuvīṇā-svanaḥ śubhaḥ |
vṛṣendra nṛpa kākānāṃ kokilā-svana pūjitaḥ ||027:003||
[vṛṣebha śikhi ka ga; mana śilā kuṣṭha karpura kha]
kuṃkumāguru-karpūrasita-gandhi ca pūjitaḥ |
haṃsachatrebha-gokumbha padmākṛtikaraḥ śubhaḥ ||027:004||
[haṃsa chatrebhyo siṃha varhiṇaṃ śailānāṃ cā maga kṛtiriṣṭada ka]
siṃha-varhiṇa-śyenānāṃ cāmarā kṛtiriṣṭidaḥ |
sadhūmo mṛtagandhā ca mūkaḥṣaḍvaramopamaḥ ||027:005||
chinna jvālo'tha vā raudro neṣṭaḥ sarvveṣu pāvakaḥ |
susaṃhataśikhaḥ śakra ūrddhvaṃ vāte'pi yāti yaḥ ||027:006||
[ chita ka; śiṣṭa ka; sva ka ]
lelihānaḥ śubhaḥ kuṇḍo dīptimān varado'nalaḥ |
evaṃvidhaḥ sadā pārtha yajñenaivāha sthāpanaiḥ ||027:007||
yātrāyāṃ śakraketau ca sarvvakāryeṣu siddhidaḥ |
nyūnā yā vaheta dhārā mānāt sarpirna sā śubhā ||027:008||
nādhikā śasyate vipra durbhikṣa-kali-kārikā |
nudate vahamānā yā śasate ca hutāśanam ||027:009||
[lodhikā ka; śakra ka]
sāpi cānyaṃ nṛpamicchet yāvad ghorāyate bhuvi |
ṛá¹junādī mahārūpā manojñā priyakārikā ||027:010||
[anojā ka]
suvarṇā hemavarṇā ca dhārā rājya-vivṛddhaye |
satataṃ patate yātu tanotība ca pāvakam ||027:011||
tanoti nṛparāṣṭraṃ sā vasorddhārā na saṃśayaḥ |
sugandhi svacchaṃ vimalaṃ kṛmi-kīṭa-vivarjjitam ||027:012||
śasyate ca vasorddhārā sarpirgavyantu pūjitam |
abhāvād gavyalājaṃ vā hotavyantu suśobhanam ||027:013||
[gavyajāsnaṃ ka]
ghṛtakṣaudra payodhārā sarvapīḍā nivāriṇī |
guḍvīśa-kalairhomaṃ sahakāradalaiḥ śubhaiḥ ||027:014||
aśvatthā mālatī dūrvvā āyurārogyaputradā |
saubhāgyañca śriyaṃ devī prayacchatyavicāraṇāt ||027:015||
[priyaṃ ka ga]
arkādi vā śubhā vatsa saphalā sarvvakāmikā |
hotavyā sarvakālantu mātarādavicchedinī ||027:016||
[sakalā hasa kāmikā ka]
sarvvakālaṃ vṛtaṃ proktaṃ nimitte cātmavittamaḥ |
viśuddhi sarpiṣā yāni tāni nātra vicārayet ||027:017||
[cārtha ka ga]
jvālā varṇa śubhaṃ gandhaṃ sarvvahomeṣu lakṣayet |
saṃyato saṃyatāhāraiḥ sarvvaśāstrārthapāragaiḥ ||027:018||
japa homaratairbhūpa dhārā deyā ca tadvidaiḥ |
pāṣanḍa vikalān luvdhān dharmmāpetān asaṃyatān ||027:019||
sarvvakāla-pradāyī tu na vadennāvalokayet |
mṛtyuñjayaṃ mahātattvaṃ catuḥ saptāṣṭa jāpinā ||027:020||
bhāvyaṃ vai nityahome tu anyathā viphalaṃ bhavet |
sāmānyā yā bhaveddhārā tasmin japyaṃ śataṃ śatam ||027:021||
[vikalaṃ ka ga]
prātarmadhyāhṇa-sandhyāsu sarvvakāma-samṛddhaye |
vasu-dravyaṃ ghṛtamājyamamṛtaṃ haviḥ kāmikam ||027:022||
tasya dhārā sadā deyā vasorddhārā hi sā matā |
vasunā svarga-kāmeṇa dakṣeṇa ca mahātmanā ||027:023||
[sarvakāmeṇa ka ga]
mayā ca viṣṇunā śakra rudreṇa ca sahomayā |
ātmānañca svarūpeṇa dhārāyāntu pradāpayet ||027:024||
[prapātitama ka ga]
devī sānnidhyamāyātā sarvvakāma-pradāyikā |
tasmāttvamapi rājendra vasordhārāṃ prapātaya ||027:025||
nātaḥ parataraṃ puṇyaṃ vidyate nṛpa-sattama |
vasorddhārā pradānasya ekāhamapi yadbhavet ||027:026||
nṛpeṇāyuṣakāmeṇa putradārasukhārthinā |
deyā dhārā sadā vatsa ripunāśāya buddhinā||027:027||
[nṛpeṇa putra rājya jigiṣuṇā ka ga; buddhimāna ka ga]
vicchedo nitya-homasya na ca kāryya kadācana |
mahādoṣamavāpnotī ye tatra vimukhāḥ narāḥ ||027:028||
[gavāmeta ye tatra vimukhā surā ka ga]
dravyā bhāve ghṛtābhāve nṛpataskaraje bhaye |
yadi no vahate dhārā tadācchidraṃ na vidyate ||027:029||
homaṃ kṛtvā kṣamāveta devadevīṃ nṛpottama |
punaḥ prāptau bhavedhomaṃ pratiṣṭhā vidhicoditam ||027:030||
mahā āśvina māse tu aṣṭamī navamīṣu ca |
kārtikyāṃ māghacaitre tu citrāyāṃ rohiṇīṣu ca ||027:031||
[piṛá¹tuchidrāyāṃ ka]
vaiśākhyāntu pradātavyā jyeṣṭhāṃ jyaiṣṭhasya sattama |
āṣāḍhe dvādaśī homaṃ aṣṭamī pūrṇimā nabhe ||027:032||
[sattamā ka]
nabhasye rohiṇī vatsa caturthyāṃ skandaje dine |
saṃkrāntiṣu ca sarvvāsu gurusauri bhavāsu ca ||027:033||
candra-sūryyoparāgeṣu pratiṣṭhā(FN) yajña-karmaṇi |
śakrocchraye pradātavyā janmapuṣyābhiṣecane ||027:034||
[ka pustake nāsti]
mārge vratanibandhe tu śubhe vā ketudarśane |
grahakṛtyopasargeṣu dhārā deyā śubhāvahā ||027:035||
evaṃ yo vāhayed dhārāṃ śāstra dṛṣṭena karbhmaṇā |
tasya bhūḥ sidhyate sarvvā sanāgā sahasāgarā ||027:036||
aśvamedhasamaṃ puṇyaṃ dinahomāt prajāyate |
vājapeyaśataṃ rātrāvagniṣṭomaśataṃ tathā ||027:037||
ādhayo vyādhayastasya na bhavanti kadācana |
āyurārogyamaiśvaryamiha cānte śinī bhavet ||027:038||
[vāte śivā bhaveta ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe vasordhārādānavidhirnāma saptaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devīpurāṇe vasordhārā samāptā ka ga]
