%%% Chapter 028
aṣṭaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

śūlino brahmaṇā prāptamindrācca  mama āgatam |
mayāpi te yathā vṛttaṃ tathā rājan prakāśitam ||028:001||
brahma viṣṇu śivānāñca mahābhaya vimokṣadam |
mantritaṃ śakra-govinda-vācaspati-pitāmahaiḥ ||028:002||
[surāṇaṃ ca ka]
rudrastotraṃ mahādevyā viṣṇvārādhana-ghorajam |
vadhaṃ mahiṣarūpasya bhūmau devyavatāraṇam ||028:003||
vrataṃ vrajocchrayaṃ dhārā maṅgaleṣu paṭhet sadā |
devyāyatane devasya śaṅkarasya harerapi ||028:004||
[yathā ka ga]
goṣṭhe vā cavvare śaile gṛhe vā sumanorame |
devīṃ sampūjayitvā tu bhojayitvā kumārikāḥ ||028:005||
[mārikā ka]
tadbhakti bhāvitān viprān-sadvṛttāñchāstratatparān |
yathāśaktyā ca pūjyet hemavastravibhūṣaṇai ||028:006||
[datte ka]
tatastān svasti vācayitvā pūjayitvā tu pustakam |
sugandha-gandha-dhūpena puṣpamālyaiḥ sucandanaiḥ ||028:007||
ghaṇṭācāmaraśobhāḍhyai darpaṇairūpaśobhite |
dukūle vastrābharaṇe daṇḍayantre niveśayet ||028:008||
vācakaṃ pūjayitvā tu yathāvibhavavistaraiḥ |
vācayet tato rājā devī māhātmyamuttamam ||028:009||
tadante śānti śabdastu janasya sa nṛpasya ca |
(FN)go brāhmaṇa pūjānāntu vanaspati mukheṣu ca ||028:010||
[ita paraṃ ga pustake nāsti]
kṣatra-viṭ-śūdra-bālānāṃ sarvameva śubhaṃ tu vaḥ |
anena vidhinā rājā yaḥ paṭhet śṛṇuyādapi ||028:011||
cintayed vācayed vāpi tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu |
aśvamedha sahasrasya vājapeyaśatasya ca ||028:012||
agniṣṭoma mahāṣṭoma rājasūya mahāmakhaiḥ |
yat phalaṃ labhyate tāta tat phalaṃ śatadhā bhavet ||028:013||
gaṅgātoyā bhiṣekādaistīrthainaimiṣa puṣkaraiḥ |
yat phalaṃ labhyate rājaṃstat phalādayutādhikam ||028:014||
brahmahatyādipāpānāṃ śamanaṃ paramaṃ śatam |
varddhanañcātha-dharmmāṇāṃ kāma-mokṣa-phala pradam ||028:015||
putradaṃ patnidaṃ tāta jayadaṃ saukhyadaṃ param |
anena vidhinā vatsa prāpnoti śravaṇānnaraḥ |
iha kīrti śriyaṃ brāhmīṃ paratra bhavati layam ||028:016||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyāstava-paṭhana-māhātmyaṃ nāma aṣṭāviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye devīpurāṇe devyāḥ pustakapaṭhanamahātmyam ka ga]
