%%% Chapter 030
triṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

śṛṇu tasyā surādhyakṣa ārādhana-rvidhiṃ parāma |
yathā sā toṣitā pūrvva śaṅkarādyaiḥ phalepsubhiḥ ||030:001||
karmma-yajñena deveśa tathā tvāmapi pūjayeḥ |
śambhuḥ pūjayate devīṃ mantraśaktimayāṃ śubhām ||030:002||
[sendre ka]
akṣamālākaro nityaṃ tenāsau vibhavavānnaraḥ |
ahaṃ śailamayīṃ devīṃ yajāmi surasattama ||030:003||
tena brahmatvamevedaṃ mayā prāptaṃ sudurlabham |
indranīlamayīṃ devīṃ viṣṇurarccayate sadā ||030:004||
viṣṇutvaṃ prāptavāṃstena adbhutaiḥ kaṃsanāśanām |
devī hemamayī kāntāṃ dhanado'rcayate sadā ||030:005||
tenāsau dhanado devo dhaneśatvamavāpnuyāt |
viśvedevā mahātmāno raupyāṃ devīṃ manoharām ||030:006||
[manoramām ka]
yajanti vidhivadbhaktyā tena viśvattvamāpnuyuḥ |
vāyuḥ pūjayate bhaktyā devīṃ pittalasambhavām ||030:007||
vāyutvaṃ tena tat prāptamanaupamya guṇāvaham |
vasavaḥ kāmikāṃ devīṃ pūjayante vidhānataḥ ||030:008||
[varuṇo'rcayate sadā ka]
prāpnuvastanmahātmāno vasutvaṃ hi śubhāvaham |
aśvinau pārthivīṃ devīṃ pūjayeta vidhānataḥ ||030:009||
tena tāvaśvinau devau divya-deha-gatāvubhau |
sphāṭikāṃ śobhanāṃ devīṃ varuṇo'rccayate sadā(FN) ||030:010||
[kapustake nāsti]
varuṇatvaṃ hi saṃprāptaṃ tena ṛddhayā samanvitam |
devīṃ mantramayīṃ puṇyāmagniryajate bhāvitaḥ ||030:011||
agnitvaṃ prāptavāṃstena tejorūpasamanvitam |
tāmrāṃ devīṃ sadā kāla bhaktyā devo divākaraḥ ||030:012||
arccate tatra saṃprāptaṃ tena sūryyatvamuttamam |
muktāphalamayīṃ devīṃ somaḥ pūjayate sadā ||030:013||
tena somena somatvaṃ saṃprāptaṃ sattojjavalam |
pravālakamayīṃ devīṃ yajante guhyakādayaḥ ||030:014||
[saṃprāpta soma ka; patagottamā ka]
tena bhogabalopetāḥ prayāntīśvara-mandiram |
vajraloha-mayīṃ devīṃ yajante mātaraḥ sadā ||030:015||
[tena nāgāstu bhogādyāḥ prayāṃtyaṃte paraṃ padam |

kṛṣṇāsamayīṃ devī pūjayantyuttarottamāḥ|
rākṣasāśca mahātmāno tena te sitavikramāḥ |

prayūsīsamayīṃ devīṃ piśācāḥ pūjayaṃtirdṛtām |
|
tena ṛá¹ddhi valopetāḥ prayāṃti paramaṃ padam |

trailohakīṃ sadā devīṃ yajaṃti guhyakādayaḥ |
]
mātṛtvaṃ prāpya tāḥ sarvvāḥ prayānti paramaṃ padam |
evaṃ devāḥ sagandharvvāḥ piśācoraṇarākṣasāḥ ||030:016||
[narra devī ka; piśocoragarollasā ka]
pūjayanti sadākālaṃ carccikāṃ suranāyikām |
tathā tvamapi devendra yadīpsasi parāṃ gatim ||030:017||
[kāmaka]
śivāṃ maṇimayāṃ pūjya labhase manasepsitān |
kāmān suravarādhyakṣa kāmikaiḥ pūjitā sadā ||030:018a-b||
dadāti sarvvalokānāṃ cintāmaṇiryathā śivā ||030:018ef||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe dravya-vidhi-pūjā-devīmāhātmyaṃ nāma triṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devīpurāṇe dravya-vidhi-pūjā devī māhātmyam |
eṣa adhyāyaḥ ga pustake nāsti |
