p. 116
ekatriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
bhakta bhojyānatapānena tatra sarvvāṃśca prīṇayet |
bhojayitvā kṣamāyeta devī me prīyatāmiti ||031:027||
[bhājayilā ka]
tathā devyā rathe kṛtvā punareva gṛhaṃ nayet |
(FN)śānta-reṇu-pathaṃ sarvvaṃ puṣpa-dūrvvākṣatairjjalaiḥ ||031:028||
[punareva gṛhaśyeta ka; ka pustake nāsti]
prakṣipyamāṇaiḥ kanyābhiḥ strībhiḥ maṅgalavādibhiḥ |
salilena pathi pāṃśuṃ kṛtvā paṅkaṃ pracakrire ||031:029||
[vāhibhiḥ ka; pathe ka]
puraśobhāṃ pathiśobhāṃ dvāraśobhāṃ gṛhe-gṛhe |
kārayīta tathā śakra sarvvavādhāṃ nivārayet ||031:030||
[kārayāta ka; śivāraghet ka]
acchedyāstaravassmin prāṇihiṃsā vivarjayet |
vandhanasthā vimoktavyā vadhyā krodhādi śatravaḥ ||031:031||
[baṃghanastvāpi tathā moktavyā ka]
akāla kaumudīṃ śakra rathayātrānte kārayet |
sarvvadā sarvvadevaistu, śaṅkarādyaiḥ pratiṣṭhitā ||031:032||
ratha yātrā tadā śakra suraiḥ svarge sadā kṛtā |
tathā kinnara-gandharvaiḥ bhū-pātāla nivāsibhiḥ ||031:033||
[sadāhutā ka]
ratha yātrā prabhāveṇa modante divi devatāḥ |
ādityo rathayātrākṛdrathena nabhasaḥ kramet ||031:034||
devā divya-vimānasthā rathayātrā prabhāvataḥ |
krīḍante vividhairbhogaiḥ sarvātaṅka vivarjitāḥ ||031:035||
[savatika ka]
tathā tvamapi devendra rathayātrā-karobhava |
śivāyāḥ śivadātāyāḥ paramena samādhinā ||031:036||
agastya uvāca |

ratha- (FN)yātrāśritaṃ puṇyaṃ brahmaṇā vāsavasya tu |
pūrvvaṃ yat kathitaṃ tāta tete sarvva mayākhilam ||031:037||
[ka pustake nāsti; brāhmaṇa ka]
sthāpitaṃ nātra sandeho devī māhātmyamuttamam |
yaḥ paṭhet śṛṇuyādvāpi bhaktimān nṛpasattama ||031:038||
sa sukhaṃ yaśaḥ saubhāgyaṃ putra prāptiṃ yathepsitām |
labhate nātra sandeha ityevaṃ brahmaṇo'bravīt ||031:039||
suvalena kṛte rājye purā śakrasya kīrtitā |
dhanadasya purā proktā varuṇasya ca vāyunā ||031:040||
kṛte sthāne kṛtānena tathā śrutvā ca nirṛtaiḥ |
bhuñjīta parayā dṛṣṭayā purī bhagavatī śubhā ||031:041||
[bhuṃjaje ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe rathayātrā vidhimāhātmyaṃ nāmaikatriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[rathayātrāvidhimāhātmya ka; eṣa adhyāya ga pustake nāsti for this matter FN no. not found in the text portion.]
