%%% Chapter 032
dvātriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[adhyāyo'yaṃ gapustake nāsti]
agastya uvāca |

rathayātrāsu māhātmyaṃ brahmaṇā upavarṇitam |
śrutvā prītiṃ parāṃ jagmu karmmayogamapṛcchat ||032:001||
[prapūkaca ka]
śakra uvāca |

bhagavan devatā gāramarccāsthāpana pūjanam |
sammārjjanamupalepaṃ dīpa-vaitānajaṃ phalam ||032:002||
[bhagavat devatā ka]
kṛtvā devyā hyaśeṣantu kiṃ labhante bravīhi naḥ ||032:003ab||
brahmovāca |

gaṅgā narmmadā vindhyādri mujjayinyāmathārvvude ||032:003cd||
[ujjayanpatha arbrude ka]
himavānniṣadhe droṇe sānnidhyāt tiṣṭate śivā |
nadī tīre tu durge ca rathyā-pitṛ-vaneṣu ca ||032:004||
sthāpitā bhavate devī sarvva kāryyārtha siddhidā |
māraṇaṃ śatru vargasya pitṛ sthāne samarcitā ||032:005||
[sāraṇaṃ prākra ka; madārccitā ka ]
ekaliṅge drume śaile gṛhe goṣṭhe trikaṇḍake |
pūjitā yatra dravyāṇāṃ sukhadārogyadā bhavet ||032:006||
[putra ka]
tathā ca sarvvagā sarvvairmokṣadā pūjitā matā |
gurau meṣagate śakra devyārcāṃ yaḥ pratiṣṭhayet ||032:007||
[sasarva ka]
ihaiva sa bhaveda dhanyo mṛto gacchet paraṃ padam |
tasmānmeṣagate śakra uttamā navamī matā ||032:008||
[sarvabhaved ka; sthite ka]
mahādyasmin nāmā'nantaṃ sāmaṃ ca sarvvakāmadam |
devī tatra tadā śakra pāṃsujā api sthāpitā ||032:009||
bhavate phaladā puṃsāṃ karkisthe ca vṛṣadhvajam |
samadṛṣṭi gataṃ kṛtvā ajau mādhava kalpasam ||032:010||
[labhate phala dāstraṃsya ka]
sthāpayed deva deveśaṃ sarvvakāmārthino yadi |
viśeṣaḥ kathitaścātra sarvva kāle'pi maṅgalā ||032:011||
[kāmānvito ka]
yena kenacid dravyeṇa sarvva kāma phalapradā |
tathā ye siddha gandharvā nṛpā vā rājyakāṃkṣiṇaḥ ||032:012||
te yajantu sadā devīṃ sthāpayitvā vidhānataḥ |
na tithirnna ca nakṣatraṃ nopavāso'tra kāraṇam ||032:013||
[vidhānatā ka]
vayamasya prabhāvaṃ tu devyāyā bhaktikāraṇam |
pūjitā vidhinā śakra nṛṇāṃ bhogān prayacchati ||032:014||
[varṣamasya ka]
hema bhāvā ca mṛdvakṣī śailacitrāyasāpi vā |
śakti śūle'jitā devī sarvvakāma phala pradā ||032:015||
yo yasya āyudhaḥ proktastasmiṃstaṃ pratipūjayet |
devī śaktyārccitā puṃsā rājyāyuḥ sutasaukhyadā ||032:016||
yāmye brahmā bhavet kāye rakta varṇo javopamaḥ |
madhye rudra ṛjuḥ śukro vāme kṛṣṇastato hariḥ ||032:017||
devayakṣagrahā nāgā lokeśaḥ sacarāparāḥ |
śūle saṃpūjite vatsa sarvvaṃ bhavati pūjitam ||032:018||
vārkṣaṃ vā śailajāṃ vāpi ratnadhātumayāmapi |
devyāmevaṃ samaṃ ṛkṣaṃ velākaraṇavāsaram ||032:019a-d||
[velākaraṇaṃ vāsava ka]
vidhinā śaka dṛṣṭeṇa daśabāhu trilocanām ||032:019ef||
kārayed bhaktimān yastu devīṃ śāstra viśāradaḥ |
sarvvalakṣaṇasampūrṇāṃ sarvvābharaṇa bhūṣitām ||032:020||
rājantīmuttamāṅgena kavarī lambitena ca |
atha muktāni bhāreṇa dhammilla daṃśitena ???||032:021||
[ślokapaṃcakaṃ ka pustake nāsti]
vyāmiśra sita puṣpairvā alipaṅktīva saṃsthitā |
rudanti tamavakreṇa tiraskṛtaṃ niśākaram ||032:022||
[karavālaṃ ka]
āyataiḥ karṇamaryyādaistaralālola nirmmalaiḥ |
bhrukṣepākṣidhṛtaiḥ pakṣaiḥ ṛá¹juḥ jihvāvalokanaiḥ ||032:023||
bhrūbhaṅga cāpa daṇḍena bhinatti dṛṣṭi sāyakaiḥ |
madhyonnata sagarvveṇa adhareṇa virājate ||032:024||
[bhiṃdatī ka]
āraktā vidrumābhena smitaṃ kiñcit smitānanā |
mayūkha danta jyotsnena cakāsāntīṃ taḍidiva ||032:025||
trirekha kandharāṃ śāntiṃ graivaiyaka vibhūṣitām |
kaṭhina stana bhāreṇa saṃśakto tau nirandhraṇau ||032:026||
mahā samunnatau pīnau vakṣau pīnaunnatau śubhau |
tanoratanuḥ madhyena madhye ca trivalī matā ||032:027||
[mahāsamut tau pānau vakto ttau śubhau ka]
romarājī nitamborddha hyanaṅgāṅkura sūcivat |
vistīrṇa jaghanā kāryyā rambhā-garbhoru komalau ||032:028||
gūḍha gulphau tu padmābhau padmāṅkita sunūpurau |
kāñcit kiṅkiṇī bhāvaṃ taṃ brahma sūtreṇa rājate ||032:029||
keyūra nāga bandhena hyaṅgadaiḥ raktakāñcanaiḥ |
greveyakā kirīṭorddhe sāvaśeṣa viśeṣakam ||032:030||
[vāṃghana ka; maghiśeṣa ka]
rājate ca tṛtīyena locanenālakena ca |
rājantī pītavāsena churitāruṇa reṇunā ||032:031||
dvibhujā yā ca viṃśāṣṭa tāvaddorddanḍadhāriṇī |
asi kheṭaka hastābhyāṃ gadā daṇḍena cāparau ||032:032||
[kalpanā ka]
śaracāpaparetābhyāṃ samudgara cāparau |
paraśu cakra dharau cānyau ḍamarū darpaṇa cāmarau ||032:033||
[paraśuṃ cakadharau ka]
śakti kuṇḍadhṛtau cānyau hala mūṣala cāparau |
pāśa tomara cānyau tu ḍhakkāpaṇava cāparau ||032:034a-d||
[śakti kuṃta ka; śarapa ka]
tarjjayantīva cānyena kurvantī kalakalāravaiḥ ||032:034ef||
abhayaṃ svastikāṅkena aṣṭāviṃśabhujā śivā |
siṃha padmāsanā saṃsthā siṃhāsana vyavasthitā ||032:035||
mahiṣadhnī śiraśchedāntaraṃ śastrograpāṇinām |
tarjjamānaṃ hataṃ mūrdhni nāgapāśena veṣṭitam ||032:036||
[syaddhṛ ka]
ghātamānā ripuṃ devī pūjanīyā purandara |
sthāpitā pūjitā śakra smaratā paṭhatāpi vā ||032:037||
prayacchati śubhān kāmān mano'bhīṣṭān yajennaraḥ |
paṅkeṣu śaila dārvva vā mṛnmaye vāpi vāsava ||032:038||
[paṃkeṣṭe ka]
sopavāsaḥ śuciḥ snātvā kāmakrodha vivarjjitaḥ |
sarvvasaṅgojjhitaḥ prītastanmanā bhāvabhāvitaḥ ||032:039||
[sata ka]
puṣpa gandhopahāraśca haviṣyāntairanekaśaḥ |
tila sarpiryavān hutvā sarvvamaṅgala mantritān ||032:040||
[syatratāt ka]
vastra hemāmvu sampātaiḥ kalasairdevīntu snāpayet |
tatastacchāstra vetāraiḥ pratiṣṭhāntu prakārayet ||032:041||
[vastra hemāṃtu saṃvītai kalavarga vātuṃ snāyet ka; pratiṣṭhā taṃ na kārayet ka]
devīṃ śāstrārtha-tattvājñairmātṛ maṇḍala vedikaiḥ |
bhūta tantra graha vāla gāruḍeṣu kṛta śramaiḥ ||032:042||
pratiṣṭhāntu śivāntaistu yathā śavatyā tu dakṣayet |
pūjayed brāhmaṇāñchakra kanyāṃ bālāstathaiva ca ||032:043||
[pratiṣṭhāpya ka]
dīnādi vikalān sarvvān yathā śaktyā kṣamāpayet |
tadante svasti vācyantu maṅgalā prīyatāṃ mama ||032:044||
sukhaṃ tiṣṭhantu rājāno gau brāhmaṇaprajāstathā |
kṣatra viṭa śūdra vālebhyaḥ sarvvaśānti karābhavā ||032:045||
[śota ka]
sarvvān kāmān prayacchantu ye janāḥ phala kāminaḥ |
tathā stavena cānyena śivagītena toṣayet ||032:046||
[ye janma yāni kāminaḥ ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre pratiṣṭhākarmmayogonāma dvātriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[vānena śivagītena toṣitaḥ ka]
Please check the footnotes.
