%%% Chapter 033
trayastriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ga pustake adhyāyo'yaṃ nāsti]
agastya uvāca |

śrutvaivaṃ debarājena karmmayogaṃ pitāmahāt |
prapaccha ca stavaṃ bhūyaḥ śambhugītaṃ yathā purā ||033:001||
śakra uvāca |

stavaṃ deva purā devyāḥ śambhunā bhārgavasya yat |
kathitaṃ siddhikāmasya tanme brūhi pitāmaha ||033:002||
brahmovāca |

śukreṇa ca purā śakra tapastaptaṃ suduścaram |
divyaṃ varṣa sahasrantu kailāse śikharottame ||033:003||
[sudustarāṃ ka]
tathāpi no'bhavat tasya varadastripurāntakaḥ |
puṣpadantagaṇaḥ stotramudīrayat madhurasvaraḥ ||033:004||
[uttapāpi ka]
taṃ budhvā tadgataṃ cittaṃ śukro vedavidāṃvaraḥ |
stavenānena deveśaṃ toṣayāmāsa bhārgavaḥ ||033:005a-d||
[śambhuḥ ka]
vicitra pada bandhena lalitaṃ madhureṇa ca ||033:005ef||
śukra uvāca |

śakraṃ veda vidaṃ kṛtāñjali puṭaṃ bhaktyā bhave bhāvitam |
saṃsārād bhayabhīta khinnamanasāṃ vijñāpayet śaṃkaram ||033:006a-d ||
[khira ka]
dehaṃ paśyata nityaroga bahulamāyāsa-duḥkhāvṛtam |
bhukṣibhi tṛṣitaṃ vibhīṣaṇa karaṃ nirlajja-kāmāturama ||033:006e-h||
[dehasthānasya ka; dūḥvṛtaṃ ka; bhakṣormi ka]
dṛṣṭvā vañcita mokṣamārga rahitaṃ krodhānaloddīpitam |
śukrovāca maheśvarasya purataḥ stotraṃ tavārādhanam ||033:007a-d ||
saṃsārādvividhān mahābhayakarādatyanta śokānvitān |
karmmā vandha suyaṃntritāt pratisavāṃ prāṇī ghaṭī yantravat ||033:007e-h
[vaddha ka; sva ka; pratisavāt ka]
dṛṣṭvā cañcala toya budabuda samaṃ prāpyeha mānuṣyakam |
sarvaṃ sarvvagatena nānyamatasā naivārccito mohataḥ ||033:008a-d||
[sāhūtaḥ ka]
te dhanyā bhuvi mānavāḥ sukṛtinaste sāttvikāste kṣamāḥ |
teṣāṃ janma kṛtārthakaṃ na ca mṛtāḥ śocyā bhavantīha te ||033:008e-h||
[ṣaṃlikāste ka]
devaṃ paramārthataḥ paśupatiṃ sarvvātmanā saṃśritāḥ |
prāptaṃ kintu na taiḥ pradhānapuruṣai rhṛd vāñchitaṃ tat phalam ||033:009a-d
[kṛtvāṃtitaṃ ka]
brahmopendra marunmahendra vasubhi rvidyādharaiḥ sādaraiḥ| liṃṅgaṃ yasya sadārccitaṃ muni gaṇairanyaiśca daityādibhiḥ ||033:009e-h
[sadārcite ka]
vyāptaṃ yena carācaraṃ jagadidaṃ viśvātmanā mūrtibhiḥ |
kastaṃ kāraṇa-kāraṇaṃ paśupatiṃ devaṃ paraṃ nārccayet ||033:010||
trailokya rājyañca tathāmaratvaṃ nāgendrakanyā surayoṣitāśca |
etāni cānyāni ca te labhante yeṣāṃ haraḥ pratimanā babhūva ||033:011||
ye lokeṣu vibhūtikānti vapuṣo dharmmārtha kāmapradā |
vibhrāṇā maṇiratna kuṇḍalaruci prodabhāsi gaṇḍasthale |
|||033:012a-d||
kurvvanti sva mayūkhakānti kiraṇaiddhaṣṭāndhakārā diśa |
tat sarvvaṃ vividhaṃ prasādya vivudhāḥ prāptā vibhūtiṃ parām ||033:012 e-h||
yannīlotpala patra gandha surabhiṃ pītvā tu rātrau madhu |
kāmaṃ cārū vilāsinā sulalitaṃ satpremamāliṅgatam ||033:013a-d||
[yaśī ka; nīlā ka; vināsinī ka]
yad vidyādharatāṃ gatāḥ sukṛtinastyaktvā tanūṃ mānuṣīm |
tat kāmāri niṣevaṇādapagataṃ teṣāṃ phalaṃ śāśvatam ||033:013e-h ||
[ekomāvi ka]
yanmātaṅga turaṅga mārgeṇa rathāḥ prakhyāta yodhā raṇe |
mattaiścāpi gajairmadaudya visavaiḥ praklinna gaṇḍasthalaiḥ |
|||033:014a-d||
[mākvalasthāḥ ka]
saṃ cūrṇānta mudānvitā saha nṛpaiḥ śvetātapatrocchritaiḥ |
rudrejyābhiratasya tat phalamidaṃ sammucyate nānyathā ||033:014e-h ||
[ saṃ cūrṇati sahastra khaṅga niśitaiḥ sainyāni yasyāliṣāṃ, vibhrāṃjantinṛpāḥ śivārdhana rodhansarva hita ceṣṭitam |
sattaibhairmadavāridhautavadanai nīlālasaiḥ pārthivā, kurvāṇa varasājirbhiḥ dṛśa diśo reṇvaṃdhakārākulāḥ ka ]
aiśvaryyāt pravarairgajaiśca turagairyad gamyate līlayā |
lagnairlagna viśiṣṭa śobhana guṇairyannāma saṃkīrttyate ||033:015a-d||
tāmbūlaṃ triphalendu pallava yutaṃ vipreṣu yadgīyate |
taccittaṃ hara sādhyapādapatanād bhaktistu maukṣe sthitā ||033:015e-h ||
yannīlāmbuja koṣa komala dala protphullanetrāḥ striyaḥ |
kāñcī mekhala nupuroruyugala vyāsaktacīnāṃśukāḥ ||033:016a-d||
[parīlāṃvuja ka; komalāsana dalā ka]
dāsyaṃ yānti vikampitastanabhara vyāvanditā bhrūlatāḥ |
prītyarthaṃ ratinātha dehadahanaḥ saṃsevyate nānyathā ||033:016e-h||
[ratidayita ka]
sindūra baddha madhuvāsita nāgavṛndam |
yad bhūpate kanaka daṇḍa sitañca chatram ||033:017a-d||
[siṃddhabhrakta ka; yadvīyate ka]
yaccañcalaṃ cāmara cārū vidhūyamānam |
tatsarvvamīśa caraṇe praṇatasya puṃsaḥ ||033:017e-h||
vīṇā-veṇu-mṛdaṅga-vādya paṇavaiḥ samÌyoga bhāvānvitaiḥ |
nārībhiḥ mada-vihvalābhiraniśaṃ ye gīyamānā nṛpāḥ||033:018a-d||
śaṅkhendu sphaṭikāvadātadhavale harmyottame saṃsthitā |
te modanti divaukasā iva ciraṃ yeṣāṃ prasanna śivaḥ ||033:018e-h||
[hampetti me ka; śaṃvidu ka; paṃktiriyaṃ nāsti ka pustake]
yat kāntā vadanāravinda daśana jyotsanābhirāmojvalam |
śvāsomodacala turaṅga capalaṃ proṅkhelanā cañcalam ||033:019a-d||
[paṃkti dvayaṃ nāsti ka pustake]
vinyastaṃ maṇibhājaneṣu vidhivad bandhūka rāgaṃ madhu |
nīlāmbhoruhavāsitaṃ sura gurau śuśrūṣayā pīyate ||033:019e-h||
yat kāñcī kala nāda pīna jaghanavyāsakta cīnāṃśukāḥ |
karṇāntāyata locanāḥ suvadanā lāvaṇya lavdhāspadāḥ ||033:020a-d||
yaddāsītvamupāgatāḥ kṣitibhujāmāśā vidheyāḥ striyaḥ |
tat sarvva bhava-bhakti pūta manasāṃ rājñāṃ jagat tatphalam ||033:020e-h||
ye suptā rajanīṣu mandiravare paryyaṅkabimbe śubhe |
nārībhi rmmadavihvalābhiraniśaṃ sotkaṇṭhamāliṅgitāḥ ||033:021a-d||
[sābhināla ka]
nidrānāśamihopayānti madhuraiḥ saṅgīta tūryyasvanaiḥ |
tat sarvvaṃ samupārjitasya vidhivacchambhoḥ praṇītaṃ phalam ||033:021e-h||
nānā yantra sahasrasāpi racitaṃ bhīmāvaruddhākulam |
taṃ bhitvā praviśanti cārū vimalaṃ daityāṅganāntaḥpuram ||033:022a-d||
[tadbhitvā ka]
siddhaṃ dravya rasāyanaṃ yuvatayaḥ kāmāśca kāmānugāḥ |
tat sarvvaṃ sulabhaṃ bhavet sudhiyāṃ prītena kāmāriṇā ||033:022e-h||
ye sarvve śaraṇāgatāḥ supuruṣāstyaktānyakāryyā daśā |
traikālyārccana japya homa rniratādrogādibhi vajiṃtāḥ ||033:023a-d||
te bhogān vividhānubhūya sakalān kālena karmma kṣayād |
vittaiśvaryya samanvitāḥ kṣititale jāyanti te bhūmipāḥ ||033:023e-f||
ye mūḍhā na śrayanti varadaṃ saṃsāra-duḥkhacchidam |
devaṃ sarvvasurāsura praṇamitaṃ śambhuṃ paraṃ kāraṇam ||033:024a-d||
[kāraṇānte ka]
te loke parapiṃḍatarpaṇaparā dīnāḥ sadā duḥkhitā |
jāyante bhuvi mānavāḥ kuvasanā dharmmārtha kāmojjhitāḥ ||033:024e-h||
ye lokādhipati surāsura gurūṃ brahmendra sampūjitam |
vedādyanta ṣaḍaṅga yoga vihitaṃ sāṃkhyādibhiḥ kalpitam ||033:025a-d||
sarvvajñaṃ prabhumīśvaraṃ trinayanaṃ sarvvātmanā bhāvitāḥ |
te bhūyo na kalā kalaṅka gahanaṃ paśyanti yornimukham ||033:025e-h||
ye tvanye sukṛtaiṣiṇaḥ pratidinaṃ protthāya bhāvānvitāḥ |
karpūrāguru candanaiḥ surucitaiḥ sragbhistathā bhūṣaṇaiḥ ||033:026a-d||
kṣīrādisnapanairvidhāna vihitaiḥ kurvanti śarvvārccanam |
bhogān sarvva gatānubhūya sudhiyo gacchanti divyaṃ padam ||033:026e-h||
[kurvīti ka]
ye kecit kupathāśritā jaḍadhiyo mandāmamajñāḥ śaṭhāḥ |
devaṃ śāntamajaṃ pradhānapuruṣaṃ nindanti mohācchivam |
||033:027a-d||
mṛtyodgocaramāgatāḥ yama bhaṭairnānāvidhaiḥ śāsanaiḥ |
śāmyante narakeṣu te prativalaiścākrandamāṇā bhṛśam ||033:027e-h||
dānaṃ bhūtadayā gurūpadaśanaṃ kṣāntirna caivāṃjitā |
satyaṃ śaucamahiṃsratā śamadama tyāgo'nukampā tathā ||033:028a-d||
yeṣāṃ naivamihāsti mūḍhamanasāṃ śarvvāccanaṃ kvacit |
teṣāṃ naṣṭa piśāca kāgatadhiyāṃ puṃsāṃ vibhūtiḥ kutaḥ ||033:028e-h||
dvaiṣṭārastu vasya ce kupuruṣā gacchanti te'dhogatim |
tāmisre krakacāsi patra narake kumbhī mahā raurave ||033:029a-d||
[ddhaiṣṭārastā ka; kumbhā ka]
yoni mārga sahasra khinnagamanāḥ prāpyeha mānuṣyakam |
rogārto jaḍa vāsanāndhavadhirā jāyanti yonau khalāḥ ||033:029e-h||
[rorgātto ka]
janma-vyādhi -jarā viyoga maraṇa kleśādibhiḥ santatām |
bhūtiṃ cañcala sāgarormicapalaṃ svapnopamaṃ jīvitam ||033:030a-d||
mātā-pitṛ-kalatra-putra suhṛdo ye ke'pi bandhātmakā |
jñātvaivaṃ naralokamadhruvamimaṃ śarvvaṃ sadā saṃśrayet ||033:030e-h||
yairdattaṃ na dhanaṃ yathāvibhavataḥ pātreṣu dīneṣu vā |
vidyā nāgamitā yaśo na vitataṃ śīlaṃ na saṃrakṣitam ||033:031a-d||
[dīneṣu ka]
satyaṃ nādhigataṃ tapo na caritaṃ kīrtirna vikrāmitā |
teṣāṃ kṣema śivaṃ na vidyati nṛṇāṃ muktvā harārādhanam ||033:031e-h||
[niṣkāsitā ka]
yeṣāṃ na śambhucaraṇāgrata bhaktivādaḥ |
kṣuṇṇāṃ lalāṭa śatajarjjaritaṃ kapālam ||033:032a-d||
teṣāṃ kuto bahula candana carccitāni |
muktā phalārccita vadhūstana-maṇḍalāni ||033:032e-h||
ye tvāṃ vibho suparikalpana kalpiteṣu |
samyak caranti vividheṣu śivārccaneṣu ||033:033a-d||
te cārū tuṅga ghanakuṅkumapiñjarīṣu |
vidyādhariṣu nivasanti kucāntareṣu ||033:033e-h||
pravrajyā na kṛtā vidhāna vihitā uktā tu yā śambhunā |
śaivajñāna mahārṇavasya vidhivannaivañca pāraṃ gatam ||033:034a-d||
puṣpaiśca sukarṇikāra tilakaiḥ nābhyarccitaḥ śṛladhṛka |
kālo'yaṃ para piṇḍa tarpaṇa paraiḥ kākairiva preṣitaḥ ||033:034e-h||
na dhyātaṃ padamīśvarasya vidhivat saṃsāra vicchittaye |
naivābhi śrutibhi stuto'harahaḥ śambhuḥ vibhurbhūtale ||033:035a-d||
naivāpyutkaṭa gandhadhūpa kusumaiḥ pūjā kṛtā śaṅkare |
dhātrā nūnamakāraṇaṃ vayamiha sṛṣṭā jagat pūraṇe ||033:035e-h||
saṃsargāt kautukādvā kṣaṇamapi yaiḥ japtaṃ pādeṣu padmeṣu śambho |
yāti brahmendra viṣṇu draviṇa pati purāṃstrīnati kramya lokān ||033:036a-d||
śāntyā bhāvena yastaṃ praṇamati satataṃ sarvva vinyasta sargī |
saṃchinnaḥ kleśa pāśaiḥ praviśati virajo rudra tejo nidhānam ||033:036e-h||
yat kiñcāsana japya homa niratā rāgādibhiḥ varjjitāḥ |
śambhoḥ pāda nipāta ghṛṣṭa śirasaḥ pratyaṅmukhāḥ patniṣu ||033:037a-d||
[patsu ka]
teṣāmeva nigūḍha nūpura varā cañcaccalan mekhalā |
sambhrāntāgraja paṅgajodyatakarā paryyeti lakṣmīḥ sthiram ||033:037e-h||
[bhuṃtāyata ka]
yairnādyāpyanyajanmasitakuvalayaiḥ miśritābhiḥ sitābhiḥ |
mālābhiḥ mālatīnāṃ tribhiramaraguruṇārccito nolakaṇṭhaḥ ||033:038a-d||
te vidyāvittahīnāḥ pracalita manasaḥ kṣuttṛṣākṣāmakaṇṭhā |
loke'smin doṣaduṣṭāḥ paribhava vibhavāste ca nityaṃ bhavanti ||033:038e-h||
Footnote Reference nos.1, 2, 5 and 6 are not found in the text portion.
ye mānavā vigatarāga parāparajñā yogeśvaraṃ suraguruṃ satataṃ smaranti |
dhyānena te prahata kilviṣa mohajālā mātuḥ payodhara rasaṃ na punaḥ pivanti ||033:039||
[te vidyā ka; sarvasya yatsarvadā ka]
tad gātraṃ praṇipātareṇudhavalaṃ sarvvasya yat sarvvadā |
te netre tapasārjjite surucire tābhyāṃ haro dṛśyate ||033:040a-d||
[paṃkti nāsti ka pustake]
sā vṛddhi vimalendu śaṅkha ghavalā yā śaṅkaradhyāyinī |
sā jihvā mṛdubhāṣiṇī hitakarī yā stauti nityaṃ śivam ||033:040e-h||
taccitta capalaṃ cinoti kuśalaṃ yanniścalaṃ śaṅkaram |
te śrotre parame śivāmṛtarasaṃ yābhyāṃ haraḥ śrūyate ||033:041a-d||
te hastāḥ śiva dharmma karmma niratāḥ pūjā pramāṇotsukā |
tau pādau samayau pradakṣiṇaratau nityaṃ vibhorbhāvitau ||033:041e-h||
pāpaṃ pāpa rataṃ hyaśuddha manasaṃ nirlajja ghagnavratam |
krūraṃ taskarasīrṣakaṃ śaṭhadhiyaṃ tṛṣṇādhikaṃ nirddayam |
||033:042a-d||
[kūraṃ takṛra mīrṣya ka]
kāma-krodhavaśaṃ kṛtaghnacapalaṃ tṛṣṇāturaṃ jihmalam |
mūrkha hiṃsana sūcakaṃ paśupate toṣākaraṃ trāhi mām ||033:042e-h||
[dharma sūcaka hiṃsakaṃ ka]
dīnaṃ duḥkhitakaṃ kucailamalinaṃ jihmaṃ śaṭhaṃ durbhagam |
kṣudraṃ pāpamatiṃ svadharmma calitaṃ bahvāśinaṃ nirddhanam ||033:043a-d||
andhaṃ vyādhita niṣṭhuraṃ vyasaninaṃ sadbhiḥ sadā ninditam |
mūrkhaṃ dharmma vivarjjitaṃ paśupate doṣākaraṃ trāhi mām ||033:043e-h||
[ahaṃ ka; nighuraṃ ka]
imaṃ stavaṃ śakva vinirmmitaṃ paṭhan dine-dine kratuphalamāpnuyānnaraḥ |
labha tyasau yadbhihitaṃ purātane tallakṣaye gacchati śāśvataṃ padam ||033:044||
No clarity in the print. Checking is needed.
evaṃ stutaḥ purā śambhuḥ stotreṇānena vāsava |
tutoṣa deva deveśaḥ śaśāṅkāṅkita śekharaḥ ||033:045||
īśvara uvāca |

varaṃ brūhi grahādhyakṣa yat manasi varttate |
surāsurādhipatyaṃ te dadāmi bhṛgunandanam ||033:046||
[hṛdi vyavasthitam ka]
śakra uvāca |

yadi tuṣṭo'si me deva kṛpā vā varttate tava |
tadāhyārādhanaṃ devyāḥ śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ ||033:047||
[śrotuṃtatvataḥ ka]
īśvara uvāca |

śruṇu vatsa pravakṣyāmi devyārādhanamuttamam |
karmmayajñantu yajñānāṃ sukaraṃ sumahatphalam ||033:048||
sāṃvatsarī yathā pūjā sukālena samārabhet |
evaṃ nakṣatravedhādīn kuryyāt kanda phalāśinaḥ ||033:049||
[āphalena ka; dhenvāhi ka ga]
yava sarpiḥpraghāsī ca gomūtraṃ dadhi gomayam |
pavitraṃ vihitaṃ tantre asavatānāñca bhārgava ||033:050||
[prasattīra ka; gotsaraṃ ka]
devī vrataṃ pravakṣyāmi sarvvakāma prasādhakam |
śrāvaṇe śukla pakṣe tu aṣṭamyāṃ vāyu-bhojanaḥ ||033:51||
snātvā sārdrayaṭī bhūtvā jitakrodhaḥ kṣamānvitaḥ |
devīṃ saṃsnāpya toyena punaḥ kṣīreṇa snāpayet ||033:052||
[paṭho ka]
tato gūggula dhūpañca saturukṣaṃ pradāpayet |
tatogandhodakasnānaṃ punastāṃ yena snāpayet ||033:053||
[tathā ka]
śrī khaṇḍena samālabhya bilvapatraiśca pūjayeta |
pāyasaṃ dāpayed devyā nivedya tena bhojayet ||033:054||
[patreṇa ka ga]
kanyā dvijāṃśca śaktyā tu teṣāmÌ dadyācca dakṣiṇām |
kātyāyanīti uccārya prīyatāṃ mama sarvvadā ||033:055||
ātmataḥ pāvanaṃ tacca kṛtvā āpnoti bhārgava |
āśvamedha phalaścāgryaṃ devyā lokañca, gacchati ||033:056||
[pāraṇaṃ ka; kulāha ka; maśraṃ ka ga]
tadāgata imāṃ bhūmiṃ pṛthivyāṃ jāyate nṛpaḥ |
tena sa labhate yogaṃ śivā prāpti karaṃ param ||033:057||
māse prauṣṭhapade śukra gośrṛṅgāgra gṛhītayā |
mṛdayā hyātmajo hyaṃgamupalipya tu snāpayet ||033:058||
tadā āmalakaiḥ snātvā śuciḥ saṅgavivarjjitaḥ |
pūjayet yūthikā puṣpai rdevīṃ kṣīreṇa snāpitām ||033:059||
[snīlā ka]
candanodaka miśreṇa kuṅkumena vilepayet |
tataḥ pūpaka naivedyaṃ kandayanyāmÌśca dāpayet ||033:060||
[karṇāśca ka]
aguruṃ dhūpena dadyāt tila tailena dīpikān |
tena tā bhojayet kanyā dvijān sadvṛttivartinaḥ ||033:061||
pāṣanḍān nāvaloketa nīcān śāstra-bahiṣkṛtān |
dakṣiṇā śaktito deyā svasti vācyeta maṅgalam ||033:062||
pāvanañcātmanastacca sautrāmaṇi-phalaṃ labheta |
gacchate viṣṇu lokañca tadā vipro'bhijāyate ||033:063||
dhanāḍhye mahati gotre veda vedānta pārage |
putravān dhanavān bhogī sukhaṃ prāpya śivī bhavet ||033:064||
āśvine aṣṭamī śukle nadī mṛdbhiśca snāpayet |
tato devīṃ snāpayed vatsa dadhinā hyudakena ca ||033:065||
[mṛdāsi ka]
ālabhya rocanā mantrairdhūpo deyastu bālakam |
saṃnakhaṃ sita-tāmiśraṃ padmapuṣpaiśca arccayeta ||033:066||
[candrai rbhupaṃdeyaṃ tu ka; miśreyaja ka]
naivedyaṃ rohitaṃ māṃsamājaṃ vā śalyakaṃ tathā |
godhūma vikṛtiṃ bhakṣyān ghṛta pakvāni dāpayet ||033:067||
[rauhiṣaṃ ka ga; śalpaṃkajaṃprivā ka; rikṛti rbhaktā ka]
tena kanyāstu bhojīyād dvijāṃścāpi kṣamāpayet |
śaktito dakṣiṇā deyā ātmanastacca bhojanam ||033:068||
[anasta vṛtabhojanāṃ ka ga]
go sahasra pradānasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ |
ārogī sukhavān dhanyo jāyate iha mānavaḥ ||033:069||
durgā nāmantu kīrtayet tasyā loke mahīyate |
kārttike darbhamūlārbhirmṛdbhiḥ snāyāt tu bhārgava ||033:070||
[kīrttiyā ga]
devīṃ gandhodakaiḥ snāpya auśīraiḥpūjya lepayeta |
dhūpaṃ pañcarasaṃ deyaṃ tila tailena dīpakān ||033:071||
[dīpayeta ka]
naivedyaṃ pāyasaṃ sarpiḥ kanyā vipreṣu cātmanaḥ |
bhojanaṃ svasti vācyeta dakṣiṇāṃ prīyatāṃ śivā ||033:072||
anenavidhinā vatsa vidyādāna phalaṃ labhet |
veda vedāṅga tattvajñaḥ tadante śivatāṃ vrajet ||033:073||
[avana ka ga; labhet ka; vedāṃte ka]
mārgaśīrṣe nabhe māsi hyaṣṭamyāṃ giri pṛṣṭhataḥ |
sthāpya devīṃ tataḥ snāyāt tīrtha toyena bhārgava ||033:074||
[aṣṭabhyaṃ giḍi mṛddabhiḥ ka ga]
lepayet bālakaṃ kuṣṭhaṃ pūjā jātī gajāhvayaiḥ |
dhūpaṃ kṛṣṇāgurūṃ dadyād ghṛta dīpān nivedayet ||033:075||
[pūṃjayeda ka; kuṃkuṣṭhaṃ ka; nibīdhayet ka]
dadhi bhaktantu naivedyaṃ kanyāstenaiva bhojayet |
dakṣiṇaṃ śaktito dadyādātmanastacca pāraṇam ||033:076||
imāṃ me prīyatāṃ vācyaṃ vājapeya phalaṃ labhet |
ihaiva dhanavān bhogī dehānte brahmaṇaḥ padam ||033:077||
[tumā ka; dhanat ka]
pauṣāṣṭamīṣu dūrvvāgraiḥ snātvā śukla paricchadaḥ |
jita krodho advandvaśca devī karpūra vāriṇā ||033:078||
snāpayet lepayecchakra māsīvālaka candanaiḥ |
dhūpañca nirdahet prājñaḥ pūjā nīla kurūṇṭakaiḥ ||033:079||
kṛṣarāguḍa naivedyaṃ kanyā bhojayet tena vai |
ātmanaḥ pāvanaṃ tacca śaktyā dakṣeta vācayet ||033:080||
nārāyaṇī sadā prītā mama devī prasīdatu |
kṛtena graharājendra bhūri dāna phalaṃ labhet ||033:081||
[bhūmi ka ga]
śubha godhana sampannaḥ paratra śivāmāpnuyāt |
māghe māsi cājagāvaṃ mṛdbhiḥ snātvā tu bhārgava ||033:082||
devīṃ toyena saṃsnāpya tathā kṣīra ghṛtena ca |
snāpayet punastoyena lepayeta kuṅkumena ca ||033:083||
dhūpaṃ devadalaṃ dadyāt kundapuṣpaiśca pūjayet |
ghṛtapūrṇañca naivedyaṃ kanyāṃ viprāṃśca tena vai ||033:084||
bhojayedātmanastacca dakṣiṇāṃ prīyatāṃ jayā |
sarvva yāga phalaṃ śakra labhate nātra saṃśayaḥ ||033:085||
[śivā ka ga; vipra ka]
phālgune sarṣapaiḥ snātvā devīmāmra-phalāṃbunā |
tathā ikṣurasenaiva bhūyastenodakena ca ||033:086||
rocane lepayet pūjā śata patrikayā graha |
dīpo ghṛtena dhūpaṃ ca candanaṃ ghṛta śarkarā ||033:087||
[phalā ka]
naivedyaṃ śoka varjyañca bhojanaṃ kanyakāsu ca |
ātmanastacca kurvvīta dakṣiṇā svasti vācayet ||033:088||
vijayā sukhadā vityamastu me cintitāni ca |
anena vidhinā śakra rājasūya phalaṃ labhet ||033:089||
labhate vāsanā yukto yato devīmayaṃ jagat |
caitrāṣṭamīṣu snāpayet mātṛsthāna mṛdambumiḥ ||033:090||
devīṃ tīrtha jalaiḥ snāpya lepyā madavilepanaiḥ |
dhūpaṃ turūṣka auśīraṃ yuktiyuktena pūjayet ||033:091||
naivedyaṃ śālijaṃ bhaktaṃ śarkarā kanyakāsvāpi |
ātmanastacca vācyantu śaktito dakṣiṇāṃ dadet ||033:092||
[nivedya ka ga]
ajitā sarvvakāmānāṃ pūraṇāya sukhāya me |
viprāḥkanyāḥ samaṃ vācyā homadāna phalaṃ labhet ||033:093||
sahakāra phalaṃ snānaṃ vaiśākhe'ṣṭamīṣu ca |
ātmano devatāṃ snāpya māṃsī bālaka vāribhiḥ ||033:094||
lepanaṃ madhu karpūraṃ dhūpaṃ pañca sugandhikam |
devyā pūjāñca kurvvīta ketakī madanena ca ||033:095||
kṣīraṃ śarkara naivedyaṃ kanyā vipreṣu bhojanam |
ātmanaḥ pāraṇaṃ tadvat dakṣiṇāṃ śaktito vadet ||033:096||
aparājītāṃ bhavānīṃ svasti nāmena vācayet |
prīyatāṃ sarvvakālaṃ me īpsitantu prayacchatu ||033:097||
[nātmānatmana ka; ka pustake viśati paṃktī na santi paraṃ ga pustake santi ]
sarvvatīrthābhiṣekantu anenāpnoti bhārgava |
sūryyalokaṃ vrajedante tat tulyo bhavate graha ||033:098||
aṣṭamyāñcaiva jyeṣṭhasya tilaiḥ snāyādvicakṣaṇaḥ |
sarvva saṅga parityāgī devīṃ jātiphalāmbunā ||033:099||
snāpayet lepayet tena candanena sugandhinā |
tato vijayenduḥ puṣpaiḥ pūjayed grahasattamaḥ ||033:100||
naivedyaṃ saktavo devyāḥ śarkarāḥ kanyakāsvapi |
dakṣiṇā śaktito deyā carccikāṃ prati vācayet ||033:101||
labhatai śukra yajñasya sautrāmaṇisamaṃ phalam |
aṣṭamī caiva āṣāḍhe niśātoyena snāpayet ||033:102||
tato devīṃ jalakuṣṭhaṃ vāriṇā udakena ca |
snātvā lepayet karpūraṃ candanaṃ rocanāmbubhiḥ ||033:103||
dhūpaṃ candana karpūra vālakāsita śalyakaiḥ |
bhaktyā śarkara pūrṇāni śubhāni yāni kāni ca ||033:104||
dāpayet kanyakāṃ viprān bhojanaṃ hyātmanastathā |
śaktito dakṣiṇā deyā mahiṣadhnīti kīrttayeta ||033:105||
[the note, at the beginning of the word dāpayet not found]
dīpa mālā ghṛtenaiva sarvvakāmān prayacchati |
sarvvayajña mahīdāna sarvva tīrtha phalaṃ labhet ||033:106||
etad vrata varaṃ śukra mayā brahmaṇā viṣṇunā |
jagato hitamicchadbhiścīrṇa durgā vrataṃ mahat ||033:107||
bhānunā graha vidhvaṃsamanena kṛtavān purā |
tathā devāsurā yakṣa-nāga-kinnara-mānavaiḥ ||033:108||
apsarobhistathā strībhiḥ saubhāgyasya vivṛddhaye |
kṛtavān graha śārddūla tvamapi kuryyā yathāvidhi ||033:109||
śravaṇādapi prāpnoti sarvvakāma sukhāni ca |
iṣṭāni labhate puṃso vandhyā putraṃ prasūyate ||033:110||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre durgāvrataṃ nāma trayastriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devyavatāre durgāvratam - ka ga] [paṃktaḥ rna santi ka pustake reference no. not found in the text for this note]
