%%%%
%%% Chapter 039
ekonacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

śaunaka uvāca |

yeṣu yeṣu ca tīrtheṣu pūjitā surasattamaiḥ |
pūrvvamindrādimi devī tīrthāṃstān pravra vīhi naḥ ||039:001||
manurūvāca |

brahmaṇā puṣkare devī pūjitā siddha kāminā |
kārttikyāṃ sarvva devaiśca tatraiva munisattama ||039:002||
[siddhi kāmini ka ga]
himavadgirau mahāpuṇye nandā rūdreṇa pūjitā |
sarvvakāma prasiddhayarthaṃ khaḍga kheṭaka dhāriṇī ||039:003||
[naimiṣeca tathāraṇye viṣṇunā pūjitā śivā |
mallākhye parvatai devī ambā sūryeṇa pūjitā |
| ka; khaṃḍa ka ]
kāmākhyājāmadagnyena kiṣkindhye parvvate nutā |
devī maheśvarī śakra pūjyate kāśikāśrame ||039:004||
[kālākhya ka ga; kālikāśrame ka ga]
sarvvakāma susiddhayartha rajeti veda parvvate |
yajedbhaumātmajo devīṃ kāmākhye girikandare ||039:005||
[sarva kāma prasiddhayartha kuṃjo vaivede parvvate |
patedbhaumārthajo devīṃ kaulākhya girikaṃdare ka]
kāśyapo yajate devīṃ sarasvatyāstaṭe śubhām |
pūrvvasindhau yajeddevīṃ sanako nāma bhāvitaḥ ||039:006||
[sarasvatyāstaṭe śubhe ka]
dakṣiṇe vāma nāmā ca kārtikeya samanvitām |
laṅkāyāṃ yajate devīṃ rākṣasendro vibhīṣaṇaḥ ||039:007||
[samanvitaḥ ka ]
paścime varūṇo devo yajate bhāvitoṃ'bhasā |
uttare nandikālau ca kailāse tau prapūjayet ||039:008||
pragastya śiṣyā munayo yajanti bhāvitāṃ śivām |
kaṇvāśrame mahāpuṇye dharmmāraṇye sadā śivām ||039:009||
kaṇvo nāma muni śreṣṭho yajate kāśyapātmajaḥ |
mahākāle mahādevī koṭitīrthe surottamaiḥ ||039:010||
[kauri ka]
pūjitā sarvva kāmāṇi prayacchatyavicāraṇāt |
bhadrākhye tu vare devī tuṣṭā hyāsīt purandara||039:011||
[vicāraṇyat ka; tuṣṭā āsītpuraṃdara ka ga]
māndhātā nāma rājendraḥ tṛtīye yaḥ praśaṃsitaḥ |
dilīpasya tathā devī tuṣṭā kāveri saṅgame ||039:012||
[māṃdhātā yamarāje iṣṭatīye yaḥ praśaṃtāṃ ka; tuṣṭā kāreri harisaṃgame]
gokarṇe rājasenasya ajāpālasya danḍake |
dhanvantaraḥ purā tuṣṭo ganḍakyāḥ saṅgame mune ||039:013||
ātreyasya mahāśoṇe nade tuṣṭā tu ambikā |
mahodaye mahādevī paraśurāmeṇa toṣitā ||039:014||
koṭi munḍeti vikhyātā pīṭhakṣetra śivopari |
mahārājeti yā devī munḍipīṭhagatā mune ||039:015||
[pīṭhe kṣeti śiropari ka ga; muṇḍa ka]
sārvva bhauma śiraistasyāḥ pīṭhaṃ rāmeṇa kalpitam |
khanḍa munḍā tathā devī aparā tena pūjitā ||039:016||
gatiṃ divyāṃgatauyena saha nakṣatra cāribhiḥ |
malayādrau tathā devī aghorā nāma pūjitā ||039:017||
jāmadagyena laṅkādrau kāliketi tathā purā |
pūjitā vijayā nāma śākadvīpe mahodayā ||039:018||
[śālmaleti varāṃganā ka please check the footnote]
kuśadvīpe tathā caṇḍāsarvvadevaṃ-prapūjitā |
krauñce'ti yoginī nāma śālmale'ti varāṅganā ||039:019||
[varṇī ka; varāṃganā kulā ka please check the footnote ]
mandare dhūtimākhyātā rāma bhadre jayāvahā |
puṣkare kīrttyate devī nāmnā nārāyaṇīti ca ||039:020||
[mārjjāre bhṛti ka ga; nāma nārāyaṇeti ka]
jalamadhye gatā devya plavā helāprakīrttitāḥ |
parvvatordhvagatā devyā dhāraṇā dharaṇā matā ||039:021||
[pravāhena ka]
etāḥ paurāṇikā devyo jāmadagnyena pūjitāḥ |
mahādharmma vināśārthaṃ brahmaṇāmitatejasā ||039:022||
mahādevī purārādhyā vadaryyākhye tu āśrame |
tapastapyati govindaḥ pūjitaḥ padmajanmanā ||039:023||
[gauciṃdaḥ ka]
evaṃ sarvvagatā devī mantra vidyāgameṣu ca |
saṃsthitā mātṛ tantre ca jyeṣṭhe tantre ca bhairave ||039:024||
pūrvvaṃ śukreṇa deveśaḥ pṛcchito vṛṣavāhanaḥ |
mantrāṇāṃ kiṃ balaṃ deva vidyānāñca maheśvara ||039:025||
īśvara uvāca |

mantrāṇāṃ paramaṃ vīryyaṃ vidyānāṃ paramaṃ valam |
śrūyatāṃ kathayiṣyāmi saṃkṣepād bhṛgunandana ||039:026||
brahmaṇā kathitaṃ pūrvva tacchraṇuṣva samāhitaḥ |
āsīd daityo valo nāma mahābala parākramaḥ ||039:027||
deva-gandharvva-yakṣāṇāṃ candrendra-bhayakārakaḥ |
yena viṣṇuryamaḥ sūryyo'gni ājau prapīḍitaḥ ||039:028||
[prakīḍitā ka]
anilānala rakṣāśca varūṇaśca vaśīkṛtāḥ |
saṃyamya yena nāgendrā mahābhogā mahāviṣāḥ ||039:029||
[brahmā ca ka; mahādhiṣā ka]
garūḍaśca kṛto bhṛtyaḥ sadājñāmati varttinaḥ |
yena saṃlikhya śailendraḥ kandukākṛti kāritaḥ ||039:030||
[varddhanaḥ ka ga]
krīḍārthaṃ yena viprendra girayaḥ prathitā bhuviḥ |
tena devāḥ sabrahmādyā divi saṃsthāśca cālitāḥ ||039:031||
[vidi ka]
dattaṃ sthānantu pātālaṃ samayaṃ śaradāṃ śatam |
tathā te bhayamāpannā mānaṃ tyaktvā gatā gurūm ||039:032||
[bhayamāpaśya ka; mānatyo ka]
pṛcchanti vinayāt sarvve śakrasya hitakāriṇaḥ |
kenopāyena devānāṃ svargavāso bhaveddvija ||039:033||
tvameva śāstravettā no hitaḥ śakrasya nityaśāḥ |
śaṅkodadhi-nimagnānāmatipotā bhava tvara ||039:034||
[balidāneva ka]
evaṃ pṛṣṭaḥ sa devaistu gurūrvacanamavravīt ||039:035ab||
bṛhaspatirūvāca |

yavayaṃ dānavaḥ śakra na yuddhe bhavate vaśaḥ ||039:035cd||
dātā sattava valopetaḥ svakāryamakhileṣvapi |
atastasya prahetavyo viṣṇurmāyāmahodadhi ||039:036||
dvirūpadharo bhūtvā yācanāya vadhāya ca |
guruṇā coditā devātataste nidhanaṃ prati ||039:037||
raṇena kṣayamāyāti ajayaḥ saṅgare yataḥ |
ataḥ kapaṭamāsthāya prārthanīyaḥ kratuṃ prati ||039:038||
gatāḥ sarvve tataḥ śāntā yatra devo janārdanaḥ |
mādhavena tato devā dṛṣṭvā bhaya samākulāḥ ||039:039||
kramārdhyāsana ālāpaiḥ sarvve te saṃstutā bhṛśam |
pṛcchitāstataḥ sarvve'pi kimāyātāvadan surāḥ ||039:040||
[ślokapaṃcakaṃ nāsti ka pustake]
devā ūvuḥ |

valena balinā deva(FN) sarvve vitrāsitā vayam |
māyāvī tvaṃ vadhe tasya nānyopāyo bhavet kvacit ||039:041||
[matter not found in the FN portion]
viṣṇurūvāca |

karomi bhavatāmiṣṭaṃ kintvasau balasaṃyutaḥ |
sāliko nayavettā ca sarvva śāstrārtha pāragaḥ ||039:042||
gūḍha mantra vicāro syāt dharmmaika kṛta niścayaḥ |
tasya māyāṃ kathaṃ karttuṃ śakyate surasattamāḥ ||039:043||
paraikā bhavate vidyā mama dattātha śūlinā |
mohinī nāma vikhyātā mohaṃ sā kurute bhṛśam ||039:044||
ato'haṃ tasya nāśāya smarāmi parameśvarīm |
smaritvā paramāṃ vidyāṃ dvijabhāvo janārdanaḥ ||039:045||
madhyakāyaḥ suveśaśca vedapāṭhī savistarī |
parigrahī hutāśasya khyāpayanto vrajan japet ||039:046||
[kṣapayannabravītejapana kha]
yajñārthaṃ yācanāṃ kasya karomi kathyatāṃ mama |
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sūryya tejābhaṃ yukto viprairvrajet suraḥ||039:047||
valaste yajña niṣpattiṃ karoti dvijasattama |
hemakūṭe mahāśaile tiṣṭhate dānavottamaḥ ||039:048||
sarvvajño'pi mahāmāyī vañcanāya tadā gataḥ |
mohinīṃ japamānastu vidyāṃ parama siddhidām ||039:049||
[paṃkti rnāsti ka pustake]
vicitraṃ danurājasya puraṃ sarvva-purottamam |
prāviśadveda vādātmā paṭhamāno janārdanaḥ ||039:050||
dvāraṃ gatvā surendrasya kuryyāt prādhyayanaṃ tadā |
dvārapālo vadatyevaṃ śrutvā vedadhvaniṃ śubham ||039:051||
purāṇi ratnāni śubhaṃ dadāmi yācyaṃ yat tava |
iṣṭaṃ dānaṃ dvijaśreṣṭhaṃ durlabhañca mahāmate ||039:052||
tenoktaṃ darśanaṃ dvāḥstha dīyatāṃ danusattama |
tadā sa pūrvvamādiṣṭaḥ preṣayāmāsa taṃ nṛpam ||039:053||
valinaṃ bala sampannaṃ dānavaṃ suramardakam |
dānodyatakaraṃ bhadraṃ dṛṣṭavā prītyāvabhāṣata ||039:054||
kimāyāto bhavāṃścātra kāryyaṃ vipra taduddiśa |
mohinī japamānastu vadate dvija keśavaḥ ||039:055||
dvija uvāca |

ahaṃ saṃpreśito devairviddhi māṃ kāśyapātmajam |
yajñāḥ sainadraiḥ samārabdhā ṛṣibhiścāsurādhipa ||039:056||
[devai ka]
tasya niṣpādanārthāya āgatohaṃ tavāntikam |
dānaṃ me dīyatāṃ rājan siddhyate yena tanmakham ||039:057||
vala uvāca |

yena saṃsidhyate yajño devānāṃ bho dvijottama |
tad vācaya dharma dārān śivamadya dadāmi te ||039:058||
[devāradyo ka]
brāhmaṇa uvāca |

yena saṃsidhyate yajño devānāmasurādhipa |
taddeyaṃ tacca ādiṣṭaṃ satyamatrāvayorapi ||039:059||
vala uvāca |

yācyatāṃ yena te kāryaṃ satyaṃ vipra dadāmi te |
saṃsmṛtya mohinīṃ vidyāṃ vadate dvijasattama ||039:060||
brāhmaṇa uvāca |

na me dhanairna dārairvā na bhūmyā gaja vājibhiḥ |
ratnaiḥ kāryyaṃ mahāvāho devayajñe'surādhipa ||039:061||
yena niṣpādyate yajñaḥ sukhadaśca divaukasām |
tamahaṃ yācayāmi tvāmÌ dīyatāṃ tadbhutaṃ mama ||039:062||
[yajñeṣu svayaṃ ka; tava ka ]
etat kāryyaṃ bhadra mama ṛá¹ṣīṇāñca viśeṣataḥ |
devāryaṃ tava kāyena sidhyate tanmakhottamam ||039:063||
[mame bhadra ka ga; tu athottamaṃ ka ga]
tadā dattā tanustena dānavena mahātmanā |
viṣṇunāpi sa cakreṇa śirasyabhihato'suraḥ ||039:064||
[sa vakreṇa vivasyamihapsaraḥ ka]
prākṛtaṃ dehamutsṛjya divyakāyastvabhūta-tadā |
tasyāvayava sañjātā vajrādayo ratna jātayaḥ ||039:065||
[divya kāsaṃmūtradā ka; saṃjñātā vajākaraṃ bhavet ka]
locaneṣu ca tejāṃsi padmarāgiṇi yābhavan |
viśuddha pātra dānena kāyorantaḥ karo'bhavat ||039:066||
[ślokāḥ na santi ka pustake]
evaṃ saṃghātitaḥ śukra vidyā mantra balena ca |
vidyā mohayitvā tu na cāstreṇa na saṅgare ||039:067||
[mohayittvāṃ vighayānavastreṇātu saṃgare ka]
tasmād vidyā valaṃ sarvvaṃ duḥsahaṃ siddhidāyakam |
smāritaṃ bhaktinā vipramanepsita phalapradam ||039:068||
[phalapradā ka]
atha daitye gate svargaṃ sutastasya mahābalaḥ |
suvalaḥ sāgarepāntāduttarādaṃsamutsukaḥ ||039:069||
[atasya ka; abalaḥ ka ga]
saṃkruddho devarājasya vadhāya vadhakāṃkṣayā |
divyaṃ rathavaraṃ ruhya manogāmi sadaśvagam ||039:070||
pādarakṣa samopetaṃ bahuśastra samākulam |
kāmagaṃ sarvvaśatrūṇāṃ pradharṣaṃ ca mahābalam ||039:071||
[apradhārpyam mahābalam ka ga]
sārathiṃ bahuśāstrajñaṃ yuddhaśāstra viśāradaḥ |
jayeti durjayo devaiḥ sārathiḥ sauvalo'bhavat ||039:072||
pādarakṣo mahābalaḥ sumāyo mantrisattamaḥ |
rukmī daityādhipo netā daṇḍādhyakṣo mahāvalaḥ ||039:073||
yena viṣṇuḥ surendraśca bahudhā saṅgare jitaḥ |
na jitaḥ sa suraiḥ saindrai rbrahma-viṣṇupurogamaiḥ ||039:074||
atha tadanu rājendre pitṛvairānalodbhave |
jajvāla vahṇivad devān hotṛvajjvalitānanaḥ ||039:075||
[hauta ka]
yaṃ yaṃ paśyati daityendraścandrendraṃ pāvakaṃ vasum |
taṃ tamamidravat kruddhaḥ paśuṃ rūdra ivājñayā ||039:076||
evaṃ te dānavairdevā bahudhāmarṣakāṅikṣabhiḥ |
dṛṣṭvā ca pīḍitā sarvve indrasya śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ ||039:077||
yāvat samājaṃ kṛtvā te brahma viṣṇu purandarāḥ |
samāgatāstadā sainyā sauvalā valagarvvitāḥ ||039:078||
danḍodyatakarāḥ keciddaityā nistriṃśa dhāriṇaḥ |
śaracāpakarāścānye cakra śaṅkuka dhāriṇaḥ ||039:079||
[hojīvajvalanānalau ka ga]
śatadhnī śatacakro ca sahasradhnī dharā pare |
vṛkṣādripaṭṭiśavetraśūlina krakacīparā ||039:080||
dhārayanto mahābāhū gaja-siṃhoṣṭragāminaḥ |
danujāste surān sarvvān ayodhyanta tadāhave ||039:081||
atha bhagnāṃstadā dṛṣṭvā devān daivapatimmarhān |
udayādrisamaṃ rudraṃ gajarāja-bubhūṣitam ||039:082||
sindūrārūṇa rāgādyaṃ ghaṇṭā cāmara manḍitam |
caturdantaṃ surūpāḍhyaṃ mahāvegaṃ mahābalam ||039:083||
gajo danuja sainyasya kāla sarpa ivābhavat |
atha tatra sthitañcendraṃ dṛṣṭvā jvālo mahābalaḥ ||039:084||
chāgarājaṃ samārūhya dīptā śaktiṃ vyadhārayat |
taṃ dṛṣṭvā mahiṣaṃ dharmmo danḍapāṇirmahāvala ||039:085||
ārūḍhaścitraguptaśca kālaketusamanvitaḥ |
kṛtānto niṣṭhuramiva vajradanḍo mahābalaḥ ||039:086||
evantu niṛti nirmeṣe purūṣe ca tadānujaḥ khaḍga pāṇiḥ suraktākṣaḥ kraddhakṛṣṇāñjanaprabhaḥ ||039:087||
[kecikṛni ka]
bahusainyān samādāya indrasainyaṃ samāgataḥ |
varūṇo vārūṇairyodhairjhaṣagaḥ pāśadhārakaḥ ||039:088||
[bahuśaṃku kuṭhāriṇaḥ ka ga]
kṛṣṇasāraṃ samādāya aṅkuśena samīraṇaḥ |
vimāne kāmage yakṣo gadādhārī mahābalaḥ ||039:089||
kubero yakṣa koṭibhirvṛtastatra samāgataḥ |
rūdrāśceśānapūrvvāśca vṛṣagāḥ śūlapāṇinaḥ ||039:090||
[dṛṭvā jvālāṃ mahojvalām ka ga]
ādityā rathagāḥ sarvve viśvedevāḥ suvāhanāḥ |
āśvinau cāśvagau bhadra nāgā yakṣā graheśvarāḥ ||039:091||
[naikṛti ka ga]
nakṣatrā bahurūpāśca siddha vidyādharādayaḥ |
brahmā viṣṇustadā tasthau sainyagoptau surottamau ||039:092||
Foot notes are not matching with the reference nos. Please check.
mahāṇaṃva iva tasthurmaryyādāṃ na mumoca saḥ |
senā bhū svarga pātāla āpūrita-digānanā ||039:093||
koṭyārvvudāyuta saṃkhyā padma padma pramāṇitā |
asaṃkhyātā mahābāho senā tatra surottamam ||039:094||
[samaṃtāchrādailātu ka]
dṛṣṭvā tu subalo vāmai śarairavarṣata meghavat |
samantācchādayitvā tu prāvṛṇmegha ivāmbubhiḥ ||039:095||
[nardayat vibhī ka]
nanāda dhanurāveṇa vādyayānasvanena ca |
atha nādaṃ tadā śrutvā cāsuraṃ bhayakārakam ||039:096||
śaktiṃ dīptāṃ samudgamya dānavān mardayan śikhī |
rukmī nāma mahādaityo netā'sau sauvale vale ||039:097||
jvalanasya rathañcodya dīptaśūlo mahābalaḥ |
nānāyudha mahāsaṃgha jvalitārka mitānalaḥ ||039:098||
śūlaṃ hutāśane preṣya sura sainya bhayapradān |
taiḥ śūlaiḥ pāvakī senāṃ bahudhā bhaya āsitām ||039:099||
[pradāṃ kha]
dṛṣṭvā śaktiṃ sudīptāntu sañcikṣepā'surottamaḥ |
tāṃ sutejāṃ mahāvelāṃ suryyāyutasamaprabhām ||039:100||
[mahāvalāṃ ka ga]
vividhya niśitairvāṇaiḥ dadāha ca tṛṇāgnivat |
śaraiḥ sātodyacānapi na nyavarttayata yadāsureḥ ||039:101||
[catuṇa gūpat ka]
tadā śilā-vināśāya śaktiṃ cikṣepa dānavaḥ |
atha śilā hatāṃ śakti dṛṣṭvā devo'surottamaḥ ||039:102||
[śakteḥsaṃkṣipya ka; āthaśaila ka]
śilāṃ mudgaraghātena hatvā daityaṃ nyapātayat |
śakti koṭyāhataṃ daityaṃ vigatāsuṃ rathopari ||039:103||
[nipātyasaḥ ka; svaṃ ka]
rukmīṃ dṛṣṭvā hataṃ śaṃkho manyunā abhyadhāvata |
||039:105ab|| (104?)
śaṅkha uvāca |

hutāśana mahābāho yāgādai bhava cāhutiḥ ||039:105cd|| (104)
anyathā rukmi mohena saṃgrāme tava kā sthitiḥ |
yā śaktiḥ śūlinā dattā dahataḥ saubalaṃ balam ||039:106||
[lobhanoka]
sā te hṛdaye suvalād gṛhya pāsyati prāṇa āsavam |
paṇya strīva yathā lobhāt kāmukānāṃ varāyate ||039:107||
[mātet trādya valā hya hyanaṃ tava prāṇā saṃ vaṃpratika; ca vāsate ka]
evaṃ te śoṇite śaktirhṛṃdi saṃskāra miṣyate |
atha jalpaṃ tadā kāle śaṅkha-vākyānileritaḥ ||039:108||
[śaktiḥ hṛdi saṃskāra miṣyati ka ga]
dundubhiḥ dānavendrāṇāṃ sainyamadhyāt samutthitaḥ |
kiṃ vākyaiḥ śiśubhistulyaiḥ pramadā iva bhāṣate ||039:109||
[bhrāpate ka]
vaira niryyātanā śaṅkhaṃ varaṃ rukmi bhavān bhavet |
bhave hate'tha govinde śakre vā saguhe hate ||039:110||
[viri ka; valaṃ ka; bhavāntare ka ga; śakevāsa guhe hate ka ]
anyathā viphalaṃ janma unmatta-śiśu-ceṣṭitam |
āmaṃtrya dundubhiḥ śaṅkhaṃ gajañca samaruhya saḥ ||039:111||
[svarathaṃ ka]
indrāyābhimukho'dhāvata jvalitaṃ gṛhya cāyudham |
śūlaṃ śūli samākāraṃ sarvvāyudha nivāraṇam ||039:112||
[mukhodhara ka ga; śūli samākaraṃ ka]
mumoca sa tu indrāya indro'pi jvalitāśanim |
śūlāya dhāraṇaṃ kṣepya sarvvāṃyudha bhayaṅkaram ||039:113||
[aśaniḥ ka ga; sarvāsura ka ga ]
taṃ vajra jvalitamindraṃ śūla bhinnaṃ dvidhākṛtam |
bhūmau papāta viphalaṃ bhramarāṇāṃ ceṣṭitaṃ kṛtam ||039:114||
[vikalaṃ śramallī vesvivahanaṃ ka]
vajre hate tathā caiva bṛhaspatiṃ mahāmatim |
gopendraṃ śaraṇaṃ jagmurgṛhītvā surarāṭ tadā ||039:115||
valo hatastvayā ca syāt subalaste caturguṇaḥ |
sa śaṅkho dundubhirnātha kenopāyena śāmyatām ||039:116||
paśya vajraṃ na vajrāya daṇḍaṃ daṇḍāya na prabho |
vihvalaṃ deva sainyaṃtu sāyudhaṃ gajavāhanam ||039:117||
[tasya ka]
tasyopāyai kathaṃ sakhye vadhāyātha śamāva ca |
kathayasva suraśreṣṭha śaraṇāgata vatsalaḥ ||039:118||
devāḥ savāsavāḥ sarvve rakṣaṇīyā mahāhave |
subalaṃ balasampannaṃ nayopāya samanvitam ||039:119||
duḥsahaṃ surasaṃdhasya vāsavasya viśeṣataḥ |
evamuktvā tathā mantrī virarāma pitāmahaḥ ||039:120||
uvāca sauṣṭhavāṃ vāṇī mādhavo ripunāśanaḥ |
||039:121ab||
viṣṇu uvāca |

yā sā ādyā parā śaktiḥ śaṅkarī mantrasambhavā ||039:121cd||
[yā ādyā ka]
padavarṇa vibhāgena sā te kṣemāya vāsava |
bhaviṣyati na sandeho mahātatvā mahāsvarā ||039:122||
[mahātalā ka]
śakaraṃ toṣayitvā tu sā mayā padamālinī |
vidyāṣṭaka samāyuktā kṣemā kṣemāya mānaghā ||039:123||
[yacālaya ka ga]
dānavo vala saṃyukto vidyā mantra balena ca |
yadi yāti vaśaṃ karttumanyathā ajayo bhavet ||039:124||
[saujayo bhavet ka]
tadā viṣṇuḥ surendraśca bṛhaspati marudgaṇaiḥ |
gatvā śambhuṃ samārādhya asurāṇāṃ vadhaiṣiṇaḥ ||039:125||
jaya tvaṃ jayatāṃ śreṣṭha paṃca mantra tanū maya |
guṇahīna guṇatvācca jagataḥ pālane sthitaḥ ||039:126||
[tanumpraya]
utpatti sthāpane nāśe rajaḥ satvaṃ tamo mayaḥ |
arupaṃ bahurūpaṃ ratvaṃ vacasāmapyagocaraḥ ||039:127||
sarvvagaḥ sarvvarūpeṣu sarvvabhāvavyavasthitaḥ |
trāhi māṃ dānavānīka-mahārṇava gataṃ harim ||039:128||
sasuraṃ gaṇamādityaṃ vasuṃ cāsmin vilokayan |
śāntiṃ vidhāya jagataḥ kṣemaṃ kuru triśūlinaḥ ||039:129||
[vasu cāgninā thalokayat ka ga]
evaṃ gadgadayā vācā vijñāpya madhusūdanaḥ |
tutoṣa ca tadā cāsau somaḥ somārddha-śekharaḥ ||039:130||
varaṃ varaya govinda yat te hṛdi vyavasthitam |
yathā ca mādhavo hṛṣṭaḥ suvalaṃ dundubhiṃ vadha ||039:131||
[gopendra ka ga]
evantu yācite rudre pratijñāte vare hare |
cintitā paramā śakti vidyāṣṭaka samanvitā ||039:132||
[paṃktirnāsti ka pustake]
tadā gatā śivā cāgre mūrttirbhūtā bravīti sā |
yat kāryyaṃ devadeveśa tadādiśaya me prabho ||039:133||
tadā devena tuṣṭena uktā sā suvalaṃ vadha |
tāvat sañcintitaṃ devyā pūrvva śāpa hato mayā ||039:134||
[soha kha ga]
virupeṇa ca hantavyo nāyudhenāsurāghamaḥ |
evaṃ sā yauvanaṃ rūpa tyaktvā vṛddhābhavat tadā ||039:135||
[vidyārūpeṇa ka ga; yasā ka ]
śirā jālena sannaddhā nirmmāṃsā koṭarekṣaṇā |
pravivaiśaiva devyoṣṭha vikāśe nāgabandhanā ||039:136||
[sajālā itvā ka; nāgabandhana kha ]
arddhālaṃkṛta kaṇau ca vāmorūkara saṃsthitā |
pīṭhasaṃsthena yāmyena viṣāde parame sthitā ||039:137||
[mudrā ka ga; vā ka]
vivṛtāsyāsaṅkampantī śatāyuta ca samā yamā |
vidyābhiraṣṭabhirmāyā guptā guptābhiḥ saṃsthitā ||039:138||
[vivitāsyā ka ga]
pathiparvvata rājasya droṇasya sumahātmanā |
kroñcadvīpe mahādvīpe madhye sā madhya saṃsthitā ||039:139||
[pathe ka]
vidyāṣṭakaṃ tatastasyā diśaiśca vidiśaiḥ sthitam |
vṛṣasiṃha pajavarhi haṃsa sarpaviṣā parā ||039:140||
[sthitī ka]
savale ṛkṣarāje ca sanniviṣṭā mahābalā |
kṛṣṇasāre gatisāre vasurāje sthitā parā ||039:141||
[garale trākṣa ka]
tā vidyāḥ śatadhā bhūtvā kula vāmasadakṣiṇāḥ |
paritrāṇāya devānāṃ martyaloke nṛpādiṣu ||039:142||
[te ka]
antaḥ striṣu viśeṣeṇa pulindaśavarādiṣu |
lokāntareṇa mārgeṇa vāmācāreṇa siddhidā ||039:143||
veśyāsu gopavālāsu udrakūpapareṣu ca |
pīṭhe himavataścaṃpā jālandharesavaidiśe ||039:144||
[oṭtaṇathasesu ka]
mahodaye varendre ca rāḍhāyāṃ kośale pure |
bhoṭa deśe sakāmākhye kiṣkindhye ca nagottame ||039:145||
[cotta ka ga]
malaye kolanāme ca kāñcyāñca hastināpure |
ujjayinyāñca tā vidyā viśeṣeṇa vyavasthitāḥ ||039:146||
prati sthāne sthitāḥ śuka śivādyā ūrdhvakeśikāḥ |
dṛṣṭāḥ krīḍanti tā vālai valitantretu jambhakoḥ ||039:147||
[paṃktirnāsti ka pustake]
aṣṭadhā graharājasya sakhāyatve vyavasthitā |
evaṃ tā vyāpayitvā tu vidyā lokānaśeṣataḥ ||039:148||
[śeṣasaḥ ka]
suvalasya vadhārthāya sthito āvṛtya tāḥ pathaḥ |
suvalo'pi tadā cakre śarabhañcāgra toraṇam ||039:149||
[śarabhaṃ gragrato balāt ka ga]
droṇādriṃ vāsavaṃ hantuṃ tvarayā valavāhanam |
mahārathaugha-nādena vādyarāveṇa cāmvaram ||039:150||
dhvajaiścihnātapatraiśca nāditaṃ chāditaṃ tathā |
atha tasmin nage dṛṣṭvā etāṃ pariṇatāṃ valām ||039:151||
[pathe sthitā ka]
āvṛtya saṃsthitāṃ mārga diṅmukhānīva bhāskaram |
tadā dānava netā yo vadate tyajatāṃ patham ||039:152||
[rovadatye tyajyatthāṃ yarthā ka]
anyathā rathanāgaistvaṃ vṛddhe kṣemaṃ na sthāsyasi |
atha vṛddhā vacaḥ śrutvā dānavena prabhāṣitam ||039:153||
[prajñāmāsitaṃ ka]
vadate anyathā kṛtvā dānavena tu kāmitam |
āpūraya prayatnena anyathā na śubhaṃ tava ||039:154||
[tu kāmitam ka]
akṣemaṃ bhavate teṣāṃ yo māṃ vṛddhāṃ na manyate |
tadā dānava netā yo gṛhītvā tāṃ karai kila ||039:155||
utthāpayed gatāsuḥ sa papāta dharaṇī tale |
netāraṃ nihataṃ dṛṣṭvā śaṅkho nāmāsurottamaḥ ||039:156||
[apīḍayat ka]
abhyadhāvat tadā devyā dharaṇyāṃ sa nipātitaḥ |
tadā tu suvalo kruddho gatvā devīṃ kare kila ||039:157||
[tato ka ga; sagitātitaḥ ka; subalaḥ ka ga ]
gṛhnāti tāvat patita sa kṣitau vigatāsavaḥ |
evaṃ tān dānavān sarvvān vināhava nipātitān ||039:158||
[gṛhāti ka; nipātane kha]
paśyanti maruto dṛṣṭāstyaktaśaṅkāḥ pitāmahā |
bhūtayonisthitāḥ devyā śūlāsi śara śakti bhṛt ||039:159||
ghaṇṭā ḍamaru veṇūni ravakāṇi ca vādayat |
śarabha śaṅkhau hatau dṛṣṭvā dundubhi rvaladarpitaḥ ||039:160||
mādhavasya vadhārthāya virathena vajet kila |
yāvad devī mahālakṣmī mahāvidyā surārihā ||039:161||
[mahālajjā kha]
nihatya dāruṇamājau dundubhiṃ saṃnipātya sā |
kapāle rudhiraṃ kṛtvā śyenakādyān mahāgrahān ||039:162||
śivādyāmÌ tarpayeda devīmipsitārtha phalapradām |
evaṃ tān dānavān hatvā mahāvalaparākramān ||039:163||
[tarpayāṃ ka ga||
avadhyān sarvvadevānāṃ vāsave kṣemadā bhavat |
kṣemaṃ deveṣu sā devī kṛtvā daityapateḥ kṣayam ||039:164||
kṣemaṅkarī śivenoktā pūjyā loke bhaviṣyasi |
anenaiva tu rūpeṇa vidyāṣṭaka samanvitā ||039:165||
ekā vā nagarāntasthā pūjitā sthāpitā śubhā |
prasāde pāṭhakuḍye vāṃ pustake jala vahnigā ||039:166||
nistriṃśe pūjayet kṣemāṃ sarvvakāma phalapradām |
damanī padamālā ca śrī ghoṣa vajra śāsanā ||039:167||
[śīghogā ka]
astraṃ pratyaṅgirā devyāḥ pūjayet samudāhṛtā |
etābhiḥ sthāpanaṃ kāryya śivāsana śavāntagam ||039:168||
kanyā saṃsthe dvijaḥ sūrye bhavate sarvvakāmadam |
yato devī bhaved vṛddhā pitaro vṛddha rūpiṇaḥ ||039:169||
pitṛgeha vaśe tasmāt sthāpitavyā śubhārthibhiḥ |
hemādimaṇi ratnāni devīñcoddiśya sthāpane ||039:170||
pātrāṇi ca vastrāṇi ca kuryyānnānā gṛhādiṣu |
śatena kārayed devaṃ sahasraṃ sanniveśane ||039:171||
ātmānaṃ dāra sarvvasvaṃ dadyāt tat sthāpake śubhe |
yataḥ saṃsārāduddharaṇe nānyaḥ śakto guruṃ vinā ||039:172||
[ātmānaṃdārasarvasvaṃ sarvadā upasthāpake ka]
ato devī ca draṣṭavyā gururmantrapradāyakaḥ |
sthāpako bhairavādīnāṃ yo bhaved dvijasattamaḥ ||039:173||
sa gururmmantra siddhāntadātā sarvva jagaddhitaḥ |
graha nāge ca ślokānāṃ devānāṃ sthāpane hitaḥ ||039:174||
[siddhāntettāsa ka]
viśeṣa vali pūjādi vettā devī niveśakaḥ |
dhātūttamena varṇena matsyamāṃsa surādibhiḥ ||039:175||
[nideśakaḥ ka ga; vargeṇā ka]
devībhyaḥ sthāpanaṃ śastaṃ bhayadaṃ bhavate'nyathā |
vihitā devatā vipra tarpaṇīyā tu rājasī ||039:176||
[vidyetā ka; purppanāyā tu rājasā ka]
tāmasī tamasā pūjyā suhṛṣṭā na tu sātvikī |
mantrāḥ padamālayākhyānāṃ kṣemāyāḥ sthāpane pare ||039:177||
[sālikā ka ga]
pūjane vā kvacicchastā naiṣṭhikā na kadācana |
kula mārga tathā vāma mātṛ dakṣiṇa vedikā ||039:178||
[kṛcisthānai ka ga]
devī pūjāvidha śastā na mandā na ca teṣṭhikāḥ |
na siddhāntaika bhāvasthā na ca devaika bhāvitā ||039:179||
[guru ka ga; vedakāḥ ka]
strī pradhānā yato devī vidyā yatnaivato yajet |
evaṃ yaḥ pūjayeddevīṃ sthāpeyad vā dvijottamaḥ ||039:180||
[devaḥ ka]
sthāpayantu tathā tena pūjāpayati mānavaḥ |
sa labhate hitān kāmāniha loke dvijottamaḥ ||039:181||
[vā naraḥ ka]
likhitvā dhārayedbhaktyā vāhau kaṇṭhe kare vare |
rājyāyuḥ suta saubhāgyaṃ prāpnuyāda vicāraṇāt ||039:182||
[āptayāda ka]
paratra bhairavaṃ sthānaṃ brahma viṣṇu namaskṛtam |
labhate nātra sandeho satyedaṃ devī pūjanāt ||039:183||
smaraṇāt paṭhanādvipra dhāraṇād vā subhāvitaḥ |
vidyānāntu prabhāveṇa labhate manasepsitam ||039:184||
catuḥ ṣaṣṭiṣu vidyāsu yathā vīryyaṃ mahāphalam |
vijayādiṣu vikhyātaṃ sarvvāṃbhyudayadāyakam ||039:185||
[dvāyakam ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe vidyā-mantra-bhāva-kṣemakarī prādurbhāvo nāma ekonacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityāde devīpurāṇe vidyāmaṃtraprabhāva kṣemaṃkarī prādurbhāvaḥ]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 040
catvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

uvāca|
mahādharmmāsuro brahman kenopāyena brahmaṇā |
nirjjito yuddha śauṇḍastu sarvvadeva bhayaṅkaraḥ ||040:001||
[vraṇā ka]
etat kautuhalaṃ deva śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ ||039:002ab||
manuruvāca |

kauñcāreḥ sthānamindrasya tapo vighna samutthitam ||039:002cd||
[kraucā vetrāramitrāda patayo vidya samutthitaṃ ka]
homāvasānikaṃ ghoramasuraṃ kṛṣṇa dharmmiṇam |
taṃ dṛṣṭvā mahatīṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā cāmuṇḍābhairavaiḥ ||040:003||
dhāturmaheti pūjāyāṃ mahādharmmā tataḥ smṛtaḥ |
pūrvvaṃ devāsure yuddhe tārakeṇa mahātmanā ||040:004||
ārādhya bhagavadviṣṇuṃ dvādaśākhyai rmahāvrataiḥ |
kratu bhāgavatairnāma mārgādyairurjja paścimaiḥ ||040:005||
[śamai ka]
toṣito vāsudevastu sarvvadevavadhaiṣiṇā |
tatastasya varo dattastena dharmmamahāsuraḥ ||040:006||
sāhāyyaṃ saṃgare tāta kariṣyati mamājñayā |
sa tadā viṣṇorādeśāt varalabdho mahāsuraḥ ||040:007||
[lavdha daṃḍo mahāsurā ka ga]
samādiśati(FN) dharmmākhyaṃ sa brahmendro vyamohayat |
evaṃ tasya samādeśānmahādharmmā suhṛṣṭavān ||040:008||
[matter not found]
sa cakrāṅgamādāya druhiṇasya vināśane |
gatavān yatra sendrastu brahmā tiṣṭhati so'suraḥ ||040:009||
rudrārādhana yuktātmā kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ phalārthinaḥ |
tatastasya mahāyuddhamabhavaccharadāṃ śatam ||040:010||
[daśa ka ga]
sannaddhānāṃ tadā tasmin surāsura jighāṃsayā |
tāvat syandanamāruḍhamugrasenaṃ mahāsuram ||040:011||
dṛṣṭvā valaṃ tadā teṣāṃ devī brahmaṇe cintitā |
bhāraṃ paraṃ samāsthāya sarvvadeva namaskṛtā ||040:012||
[dṛṣṭavā mahāvalaṃ tāta ka ga]
āgatā kṣaṇa mātreṇa ugrasena vadhaiṣiṇī |
viniyuktā tu saṃpūjya vadhāya danusattame ||040:013||
muṇḍaṃ saṃpīḍayeddevīṃ ugrasenasya nāyakam |
tatastaṃ pīḍitaṃ dṛṣṭvā ugrasenaśca dānavaḥ ||040:014||
[saṃpīḍaya ka ga; ślokadvaye nāsti ga pustake]
indrāya preṣayat śaktiṃ yamadaṇḍasamaprabhām |
indro'pi vajranārācairbahudhogramatāḍayat ||040:015||
ugrasenastadā kruddha indraṃ khaḍgena tāḍayet |
khaḍgāhatastadā cendro gajopari niṣaṇṇavān ||040:016||
devī dṛṣṭvā tadā candraṃ mūrcchitaṃ vraṇavihvalam |
ugrasenasya saṃkruddhā āgneyāstraṃ prayuktavān ||040:017||
tenāhatastadā ugro dahyamānaḥ sasyandanaḥ |
vāruṇaṃ preṣayāmāsa śamāya jvalanāpaham ||040:018||
[mājaṃjva suṃnāpahaṃ ka]
vāyavyaṃ prakṣipaddevī tadā vārūṇa śāntaye |
vikṣiptameghasaṃghātaṃ bhagnapādapabhūdharam ||040:019||
mṛgāruḍhaṃ tadā devaṃ pāśāṅkuśa karodyatam |
veṣṭayitvā tu taṃ caugraṃ mahābala parākramam ||040:020||
ugrasena balaṃ hatvā sa ca pāśena pāśitaḥ |
asya śarāsanaṃ chitvā hatvā cogro nipātitaḥ ||040:021||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe trailokyāmyudaye ugrasenavadho nāma catvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye trailokyābhyudaye ugrasenavadhaḥ ka ga]
%%% Chapter 041
ekacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

śaunaka uvāca |

ugrasene hate tāta kiṃ kuryyāt sa mahāsuraḥ |
kṛṣṇadharmmā mahābāho tanme brūhi mahāmune ||041:001||
manuruvāca |

hate cogre tadā kruddhaḥ kṛṣṇadharmmā mahāsuraḥ |
vāle mahāhavaṃ cakruṃ brahmendraṃ pari rakṣase ||041:002||
[yadi ga]
evaṃ sa tarjjaṃyitvā tu devīṃ cakreṇātāḍayat ||041:003ab||
siṃhaṃ paṃceṣubhirbhittvā punardevīṃ vyatāḍayat |
||041:003cd||
devī kruddhā tadā vatsa kṛṣṇaṃ vajre'ṇatāḍayat||041:003ef||
vajrāhataṃ tadā kṛtvā rathopasthagataṃ tathā |
tadā drutaṃ samādhāvad devyā daṇḍakarodyataḥ ||041:004||
āyāntaṃ taṃ śarairdevī pañcabhiryamasādanam |
preṣayāmāsa saṃkruddhā tadā kṛṣṇasya sārathim ||041:005||
hate kṛṣṇa rathādhāre kṛṣṇadharmmā mahābalaḥ |
pādasthaścakramādāya devyāḥ sa saṃmukhau yayau ||041:006||
āyāntaṃ taṃ mahābāhuṃ śaraiḥ sannata parvvabhiḥ |
vidhyahṛdi śirastasya cakraghātenāpātayat ||041:007||
evaṃ tu kṛṣṇadharmmāṇaṃ mahābala parākramam |
saṅgare nihataṃ vatsa brahmendra parirakṣitam ||041:008||
[saṃgrāme ka ga]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre kṛṣṇadharmmavadho nāmaika catvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
[kṛṣṇadharmaṃ vadhaḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 042
dvicatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

vaśiṣṭha uvāca |

candreśe cograkṛṣṇe ca hate tasmin mahābale |
devāstuṣṭāstadā devīṃ pūjayā vāgbhiḥ sāntvayan ||042:001||
[cābhiḥ sāṃtvayat ka]
tvaṃ devī parirakṣā no brahmādīnāṃ bhayārṇave |
yathā kṛṣṇa mahāghoraḥ krīḍayā vinipātitaḥ ||042:002||
[ddheddheripava ka]
tvaṃ buddhiḥ śuddhirmedhāśca kāntirdāptirmatiryaśaḥ |
rakṣā ca paramā devī viṣṇivandra druhiṇādiṣu ||042:003||
rakṣaṇāya nṛpāṇāñca martye tvaṃ devī pūjitā |
jālandhare mahādevī pīṭhasthāna gatā śivā ||042:004||
tvadaṃśagā striyo devī bhaviṣyanti varapradāḥ |
bhaktānāmabhayadāḥ sarvvakāma phalapradā ||042:005||
yugānurupadharmmeṇa dharmmināṃ kāmadāyikāḥ |
sthāne sthāne bhaviṣyanti dṛṣṭādṛṣṭa prasādhikāḥ ||042:006||
[kāmadātmikā ka; cariṣyati ka ga]
malaye sahyavindhye ca himavatyarvudādiṣu |
citre gope nare kāle nīcākhye parvvate tathā ||042:007||
[lavekāle ka ga; nāyākhye ka]
laṅkāyāñcoḍradeśe ca strīrājye kāśikāvane ||042:004ab||
[lapākeyoṣṭradeśe ka; cale ka ga]
kāmarūpe tathā kāñcyāṃ campāyāñcātha vaidiśe ||042:008cd||
varendre codriyāṇe ca malākhye śikhare tathā ||042:008ef||
navadurgā sthale jale cole hairaṇye kanakākare |
siṃhale veṇudanḍe ca karṇakubje ca vaidiśe ||042:009||
[kruśa ka ga]
navadurgāsthale kṛtvā trimuṇḍāstatra krīrttitā |
devyāḥ sarvvārtha dātāraḥ sarvvakāma phalapradāḥ ||042:010||
vaidiśe madhyagā devī siṃhayāne vyavasthitā |
urdhvaṃ jayāvahā devī mahākālīti viśrutā ||042:011||
parā jambukanāthasya vahṇibhāgagatā mune |
bhadrakālīti vikhyātā mahālakṣmī rgirau smṛtā ||042:012||
[parājadyukanāpasya ka ga]
yatra sā sādhitā vidyā padamālā virājitā |
mṛtyuñjayāt tathā cānyā nandikeśo yathāptavān ||042:013||
[parājitā ka ga]
rātrau japtā mahābāho sā vidyā śaśinaḥ kṣaye |
vināśayen mahāmṛtyumapamṛtyuṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||042:014||
kalāṃ kalāṃ yadā candro gacchate ravi maṇḍalam |
tadā vidyāṃ japedrātrau divācandre vivarddhite ||042:015||
jarāmṛtyu bhayaṃ ghoraṃ brahma hatyādi pātakam |
śamate sā nāsandeho vidyā japtā mahāmune ||042:016||
[pātake ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe sthāna praśaṃsā nāma dvicatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityāde devyavatāre sthāna praśaṃsā ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 043
tricatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

śaunaka uvāca |

kathaṃ vidyā tu sā prāptā nandinā vṛṣavāhanāt |
kathaṃ tāṃ labhate tāta somo nandi sakāśataḥ ||043:001||
[tu sā māśaprāptā ka]
evaṃ sarvvaṃ yathānyāyaṃ kathayasva mahāmune |
||043:002ab||
[etat ka ga]
manuruvāca |

mahādevī tvidaṃ ghoraṃ hatvā devena viṣṇunā ||043:002cd||
[mahādevaṣṭadaṃ ka]
dattāparājitā candre tena candre budhe punaḥ |
kramāta puruṣebhyaḥ prāptāṃ yāvat pāṇḍusutādayaḥ ||043:003||
tathā sā kīrttitā loke sarvvakāma prasādhikā |
padamālā mahāvāho rghora yuddhe prakāśitā ||043:004||
puṣpākhyā mṛtyunāśāya nandine mṛtyuhā mune |
dattā vidyā mahāvāho tena rāmasya kīrttitā ||043:005||
amayaṃ nāśanārthāya tena japtā mahātmanā |
yena pūrvā jitā devā brahmādyā bahudhā yudhi ||043:006||
[mahāmune ka]
śaśāpa kālikā kruddhā bipreśasya vadhaiṣiṇam |
mahāsura suratrāsa yathā tvaṃ vidhnavāhinīm ||043:007||
[laṃṣidhū ka ga]
vādhase vidhnakopena tadā tvaṃ parśunā hataḥ |
śama kopa samudbhūte vahṇau dāhaṃ gamiṣyasi ||043:008||
evaṃ pūrvva sa śāpena amayaḥ śāpito'suraḥ |
jayyākhyaṃ parvvataṃ gatvā cacāra duścaraṃ tapaḥ ||043:009||
[jaṭharākṣaṃ ka]
phalamūla kaṇāhāraḥ parṇāśaḥ athavābhyudaḥ |
japahoma kriyāsaktaḥ keśavārādhane rataḥ ||043:010||
rauhiṇya vrata bhūyiṣṭhaḥ samacittaḥ samādhigaḥ |
cacāla tapasā devān prabhutāddhairmarudgaṇān ||043:011||
[sasargakān ka ga]
kṣātraṃ vrataṃ samādhāya tāvat tuṣṭo janārdanaḥ |
ajayastavaṃ mahābāhu rdevāsura bhayaṅkaraḥ ||043:012||
[bhavedruṣṭo ka]
bhaviṣyasi na sandeho nāśaṃ vyūhe vrajiṣyasi |
pañcatriṃśat kramāda vāhaṃ bhittvā gatvāsurādhipa ||043:013||
na yoddhavyaṃ mayā vatsa ṣaṭ triṃśastu bhavāntakaḥ |
evaṃ pūrvvaṃ mahābāho tapasā sa surāsurān ||043:014||
[ṣadrirjñaṅgaṃtarāṃtakaḥ ka ga]
vijitya krīḍate tāta pṛthivīṃ vana kānanām |
dvijān devān pitṛn jitvā ṛá¹ṣīn mukhyānabhidravat ||043:015||
[tātṛṣṭaṃ ka ga; saralakānāṃ ka; saravīna ka]
paribhramad yathākāmaṃ tridaśairapi vāritaḥ |
danḍakaṃ vanamāsādya yatra devo gajānanaḥ ||043:016||
vāmamitraḥ suhṛṣṭātmā vyūha tattva viśāradaḥ |
astragrāma praṇetā ca nisargāhlāda pūrvvakaḥ ||043:017||
[tala ka ga]
tatra gatvā mahābāho sumatiṃ pratyayāśramaḥ |
agastya duhitaraṃ devīṃ gajavakrapriyāṃ sadā ||043:018||
[agarūya ka]
tadā kruddhā paraśu rghṛñū lāghavena valena ca |
viniryaṃyau suptambandho gaja vaktra suhṛnmune ||043:019||
rāma uvāca |

sthīyatāṃ suraśreṣṭha saṅgarāya śamāya ca |
anyathā adya te vakṣe parśuḥ pivati śoṇitam ||043:020||
rāmavākya śaraiḥ viddho amayo manyunā tadā |
mumoca sahasā vāṇān prāvṛṣīva ghano jalam ||043:021||
[jano jale ka]
tasya vāṇa ghanāviddhaṃ kakubhontaṃ na labhyate |
nīhāra śata sañchanne niśānte śaśināḥ kṣaye ||043:022||
[vilaṃ ka ga]
tatastaṃ vāṇa tamasācchannaṃ dṛṣṭvā gajānanaḥ |
sumatiṃ pṛṣṭhato dattvā kramāda vyūhān vinirmmame ||043:023||
kākapakṣo urayaśca danḍābhogaḥ samanḍalaḥ |
saṅghātāḥ prākṛtā vyūhāḥ sapta proktāḥ kramādiṣe ||043:024||
pradadho dṛḍhakośādyaḥ so nācoraḥ sakukṣikaḥ |
(FN) pratiṣṭhaḥ supratiṣṭhaśca sañjayo vijayastathā ||043:025||
[ka pustake na santi]
sthūṇākarṇo viśālaśca vījābhaḥ sa ca sumukhaḥ |
ṛṣa sūcī kuvalayo durjjayaśca tathā pare ||043:026||
bhogo gomūtra śakaṭo makaro'tha pataṅgakaḥ |
maṅgalaḥ sarvvatobhadro durdharaśca susaṃyataḥ ||043:027||
[asaṃdyataḥ ka]
vajragodhā(FN) samudvālaḥ kākapakṣastathāparaḥ |
arddha candro mahāvyūhaḥ kaṅkaṭaḥ śṛṅga eva ca ||043:028||
[ka pustake nāsti]
ariṣṭaścācalaścāpi tathā pratihato mataḥ |
prākṛtairahitān vyūhān ṣaṭtriṃśataṃ mahāmune ||043:029||
bhūbhṛta sutātmajastāta śapayāmāsa āhave |
ākārairnāmarupaiścāśvanāgāśca pattibhiḥ ||043:030||
kuryyāt(FN) kramānurupeṇa śataśo'tha ca sahasraśaḥ |
viṣame ca same bhūmau tiryyañcaḥ nṛpajāṅgale ||043:031||
[ka pustake nāsti; sameṣa ciṣa ka ga; gātmapajāṃgale ka ]
avāyaḥ pratyavāyaśca kāryaścaivāvalambane |
tasmin gajānanastāta sapatākān satoraṇān ||043:032||
[vatvāvale ka]
tūryya-śaṅkharavopetān kṛtvā yuddhaṃ samunmahat |
amayo'pi tadā kruddhaḥ kramād vyūhān vyayodhasaḥ ||043:033||
[petān kṛlāryoda vatsamutsahe ka]
prativyūheṃryathā yogaṃ yāvat triṃśat samādhikā |
pañcabhistāvato vyūhān sa nighnan arimardanaḥ ||043:034||
ṣaṭtriṃśe ca tathā vyūhe(FN) bhidya māne surāriṇā |
rāmaḥ śarāsanaṃ sajyamiṣubhiḥ sannivārayet ||043:035||
[ka pustake na santi]
tadāmayaḥ susaṃkruddho śarān prati śarairhanet |
chittvā śarāsanaṃ medhyaṃ paśuṃ vivyādha pañcabhiḥ ||043:036||
śarairulkā samākārairdaśabhiḥ tāḍayecchire |
tadā śarāhataṃ rāmaṃ dṛṣṭvā pārvvatinandanaḥ ||043:037||
mahāmegha ninādena mumoca dāruṇaṃ śaram |
vidyuta-pūrvva-mahārāvaṃ mantrodadhi samākulam ||043:038||
[nākulam ka ga]
alivṛnda varārāvi śikhidardura saṅkulam |
kekibhiśca sadā dhṛṣṭaṃ cātakecchā pravarttakam ||043:039||
[ravāviśi ka; kekikaṃṭha ka ga; chāstra varttatkaṃ ka]
nīlalohita-madhyāntaṃ garalebha sama prabham |
chādayanto diśaḥ sarvvāḥ pūrayanto navāmbubhiḥ ||043:040||
[līlāṃ ka ga; gavāla ka ga]
pāśodyatakaraṃ ghoraṃ samayopari papāta saḥ |
rathanāgāśvapādātaṃ hanyamānaṃ sahasradhā ||043:041||
na saṃkhyā vidyate tāta ghātamānasya dānavāt |
tadāmayaḥ susaṃkruddho vāyavyāstraṃ vyacintayat ||043:042||
sāraṅga rathamāruḍhaṃ sa patākā dhvajākulam |
nāgādri śikharotkhāta bhagna prāsāda toraṇam ||043:043||
[śāradaṃ ka śāraṃgaṃ ga; śikharotthāta ka ga]
vāruṇaṃ nāśayāmāsa jalāstraṃ pāvanastadā |
(FN) tadā rāmeṇa kruddhena āgneyaṃ cintitaṃ śaram3 ||043:044||
[ka pustake na santi]
piṅgākṣa chāgamārūḍhaṃ saptajihvaṃ bhayānakam |
śakti hastaṃ mahā ugraṃ kālāgni sama tejasam ||043:045||
dahantaṃ dānavī senāṃ bhasmīkurvañcarācaram |
tadā dānavanāthena muktaṃ nārāyaṇaṃ śaram ||043:046||
śaṅkha cakra gadāhastaṃ khaga pṛṣṭha vyavasthitam |
tadā śaṅkāṃ surā jagmustena rāmo nipātitaḥ ||043:047||
vimutto'yamamoghātmā surārccanaiva saṃkṛtiḥ |
prakṛtvā saṃkṣayaṃ yāti arirsainyaṃ kadāvana ||043:048||
divyā na saṃhatiścāsya rāmaprāṇairasaṃkṛtaiḥ |
tadā rāmeṇa kruddhena brahmāstraṃ prativāraṇe ||043:049||
nārāyaṇa vighātārthaṃ cintitaṃ caturānanam |
muñja mekhala daṇḍākṣaṃ sruvadarbhakṛtājinam ||043:050||
hūṅkāra rāva vahulamāgatya purataḥ sthitam |
tadābhayaṃ mahaṃścāsīd daityeṣu ca sureṣu ca ||043:051||
[daityasya ca surasya ca ka ga]
amoghe divyavapuṣe asaṃhāryye mahāvale |
divyāstre brahma viṣṇuje kathaṃ moghānnirarthake ||043:052||
akṛtvā nāyakānāntu svaṃ svaṃ sthānaṃ vrajanti te |
evaṃ te yuddha saṃravdhe dṛṣṭvā te brahma viṣṇuje ||043:053||
gajānano'pi sañcintya yattat pāśupataṃ śaram |
mahārūpaṃ mahāmāyaṃ yugāntāgni samaprabham ||043:054||
pañca vaktraṃ mahāghoraṃ daśavāhuṃ trilocanam |
saumyaṃ ghoraṃ sughorasya ūrddhakeśaṃ bhayotkaṭam ||043:055||
[sainya ghoraṃ aghorāsyaḥ mūrddha ke śaṃbhayotkaṇṭhaṃ ka]
jaṭā bhārendu gaṅgāhi dhāramāṇaṃ śivātmakama |
veṇu vīṇā śaṅkha ghaṇṭā ḍamaru śava saṅkalam ||043:056||
[śivātmajaṃ ka ga]
ulkā danḍojvalaṃ jālaṃ gonāgakṛta bhūṣaṇam |
lalan mekhalā nāgendraṃ gaja carmmārdra vāsasam ||043:057||
[śivārāva bhayotrāsagṛdhra vāyasaveṣṭitaṃ ka ga]
kekaraṃ tarjjamānantu śūla khaṭvāṃga dhāriṇam |
grasamānaṃ samastedaṃ trailokyaṃ sacarācaram ||043:058||
purato vidhnanāthasya lelihānaṃ vyavasthitam |
vada tāta bhayaṃ kiṃ te yenāhaṃ smaritastvayā ||043:059||
kena vākyasya nāśāya tvarayā me udīraya |
evaṃ taṃ pūjayitvā tu amayopari mocitam ||043:060||
tadā sa tarddamānastu bhittvā dānava vāhinīm |
vidāryya brahma viṣṇvastraṃ madhye gatvā vicāryya ca ||043:061||
[nivāryyavā ka ga]
dānavāntaṃ tadā cakruḥ koṭidhā bahudhā mahat |
kṛtvāntaṃ dānavānāntu astrāṇāṃ bhedanaṃ tathā ||043:062||
amayaṃ ghātayitvā tu āgatastaṃ sakāraṇam |
tena śūla prahāreṇa vigatāsurmahāvalaḥ ||043:063||
prākṛtaṃ dehamutsṛjya gaṇalokaṃ samāyayau |
te ca astrāṇi sam(FN) pūjya svaṃ svaṃ sthānaṃ visarjjire ||043:064||
[ka pustake na santi]
hate tasmin mahāmātye sarvvadevārikaṇṭake |
daṇḍake pūjitā devī rudrāṇīti tadāla matā ||043:065||
[rudrāṇī ti tatoḥ gaṇāḥ ka]
navamyāṃ(FN) kujavāreṇa kumbha saṃsthe tu bhāskare |
kṛṣṇapakṣe tu yāmārddhe amayo vinipātitaḥ ||043:066||
[ka pustake na santi]
gaṇāḥ sampūjitā devai rdevī ca vidhinā tataḥ ||043:067ab||
sarvvavādhā vinirmuktā devā yātā nṛpāstathā ||043:067cd||
pūjā snānaṃ tathā dānaṃ kṛtameteṣu kāmikam ||043:067ef||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre trelokyābhyudaye'mayavadho nāma tricatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye trailokyābhyudaye amayavadhaḥ ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 044
catuścatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

gajānano'pi svasthānaṃ gato mālavya bhūdharama |
rāmo'pi pṛthivīṃ jitvā dvijadeveṣu vinyaset ||044:001||
nyasta rājyastadā tāta devīnāṃ kārayet puram |
sāgarānte mahāpuṇyaṃ yaśodaṇḍamahārṇave ||044:002||
[punaḥ kha]
tatrasthāmānaced devīṃ kālikā kālanāśinīm |
ayodhyāyāṃ mahādevī tena sā sanniveśitā ||044:003||
[bhaṭusthā ka; sāsattivetā ka ga]
tadaṃśā pūrvvamākhyātā yā durgā nava kīrttitāḥ |
mahodaye mahāvāho ye cānye vaidiśe sthitā ||044:004||
[vaidiko sthito ka]
mṛtyuñajayaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ yatra sannihitaḥ śivaḥ |
bhṛguṇā pūjitā devī sā vai kālikā matā ||044:005||
[viguṇā ka]
rāmeṇa jāmadagyena sarvvakāma samṛddhaye |
tathānye'pi ye ca vātra devī bhaktā yajanti ca ||044:006||
te vidyāyuryaśo'rthādi sukhaṃ prāpnotyanuttamam |
kāmikaṃ kāmikā devī dadayād vai malayālaye ||044:007||
[kāmitaṃ ka ga]
mandākṣe dāpayaddevī sarvvakāmāstu ambikā |
tārā mandāra śikhare kāmikaṃ dadate phalam ||044:008||
[ka pustake na santi |
gandhāra śikhare ga]
vairocanena danunā kanyārddhai candra parvvate |
pañcasūrtigatā devī pūjitā sarvvakāmadā ||044:009||
[kalpaseśri ka ga]
medhā gaurī yathā yakṣī jvālāsyā vindhyavāsinī |
pūjitā saṃstutā brahman sarvvakāma phalapradā ||044:010||
[yatathā ka; paktī ka]
kiṣkindhye bhairavī devī sarvvakāmān prayacchati |
vindhye vindhyāvaṭī nāma pūjitā tala samvare ||044:011||
pañcāsthā pūjitā devī apamatyuṃ vyapohati |
evaṃ saṃsthāna rūpeṇa pūjitā tāritātmabhiḥ ||044:012||
[paṃkās ka ga]
sarvva kāmapradā tāta bhavet sarvva sukhāvahā ||044:013||
[tavet sa sukhāvahā ka ga]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre trailokyāmyudaye devyā mahābhāgyaṃ nāma catuśacatvāriṃśo'dhāyāyaḥ |
|
%%%%
%%% Chapter 045
pañcacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

śakra uvāca |

svalpainaiva tu dravyena mahāpuṇyaṃ yathā bhaveta |
tadahaṃ śrotumicchāmi grahayāgaṃ sureśvara ||045:001||
brahmovāca |

śruṇa vatsa pravakṣyāmi yathā tvaṃ paripṛcchasi |
alpakleśaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ grahārkatithi yaugikam ||045:002||
bhṛgu pūrṇāṣṭamī yogaṃ śiva yogeṣu cottamam |
mṛdu vargañca bhāgyañca umāyā bhṛguvāsare ||045:003||
[śivayāṣu ka; tamayā ka ga ]
daivayogād yadā ṣaṣṭhi puṣyarkṣa ravivāsaram |
skanda yāgastadā kāryyaḥ sarvvakāma prasādhakaḥ ||045:004||
vāreṇa vāyadā sūryyaḥ saptamī vijayā matā |
tadā tu bharate bhānoryogaḥ sarvvaguṇāvahaḥ ||045:005||
śaśi riktānyasaṃyoge ārdrarkṣai mātarāsu ca |
navamyāṃ maṅgalāyogo bhānu muladinaṃ yadā ||045:006||
aṣṭamya vathāṃ candrāhe śrāvaṇena sukhāvaham |
ahi bradhne kujāhe tu gaṇeśe tasya cāhani ||045:007||
punarvvasau gururvāre dvādaśyāṃ śravaṇena vā |
somagrastaṃ tadā yogaṃ viṣṇoḥ sarvvārtha sādhakam ||045:008||
[somaśastaṃ ka ga]
dvitīyāyāṃ yadā saumye kṛttikākṣaṃ bhavet kvacit |
grahayāgastadā kāryyaḥ sarvvaśānti-pradāyakaḥ ||045:009||
svātī śani caturthī ca umāyāge varā smṛtā |
uttarāsu ca sarvvāsu bhānu paurṇāṣṭamīṣu ca ||045:010||
yāntyabhīṣeka yāgeṣu sarvvakāmā vahāṣṭamī |
gurorekādaśī puṣyerohiṇyāṃ vā yadā śani ||045:011||
[vasuṣṭamī ka; puṣye ka]
suta saubhāgyakāmāya yāgaṃ rudravināyake |
pūrṇimāsu ca sarvvāsu aṣṭamī dvādaśīṣu ca ||045:012||
caturdaśyāṃ tṛtīyāsu graharkṣeṣu śubheṣu ca |
sarvveṣāṃ bhavati yāgo bhakti pūrvvo mahāmune ||045:013||
yoga jñānaṃ yaśaḥ siddhiṃ mahādevādavāpnuyāt |
ārogyaṃ sapratāpatvaṃ bhāskarāt prāpyate dhruvam ||045:014||
[maṃtrasāṃdhana havyāya rudrayāgādavāpte |
śrī medhājñā vātsataya amāyāgānmahāmune ka; mahādevāhyagrāt ka]
gatimiṣṭāṃ yathākāmaṃ prayacchati trivikramaḥ |
vidhno na bhavate tasya yastu paśyedvinā yakam ||045:015||
[paśyeri ka]
vigatarāvirbhaṃvet ṣaṣṭhyāṃ skandaṃ dṛṣṭvā makhe kṣaṇāt |
mātṛ yāgānmahā siddhi sarvveṣāmapi jāyate ||045:016||
[ṣaṣṭhyāṃ dṛṣṭvā skandaṃ makha kṣaṇāt ka]
bhavate dhanavān puṃsaḥ prathamāhe hutāśanāt |
svargāpavarga-saṃsiddhi rdurgā-yāgāt prajāyate ||045:017||
māghādyai rmaṅgalāṃ saukhyāṃ jyaiṣṭhādyai rbrarhmajaṃ yajet |
īṣādyaiḥ kālikādyāstu yaṣṭavyā vidhinā mune ||045:018||
[gothājaiṣṭhāka ga]
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe trailokyābhyuṣaṭcatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

