%%% Chapter 046
brahmovāca |

devī  guṇa trayāviṣṭaṃ maṇḍapaṃ koṭivistaram |
brahmādi stambaparyyantamutpannaṃ sacarācaram ||046:001||
[paṃkti dvayaṃ nāsti ka pustake]
aṇḍe hiraṇyagarbhasthaṃ yat tatvaṃ garbhasaṃśritam |
tatrotpannamidaṃ vyīma rūpāṇi dyau  rmahī bhavet ||046:002||
[vyomakapāle ghau ka]
ardhoddhamÌ  kāñcana mayaścaturasrocchrito mahān |
utpatnaḥ sa catuḥśṛṅgo merurdaivata saṃśrayaḥ ||046:003||
[atho ka]
pṛthivīṃ padmaṃ diśaḥ patraṃ  merustasya tu karṇikā |
yugākṣa koṭi vinyastaṃ tatra kṛtvā rathaṃ raviḥ ||046:004||
[divyajaṃ ka ga]
devīñca saṃvṛto devairyāti tasya pradakṣiṇam |
tasmin merau trayastriṃśat vasante yājñikāḥ surāḥ ||046:005||
rudrā ekādaśa jñeyā ādityā dvādaśaiva tu |
tathaiva vasavo  hyaṣṭau aśvinau dvau ca yājñikau ||046:006||
[casavo ka]
vasan vadanti tu pitṛn rudrāṃścaiva  pitā mahān |
prapitā  mahānādityānarśvinau cātmanastanum ||046:007||
[rudrāṃścāpi ka ga; setu ka ga]
pitṛn bhūyaḥ pracakṣiṣye ṛtuṃ  saṃvatsarārttavān |
ato yajñabhujāmeṣāṃ pṛthak nāmāni me śṛṇu ||046:008||
[]
ājaikapāda hi brahman aṣṭau rudraśca vīryyavān |
haraścaivātha sarvvaśtryambakaścāparājitām  ||046:009||
[]
vṛṣākapiśca śambhuśca kaparddī raivatastathā |
īśvaropi bhuvanaścaite rudrā ekādaśa smṛtāḥ ||046:010||
ādityānāntu nāmāni viṣṇuḥ śakraśca vīryyavān |
aryamā  caiva dhātā ca mitro'tha varuṇastathā ||046:011||
[]
vivasvātṛ savitā caiva pūṣā tvaṣṭā tathaiva ca |
aṃśo bhagaścāti tejā  ādityā dvādaśā smṛtāḥ ||046:012||
[]
in the text 11nos. are there. But matter is found only for 10 notes. So I did not remove the FN nos.
