dhruvo dhavaśca somaśca āpaścaivānilo'nalaḥ |
pratyūṣaśca pramāṇaśca vasavo'ṣṭau prakīrtitā ||046:013||
[dharo dhruvaśca ka ga]
nā satyaścaiva dasraśca smṛtau dvāvaśvinau api |
viśvedevān pravakṣyāmi nāmatastān nivodha me ||046:014||
[skṛtau ka; dvāvaśvināvapi ka ga; viśvedevān pravakṣyānnibodhame ka ga]
kraturdakṣaḥ suraḥ satyaḥ kāmaḥ kālo dhṛtiḥ kuruḥ |
manumān rocamānastu viśvedevā daśasmṛtā ||046:015||
[sravaḥ ka; kāloṣṭatiḥ ka]
varttamānā ime devāḥ śṛṇu manvantaro bhavān |
yāmāśca tuṣitāścaiva tathaiva vaśavarttinaḥ ||046:016||
[śṛṇa macaṃtare ka]
satyā adbhutarajasaḥ sādhyāśca tadanaṃntaram |
ṣaṭsumanvantareṣvete devā dvādaśa dvādaśa ||046:017||
[abhūta ka; puṭsu ka ga]
yāmyā gatāstathā tvanye satyaiḥ satuṣitaiḥ saha |
ete yaśabhujo devā nityaṃ yajñe pratiṣṭhitāḥ ||046:018||
[satyāḥ ka ga; sādhyāndevān pravakṣyāmi nāmatastathā nivodhaye cittirtta roharaścaiva haṃso dharmmaṃśca vīryyavān |
vibhuścāpi prabhuścaiva sādhyā dvādaśa kīrttitāḥ ka ga; yajña bhujo ka ga ]
atītān varttamānāṃśca punaścāpi nivodha me |
ādityā maruto rudrāḥ kaśyapasyātmajāḥ smṛtāḥ ||046:019||
[atītā cartta ka ga]
viśve'tha vasavaḥ sādhyā vijñeyā dharmmasūnavaḥ |
evaṃ dharmmasutaḥ somastṛtīyo vasurucyate ||046:020||
[viśve savaḥ ka ga; sūtravaḥ kha; rucyāte ka]
dharmmo'pi brahmaṇaḥ putraḥ purāṇe niścayo mataḥ |
atha indrān manuścaiva nāmabhistu nivodha me ||046:021||
svāyambhuvo manuḥ pūrvvaṃ tataḥ svārociṣaḥ smṛtaḥ |
auttamastāmasaścaiva raivata ścākṣuṣastathā ||046:022||
[ścārociṣaḥ ka; śveta kha]
ityete ṣaḍatikrāntā saptamaḥ sāmprato manuḥ |
vaivasvata iti jñeyo bhaviṣyāḥ sapta cāpare ||046:023||
[viśvacet ka ga |
saptarmasāḥ sāṃprataṃ manuḥ ka]
teṣāmādyo'rkarṇiḥ dharmmasāvarṇireva ca |
tasmācca bhavasāvarṇiḥ brahma sāvarṇi rityataḥ ||046:024||
[teṣāmātmorka ka ga; brahma ka ga; tasmāca sāvarṇi ka ga; vidyataḥ ka]
pañcamo dakṣasāvarṇiḥ sāvarṇāḥ pañca kīrtitā |
raucyo bhautyaśca dvāvanyau ityete manavo matāḥ ||046:025||
[tābhyaśca ka]
indraśca viścabhuk jñe. vipaścit tadanantaram |
vibhuḥ prabhuḥ śikhi caiva tathaiva ca manojavaḥ ||046:026||
[vipaścityādanaṃtaraṃ ka ga]
aujasvī sāmpratastvindro balirbhāvyastvanantaram |
adbhutastridivā caiva daśmastvindra ucyate ||046:027||
[divācaiva ka ga]
suśāntiśca sukīrtiśca ṛtadhāmā divaspatiḥ |
iti bhūtā bhaviṣyāśca indrā jñeyāścaturdaśa ||046:028||
[dvijapati kha]
kāśyapo'tri vaśiṣṭhaśca bharadvājo'tha gautamaḥ |
viśvāmitro jamadagniśca saptaite ṛṣayaḥ smṛtāḥ ||046:029||
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi maruto'gnīn pitṛn grahān |
pravaho nivahaścaiva udbhava saṃbhavastathā ||046:030||
pravāho vivahaścaiva parivāhastathaiva ca |
antarīkṣe carā hyete pṛthaṅmārgaṃ vicāraṇāḥ ||046:031||
[vibhadaḥ saṃbhavaścaiva ka ga]
mahendrapravibhaktāṅga marutaḥ sapta kīrttitāḥ |
sūryyāgniśca śucirnāmnā vaidyutaḥ pāvakaḥ smṛtā ||046:032||
nirmmathyaḥ pavamāno'gnistrayaḥ proktā ime'gnayaḥ |
agnīnāṃ putra pautrāśca catvāriṃśat tathaiva tu ||046:033||
[paramagni strayaḥ ka]
marutāmapi sarvveṣāṃ vijñeyāḥ sapta saptakāḥ |
evaṃ saṃvatsaro hyagnirṛtavastasya jajñire ||046:034||
[yajñire ka]
ṛtuputrārttavāḥ pañca iti sargaḥ sanātanaḥ ||046:035ab||
saṃvatsaraśca prathamo dvitīyaḥ parivatsara ||046:035cd||
[ārtāṃvā ka; saṅkaḥ ka ga]
sāṃvatsarastṛtīyastu caturthastvanu vatsaraḥ ||046:035ef||
[idvatsara ka ga]
pañcamo vatsarasteṣā tatebhiḥ pañcabhiryugam |
teṣu saṃvatsaro hyagniḥ sūryyastu parivatsaraḥ ||046:036||
soma idvatsarasteṣāṃ vāyuścaivānu vatsaraḥ ||046:037ab||
rudrastu vatsaro jñeyaḥ pañcābdā ye yugātmakāḥ ||046:037cd||
dvādaśaṃ pañcadhā bhinnāḥ ṣaṣṭibhedā gurorgamāt ||046:037ef||
[gurorgamāḥ ka]
viṣṇuḥ surejyaḥ śakraśca agnistvaṣṭā tathaiva ca |
arhi vradhnaḥ-pitṛ-viśvaḥ-soma-indrogni-aśvinaḥ ||046:038||
bhago dvādaśamasteṣāṃ yugānāṃ dvādaśo mataḥ |
prabhavo vibhavaḥ śuklaḥ pramodo'tha prajāpatiḥ ||046:039||
[śukra ka ga]
aṅgirā śrīmukho bhāvo yuvā dhātā tathaiva ca |
īśvaro vahūdhānyaśca pramāthī vikramo vṛṣaḥ ||046:040||
[agrīrāśrī ka; abādhītā ka ga ]
citrabhānuḥ subhānuśca tāraṇaḥ pārthivo'vyayaḥ |
sarvvajit sarvvadhārī ca virodhī vikṛtaḥ kharaḥ ||046:041||
[sarvajit sarva sarvadharīva virodhīkṛtaḥ kharaḥ ka]
nandano vijayaśceva jayo manmatha durmukhaḥ |
hemalambo vilambaśca vikārī śarvvarī plavaḥ ||046:042||
[vayo ka ga]
śobhakṛcchubhakṛt krodhī viśvāvasuḥ parābhavaḥ |
plavaṅga kīlakaḥ saumyaḥ sādhāraṇa virodhakṛt ||046:043||
parivādī pramāthī ca ānando rākṣaso'nalaḥ |
piṅgalaḥ kālayuktaśca siddhārtho raudradurmmatiḥ ||046:044||
dundubhī rudhīrodgārī raktākṣaḥ krodhana kṣayaḥ |
ṣaṣṭi saṃvatsarādante yugai rdvādaśabhiḥ sthitā ||046:045||
[rucirau ka ga; saṃvatsarā hyete ka; smṛtāḥ ka ga]
gurordvādaśa māsānte vatsaramudayāstayoḥ |
nāmnā ṛkṣa vibhedena pañcadhā parivarttanam ||046:046||
[vatsarratradayo ka; nāma vidya ka; parivarttanā ka ga]
anu gacchati kālo'yaṃ brahmādikalano'tha vā |
sūkṣma sthūlavibhedena kalate sacarācaram ||046:047||
[kamalādhara ka]
kārtikaṃ śobhanaṃ rāṣṭraṃ saumyantu madhyamaṃ matam |
puṣyamāghau śubhau varṣau madhyamau phalgumādhavau ||046:048||
[śachaṃ ka; phālgunāghaiṇai ka]
vaiśākhaḥ pravarasteṣāṃ madhyamaḥ śuci saṃjñitaḥ |
āṣāḍho hyadhamaḥ prokta utkṛṣṭaḥ śrāvaṇo mataḥ ||046:049||
[āṣāṭho hyavamaḥ praddho uttamaḥ śrāvaṇo mataḥ ka]
bhādrapado madhyaphalaḥ śreṣṭhaphalo'śvino varṣaḥ |
kṛtikā rohiṇī kāyamāṣāḍhenābhi saṃjñitam ||046:050||
āśleṣāṃ hṛdayaṃ viddhi maghā pūṣantu vatsaram |
etaiḥ śuddhaiḥ śubhaṃ krūrahastaiścāśubhaṃ bhavet ||046:051||
[ṛá¹kṣeṣa hṛdayaṃ viddhaiḥ māghapuṣpaṃ ca vatsaraṃ ka; śubhaṃ ka ga]
madhyamaṃ prabhavaṃ varṣamītayaḥ santi no bhayam |
catvāro vibhavādyāśca śobhanā viyutā grahaiḥ ||046:052||
[pravaraṃ vatsarṣaḥ ka ga]
aṅgirādyāḥ śubhā strīṇi madhyamāvaparau matau |
īśvaro bahudhānyaśca śubhau pāpau pramāthinau ||046:053||
ādyai tu madhyame varṣe yuge'smiṃstu tṛtīyave |
śreṣṭhamādyaṃ caturthaṃsya madhyaṃ proktaṃ dvitīyakam ||046:054||
trīṇi cānyāni śreṣṭhāni sarvvakāma phalāni ca |
pañcame pravaramekaṃ sarvvadhārīti sanmatam ||046:055||
[yanmatam ka ga]
eṣāḥ kaṣṭaphalāḥ sarvve sarvvadoṣa bhayāvahāḥ |
catvāraḥ śobhanā ṣaṣṭhe yuge antyame śobhanam ||046:056||
ādhārastu saptame varṣe catvāro bhayadā matāḥ |
śobhanamantimaṃ varṣaṃ sarvvakāma phala pradam ||046:057||
aṣṭame dvau śubhau cānyau aśubhaṃ madhyamaṃ matam |
madhye dve cāntime varṣe guru cāravaśānnṛpa ||046:058
[puru ka ga]||
ādyamantau ca na śubhau navame dve pare śubhe |
daśame madhyamaṃ śreṣṭhamādyau antau ca ninditau ||046:059||
[aṃtyauva naṃditau ka]
tadvadekādaśe vidyādādyamadhyantu śobhanam |
yuge guruvāsād vatsa śubhāśubhaphalaṃ nṛṇām ||046:060||
janmarkṣaṃ kṛta karmmeṣu aṣṭadhānu gateṣu ca |
parivarttāḥ sadā kaṣṭāḥ śeṣāḥ sarvve śubhāvahāḥ ||046:061||
[dharmmeṣu aṣṭādhāna ka ga]
kūrmmakāla vibhāgena yathācāra gamena tu |
śubhāśubhantu deśānāṃ prayacchanti mahāgrahāḥ ||046:062||
āgneyādi vibhāgena trikarṇanavadhākṛtam |
kūrmmāṅga bhavate loko yatreyaṃ pṛthivī sthitā ||046:064||
[agni pādite bhāgena triṃkatu ka]
kecit kālaṃ vadantyanye svabhāvamāgame'pare |
grahabhāga gataṃ sarvvaṃ dṛśyate'smin śubhāśubham ||046:065||
[svabhāva mapare vudhāḥ ka ga; grahavamataṃ kha]
jambudvīpe tu vedeśe vyavahāro bhavinnṛṇām |
tadahaṃ sampravakṣyāmi saṃkṣepāt munipuṅgava ||046:066||
[jaṃbudvīpe tu yeda ka]
mithilā mekhalā kāśyā ahicchatrā purañjakāḥ |
sūryyāvarttāṃ nāma purī kauśāmbī yāśca śobhanāḥ ||046:067||
[mūryya varttāṃ nāma purā kauśāṃvī paṃca viṣayāśca ka]
pāṭaliputraṃ bhirahutī gaṅgāparaṃ yamunāntaram |
ānarttapuraṃ pṛthvīmadhyāntaṃ na dṛśyate krūraiḥ ||046:068||
[tirahutī ka ga]
māgadhā aṅgavaṅgāśca kaliṅgāḥ pūrvvasāgaram |
māhendrī viṣayaṃ gaṅgā militā yatra sāgare ||046:069||
samataṭaṃ varddhamānaśca śiropetai rvinaśyati |
kāmarūpaṃ videhāśca nepālaṃ revato giriḥ ||046:070||
[vinaśyaṃte ka]
kāśmīramambaraścaiva uttarapāde vinaśyati |
kaikaya acchodavanaṃ citraṃ kailāśameruñca ||046:071||
[kāśmīrāmÌ duṃvaraṃcaiva ka ga]
kanaka muttara deśāḥ kukṣyo'pahate vinaśyanti |
vāhikā mathurā vīthī puruṣapurā kākolī ||046:072||
[kṣovohate ka]
pārśve yā ca mahī paścimapāde vinaśyanti |
vaidiśaśca sauvīra sindhu bālā mahārāṣṭrāṇi ||046:073||
[vaideśa saurīvā ka; mahārājyāni ka ga]
saurāṣṭrapurādhigatā deśāḥ pucche vinaśyanti |
avantikā vidarbhāśca kāmÌcī pūrikāḥ siṃhalā ||046:074||
valaṃ malayavāsī ca laṅkāpurī tathaiva ca |
cakrākṣaṃ dakṣiṇe pāde hate naśyanti pīḍitāḥ ||046:075||
narmmaṃdāyā mahī madhyaṃ vaijayantī ca koṅkaṇam |
puruṣapuranāmā ca sahyākhyaśca mahāgiriḥ ||046:076||
[puruṣa puranvī sā ca kāryyāṃkhcaśca ka]
araṇyaṃ gopuraṃ bhīmaṃ kukṣau dakṣīṇa saṃyutam |
veśaṃ kośala kāntāra hara kūṭa mahādhvanāḥ ||046:077||
[saṃhatā ka ga; hara kroḍā mahādhanāḥ ka]
veṇyā taṭaṃ samastañca gatāḥ pūrvvāṅgghrisaṅgatā |
vinaśyanti hatāḥ krūrairgrahairutpāta sūcitāḥ ||046:078||
[pūrvā hane māhatāḥ ka; krūraiḥ arupete sūcitā ka]
sūryyasyodayamarutādi saṃkrātau krama pīḍitāḥ |
tiryyag gataśca madhyāhṇe astamite adhomukho raviścarate ||046:079||
[tiryyagāto madhyohne asta mahedhomuvi raviścarate ka]
arddha niśāyāṃ śayitaḥ kramate urddhva prabhāte tu |
viniviṣṭastu vakārādau śayito garatai tile ||046:080||
koleva cocchrito rāśiṃ raviḥ saṃkramate sadā |
dhanuḥ siṃha vṛṣakuṃbhairupasaṃsthaiḥ sadā varaiḥ kṣemam ||046:081||
[cotthito, ka ga; śiṃkhi ka]
anupacayasthaiḥ krūraistairdṛṣṭo lokanāśāya |
a i ta e kṛttikā o va vi vu rohiṇī ||046:082||
[cāvidhu ka]
ve vo ka ki mṛga śirāḥ ku gha ḍa cha ārdrā |
ke ko ha hi punarvvasuḥ hu he ho ḍa puṣyā ||046:083||
[re vo kā kī syā śivā ka; ku pa ṭhā ścādrī, ka; ko ko hī punarvasu, ka; ku he ho ḍā puṣyā, ka ]
ḍi ḍu ḍe ḍo āśleṣā ma mi mu me maghā |
mo ṭa ṭi ṭu pūrvvāphālgunī ṭe ṭo pa pi uttara phālgunī ||046:084||
[ḍi mi ḍe ḍe, ka; somisva me maghā, ka; moṭhā hodu pūrvāṣāḍhā, ka]
pu ṣa ṇa ḍha hastā pe po ra ri citrā |
ru re ro ta svātī ti tu te to viśākhā ||046:085||
[ṭhiṭhoṣāyi uttarā ka; purāṇe ṭha hastā, ka; ye yo vā vicitrā, ka; ru re vo bhāsvotī, ka; tu te to viśākhā ka ]
nā ni nu ne anurādhā no ya yi yu jyeṣṭhā |
ye yo bha bhi mūlā bhu dha pha ḍha pūrvvāṣāḍhā ||046:086||
[lopāpi pūjyeṣṭā, ka; bhe bhe mo bhā bhī mūlā ka; bha dha pha ṭha pūrvā, ka]
bhe bho ja ji uttarāṣāḍhā ju je jo kha abhijit |
khi khu khe kho śravaṇā ga gi gu ge dhaniṣṭhā ||046:087||
[bhe bho yājī uttarā, ka; ju jo thā, ka; khi lu khe kho, ka; gā gigū ge, ka]
go śa śi śu śatabhiṣā śe śo da di pūrvva bhādrapadā |
du tha jha ja uttarabhādrapadā de do ca ci revatī ||046:088||
[śī sā si sū ka; so sā dā dī ka; la tha ja uttara, ka; cā cī ka]
cu ce co lā aśvinī li lu le lo bharaṇī |
etairvarṇākṣarai sarvva trailokyaṃ sacarācaram ||046:089||
[sarvaṃ dṛśyādṛśyacarāṃ ka]
ādyākṣarasya nāmena budhyā kathaya śubhāśubham |
viśākhādi sthite sūryye utpāta mṛtyu kāraki ||046:090||
[kārakāḥ ka]
siddhi yogāśca jāyante ādyantāḥ svāti paścimāḥ |
viṃśa ṣoḍaśa saṃkhyātāḥ pañcadaśa ca caturdaśa ||046:091||
[śrāvyatāṃ, ka ga; viśeṣo' saṃkhāt ka ga]
viśve sūryyāṃśca grahāśca sūryyādyāḥ śanipaścimāḥ |
chāyā sarvveṣu kāryyeṣu sādhanāya prakīrttitā ||046:092||
vivāha maṅgalādīnāṃ saṃpratiṣṭhādyabhivecanam |
yātrā puṣyābhiṣeke ca chāyā saṃsādhanī śubhā ||046:093||
iti śrī devī purāṇe'bhyudayapāde kālavyavasthānāma ṣaṭcatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

daye udayatithyṛkṣaṃ yoga māhātmya kīrttanaṃ nāma pañcacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

%%%%
%%% Chapter 047
saptacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |

vargāḥ ka ca ṭha ta pādayāḥ |
lohita bhṛgu saumya- saurāṇām ||047:001||
[pālohita ka ga; saumya jīva, ka ga ]
sūryyasya akārādyāḥ śarśino varṇā yakārādyāḥ |
meṣādiṣu navabhāgārthe sasvaravarṇāḥ krameṇa samabhigatāḥ ||047:002||
[śaśināṃnā, ka; mipādipu nava māgāt sasvaravarṇāḥ krameṇa samabhigatāḥ, ka]
varge ca parisamāpte pūrvvavadāramyate bhūyaḥ |
svara vyañjana saṃyogo bhūtattva latā yathā yogam ||047:003||
[bhṛgu tanya natā, ka]
jñātvā sarvvameśeṣa dharmmādikamārabhennityam |
truṭyanupakṣamāsa kramāyan samādiṣu ||047:004||
pitaraḥ sarvvadevānāṃ grahādīnāṃ nivodhata |
ārttavā pitaro jñeyā ye jātā ṛtusūnavaḥ ||047:005||
prapitāmahā ṛtavaḥ pañcāśat brahmaṇaḥ sutāḥ |
saumyā varhiṣadaścaiva agnisvārttāśca te tridhā ||047:006||
[mātaraḥ, ka ga]
ādityaścaiva somaśca lohitāṅgo vudhstathā |
vṛhspatiśca śukraśca tathā caiva śanaiścaraḥ ||047:007||
rāhuśca dhūmaketuśca ete navagrahā smṛtāḥ |
trailokyasya me nityaṃ bhāvā bhāva vivecakāḥ ||047:008||
[vivekadāḥ ka]
ādityaścaiva somaśca dvāvetau maṇḍalau grahau |
rāhuśchāyā grahasteṣāṃ śeṣāstārā grahāḥ smṛtāḥ ||047:009||
nakṣatrādhipatiḥ somo graharājo divākaraḥ |
pacyete cāgnirādityo udakaṃ candramāḥ smṛtaḥ ||047:010||
ādityaḥ paṭhyate(FN8) śambhurumāṃ vidyān niśākaram(FN9) |
pitāmahastu vijñeya tṛtīyo'ṅgārako grahaḥ ||047:011||
[matter not found]
kāśyapasya sutaḥ sūryyaḥ somo dharmmasutaḥ smṛtaḥ |
devāsura gurū dvau ca bhānumantau mahāgrahau |
||047:012||
prajāpati sutāvetāvubhau śukravṛhaspatī |
vudhaḥ somātmajaḥ śrīmān sūryya putraḥ śanaiścaraḥ ||047:013||
saiṃhikeyaḥ smṛto rāhūḥ ketuśca brahmaṇaḥ sutaḥ |
sarvveṣāntu grahāṇāṃ vai adhastāccarate raviḥ ||047:014||
raverurdhvaṃ sthitaḥ somaḥ somāt nakṣatramaṇḍalam |
nakṣatrebhyo vudhastūrdhvaṃ vudhādūrdhvantu bhārgavaḥ ||047:015||
tasmādaṅgārakaḥ corddhvaṃ tasya cordhvaṃ vṛhaspatiḥ |
tasmācchanaiścaraḥ cordhvaṃ tasyordhvaṃmṛṣi maṇḍalam ||047:016||
ṛṣibhyaśca dhruvaścordhvaṃ māyānte tridivaṃ dhruve |
āditya nilayo rāhuḥ kadācit somamārgaṃṇaḥ ||047:017||
sūryya maṇḍala saṃsthastu nityaṃ ketuḥ prasarpati |
nava yojana sahasrāṇi vistāro bhāskarasya tu ||047:018||
vistāro triguṇañcāsya pariṇāhe tu maṇḍalam |
dviguṇaḥ sūryya vistārād vistaraḥ śaśinaḥ smṛta ||047:019||
dviguṇaṃ maṇḍalañcāsya yathaiva savitustathā |
candrataḥ ṣoḍaśo bhāgo bhārgaṃvasya vidhīyate ||047:020||
bhārgavāt pādahīnastu vijñeyo vai vṛhaspati |
vṛhaspateḥ pādahīnau vakra saurāvudāhṛtau ||047:021||
[vajra ka]
vistāra maṇḍalābhyāntu pādahīnāstayorvuṃdhaḥ |
budhasya tulyāni ṛkṣāṇi sarvvahrasvāni yāni tu ||047:022||
yojanārdva pramāṇāni(FN) tebhyo hrasvaṃ na vidyate ||047:023ab||
[ka pustake nāsti]
rāhuḥ sūryyaṃ pramāṇastu kadācita soma saṃśitaḥ ||047:023cd||
tasmād graha pramāṇastu ketustvaniyataḥ smṛtaḥ ||047:023ef||
bhū rlokaṃ bhuvaḥ svarlokaṃ trailokyamidamucyate |
maharjjanastapaḥ satyaṃ sapta lokāḥ prakīrttitāḥ ||047:024||
bhūrlokaḥ pārthivo lokāt antarīkṣaṃ bhuvaḥ smṛtaḥ |
bhāvyo loko divi hyetāccheṣā ūrdhvaṃ yathākramam ||047:025||
[chāyā ka]
bhūtasyādhipati hyagnistato bhūtapatistu saḥ |
vāyu rnabhaso'dhipatistena vāyunabhaspatiḥ ||047:026||
bhāvyasya sūryyo .adhipatistena sūryyo divaspatiḥ |
gandharvvāpsarasaścaiva guhyakāḥ saha rākṣasaiḥ ||047:027||
bhūrllokavāsinaḥ sarvve antarīkṣacarān śṛṇu |
marutaḥ saptabhiḥ skandhaiḥ rudrāstathaiva cāśvinau ||047:028||
[samabhiḥ ka ga]
ādityā vasavaḥ sarvve tathaiva ca gavāṃ gaṇāḥ |
caturthe tu maharloke tiṣṭhante kalpavāsinaḥ ||047:029||
prajānāṃ patibhiḥ sarvai sevyate pañcamo mahān |
manuḥ sanatkumārādyā vairājāśca sutāśayaḥ ||047:030||
[āditthāvasavaḥ svarge tathaiva ca gavāṃganāḥ ka; caturthaitipahallorke tiṣṭaṃte kalpa vāsinaḥ |
prajānāṃ patibhiḥ sarvai. sevyate paṃcamo ka; tapāścayaḥ ka ]
ṣaṣṭhe tu saṃsthitā hyete devā deva vibodhakāḥ |
satyantu saptamo loko hyapunarbhava vāsinām ||047:031||
brahmalokaḥ samākhyāto hyapratighāta lakṣaṇaḥ |
mahītalāt sahasrāṇāṃ śatādūrdhvaṃ divākaraḥ ||047:032||
daśa tāni dhruve yāvad dviguṇe dviguṇāntare |
daśa yojana koṭyastu bhūmerūrdhvaṃ dhruvaḥ smṛtaḥ ||047:033||
trayoviṃśati lakṣāṇi trailokyāt megha ucyate |
dviguṇeṣu sahasreṣu yojanānāṃ śateṣu ca ||047:034||
[nakṣatrāṇi ka ga; trailoktsaka ucyate ka ga]
lokāntaramathaikaikaṃ dhruvādūrddhvaṃ vidhīyate |
deva dānava gandharvva yakṣa rākṣasa pannagāḥ ||047:035||
[kratāchardva ka]
bhūtā vidyādharāścaiva aṣṭau te devayonayaḥ |
te brahmāṇḍasya madhyasthāḥ paratastamasāvṛtam ||047:036||
[gadhyāsthā ka; samāvṛtam ka ga ]
tato'gnirvāyurākāśaṃ tato bhūtādirūcyate |
tato mahān pradhānaśca prakṛtiḥ puruṣastataḥ ||047:037||
purūṣādīśvaro jñeyo yasya śaktyāvṛtaṃ jagat |
śivomā bhānudevānāṃ parātparatarā matā ||047:038||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe trailokyābhyudaye grahagatirnāma saptacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
%%%%

%%% Chapter 048
aṣṭacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
brahmovāca |

rākā cānumatī caiva dvividhā pūrṇimā tathā |
sinī'vālī kuhuścaiva amāvasyā dvidhaiva tu ||048:001||
[smṛtā ka]
amā nāma rave raśmiścandraloke pratiṣṭhitā |
yasmāt somo vasatyasmāt amāvāsī tataḥ smṛtāḥ ||048:002||
pūrvvodite kalābhinne paurṇamāsyāṃ niśākare |
pūrṇimānumatī jñeyā yaścāstamita bhāskare ||048:003||
[pūrṇamāṃsyāṃ ka ga]
yasmāt tāmanu manyante devatā pitṛbhiḥ saha |
tasmātanumatī nāma pūrṇimā ca tadā smṛtā ||048:004||
[prathamā ka]
yadā cāstamite sūryye pūrṇacandrasya codgamaḥ |
yugapat sottarā rākā tadānumati-pūrvvikā ||048:005||
[yadāstamate ka; pūrṇimāḥ ka ga]
rākā tāmanumanyete devatāḥ pitṛbhiḥ saha |
rañjanā caiva candrasya rāketi kavayo'vruvan ||048:006||
[karayobruvat ka]
sinī vālī pramāṇantu kṣīṇa śeṣo niśākaraḥ |
amāvasyāṃ viśetyaṃrka sinīvālī tataḥ smṛtāḥ ||048:007||
kuhvati kokilenokte yaḥ kālastu samāpyate |
tattatkāla saṃjñā tveṣā vai amāvasyā kuhuḥ smṛtā ||048:008||
[kuheti ka; palktālastu ka]
anumatyā sarākāyā sinī vālyā kuhuṃ vinā |
etāsāṃ dvi-navaḥ kālaḥ kumātreti kuhuḥ smṛtāḥ ||048:009||
kalāḥ ṣoḍaśa somasya śukle varddhayate raviḥ |
anṛ tenāmṛtaṃ kṛṣṇa pīyante daivataiḥ kramāt ||048:010||
prathamāṃ pivate vahṇi rdvitīyaṃ tapanaḥ kalām |
viśve devāstṛtīyāntu caturthīntu prajāpatiḥ ||048:011||
pañcamī varuṇāścāpi ṣaṣṭhiṃ pivati vāsavaḥ |
saptamīmṛṣayo divyā vasavoṣṭau tathāṣṭamīm ||048:012||
navamīṃ kṛṣṇapakṣasya pivatīndraḥ kalā mapi |
daśamīṃ marūtaścāpi rudrā ekādaśīṃ kalām ||048:013||
[pivatīcandraḥ kalāmapi ka]
dvādaśīntu kalāṃ viṣṇurdhanadaśca trayodaśīm |
caturdaśīṃ paśupatiḥ kalāṃ pivanti nityaśaḥ ||048:014||
tata pañcadaśīñcaiva pivanti pitara kalām |
kalāvaśiṣṭo niṣpītaḥ praviṣṭaḥ sūryyamaṇḍalam ||048:015||
amāyāṃ viśati raśmau amāvāsī tataḥ smṛtā ||048:016ab||
[viśate ka ga]
pūrvāhne praviśatyarka madhyāhne tu vanaspati ||048:016cd||
[pūrvāhe prari śatyaṃ rka madhyāhe tu vanasyati ka]
aparāhṇe viśatyapsu svayoniṃ vāri sambhavaḥ||048:016ef||
āpaḥ praviṣṭa somastu śeṣayā kalayaikayā |
tṛṇa gulma latā vṛkṣān niṣpādayati cauṣadhīḥ ||048:017||
[ aparānhe ka ]
tamoṣadhiḥ sthitaṃ gāvaścaratyo'paḥ pivanti ca |
tadaṅgānugataṃ gobhyaḥ kṣīratvamupagacchati ||048:018||
tat kṣīrasamavṛtaṃ bhūtvā mantrapūtaṃ dvijātayaḥ |
svāhākāravaṣaṭakāraiḥ juhvatyā hutayaḥ kramāt ||048:019||
[ juhayādyā ka; aginaścaḥ ]
hutamagniṣu devāya punaḥ somaṃ vivarddhayet ||048:020ab||
evaṃ saṃkṣīyate somaḥ kṣīṇaścāpyāyate punaḥ ||048:020cd||
tasmāt sūryyaḥ śaśāṅkasya kṣayavṛddhi rvidhedvibhuḥ ||048:020ef||
[ka pustake paṃktī rna santi]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe candrakṣayavṛddhirnāma aṣṭacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye devyavatāre candrakṣayavṛddhiḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 049
ekonapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

yadayaṃ vadate loko vāliśatvān mahāmate |
tadahaṃ saṃpravakṣyāmi candra sūryyoparāṇikam ||049:001||
[paṃktī rna santi ka pustake]
yadi satyamayaṃ grastastejorāśi rdivākaraḥ |
tat kathantūdarasthena rāhuṇā bhasmasāt kṛtaḥ ||049:002||
[kathaṃnodaraḥ ka ga; rāhurna ka ga]
athavā rāhuṇākramya śatruvaktraṃ praveśitaḥ |
tat kathaṃ daśanaistīkṣṇaiḥ śatadhā ca vikhaṇḍitaḥ ||049:003||
[gatavān ka]
vimuktaśca punardṛṃṣṭastathaivākhaṇḍamaṇḍalaḥ |
na cāsyāpahṇutaṃ tejo na sthānādapasāritaḥ ||049:004||
yadi vāpyeṣa niṣpītaḥ kathaṃ dīptataro'bhavat ||049:005ab||
tasmānna tejasāṃ rāśī rāhorvaktraṃ gamiṣyati ||049:005cd||
bhakṣyārthaṃ sarvva devānāṃ somaḥ sṛṣṭaḥ svayambhuvā ||049:005ef||
[svāyaṃbhuva kha]
tatrasthamamṛtañcāpi sambhavaṃ sūryatejasā |
pibanti yastūbhayaṃ devāḥ pitaraśca svadhā mṛtam ||049:006||
[pivatyaṃ vrumarya devāḥ pitaraḥ ka]
trayaśca triśataṃ caiva trayastriṃśat tathaiva ca |
trayaśca rtrisahasrāśca devāḥ somaṃ pivanti ca ||049:007||
[ye ka]
rāhorapyamṛtaṃ bhāgaṃ purā sṛṣṭaṃ svayambhuvā |
tasmāt tadrāhurāgatya pātu micchati parvvasu ||049:008||
[ttatrādrāhu ka]
uddhṛtya pārthivīṃ chāyāṃ mandakāmaṃ tamomayaḥ |
pātumicchan tataścendumācchādayati chāyayā ||049:009||
[mabhrākārāṃ ka]
śukle ca candramabhyeti kṛṣṇe parvvaṇi bhāskaram |
sūrya maṇḍala saṃsthastu candrameva jighāṃsati ||049:0010||
[candre kha; saṃsthātu ka]
tasmāt pivati taṃ rāhustanumasya vināśayan |
avihiṃsan yathā padmaṃ pivati bhramaro madhu ||049:011||
candrasya amṛtaṃ tadvad bhedādrāhuraśnute |
candrakāṃto maṇiryadvat tuhinaṃ kṣarate kṣaṇāt ||049:012||
kṣarannapi na hīyate tejasā naiva mucyate |
yathā sūryyamaṇiścāpi sūryyādutpādya pāvakam ||049:013||
na bhavatyaṅga hīno'pi tejasā nava mucyate |
evaṃ candraśca sūryyaśca chāditāvapi rāhuṇā ||049:014||
svatejasā na mucyete nāṅgahīnau vabhūvatuḥ |
parvvasvatha ca candrasya māṇikya kalasākṛtiḥ ||049:015||
somo daivata saṃyogācchāyā yogācca pārthive |
rāhośca varalabdhādvai prakṣaredamṛtaṃ śaśī ||049:016||
[somau devata ka ga; yogādha pārthivāta ka; mṛtāpi ka ]
svadoha kāle saṃprāpte vatsaṃ dṛṣṭvā yathā ca gaḥ |
svāṅgadeva kṣaret kṣīraṃ tathenduḥ kṣarate'mṛtam ||049:017||
piteva sūryyo devānāṃ somo māte lakṣyate |
yathā mātuḥ stanaṃ pītvā jīvanti sarvvajantavaḥ ||049:018||
pītvāmṛtaṃ tathā somāt tṛṣyante sarvva devatāḥ |
saṃbhūtaṃ parvva yogeṣu tathāyaṃ kṣarate śaśī ||049:019||
taṃ kṣarantaṃ yathābhāgamupajīvanti devatāḥ |
tasmin kāle samabhyeti rāhurapyavakarṣati ||049:020||
sarvvaṃmarddhaṃ tribhāgaṃ vā pādaṃ pādārddhaṃmeva vā |
ākramya pārthivīṃ chāyāṃ yāvaṃtī candra maṇḍalam ||049:021||
[paṃktī rna santi ka pustake]
smṛtaḥ sa bhāgo rāhostu deva bhāgāstu śeṣakāḥ |
tṛptiṃ vidhāya devānāṃ rāhoḥ parvvagatasya ca ||049:022||
[śeṣagā ka ga; dṛṣṭiṃ ka ga]
candro na kṣayamāyāti tejasā naiva mucyate |
tithi bhāgāśca yāvantaḥ punastvarkaṃ pramāṇataḥ ||049:023||
parvvacchāyāsthitaḥ kālastāvānevaṃ prakīrttitaḥ |
adhorāhupuraḥ somaḥ somādūrdhva divākaraḥ ||049:024||
[ato kha]
parvvakāle sthiti stvevaṃ viparītaḥ punaḥ punaḥ |
ataśchādayate rāhurabhavacchaśi bhāskarau ||049:025||
rāhurabhrakasaṃsthānaḥ somamācchādya tiṣṭhati |
uddhṛtya pārthivī chāyāṃ dhūmamegha ivotthitaḥ ||049:026||
[somamāgha ka]
candrasya yaddṛṣṭavyaṃ rāhuṇā bhāskarasya vā |
nāmnā ca khaṃḍitaṃ tasya kevalaṃ śyāmalī kṛtam ||049:027||
[ghyāmanī ka]
kardamena yathā vastraṃ śuklamabhyupahanyate |
ekoddeśe tu sarvva vā rāhuṇā candramāstathā ||049:028||
prakṣālitaṃ tadevāstu punaḥ śuklataraṃ bhavet |
rāhu muktaṃ bhavet tadvannirmmalaṃ candramaṇḍalam ||049:029||
[tadeveha ka ga]
rāhuṇācchāditau vāpi dṛṣṭvā candra divākarau |
viprāḥ śāṃti parā bhūtvā punarāpyāya yantritam ||049:030||
[paṃtitam ka ga]
evaṃ na gṛhyate sūryyaścandramāstatra gṛhyate ||049:031ab||
avudhāstaṃ na paśyanti mānuṣā māṃsa cakṣuṣā ||049:031cd||
jagat sanmohanaṃ caiva grahaṇaṃ candra sūryayoḥ ||049:031ef||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe grahaṇavikalpo nāmaikonapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
[ityādye devyavatāre grahaṇavikalpaḥ ka ga]
