%%% Chapter 051
ekapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

yeyaṃ devī ihāmutra hitāya samupāśritā |
svārtha siddhau parārthe vā bhavantī kathayāmite ||051:001||
maṅgalā śākambharī kālī devyā yā trividhā tanuḥ |
ghorahā ruruhā vatsa śubhā kandaka nāśinī ||051:002||
[kaṃbhavā ka; śubhāṃdhakārī ka ga]
damanī mahiṣadhnī ca tathā ca mahiṣāsurā |
etā mūlagatā devyaḥ ṣaṣṭidhā koṭidhāparāḥ ||051:003||
[madanī ka ga; bhedāḥ ka ga]
eteṣāṃ śāstravettāro devī pūjāvidhau śubhā |
mātṛ maṇḍala vettā ca brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo'pi vā ||051:004||
[etāsāṃ ka ga; kṛtriyo ka]
praticārī viśorvāpi śūdro vā tattvavidyadi |
pūjāvidhau bhavet śreṣṭho na mando na kuśīlavaḥ ||051:005||
[sasagurna kuśīnaraḥ ka]
na naiṣṭhiko viśāstro vā pūjako bhavate śubhaḥ |
abhidhau ya śivāṃ pūjyetā pareṇa niyājitaḥ ||051:006||
[stotya ka; pūjyeda ka]
sa yāti narake ghoraṃ svāmī rājā ca naśyati |
tasmācchivavidhā devī viṣṇurbhārgava taiḥ śubhaiḥ ||051:007||
pūjitaḥ śivavataḥ sūryyaḥ śivaḥ sarvvaphala pradaḥ |
agre vā śiva siddhānta tilakādi pravedibhiḥ ||051:008||
[ śaivaiḥ ka ga; mṛgai ka ga ]
māṭharokta vidhau vāpi sarvvakāma pradāyakaḥ |
ahañca veda vidhinā grahā nāgā pare surāḥ||051:009||
[kumārokta ka; ahaca ka ga]
suśāstravidhimāśritya pūjitāḥ phaladā nṛṇām |
vaiparityādbhayaṃ kuryyāt apade rājanastha ca ||051:010||
[phaladānyayāṃ ka]
tasmāt parārdhyamuddiśya pūjāṃ vidhi śubhāvahā |
madhurāmlādinā kecit tuṣyante baṭukaiḥ pare ||051:011||
kaṣāya lavaṇaistiktairevaṃ bhinnā nṛṇāṃ matiḥ |
devā mūrttigatāḥ sthūlāḥ śabdagā dhyānagāḥ pare ||051:012||
svārtha siddhau parārthe vā manasā yānti cintitāḥ |
tathāpi upacāreṇa jāti bheda kriyādibhi ||051:013||
śive vivarjjayet kundamunmattañca harestathā |
devīnāñcārka mandārau sūryye keśayutaṃ mṛgam ||051:014||
evaṃ vidhiṃ samāśritya pūjayellabhato phalam |
hema pātreṇa sarvvāṇi labhate ca hitān mune ||051:015||
[pūjayan labhato phalaṃ ka  ga; pātrāṇi ka ga]
ardhyaṃ datvā tu raupyeṇa āyu rājya sutāmÌllabheta |
tāmra pātreṇa saubhāgyaṃ dharmmaṃ mṛnmaya sambhavaiḥ ||051:016||
[grāha ka ga]
vārkṣapātrāṇi pātrāṇi naiṣṭhikādiṣu kārayet |
śailāni krūra jātīnāṃ raktādi sarvvakāmikam ||051:017||
[ratnādi ka]
dhātūttamāni pātrāṇi nṛparāṣṭra vivṛddhayai |
trapusīsa kalau hāniranya jātiṣu kārayet ||051:018||
[atajākiṣu ka]
vivāha yajña śrāddheṣu pratiṣṭhāsu viśeṣataḥ |
pātrāṇāñcādaraḥ kāryyaḥ pātrāṇyevottamāni ca ||051:019||
pātreṣu pṛthivī dugdhā sudhā pātreṣu dhāryyate |
vedāḥ somaṃ kraturpajñāḥ pātrāṇyeva vidurvudhāḥ ||051:020||
bali homa kriyādīni binā pātre na sidhyati |
tasmād yajñāṅgamevāhuḥ pātrañcāgpraṃ mahāmune ||051:021||
yo yasya āyudhaḥ proktastasya tallāñchanaṃ bhavet |
vāhana dhvajacchatreṣu lāñchanaṃ parikalpayet ||051:022||
[cāyudha ka ga]
ṣaṭtriśadaṅgulaṃ pātrañcottamaṃ parikīrttitam |
rasa aṅgula kīnantu na pātraṃ kārayet kvacit ||051:023||
[paṃktī na santi ka pustake]
nānā vicitra rūpāṇi puṇḍarīkākṛtīni ca |
śaṅkha nīlotpalākārān pātrāṇi parikalpayet ||051:024||
vinā pātrāṇi yaḥ kuryyāt pratiṣṭhāṃ yājñikī kriyām |
viphalā bhavate sarvvā vāhanāddhi dhanāpahā ||051:025||
[ratvādi racitāṃ kuryyātakāṃcī mūla susaṃcitān |
yathā śobhā yathā lābhaṃ pātrāṇi rikalpayet ka; pātreṇa ka ]
balihīne tu durbhikṣaṃ gandhahīne abhogyatā |
dhūpahīne ca udvegaṃ vastrahīne dhanakṣayam ||051:026||
ratnahīne haredbhāryyāṃ patākai rddaṇḍanāyakam |
chatra hīne harecchatraṃ vitāne makaraṃ bhavet ||051:027||
[vitāsavakaṃ ka ga]
vedīhīne tu cālaṃ syānnagarasya purasya ca |
kalasai rbandhu nārāśva bhavati munisattama ||051:028||
[nāśantu ka ga; bhavate ka]
toraṇānāmabhāve tu harejjātīśca vāndhavān |
sruvi kuṇḍavihīnaṃ tu yajñaṃ lupyanti rākṣasāḥ ||051:029||
[hanetajñā; lupati ka]
rajohīnaṃ tu daurbhāgyaṃ prāpnuyāt kāraka sadā |
dakṣiṇā rahite sarvvaṃ bhavate avicāraṇāt ||051:030||
[rajahīne ka; dārakaḥ ka ga]
mantra vidyā vihīnantu sampūrṇamapi naśyati |
pātra mantra samāyuktaṃ sarvva doṣān nivārayet ||051:031||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe pātravidhirnāma ekapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
%%%%

%%% Chapter 052
dvipañcāśodhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

śṛṇu śaunaka tattvena apa mṛtyu nivāraṇam |
sarvva kāma pradaṃ puṇyaṃ raviyāga manuttamam ||052:001||
[midaṃ ka]
grahā māghādi bhedena ādityaṃ makare yajet |
hasta mātre śubhe padme karṇikā keśarojjvale ||052:002||
[ṣakṣe ka]
kuṅkumādi rajairlikhyamaṣṭapatraṃ ravergraham |
ādityaṃ pūjayenmadhye pūrvvapatre niśākaram ||052:003||
maṅgalaṃ vahnipatrasthaṃ dakṣiṇena budhaṃ yajet |
śani nairṛta patrasthaṃ surejyaṃ varuṇālayam ||052:004||
vāyavye saihiṃkeyantu bhārgavañcottare yajet |
ketuṃ śivāṅge deyaṃ yāge sarvvaśubhodaye ||052:005||
[śivāśaṃga ka]
ādi varṇa kṛtādhāraṃ ādityaṃ śambhunā yajet |
śeṣā vāruṇa varṇena aṣṭadhābhi rdivena tu ||052:006||
gandha puṣpaṃ pavitrantu hṛdayena pradāpayet |
varadābhaya mudrau tu madhye vyomaṃ pradarśayet ||052:007||
[ghūpa ka ga; vāma ka ga]
sarvva raktopacārantu ādityāya prakalpayet |
sva sva varṇaṃ grahāṇāntu deyaṃ puṣpavilepanam ||052:008||
homaṃ tilājyakṣaudrantu pāyasantu nivedayet |
evaṃ kṛtvā japaṃ devamādityāya susaṃkhyayā ||052:009||
[pāyasaṃra ka ga; kratvādyajaṃ ka]
snānaṃ śiṣyāya karttavyaṃ mantra pūtena vāriṇā |
sarvva kāmānavāpnoti yo vidhiṃ kārayedimam ||052:0010||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe ādityayāgonāma dvipañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
%%%%

%%% Chapter 053

tripañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |

ādityaṃ bhāskaraṃ sūryyaṃ raviṃ bhānuṃ divākaram |
sraṣṭāraṃ tejinaṃ bhāvaṃ jayantaṃ śubhadaṃ śivam ||053:001||
makarādi prabhedena ādityādi śubhodayam |
yaṣṭavyā hastamātre tu dvivṛdhyā dhanuṣāvadhi ||053:002||
[bhanuravī ka]
śubhado'yaṃ jayaṃ bhāgyaṃ kalyāṇamaparājitam |
maṅgalamiṣṭa siddhiñca vibhavaṃ śubhadaṃ śubham ||053:003||
[śubhodayaṃ javaṃ ka; sutadaṃ ka ga]
iṣṭākhyaṃ vyādhināśantu makarādau samārabheta |
sarvvapāpaharā yāgāḥ sarvve āyurdhanapradāḥ ||053:004||
sarvva roga vināśāya sarvve kāryyāḥ sukhāya ca |
nityaṃ śvetopahāreṇa āyurārogyadāyakāḥ ||053:005||
[śvetopacāreṇa ka ga]
suta saubhāgya kāmena kāryyā raktopacārikāḥ |
pītena grahanāśārthaṃ kṛṣṇaiḥ śatrunivāraṇam ||053:006||
grahāṇāṃ yajanaṃ kāryyaṃ samantraṃ valipūjanam |
phala ratnauṣadhī gandhavīja dhātu mṛtādibhiḥ ||053:007||
saptodaka samantreṇa snātvā bhāgyodayo bhavet |
gajānāṃ turagāṇāñca raviśakra samanvitam ||053:008||
[maṃtritāṃ ka]
snānaṃ homaṃ prakarttavyaṃ lakṣāyuta sahasrikam |
mātarāṇāṃ sada cakraṃ hemarājatatāmrajam ||053:009||
[tāmrakaṃ ka ga]
pūjanaṃ vidhinā vipra saṃvatsaraṃ bhayāpaham ||053:010||
[pūjitaṃ ka; saṃvatsara bhayāpahaṃ ka ga]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe grahamātṛvidhirnāma tripañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
[ādye grahamātṛvidhiḥ ka ga]
%%%%

%%% Chapter 054

catuḥpañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

sahasra lakṣaṇopetaṃ vaidūryye kārayecchivam |
haima pīṭhaṃ suśobhāḍhyaṃ vajrāṅkaṃ tatra mātarāḥ ||054:001||
[ṣaḍas ka; ka pustake nāsti; harapīyaṃ ka; vajrārddha ka]
carccikādyāḥ prakarttavyāḥ pūrvvādi parikalpitāḥ ||054:002||
mahābhaya vināśāya ṛtuyāga prapūjitāḥ |
śivaṃ(FN) rudraṃ sadā vatsa karṇikāyāṃ niveśitam ||054:003||
[ka pustake nāsti]
mahāvibhava sāreṇa vastra gandhaṃ supūjitam |
prayacchati śubhān kāmān mano'bhīṣṭān sadā jane ||054:001||
[sadājale ka ga]
tasya pūjā prakarttavyā gehe sarvvatra kālike |
japa homārccanaṃ pūjā trikālaṃ satataṃ bhavet ||054:005||
[gṛhe sarvarttukāmike ka]
kuṅkumāgurū karpūra mada candana rocanāḥ |
gandha puṣpāśca dātavyāḥ sitaniryyāsasiddhakāḥ ||054:006||
[sihūkāḥ ka ga]
sarvvabhaya vināśāya pramāthī piṅgalāpi vā |
śani sūryyā ca rāhūtthā kṣayādi mahadāpadaḥ ||054:007||
[mahadāsayaḥ ka]
anna janmarkṣa mṛtyusthāḥ samaṃ yāntyavicāraṇāt |
tāmre patre prakarttavyā grahabhāga prakalpitā ||054:008||
[anu ka; bhāva prakalpitā ka]
rakta candana miśreṇa toyena satate jitāḥ |
rakta karavīrapuṣpairmantra pūtārdha pūjitāḥ ||054:009||
[pūrṇārgha ka ga]
vyome vā maṇḍale vāpi sarvvakāma phala pradā |
arka palāśa khadirā apāmārgo'tha pippalā ||054:010||
śrī phalā śamī dūrvvā ca kuśāgrāḥ samidho matāḥ |
dhūpaṃ guggululodhrasya sarjja cola dalaṃ param ||054:011||
[sa phalāśami ka; kuśārkāḥ ka ga; kuṃdura ka]
śrīveṣṭakaṃ kuṣṭhañca vṛkṣādi guggulaṃ tathā |
guḍaudanaṃ raverdeyaṃ pāyasaṃ haviṣānvitam ||054:012||
[grā ka grī ga; haviṣātvita ka]
dadhyodanaṃ budhe deyaṃ gurau kṣīraudanaṃ tathā |
ghṛtānnaṃ tilamāsānnaṃ māsaṃ citraudanaṃ tathā ||054:013||
gāṃ suraktā ravau dadyācchaṅgī some vṛṣaṃ kuje |
kāñcanaṃ vastramaśvañca gāṃ sukṛṣṇāmajāyamasama ||054:014||
[suvarṇāṃ ka ga; dradyāchaṃsvaṃ ka; sudṛṣṭā ka ga]
dakṣiṇāṃ gandha puṣpādiṃ svaṃ svaṃ varṇaṃ pradāpayet |
homa grahādi pūjāyai śatamaṣṭādhikaṃ pi vā ||054:015||
aṣṭāviṃśāṣṭa homantu yathā prāptirvidhīyate |
lakṣahomaṃ prakarttavyaṃ sarvva pīḍā nivāraṇma ||054:016||
gāyatryā grahamantraiśca kuṣmāṇḍī jātavedasaiḥ |
aindra vāruṇaścāgnaiśca vāyu yāmasa vaiṣṇavaiḥ ||054:017||
[vī ka ga]
homaṃ śatasahasrantu aṣṭautkṛṣṭaṃ vidhīyate |
sarvva pīḍā vināśāya koṭi homaṃ śubhāvaham ||054:018||
[guḍa ka ga]
yava vrīhi ghṛtaṃ kṣīraṃ tilākaṅgu praśāntikaṃ |
paṅkajośīra vilvāmra dalaṃ home prakīrttitam ||054:019||
[kṣīraṃ tilāḥ kuṃgu ka śāṃtikāṃ ka; prakīrttitāḥ ka]
sarvva śāstrārthaṃ kuśalai rgrahamātṛ prapūjakaiḥ |
homaṃ kāryya sadā vipra sarvva śānti pradāyakaiḥ ||054:020||
graha kṛtyopasargādi ṛá¹tumāsa samāḥ śubhāḥ |
yakṣarakṣaḥ kṛtā pīḍā lakṣahomāt praśāmyati ||054:021||
[vṛtā ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe mātṛ grahalakṣahomavidhirnāma catuḥpañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye'bhyudaye mātṛgṛhalakṣahomavidhi ka ga]
%%%%

%%% Chapter 055

pañcapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ
śaunaka uvāca |

sarvva lokopakārāya saṃkṣepānna tu vistarāt |
utpāta śamanī śāntiṃ śrotumicchāmi tattavataḥ ||055:001||
manuruvāca |

apacāreṇa lokānāmupasargaṃ mahātmanām |
aparavatā vināśāya sṛjante devatā mune ||055:002||
[kṛtātmanāṃ ka ga]
utpātān vividhākārāṃstridhāvasthānupasthitān |
divyāntarīkṣān bhaumāṃśca yathāvattān nibodhata ||055:003||
[upasthitān ka ga]
sa prācīndiśamanvāvarttate |
||055:004:P1||
atha yadāsya maṇi maṇika kumbha sthālī daraṇāmāyāso rājakula vivādo vā yānacchatra śayyāsanāvasatho dhvajagṛhaikadeśaḥ prabhajyate |
||055:004:P2||
[vivāho ka ga]
gajavāji
mukhyā pramriyante hastinī vā mādyati ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvvāṇi indra daivatyānyadbhutāni prāyaścittāni bhavanti| ||055:004:P3||
indraṃ viśvā avīvṛṣamiti sthālī pākaṃ
[adhi ka ga]
kṛtvāpañcabhirājyāhutiḥ juhoti |
||055:004:P4||
[hutvā ka ga]
indrāya svāhā |
||055:004:P5||
śacī pataye svāhā |
||055:004:P6||
vajrapāṇaye
svāhā |
||055:004:P7||
īśvarāya svāhā |
||055:004:P8||
sarvva pāpapraśamanāya svāheti |
||055:004:P9||
vyāhṛtīśca pṛthak kṛtvā ||055:004:P10||
sa dakṣiṇāṃ diśamanvā varttate |
||055:005:P1||
atha yadāsya śarīre cāviṣṭāni bhavanti vyādhayo vāneka vidhāḥ |
||055:005:P2||
[vāniṣṭā ka]
svapnamasvapanāti bhojanamabhojanamatinidrā svālasyaṃ gṛhadvāreṇa vā sarpo'pagacchate
[gacchrati ka]
kapotaḥ praviśati |
||055:005:P2||
strī śarīre vārohati |
||055:005:P3||
[vāruhati ka ga]
kṛṣṇa strī darśan mādeśyam ityevamādīni
[mādeśa ka ga]
tānyetāni sarvvāṇi yama devatānyadbhutāni prāyaścittāni bhavanti |
||055:005:P4||
nāke suparṇamiti(FN)
[pustake nāsti ka]
sthālī pākaṃ kṛtvā pañcabhirjuhuyāt |
||055:005:P5||
[ājyāhutibhi ga]
yamāya svāhā |
||055:005:P6||
pretādhipataye svāhā |
||055:005:P7||
daṇḍapāṇaye svāhā |
||055:005:P8||
īśvarāya svāhā |
||055:005:P9||
sarvva pāpa praśamanāya svāheti |
||055:005:P10||
sarvvatrapraṇavādi svāhāntatā vyāhṛtīśca pṛthak kṛtvā ||055:005:P11||
sapratīcīṃ diśamanvāvarttate |
||055:006:P1||
atha yadāsya kṣetre gṛha saṃstheṣu dhānyeṣvībhaya āraṇye paśu mṛgāścā rauhanti |
||055:006:P2||
ākhu pataṅga paipīlikā śāśaka bhaumaka sūkṣmaka śalabha ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvvāṇi varuṇa devatānyadbhutāni prāyaścittāni
bhavanti |
||055:006:P3||
varuṇaṃ vā viśādaṇḍamiti sthālī pākaṃ hutvā pañcabhirjuhuyāt |
||055:006:P4||
varuṇāya svāhā |
||055:006:P5||
apāmpataye svāhā |
||055:006:P6||
pāśapāṇaye svāhā |
||055:006:P7||
sarvvapāpaśamanāya svāhā |
||055:006:P8||
īśvarāya svāheti |
||055:006:P9||
vyāhṛtibhiśca pṛthak kṛtvā ||055:006:P10||
sa pratyudīcīṃ diśamanvā varttate |
||055:007:P1||
[sa yadi udiyam ga]
atha yadāsya maṇi kanaka rajata vastra vajra vaidūryya maṇika viyogā bhavanti |
||055:007:P2||
ārambhakāṇi ca vipadyante |
||055:007:P3||
mitrāṇi vā virajyante |
||055:007:P4||
veśmani avāvūni vā jāyante |
||055:007:P5||
valmīkāścoddhṛyante |
||055:007:P6||
[vālmīkā kodhriyaṃte ka ga]
śuṣka vṛkṣāḥ prarohanti |
||055:007:P7||
tailaṃ tyajanti |
||055:007:P8||
[svidyaṃte ka ga]
madhūni vā pīyante |
||055:007:P9||
rātrāvindradhanu draṣṭvā śvetāśvetañcavāyasaṃ |
||055:007:P10||
[divāścetaṃ ka ga]
śmaśāne dhūmo jāyate |
||055:007:P11||
aśvatarī vā garbhaṃ gṛhnāti ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvvāṇi vaiśravaṇa devatānyatyadbhutāni prāyaścittāni bhavanti |
||055:007:P12||
[garddhamam ga]
ādityaṃ devamiti sthālīpākaṃ kṛtvā pañcabhirājyāhutibhiḥ juhuyāt |
||055:007:P13||
vaiśravaṇāya svāhā |
yajñādhipataye svāhā |
hiraṇya pāṇaye svāhā |
||055:007:P14||
[arccidy hāṇaye svāhā ka ga]
īśvarāya svāhā |
||055:007:P15||
sarvvapāpa śamanāya svāheti |
||055:007:P16||
vyāhṛtibhiśca pṛthak hutvā ||055:007:P17||
sa pṛthivīmanvā varttaṃte |
||055:008:P1||
atha yadāsya pṛthivī sphuṭati |
||055:008:P2||
kūjati, kampati, ghūmāyati akasmāt salilamudgirati |
||055:008:P3||
akāle ca vṛkṣāḥ puṣpaphalāni vā varttante |
||055:008:P4||
ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvvāṇi agnidaivatyāni adbhutāni prāyaścittāni bhavanni |
||055:008:P5||
agniṃ hutamiti sthālī kṛtvā pañcabhirājyāhutibhiḥ abhijuhoti |
||055:008:P6||
agnaye svāhā |
||055:008:P7||
arcciṣpataye svāhā |
||055:008:P8||
īśvarāya svāhā |
||055:008:P9||
sarvvapāpa śamanāya svāheti |
||055:008:P10||
vyāhṛtibhiśca pṛthak hutvā ||055:008:P11||
so'ntarīkṣamanvā varttate |
||055:009:P1||
atha yadāsyāntarā varṣāṇi colkāḥ patanti |
||055:009:P2||
[tārā varṣāṇi ka ga]
nipatanti, ghūmāyanti, diśo dahyanti |
||055:009:P3||
ketavaścottiṣṭhante |
||055:009:P4||
gavāṃ śṛṅgeṣu rudhiraṃ sravanti |
||055:009:P5||
atyaryaṃ himānyutpatanti |
||055:009:P6||
ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvvāṇi somadaivatānyadbhutāni prāyaścittāni bhavanti |
||055:009:P7||
somaṃ rājānamiti sthālīpākaṃ kṛtvā pañcabhirājyāhutibhi rabhijuhoti pṛthak pṛthak |
||055:009:P8||
somāya svāhā |
||055:009:P9||
nakṣatrādhipataye svāhā |
||055:009:P10||
sīrapāṇaye svāhā |
||055:009:P11||
īśvarāya svāhā |
||055:009:P12||
sarvvapāpa śamanāya svāheti |
||055:009:P13||
vyāhṛtibhiśca pṛthaka kṛtvā ||055:009:P14||
sa diva manvāvarttate |
||055:010:P1||
atha yadāsya vidhātā dhāryate |
||055:010:P2||
[dhāryate ga]
vātā vāyante |
||055:010:P3||
abhreṣu karakāṇi dṛśyante kharakarabhakaṅkolūka gṛghraśyena bhāsa vāyasa kapota gomāyusaṃsthānyupala pāṃśu māṃsa paśvasthi rudhira varṣāṇi prarkttante |
||055:010:P4||
ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvāṇi vāyudaivatyānyadbhutāni prāyaścittāni bhavanti |
||055:010:P5||
idaṃ viṣṇu rvicakrama iti sthālīpākaṃ kṛtvā pañcabhirājyā hutibhirabhijuhoti |
||055:010:P6||
viṣṇave svāhā |
||055:010:P7||
sarvvādhipataye svāhā |
||055:010:P8||
[sarvadevādhipataye svāhā ga]
cakrapāṇaye svāhā |
||055:010:P9||
īśvarāya svāhā |
||055:010:P10||
sarvvapāpa śamanāya svāheti vyāhṛtibhiśca pṛthak pṛthak ||055:010:P11||
[hutvā pṛthak ka ga]
bhūmikampo diśāṃ dāho grahayuddhaśca jāyate |
gagane dṛśyate keturādityaścaiva kampate ||055:011||
ādityājjāyate cchidraṃ kṛṣṇavarṇo hi jāyate |
viparītānnadīṃścaiva rudhirañca pravāhayet ||055:012||
śilā vā plavate yatra ravirmadhye yadā kvacit |
gaganāt śrūyate divyaṃ nirghātaścaiva jāyate ||055:013||
atyadbhutaṃ mahāghoraṃ sṛṣṭi saṃhāra kārakam |
rājyopasaṃharañcaiva rājānāṃ kṣayakārakam ||055:014||
ityevamādīni tānyetāni sarvvāṇayadbhutāni proyaścittāni bhavanti |
gṛhe gṛhe bhavecchāntiḥ mātṛṇāṃ pūjanaṃ baliḥ |
dānaṃ rudraṃ japennityaṃ bhāskarejyā grahārccanam ||055:015||
lakṣahomaṃ mahāhomaṃ koṭihomaṃ puroditam |
gomū hiraṇya vastrānna tiladānaṃ śubhāvaham ||055:016||
pāyasaṃ dadhikṣīrājyaṃ deyaṃ sarvveṣu bhojanam |
evaṃ prajāyate śāntistato dravyāṇi āharet ||055:017||
tāni toyena prokṣīyodupahārāṇi yāni tu |
||055:018:P1||
atha pūrvvāhṇe ca yathā vadājye cāhutiṃ hutvā dūrvvā payodadhisarpiḥ sarṣapān phalavatī apāmārga tila brīhi-yava-samidhānyetānyāhared vā snātaḥ prayataḥ śuciḥ śucivāsāḥ sthaṇḍilamupalipya nitya tantreṇodana-kṛṣara-yavāgū-saktu-pāyasaṃ-dadhimadhu dhṛtāktāḥ pṛthak ca varaḥ sarvveṣāṃ vā pāyasaṃ tataḥ agnimupasamādhāya juhuyāt yathāvaditi ||055:018:P2||
[prātarāhutibh ka ga; dūrvā uprīnimi ga]
iti śrī devīpuruṇe sārvvadaivikī sarvvotpāta śāntirnāma pañcapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ
[mahāmyudayādi sārvadaivikī sarvotpāta śāṃtiḥ samāpta ga]
%%%%

%%% Chapter 056


ṣaṭ pañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ
indraṃ viśvā avāvṛṣaṃ samudravya saṃśiraḥ |
rathītamaṃ rathīnāṃ vā rājānāṃ śatapatiṃ patim ||056:001||
[saṃgiraḥ ka ga; idraṃ aścāvaghī vṛdhase atravya visaṃgiraḥ |
sathīta saṃjñaṃ rathānāṃ vājīnāṃ satāpatiṃ ka ga ]
nāke suparṇaṃmupatyāṃta havā revanto abhya ca kṣata tvā |
hiraṇyākṣaṃ varuṇasya dūtaṃ yamasya bhūraṇyaṃ yonau śakunam ||056:002||
[avanaṃto ka; nyavakratatvā ka; hiraṇyakṣaṃ ka; bhūtaṃ ka; yamasya yonau śakanaṃturaṇyaṃka ]
varuṇaṃ vodhipādamṛcāmindraṃ havāmahe |
parivrajecca vāhvorjjaṃgandhāso svarṇavaṃ naram ||056:003||
[varuṇaṃ vevisāda mṛcā mitraṃ śakalaṃ muraṇa ka ga; vārddhorjagaṃdhīt sāsvannaraṃ ka ga]
ādityaṃ devaṃ savitā manyoḥ kavi kratumarccāmi |
satyasavaṃ(FN) ratna dhāmabhi priyamatitaraṃ kavim ||056:004||
[ālyaṃ ka; savitā rāmāṇyaṃkāra ka; paktī rna santi ka ga pustake]
ūrdh rva yasyā matibhā ādityutsavo maṇi |
hiraṇyapāṇi tvamimīte sukratuḥ kṛpāpayaḥ ||056:005||
agniṃ dūtaṃ vṛṇīmahe hotāraṃ viśva vetasam |
asya yajñasya sukṛtam ||056:006||
somaṃ rājānaṃ bhavate agnimanvārabhāmahe |
ādityaṃ viṣṇuṃ sūryyaṃ brāhmaṇañca vṛhaspatim ||056:007||
||somaṃ rājaṃ varuṇaṃ yamaṃ manutva bhiraṅgirami siṃcāmi ka ga]
idaṃviṣṇu rvicakrame tredhā nidadhe padam |
samūḍhamasya pāṃśūle ||056:008||
vāta āvāta bheṣajaṃ śantu mayā ttanā kude |
praṇatāyuṃṣi tāriṣat ||056:009||
[bheṣajaṃ saṃbhu mayā tunā kṛde praṇa āyuṃsitārimat ka ga]
gaurīrmimāya salilāni takṣatyekapadī sā catuṣpadī ||056:010||
[gaurīrmimaye salilāni ka ga]
aṣṭāpadī nava padīṃ bhūmīṃ sahasrākṣaṃ vā parame vyoman ||056:011||
kāṇḍāt kāṇḍāt prarohantī puruṣaḥ puruṣaḥ pari |
dadhāno dūrvve pratanu sahasreṇa śatena ceti ||056:012||
[paribhāno ka ga]



yathaiva yajñastathaiva bandhūryāsi tanosi pratanosi athainamabhivādya vācayati ||056:013||
[vedya ka ga]
dhruvosi dhruvo'yaṃ yajamāno .asminnāyatane prajayā bhūyāsamiti ||056:014||
[bhūyāditi ka ga]
paśubhiriti caivaṃ yaṃ kāmaṃ kāmayate so'smai kāmaḥ samṛddhyate ||056:015||
[sosmikasyaḥ ka]
yo jānāti na jīyate hanti śatrumabhidya sa eva bhaved vasu sahasrajit ||056:016||
[yojinātina ka ga]
ihaiva staṃ mā viyauṣṭaṃ dīrghamāyu vyasrutam |
krīḍantau purtrairnaṃptṛbhiḥ modamānau ca sve gṛhe ||056:017||
punaḥ patnī agnivadāyuṣā saha varccasā |
dīrghāyu rāsyāpaḥ patibhi rjīvāti śaradaḥ śatam ||056:018||
sthālīpākādikarma vidhirucyate |
parisamūhya-upalipya-ullikhya-uddhṛtya-abhyukṣya-agnimupasamādhāya-dakṣiṇato brahmāsanamāstīrya-praṇāya-paristīrya-ātmavadāsādya-pavitrīkṛtvā-prokṣanī-saṃskṛtya-ātmavat prokṣaya-nirupādhamadhistutya-paryagnikuryāt ||056:019||
sruvaṃ pratāpya samuhya abhyukṣya punaḥ pratāpya nidadhyāt saṃttāpyotpūya avekṣya prokṣaṇī pūrvavadupayamanān kuśānādāya samidho'bhyādhāya paryukṣya juhuyāt |
eṣa eva vidhiryatra kvaciddhaumaḥ ||056:020||
parisamūhanādibhirdevatā pratibhāgamaṃtrāśca vyākhyāsyāmaḥ ||056:021||
yaddevo devahelanamiti parisamūhanam |
mānastoketyupalepanam |
tvāṃ vṛtre jindra satpatim ityullikhya |
brajaṃ gacchetyudvṛtya |
devasya tveti abhyukṣya |
agnimṛtveti agnimupasamādhāya |
samidhāgni dravyasya ceti samidādhānaṃ dadhāt ||056:022||
mayi gṛhṇāmīti agrahastaṃ kṛtvā hiraṇyakarbha iti dakṣiṇato brahmā |
āpo hiṣṭheti ca uttarataḥ praṇītā |
kayānaścitrā iti praṇītya paritaḥ paristaraṇam |
pavitrastho vaiṣṇavya iti pavitrachedanī |
iṣetvetyājyanirupaṇam ||056:023||
trātāramiti sruvaṃ pratāpya |
aniśitoṣi prakṛtyābhi sammārjanam |
pratyuṣṭaṃ rakṣeti punaḥ pratapanam ||056:024||


saviturvaḥ prasava tat punāmi ityutpavanam |
tadevāgnirityarccanam |
ṣūrasīti paryukṣaṇam ||056:025||
evaṃ lakṣaṇa saṃyuktaṃ sarvaṃhomeṣu yājñikam |
vidhānaṃ vihitaṃ tatra brahmaṇāmita tejasā ||056:026||
anyathā ye prakurvanti sūtramāśritya kevalam |
nirvāsāstatra gacchanti sarve devā na saṃśayaḥ ||056:027||
paddevā devahelanaṃ devāsaśca kumārayam |
agnirmatiḥ syādena goviśvān muñca tvaṃhasaḥ ||056:028||
iti parisamūhanamantraḥ |
