%%% Chapter 057

saptapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

dhenuṃ tilamayīmāghyāṃ dadayād puruṣaścottarāyaṇe |
sarva kāmānavāpnoti jyaiṣṭhe jalamayīṃ dadet ||057:001||
puṣye ghṛtamayīṃ dadyācchreṣṭhāhi vidhinā mune |
ihitāmÌllabhate lokān sthāneṣu vividheṣu ca ||057:002||
śaunaka uvāca |

prabhavādi tvayā tāta devyāḥ ṣaṣṭirudāhṛtā |
vistarāt pūjanaṃ tāsāṃ kālāntaraphalapradam ||057:003||
saṃkṣepādekakāyasthāṃ devīmātṛgrahānvitāḥ |
tridiva lokapālena saṃyuktāḥ sarvvakāmadāḥ ||057:004||
[kāmasthā ga]
ṣaṣṭivarṣakṛtā pūjā māsaikena prayacchati |
tathā kathaya me sarvvaṃ sarvvalokasukhāvaham ||057:005||
[samaike na ga]
manuruvāca |

hema rājatatāmā vā kāṣṭhādyā mṛnmayāpi vā |
citrā vā ratnajā cāpi kāryyā devī sulakṣaṇā ||057:006||
[hematāmragayīṃ vāpi ka ga]
śubhadravyabhavā cānyā siṃha padmagrahānvitā |
mātaro bhaya saṃyuktā carccitā mukuṭānvitā ||057:007||
[carcikāṃ ka ga]
gaṇeśaskanda sampannā lokapālasamanvitā |
brahmeśaviṣṇu śirasā nīlotpalakarā varā ||057:008||
khaḍga kheṭakadhārī ca śaraccandrakarāpi vā |
candra sūryyakarā kāryyā yāvat ṣaṣṭi kṛtādhikā ||057:009||
[yāvacchāntiḥ kṛtādhikā ka]
dvibhujāṃ bhāvarūpeṇa kārayed bhujakalpanām |
evaṃ kṛtvā śubhāṃ devīṃ indramaṇi gṛhe yajet ||057:010||
[rudramāte grahe yajet ka ga]
dvivaddhā śatamaṣṭau ca śaradaṇḍamathāpi vā |
saumyāsye saumyasaṃsthānāṃ yaścākyantaijase gṛham ||057:011||
[dvivṛdhyā śata yaṣṭau karadaṃḍaṃ ka ga; saukhya saṃsthānāṃ kha]
tasya pūrve samaṃ kuṇḍaṃ kāryyamaindraṃ sukhāvaham |
pūrvvāsyaṃ paścimāsyaṃ vā yatra vā ramate manaḥ ||057:012||




tataḥ pūjā japaṃ homaṃ mantrastotra prakīrtanam |
yātrā maṇḍalapūjā ca pustakādeśca pāṭhanam ||057:013||
loka yātrā ratha yātrā kāryaṃ homaṃ dine dine |
ghṛt-kṣīra-madhu-vrīhi-tila-bilva-dalādikam ||057:014||
homaṃ kāryyaṃ sugandhaiśca dhūpaiḥ puṣpai sadārccanam |
||057:015ab||
karpūrā gurulepādi vitānadhvaja cāmaram |
||057:015cd||
deyaṃ sarvārtha siddhyarthaṃ sarvvapāpa praṇāśanam ||057:015ef||
brahmovāca |

meṣādāramya devīnāṃ pūjā kāryyā sadā mune |
yāvat saṃvatsaraṃ pūrṇaṃ sarvvakāmaphalārthibhiḥ ||057:016||
dilīpena yathā pūrvaṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā kramāgatām |
surottame mahākalpe bhāgyaṛddhisvakāminā ||057:017||
tathā ca ambarīṣeṇa anyaiśca nṛpasattamaiḥ |
kṛtā śivārcane buddhistithikālakramāgatāḥ ||057:018||
yo vibhājya pūrā hyekaḥ kālavyāpī maheśvaraḥ |
sarvadevatanu rbhūtvā prayacchati phalaṃ nṛṇām ||057:019||
[kālarūpī ka ga]
yajñamājyaṃ tathā pūpaṃ vedavaktra sa manvitaḥ |
datvā phalaṃ dvijātiṣu pūtaiḥ sarvveṣu dharmmiṣu ||057:020||
[vedoktaṅkāraktamānvitaḥ kha]
sarvāṃ ca maṅlāṃ rūpāṃ kṛtvā cāṣṭaśatāṃ tanum ||057:021||
punāti sarvalokān sa kriyābhāvāṅgamīśvaraḥ |
sarvveṣu cāgatā devī sarvvadevai rabhiṣṭutā ||057:022||
vaiṣṇavīṃ tanu māsthāya sthitā sā vyavahārataḥ |
varṇāśramāgatān dharmān yathākālaṃ kramāgatān ||057:023||
[tattvaṃ ga]
tathā tathā sureśāna prayacchati nṛṇāṃ sadā |
rajastomāṃ vijānīyāt sṛṣṭihetuṃ sthitau punaḥ ||057:024||
[rajasthormā ka]
viṣṇuḥ sattvaṃ gato nāśe kālaḥ satatamāśritaḥ |
trayāṇāṃ samatāṃ vatsa mahādevaḥ sadāśivaḥ ||057:025||
[śatasamāśritaḥ ka]
sa īśaḥ sarvvadevānāṃ nānā bhetagataḥ punaḥ |
kriyākhyā jñāna bhedena śatadhātha sahasraśaḥ ||057:026||
bhedo na śakyate vaktuṃ lokeṣu svalpavuddhiṣu |
evaṃ viditvā bhinnecchā iṣṭāpūrttagataṃ vibhum ||057:027||




pūjanīyaṃ muniśreṣṭha sarvvakāmeśvareśvaram |
ekānaika vibhāgasthaṃ sarvvaśāstre kriyāyutam ||057:028||
[evaṃ naika ka ga; kriyātanum ka ga]
kāmarūpī mahādevaṃ kāmadaṃ bhavate mṛṇām |
||057:029ab||
surāsura manuṣyāṇāṃ yakṣarakṣoragādiṣu |
||057:029cd||
phalaṃ prayacchati ceṣṭaṃ sarvvavuddhiḥ prabhāvajam ||057:029ef||
karmmayajñastapopajñaḥ svādhyāyaṃ ca śāntidam |
prayacchati phalaṃ yasmāt paṃcadhā parameśvaraḥ ||057:030||
[svādhyāyadhyāna śāntidaṃ ka]
tasmāt tasya sadā caryyā karttavyā hitamicchatā |
hitantu ceṣṭaṃ saṃsiddhi rniravadyaṃ sukhaṃ yataḥ ||057:031||
sarvvadvandva vinirmmukto dhyānayogaṃ sadābhyaseta |
||057:032ab||
[dhanayogaṃ samācaren ga ka]
tacca bhakti kramāt prāpyaṃ karmayogāccānyathā |
||057:032cd||
karmma pūjā japo homaṃ devārcāsthāpanādikam ||057:032ef||
iti śrī devī purāṇe trailokyābhyudaye pāde pūjā praśaṃsā nāma saptapaṃcāśo'dhyāyaḥ
[trailokyābhyudaye pūjāpraśaṃsā ga ka]

