%%% Chapter 058
aṣṭapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |

vṛhaspatiruvāca |

kathaṃ sa rājāṃ bhāgyantu sarvvalokādhipo vibhuḥ |
kathañca divyatāṃ yāyād viṣṇu sāyujyatāṃ vibho ||058:001||

sarvvadaiveśvarastasya kathaṃ tuṣṭa umāpatiḥ |
etat kautuhalaṃ deva śrotumicchāmi tatvataḥ ||058:002||

[tuṣṭamumāpatiḥ kha]
brahmovāca |

kalpe surottame pūrvvaṃ kailāse parvvatottame |
divyena tapasā yuktaṃ bhāgyarkṣe toṣitaṃ śivam ||058:003||
tena varaprasādena sarvvalokeśvarā dvija |
bhāgyo hyāsīnmahāvāho sarvva devairabhiṣṭutaḥ ||058:004||
[lokeśvarā dvijā kha]
medhādiguṇa saṃyuktaḥ kāmakrodhādivarjjitaḥ |
sāṃvatsarastathāmātyaḥ purodhā bhiṣajānvitaḥ ||058:005||
sāṃvatsaro'tha tatrajña amātya sarvva śāstravit |
purodhā vedapaurāṇa daṃḍyātharvaśāstravit ||058:006||
daśa yajña kriyā devā hitakṛdahita'nyathā |
bhiṣajo'ṣṭāṅga vedāṅgo laghuhasto jitendriyaḥ ||058:007||
[vedajño ga]
anuraktastathā bhakto dvandvādvandvaguṇānvitaḥ |
koṣaṃ ratnādi sampannaṃ subhakta bhogasaṃyutam ||058:008||
bhāryā iṣṭā hitā nityaṃ puraṃ harmyasamākulam |
aśvebhavāhanaṃ puṣṭaṃ tasya cāsīd dvijottamaḥ ||058:009||
evaṃ sarvva guṇopetaṃ purodhānumate sthitaḥ |
sāṃvatsarodite kāle vijayāya samārabhet ||058:010||
[sāmvatsaro yathākāle ga]
tataḥ kālena mahatā śaṅkarasya nṛpottamaḥ |
tapaścaranmahātejā putrāyuta samāvṛtaḥ ||058:011||
prāpte saṃvatsare puṇye yuge'pitu nirāmaye |
bhāgyarkṣa dvādaśī nāma sarvvabhāgyapradāyikā ||058:012||
[yāgāni tu kha]
tatra kṛtvā harerarccāṃ yaṣṭā padme yathāvidhi |
sarvva lakṣaṇa sampannā śreṣṭhamṛkṣabhavā mune ||058:013||
śakaṃrārddhahariṃ puṃsaḥ umeśaṃ sthāpayed balāt |
||058:014ab||
bhaktyā sarvvopahāreṇa dvādaśāre tu maṇḍale |
||058:014cd||
ādyena cakrarājena pūjitaṃ madhusūdanam ||058:014ef||
tutoṣa tasya nṛpatestena bhāgyatvamāpnuyāt |
tuṣṭena devadevena varaṃ dattaṃ dvijottamam ||058:015||
aniruddhastu tvaṃ vatsa mama tulyo bhaviṣyasi |
śaṃkhacakrāsi pāṇistvaṃ sarvvakāmāmÌllabhiṣyasi ||058:016||
kṛtvā divyāyutaṃ rājyaṃ mama sāyujyamāpyasi |
bhāgyasyaikādaśārkṣaṃ ntu tena cānyāpi yā tithiḥ ||058:017||
tasmin saṃpūjitā devāḥ sarvvakāmapradāyakāḥ |
prabhavādi same śreṣṭhe yuge caiva manorame ||058:018||
bhāgyākhyā dvādaśī tāta aṣṭamyāṃ vā tadarccanam |
yāgamaṇḍala pūjārccā harimuddiśya kārayet ||058:019||
ācāryyāya pradātavyaṃ hemagobhūtilādikam |
dakṣiṇā ātmasāreṇa punāti narakārṇavāt ||058:020||
yugaṃ bhāgyaprabhāveṇa prayacchati phalaṃ hariḥ |
yathā kāle ca kṣetre ca ekāpi karṇikā matā ||058:021||
prayāti śatadhā vṛddhiṃ yathā cādye yuge dvijaḥ |
yathā māghe tathā pauṣye vāsare'pi dvijottama ||058:022||
tulyaṃ puṇyaṃ vijānīyād dvādaśyāmaṣṭamīṣu ca |
tuṣyate deva deveśaḥ śaśāṅkāṅkita śekharaḥ ||058:023||
[śaraṃ kokataśekharaḥ ga]
putrāyu-rājya-saubhāgyaṃ prayacchati janārdanaḥ |
yaḥ punarmāghamāsena karoti harirarccanam ||058:024||
padme sulakṣaṇopete varṇakairupaśobhite |
tasya tuṣyati deveśaścakrapāṇi rjanārddanaḥ ||058:025||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe bhāgyadvādaśī nāmāṣṭapañcāśo'dhyāyaḥ |
