brahmovāca |

sarvvakāma prasidhyartha pūjanīyā yathā śivā |
tathā te kathayiṣyāmi śṛṇu vatsa samāsataḥ ||059:001||
caitrādau yā samākhyātā pūjā sarvvārtha sādhanī |
tasyā bhedān pravakṣyāmi iṣṭāpūrti prasiddhaye ||059:002||
[tasya bhedāna ka ga]
caitrāṃ citrakṣaṇāṃ pūjā kṛtvā tvaṣṭā phalaṃ labheta |
tṛtīyāyāntu vaiśākhe rohirṇyakṣe prapūjayet ||059:003||
[ga pustake ślokadvayaṃ nāsti]
udakumbha pradānena brahmaloke mahīyate |
indrāgni daivate mṛdo paurṇamāsyāṃ tathaiva ca ||059:004||
pūjāṃ kṛtvā bhaved brahman vigatāgho narottamaḥ |
agnau parigrahaḥ kāryyo dānaṃ deyaṃ dvijātiṣu ||059:005||
trayāṇāmekamādāya agniṃ devīṃ prapūjayet |
agnihotrī bhavet pūtaḥ śeṣaṃ varṇākitaṃ phalam ||059:006||
mūlarkṣe paśupātena jyeṣṭhāṃ devīṃ prapūjayet |
sarvvakāmānavāpnoti bhāvaśuddhena karmmaṇā ||059:007||
āṣāḍhe māsi yo devīmāṣāḍharkṣe prapūjayet |
sarvvān kāmānavāpnoti devī lokaṃ ca gacchati ||059:008||
[padyamidaṃ ga pustake nāsti ka pustake'pi nāsti]
śrāvaṇe pūjayed devīṃ pratipadyāditaḥ kramāt |
brahmamūrtigatā ṛá¹kṣe pauṣye bhaujaṅgame'pivā ||059:009||
[dhāmāt ka]
athavā suvidhānena pavitrārohaṇaṃ bhavet |
brahmāgnyumā gaṇeśasya nāgaskandhatanusthitā ||059:010||
ravimātara rūpā tu maṅgalāyanarūpagā |
vṛṣaviṣṇu samākārā kāmarudra samākṛtī ||059:011||
śakrarūpā prayaṣṭavyā devyā gandha sragādibhiḥ |
prathame cāśrame pūjā gṛhya karma vratādi ca ||059:012||
kṛtvā kāmānavāpnoti vigatāgho munīśvaraḥ |
prauṣṭhe paurṇāsu karttavyā pūjā jāgaraṇaṃ niśi ||059:013||
mahotsavavidhānena sautrāmaṇiphalaṃ labhet |
aṣṭamyāṃ rohiṇīṃ ṛkṣe sopavāsantu pūjayet ||059:014||
viṣṇulokamavāpnoti sarvvakāma samṛddhidam |
tatraiva kārayed devīṃ pitṛrūpāṃ mahodayām ||059:015||
[pitṛrūpīṃ ga]
kanyāsthe ca ravau vatsa pūjanīyā yathāvidhi |
bhaujaṅgīṃ tithimāśritya yāvaccandrārkasaṃgamam ||059:016||
[āsādya ka ga]
ṛkṣe piṇḍa pradānantu jyeṣṭha putrīṃ vivarjjayet |
āhaveṣu vipannānāṃ jalāgni rbhṛgupātiṣu ||059:017||
[jayāgni mṛgupātriṣu ka ga]
caturdaśyāṃ bhavet pūjā amāvasyāntu kāmikī |
kanyāsthe tu ravau dive śuklāṣṭamyāṃ prapūjayet ||059:018||
sopavāso niśārddhe tu mahāvibhavavistaraiḥ |
pūjāṃ samārabhed devyā brahmarkṣe varuṇo'pi vā ||059:019||
[rakṣarkṣe ka ga]
paśughātaḥ prakarttavyo garalājavadhastathā |
valikṣepastu rakṣāṇāṃ kāryyaḥ sarvveṣāṃ śāntaye ||059:020||
rathayātrā prakarttavyā yā purā saṃprakīrttitā |
mahotsavaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ tasmin devī prapūjayet ||059:021||
tulāsthe dīpadānena pūjā kāryyā mahātmanā |
dīpavṛkṣāḥ prakarttavyā dīpa cakrāstathāparā ||059:022||
[mahāphalā ga]
dīpayātrā prakarttavyā caturddaśyāṃ kuhūṣu ca |
sinī vālī stathā vatsa tadā kāryyaṃ mahāphalam ||059:023||
[śinīvālī ga]
sarvvaśeṣe prakarttavyaṃ balipūjā homotsavam |
devatānāṃ samutthānaṃ kāryyaṃ pauṣṇāsu buddhimān ||059:024||
[mahautsavam ga]
nairājanaṃ prakarttavyaṃ nṛnāgaturagādiṣu |
kārttikyāṃ kārayet pūjāṃ yāgaṃ devīpriyaṃ sadā ||059:025||
brahmaviṣṇu śivādīnāṃ tatra pūjā mahāphalā |
gavāṃ sarga prakarttavyaṃ nīlaṃ vā vṛṣamutsṛjet ||059:026||
sarvva yajña phalaṃ brahman prāpnuyādavicārayan |
astrāṇāṃ pūjanaṃ tatra karttavyaṃ sarvvasiddhaye ||059:027||
mārge pūjā prakarttavyā ahirbughnekṣaṇā śubhā |
somārke kārayet pūjāṃ sarvvakāma phalapradām ||059:028||
puṣye puṣyāmiṣekantu karttavyaṃ pūjayejjayām |
caturthyāṃ śuklamāghasya mahāpūjā vidhīyate ||059:029||
māghyāṃ pūjā prakarttavyā devīṃ vai maṅgalāṃ yajet |
phālgune pūjayed devīṃ caṇḍiketi ca yā matā ||059:030||
mātarāṇāṃ viśeṣeṇa tatra pūjā vidhīyate |
evaṃ sarvva gatā devī sarvvadeva tanusthitā ||059:031||
pūjitā vidhinā vatsa sarvvakāmān prayacchati ||059:032||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe trailokyābhyudaye pāde pūjāpraśaṃsānāma ekonaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityabhyudayapāde kramapūjā ga]

%%%%
%%% Chapter 060
ṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

aśvamedha samaṃ puṇyaṃ vṛṣotsargādavāpyate |
revatyāñcāśvine māsi kārttikyāṃ kārttikasya vā ||060:001||
[nṛpotsārtat ga]
go vivāho'thavā kāryyo'māyāṃ vai phālgune'pi vā |
śivāyā maṅgalaṃ caitraṃ tṛtīyāyāṃ mahāphalam ||060:002||
[śivo vāṇagataṃ ka]
aśvatthoḍumvarīyāgaṃ vivāha vidhinā bhavet |
satoraṇaṃ bhavet tīrthe utsargaṃ gokule'pi vā ||060:003||
catasro vatsikā bhadrā dvau vā sambhavato'pi vā |
vatsaṃ sarvvāṅgasaṃpūrṇaṃ kanyā sā lohitā bhavet ||060:004||
[vatsikāmavet ga ka]
alaṅkṛtya yathā śobhā utsargaṃ kārayenmune |
vivāhameka vatsaikaṃ nīlena bhavate sadā ||060:005||
vṛṣeṇa aśvamedhasya yajñasya phaladāyakam |
jāyeran bahavaḥ putrā yadyeko'pi gayāṃ vrajet ||060:006||
yajedvā aśvamedhaṃ nīlaṃ vā vṛṣamutasṛjet |
lohito yastu varṇena śaṅkhavarṇa mukho vṛṣaḥ ||060:007||
[rohiṇeyastu ga ka; śaṃkhavarṇakhuro vṛṣaḥ ka ga]
lāṅgūlaśirasa ścaiva sa vai nīlavṛṣaḥ smṛtaḥ |
aṅkita sṛjyate pūrvva gāñcālaṅkṛtya sarvvataḥ ||060:008||
[oṃkita ka]
taptena vāmataścakraṃ yāmye śūlaṃ samālikhet |
dhātunā hemabhāvena āyasenātha vāṅkayet ||060:009||
[hiṃsabhāreṇa ka]
evaṃ kṛtvā avāpnoti phalaṃ vājimakhoditam |
yamuddiśya sṛjed vatsaṃ sa labhate'vicāraṇāt ||060:010||
yathā śivo ajā arccā pūjitā sarvvakāmadā |
evaṃ devatrayaṃ japtvā anantaṃ labhate phalam ||060:011||
[majā arccā ka]
maṅgalā vihitaṃ yacca godānajaṃ phalaṃ tathā |
sahasra kratavastena vṛṣotsargādavāpnuyāt ||060:012||
gandhāṣṭamī bhavenmārge gandharva phala dāyikā |
sahasra kratavastena vṛṣot sargādavāpnuyāt ||060:013||
[ka pustake paṃktirnāsti]
kṣīrāṣṭamī mahāpuṇyā candralokaphalapradā ||060:014||
dadhnā viṣṇupadaṃ yāti haviṣā ravimaṇḍale |
madhunā devatāḥ sarvvāḥ śivaṃ śālikṛtānnajaiḥ ||060:015||
brāhmaṃ nīvāra pūjābhi rmaṅgalā saṃprayacchati |
i haiva sarvvakāmāni pradadyāt sarvva maṅgalā ||060:016||
yathepsitāni lokānāṃ śivā pūrvena pūjitā |
prayacchati suraloke ceṣṭānyapi samantataḥ ||060:017||
[pūrtte na ka ga]
prapārāma taḍāgāni devatāyatanāni ca |
pūrttāni teṣvapi ceṣṭaṃ hemadānaṃ mahāmune ||060:018||
[kūpārāma ka ga]
upakalpitṣu bhāgeṣu yadi vidhnopajāyate |
tadā durgādiṣu kāryyā tithiṣu sarvvakāmadam ||060:019||
[homadānaṃ mahāmune ka ga; yugādiṣu ka ga]
vaiśākha śuklasya tu yā tṛtīyā navamyasau kārtika śukla pakṣe |
nabhasya māsasya tamisrapakṣe trayodaśī pañcadaśī ca māghe ||060:020||
uparāge candramase raveśca taṃ misro'ṣṭa kāyāmayana dvayaṃ ca |
pānīya mapyatra tilairvibhinnaṃ dadyāt pitṛbhyaḥ prayato manuṣyaḥ ||060:021||
[upalpabe ka ga]
śrāddhaṃ kṛtaṃ tena samāḥ sahasraṃ rahasyametat pitaro vadanti |
||060:022ab||
[śrītvam ga]
eteṣu kāleṣu ca dāna homamutsargadhātā yatneṣu dattam |
||060:022cd||
anantakalpaṃ sura siddhagītam vedeṣu ceṣṭaṃ munayo vadanti ||060:022ef||
athavā jīrṇa saṃskāra vidhiḥ puṇyo mahāmune |
devatādiṣu karttavyo mahābhoga phalepsubhiḥ ||060:023||
mūlādaṣṭaguṇa puṇyaṃ jīrṇasaṃskārake bhavet ||060:024||
tasmādanātha jīrṇeṣu kāryyaṃ saṃskaraṇaṃ mune |
svakīyaṃ parakīyaṃ vā yathāvibhava vistaraiḥ ||060:025||
svato vā parato vāpi yastu saṃskurute surān |
sa yāvaccandra sūryyau dyaustāvat kālaṃ sukhī bhavet ||060:026||
lokeṣu teṣu devānāṃ virata steṣu ṭṭaṣṭadhīḥ |
yathā gomedha yajñeṣu paśuromasamāḥ samāḥ ||060:027||
[virajaḥ ka ga]
vasate divi hṛṣṭātmā jīrṇa saṃskāra kārakaḥ |
anāthā vā sanāthā vā pūjanīyāḥ sadā surā ||060:028||
[vasatte viraje loke tathāreṇusamaḥ ka ga]
viśeṣeṇa tu ye pūrvvāste te cejyā satataṃ mune |
pṛthunā ceṣṭamānādau maināke umāśaṅkaram  ||060:029||
[yamaśaṃkaram ka]
yayātinā ca gomante śaṅkaraṃ hariṇā saha |
kailāse'rdhanārīśaṃ raghuṇā pūjitaṃ purā ||060:030||
[kumāṇīsāṃ kha]
dilīpena tathā rājye trimūrti kāmike'cale |
dakṣiṇāpi hi saṃprāptaṃ devīmiṣṭvā ihitaṃ phalam ||060:031||
anye'pi ṛá¹ṣayaḥ rsiddhiṃ gatāḥ pūrttena karmmaṇā ||060:032||
iti śrī devī purāṇe devyavatāre pūjāvidhirnāma ṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devyavatāre pūjāvidhi ka ga]

%%%%
%%% Chapter 061
ekaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

catrādau kārayet pūjāṃ mama vatsa yathāvidhi |
gandhadhūpārccanādānairmālābhirdamanodbhavaiḥ ||061:001||
sahomaṃ pūjayed devaṃ sarvvakāmānavāpnuyāt |
sarvvatīrthābhiṣekasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ ||061:002||
umāṃ śivaṃ hutāśañca dvitīyāyāntu pūjayet |
haviṣyaâmantraânaivedyaṃ deyaṃ gandhārccanaṃ purā ||061:003||
phalamāpnoti viprendra umayā yat prabhāṣitam |
tṛtīyāyāṃ yajeddevīṃ śaṃkareṇa samanvitām ||061:004||
[ulkāyāṃ yat prabhāṣitam ka ]
kuṅkumāgurâkarpūraâmaṇiâvastraâsragarccitām |
sugandha-puṣpa-dhūpaiśca damanena sumālitām ||061:005||
[sumālinī ga]
āndole dolayed vatsa śivomā tuṣyate sadā |
rātrau jāgaraṇaṃ kāryya prātardeyā tu dakṣiṇā ||061:006||
hemavastrānupātrāṇi tāmbūlāni srajāni ca |
saubhāgyāya sadā strībhiḥ kāryyaṃ putrasukhārthibhiḥ ||061:007||
[anuyātrāṇi vastrātrapātrāṇi ka ga]
gaṇeśe kārayet pūjāṃ laḍaḍukādibhirbhāvitaḥ |
caturthyāṃ vidhnanāśāya sarvvakāmaâsamṛddhaye ||061:008||
pañcamyāṃ pūjayennāgānanantādyān mahoragān |
kṣīrasarpistu naivedyaṃ deyaṃ sarvvarviṣāpaham ||061:009||
[anaṃtārdhyān ka ga]
ṣaṣṭhyāṃ skandasya karttavyā pūjā sarvvopahāriṇī |
ihaiva sukhasaubhāgyamante skandapuraṃ vrajet ||061:010||
bhāskarasya tu saptamyāṃ pūjāṃ damanakādibhiḥ |
kṛtvā prāpnoti bhogādīn vigatārirmahātapāḥ ||061:011||
mātarāṇāñca aṣṭamyāṃ pūjāṃ sarvvārtha gandhikīm |
kṛtavāṃllabhate vatsa siddhimiṣṭāṃ tu damanakaiḥ ||061:012||
[sarvānnagaṃdhakām ka]
navamyāṃ pūjayeddevīṃ mahāmahiṣaâmardinīma |
kuṅkumā-guru-karpūra-dhūpānna-dhvaja-darpaṇaiḥ ||061:013||
damanairmarūpatraiśca vijayākhyaṃ pradaṃ labhet |
dharmmarāje daśamyāntu pūjā kāryyānugandhakīm ||061:014||
vigatārirnirātaṅka iha cānte paraṃ padan |
ekādaśyāṃ vṛṣe pūjā kāryyā sarvvopahārakā ||061:015||
[gaṃdhopakārikī ka ga]
dhanavān putravān kānte vṛṣaloke mahīyate |
dvādaśyāṃ pūjayedviṣṇuṃ karpūrāguru candanaiḥ ||061:016||
haviṣyānnaṃ mahāvāho karttāṃ viṣṇupadaṃ labhet |
kāmadevastrayodaśyāṃ pūjanīyo yathāvidhi ||061:017||
rati-prīti-samāyukto aśokaâmaṇiâbhūṣitaḥ |
kumbhe vā sitavastre vā lekhyaḥ patraphalādibhiḥ ||061:018||
khaṇḍaśarkara naivedyaiḥ saubhāgyamatulaṃ labhet |
caturddaśyāntu deveśaṃ śaśāṅkāṅkita śekharam ||061:019||
kṣīrādisnapanaiḥ snāpyaṃ dhūpa-puṣpa-sugandhibhiḥ |
pūjanīyaṃ yathānyāyaṃ damanairhomasaṃyutaiḥ ||061:020||
[hemarsacitaiḥ ka]
vastrānna maṇīpūjā ca karttavyā mahatī śive |
vitānadhvajachatrañca deyaṃ kāryyantu jāgaram ||061:021||
mahāpuṇyamavāpnoti aśvamedhaṃ śatādhikam |
paurṇamāsyāṃ tathā kāryyā sarvvakāma samṛddhaye ||061:022||
indrāya śacīyuktāya kāmikaṃ labhate phalam |
evaṃ pañcadaśāhaṃ ca yastu pūjā prakurvvate ||061:023||
sarvvayajña tapodāna phalānyasya avāpnuyāt |
vicitra deva bhogeṣu krīḍate divi svecchayā ||061:024||
[deha ka ga]
puṇyakṣayādihāyātaḥ pṛthivyāṃ bhavate nṛpaḥ |
vigatārirna sandeha ityāha bhagavāna śivaḥ ||061:025||
iti śrī devī purāṇe mahābhyudaye damanakī pūjānāmaikaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye mahābhyudaye damanakīpūjā ka]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 062
dviṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

vaiśākhe tu prakarttavyā pūjā pāṭalajaiḥ srajai |
sarvvakāmamavāpnoti jyaiṣṭhe padmārjjunaistathā ||062:001||
āṣāḍhe vilva kahlārairihitaṃ labhate phalam |
||062:002ab||
nomālī kusumaiḥ pūjā na bhe kāryyā mahāphalā |
||062:002cd||
kadamba campakairīṣe sarvvakāma phalapradā ||062:002ef||
pūjā paṅkajamālābhyāṃ sarvvābhyudayadāyikā |
śatapatrikayā pūjā kārttike sarvvakāmikā ||062:003||
[sarvakāryakī ga]
mārge nīlotpalā pūjā puṣye kuṃja kajāstathā |
māghe kundakṛtā pūjā sarvvakāma pradāyikā ||062:004||
phālgune marupatrotthā mādhavī śubhadāyikā |
evaṃ savatsaraṃ caitryāṃ yaḥ kuryyād grahasattama ||062:005||
gandhapuṣpānna vastraiśca tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śraṇu |
hemago bhūmi vastrānna vidyādāna phalaṃ labhet ||062:006||
vājapeya mahāmedha rājasūya śatādhikam |
aśvamedhaṃ paśumedhaṃ gomedhaṃ kramaśaḥ phalam ||062:007||
labhate dakṣiṇā homaṃ vratānte vidhinā dadet |
pūraṇaṃ phalapuṣpaiśca vastrapaṭṭasrajānnajam ||062:008||
[hemaṃ ga; daśa ga]
dhṛta kṣīradadhibhaktaiḥ sarvvakāma phalapradaḥ |
evaṃ bhāvānurūpeṇa yastu pūjāṃ prakalpayet ||062:009||
śivāya saṃbhaved vatsa śiva sthānacaraḥ sadā ||062:010||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe pratimāpūjā nāma dviṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye pratimāpūjā ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 063
triṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

mandarasthaṃ mahādevaṃ brahmā pṛcchati śaṅkaram |
keṣu keṣu ca sthāneṣu draṣṭavyo'si mayā prabho ||063:001||
īśvara uvāca |

vārāṇasyāṃ mahādevaṃ prayāge tu maheśvaram |
naimiṣe devadevantu gayāyāṃ prapitāmaham ||063:002||
kurukṣetre viduḥ sthānaṃ prabhāse viśvarūpiṇam |
puṣkare tu ayogaṃdhaṃ viśvañca vimaleśvare ||063:003||
aṭṭahāse mahānādaṃ mahendre tu mahābratam |
||063:004ab||
ujjayinyāṃ mahākālaṃ mākoṭe tu mahotkaṭam |
||063:004cd||
śaṅkukarṇe mahātejaṃ gaukarṇe ca mahābalam(FN) ||063:004ef||
[ga pustake nāsti]
rudrakoṭyāṃ mahāyogī mahāliṅgaṃ sthaleśvare |
harṣe ca harṣitañcaiva sarvvaṃ madhyamakeśvaram ||063:005||
kedāre caiva īśānaṃ rudraṃ rudre mahālaye |
suvarṇākṣe sahasrākṣaṃ vṛṣabhe vṛṣamadhvajam ||063:006||
[varṇā ranyo tu sahasnākhyaṃ ga]
bhairave bhairavākāraṃ bhava śastrapade viduḥ |
ugraṃ kanakhale caiva bhadrakarṇa hrade śivam ||063:007||
[vastrāpade ka ga]
devadāruvaṇe diṇḍiṃ caṇḍaṃ madhyama jaṅgale |
urdhvaretaṃ turuṇḍe ca sukalānte kaparddinam ||063:008||
[daṇuṃ ga; jaṃgama ga; svaphalāṃ ga]
kṛttivāsañca ekāgre sūkṣmañcābhratikeśvare |
||063:009ab||
kālaṃjare nīlakaṇṭhaṃ śrīkaṃṭhaṃ maṃḍakeśvare |
| ||063:009cd||
dhyānasiddheśvare yogī gāyatrīñcottareśvare ||063:009ef||
vijayaṃ nāma kāśamīre jayantaṃ marukeśvare |
hariścandre hariñcaiva puriścandre tu śaṅkaram ||063:010||
jaṭiṃ rāmeśvare vidyāt saumyaṃ kukkuṭakeśvare |
bhūteśvare bhasmagotraṃ jalaliṅge jaleśvaram ||063:011||
[jalapriyam ga]
bhikṣukaṃ karikāyāntu vārāhaṃ vindhyaparvvate |
tāmraṃ paścimasandhyāyāṃ virajāyāṃ trilocanam ||063:012||
tṛpteśvare triśūlī ca śrīśaile tripurāntakam |
jala liṅge viduḥ kālaṃ kapālī karavīrake ||063:013||
dīptacakreśvare vedaṃ nepāle paśupatiṃ patim |
śrīkārā rohaṇe lakuṭiṃ vedīkāyā mumāpatim ||063:014||
[vaktrekhaṭe ga; devikāyām ga]
gaṅgāyāṃ sāgare tvamayamoṅkāramamarakaṇṭake |
saptagodāvare bhīmaṃ svayambhūrnakuleśvare ||063:015||
karṇikāre gaṇādhyakṣaṃ bhūrbhuvaṃ gandhamādane |
siddheśvarantu ākāśe pātāle hāṭakeśvaram ||063:016||
aṣṭaṣaṣṭistu nāmāni devadevasya dhīmataḥ |
purāṇe copagītāni brahmaṇā ca svayambhuvā ||063:017||
[dhīmato ka ga]
yaḥ paṭhet prātarutthāya snāto vā yadi vā śuciḥ |
mucyate sarvvapāpebhya śivalokañca gacchati ||063:018||
iti śrī devī purāṇe mahādevasyāṣṭaṣaṣṭināmakīrttanaṃ nāma triṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devīpurāṇe aṣṭaṣaṣṭi nāmāni mahādevasya ga]
%%%%

%%% Chapter 064
catuṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

vṛṣaṃ gāvau samādāya yuvānau lakṣaṇānvitau |
hemaśṛṅgau śaphe raupyau savastrau pūjayenmune ||064:001||
śivomāṃ pūjayitvā tu taddine yaḥ prayacchati |
śivabhaktāya viprāya rohiṇyāṃ vā mṛgeṇa vā ||064:002||
na viyogo bhavet tasya sutapatnīpati vṛta |
vātaraṃhasa vai mānairgacchecchivapuraṃ dvijaḥ ||064:003||
tatra bhogāṃścirān bhuktvā iha āgatya jāyate |
samṛddho dhanadhānyābhyāṃ putramitra samākulaḥ ||064:004||
vigatārirbhaved brahman vratasyāsya prabhāvataḥ |
yo vā ratnasamāyuktaṃ goyugaṃ pūjayenmune ||064:005||
[yo yuga ka ga]
prayacchati śivome ca prīyetāṃ bhāvitātmanaḥ6 |
||064:006ab||
sa sarvvapāpañca duḥkhebhyo vimuktaḥ krīḍate sadā ||064:006cd||
ihaloke bhaveddhanyo dehānte paramaṃ padam |
| ||064:006ef||
iti śrī devī purāṇe goratnavrataṃ nāma catuṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityabhyudaye gau ratnavratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 065
pañcaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

tṛtīyāyāntu śuklāyāṃ likhedvastrayuge śubhe |
rocanāsita kāśmīraiḥ śivomāṃ pūjayet tataḥ ||065:001||
hemaratna srajairvatsa mantrayugmamudīrayet |
nadamāna mantra śaṅkha yattat pūrvvaṃmudāhṛtam ||065:002||
tena japyārccanaṃ homaṃ karttavyaṃ dvijasattama |
aviyogāya nārīṇāṃ vratarājaṃ sadā hitam ||065:003||
[navīnāṃ ga]
sahemaṃ ratnapuṣpāḍhyaṃ sahasraṃ dāpayeddhutam |
mahāpuṇyaṃ mahābhāgyaṃ sarvvakāma pradāyakam ||065:004||
suta bhrātṛviyogantu na bhavet tena bho dvija |
na vyādhirnopasargaśca yāvat tanturaja mune ||065:005||
[vrajaṃ kha]
tāvat kālamumāloke krīḍate muditaściram |
hasta mātrā tṛṇa kāryyā aṅguṣṭhā tarjjanīgatā ||065:006||
pradīpya yāvat sādīptā tāvat bhojyaṃ samārabhet |
devīṃ saṃpūjayitvā tu ṣoḍaśāntena bhāvitaḥ ||065:007||
hema puṣpaistathā gandhai ratnaiścitrairyathā vidhi |
saṃvatsaṃraṃ yathānyāyaṃ satyān kāmānavāpnuyāt ||065:008||
[samutsavam ka ga]
pradīptā navamī vatsa hema godakṣiṇā matā |
vratānte vidhinā tena saṃgrāme aparājitaḥ ||065:009||
bhavate śatrusaṃghasya yathā devo maheśvaraḥ |
anenaiva vidhānena guggulā guḍikāthavā ||065:010||
[guggulī gulukaṃ yavā ga]
pūjayitvā śivāṃ mantraiḥ pradīpte homayedvidhau |
pūrvvoktā dakṣiṇā cātra phalaṃ vājimakhoditam ||065:011||
manuruvāca |

grahadoṣāpasṛṣṭasya rājño rājasutasya vā |
mahiṣyā vā mṛtāpatyā dvijātiṣvatha rājani ||065:012||
vipadad gate phalaṃ yasya suprayatna kṛtodyame |
gajāśva govṛṣāṇāñca yatra hāniḥ prajāyate ||065:013||
yatra bhaumāntarīkṣe ca upasargaḥ pradṛśyate |
tatra kuryyānmahāyogaṃ prājñaṃ puṣyābhiṣecanam ||065:014||
mūlaṃ rājā samākhyātastasya śākhā prajādikam |
tadupaghātasaṃskāraiḥ śubhe vā aśubhe'pivā ||065:015||
â
yatnaḥ kāryyaḥ sadā vatsa mūlaṃ śākhādikaṃ bhavet |
mūle vinaṣṭe naśyanti śākhādyāḥ phalasañcayāḥ ||065:016||
tato'rthaṃ mūlarakṣāṇāṃ yatitavyaṃ mahāmune |
dharmārtha kāmamokṣāṇāṃ sa hi hetuḥ prapadyate ||065:017||
vrahmaṇā yā purā śānti rmahendrārthaṃ vṛhaspatiḥ |
vyākhyātā kīrttayiṣyāmi tāṃ te śaunaka śṛṇuṣva tām ||065:018||
puṣye snānaṃ tathā puṇyaṃ sarvva pāpapraṇāśanam |
utpāta śamanaṃ divyaṃ yatra kāryyāvadhāraya ||065:019||
[mahāpuṇyam ga; kutravadhāraya ka ga]
valmīka tuṣakeśāsthi kaṭuṃ kaṇaṭaka varjite |
snigdhaśleṣmāti daurgandhi vigatākṣe mahītale ||065:020||
kaṅka kāpota gṛdhrolūkākādi parivarjjite |
suśubhe carmmakāśoke vakulābhrābhraśādvale ||065:021||
[supūte ka ga]
taruṇā taru vellipratate nirupahatadalānvite |
sumadhure vṛkṣaprāye phala pallava śobhite ||065:022||
pakṣiśāva gaṇākīrṇe kṛkavākūpa śobhite |
jīvaṃ jīvakahārīta śatapatra śukākule ||065:023||
cakoraṃ kuru vā vatsa cakravākopaśobhite |
śikhi pārāvataśrīka koka kokila nādite ||065:024||
madhu puṣpa surāpāna matta ṣaṭkarṇākule |
yāgaṃ kuryyādvanoddeśe kṣetrāraṇye'thavā śubhe ||065:025||
[bhadhupuṣpāsava pāna ga]
himādrau juhuyāt yāvat sahye vindhyācale'pi vā |
nadīnāṃ puline vātha saṅgame vā manorame ||065:026||
sikatā-paṅka-utkīrṇe jalapakṣi nakhakṣate |
protpluta haṃsacchatrābhe gīte kāraṇḍa sārasaiḥ ||065:027||
sahasrākṣa samāramye sare indīvarekṣaṇe |
vikasat kamala vadanā kule kalahaṃsabhāṣiṇī ||065:028||
prodabhinnakuḍmala kucā nalinī patra nivāsinī |
gorīmanthajaśakṛt khurāḥ phenaravākule ||065:029||
[vilāsinī ka ga]
suta sampūrṇa huṅkāra govatsavaravallite |
samudratīre kuryācca yatrāyātāḥ sutāgatāḥ ||065:030||
[śubhāvatāḥ ga]
ratnasampūrṇa koṣāśca nivasanti nirākulāḥ |
svanīla niculākīrṇe upānte vā khagānvite ||065:031||
siṃhakola gajānāñca yatra ekatra bhūbhṛdā |
vibhīyo yatra āsate khagā mṛgasamanvitāḥ ||065:032||
tatra kuryyād sadā snānaṃ yatra mātṛ gṛhaṃ śubham |
kāñcī kalāthanūpūrajaghanorūbharālasā ||065:033||
[yatra vā atra mātaṃge gamanā pramadālasāga]
â
śrīmatī mṛgekṣaṇā vā parapuṣṭa prabhāṣiṇī |
gṛhe yatra mudā āste tatra kuryāyācca vā mune ||065:034||
[parapuṣpapradāyinī kha]
pūrvvodak plavane bhūmau pradakṣiṇapathe jane |
śvāvinmudhi kevivaraiḥ karkaṭivāsavarjjite ||065:035||
varṇā gandha rasopetāḥ ghanā snigdhā samāḥ śubhā |
ṭṭaṣṭā sā vījarohādyairvahuśaḥ suparīkṣitā ||065:036||
gatvā tāṃ śubhe muhūrte kauveryyāmadhivāsayet ||065:037||
vali puṣpopahārañca mantrayuktaṃ nivedayet |
āgacchantu surāḥ sarvve yatra pūjābhilāṣiṇaḥ ||065:038||
diśo dvijā nagāścaiva ye cāpyanyeṃ'śa bhāginaḥ |
āvāh yaivaṃ tataḥ sarvvānnevaṃ brūyāt purohitaḥ ||065:039||
śvaḥ pūjāṃ prāpya yātāro dattvā śāntiṃ mahībhuje |
kṛtvā pūjāṃ tatastāsāṃ rātrau tasmin parāvaset ||065:040||
[mūṣikāvivarai ka ga]
svapanāḥ śubhāśca govatsadadhi devāṅgadarśanam |
dṛṣṭā dūrvvākṣataṃ ratna phala śailā jayāvahāḥ ||065:041||
[tasyāṃ vṛtī vaset ga; dūrvādidarśanām ga]
chatra cāmaraśaṅkhābja sita vāsādidarśanam |
lābho vā sarvvakāmānāṃ pūraṇāya prakīrtitāḥ ||065:042||
phala puṣpalatā vṛkṣāḥ kṣīriṇaḥ śubhadā matāḥ |
teṣāmārohaṇaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ prāsāde vṛṣabhādiṣu ||065:043||
candrārka grahaṇaṃ śastaṃ parvvatārohaṇaṃ śubham |
nigaḍairvandhanaṃ svapne vidviṣaśca jayāvaha ||065:044||
parivarttaṃ gireḥ kuryyācchatrurvācāvagūhati |
veṣṭayed yastu prāsādaṃ svāntestasya jayo bhavet ||065:045||
mṛtarodanamāgamyāgamanañca śubhāvaham ||065:046||
svapne tu kūpapaṅkeṣu garttādvā taraṇaṃ śubham |
nadīṣu taraṇaṃ śastaṃ samudrottaraṇaṃ tathā ||065:047||
nirjjitya śatrusainañca jayaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ |
kaṭakādi-alaṅkārāḥ putrarājya sukhapradāḥ ||065:048||
suhṛda jana vaipañcī lābhāḥ strīdhana dāyakā |
rūdhirantu pivedyastu tarate vā yadi kvacit ||065:049||
māsādi bhakṣaṇe lābhe labhate cehitaṃ phalam |
hāsyanṛtya cotsāha pāṭhanāḥ kalikārakāḥ ||065:050||
yāmyayānāṅganā kṛṣṇānayanaṃ bhayamṛtyudam |
paṅkajā godhagāmitvaṃ kūpamanupraveśanam ||065:051||
uttare bhayadaṃ svapne raktamālyāmbarāgamaḥ |
svarāṣṭre kapikākolū varāhāhi nirgranthayaḥ ||065:052||
â
dṛṣṭvāśubhān japaḥ kāryyo dhātujāḥ na phala pradāḥ |
vātapitta kaphottheṣu yānāgnitaraṇādikā ||065:053||
[dhātumān ga]
grīṣma śaradvasanteṣu prakopā na phalapradāḥ |
śrutānukīrttane dṛṣṭamanubhūtānugarhitāḥ ||065:054||
na ceṣṭā yadi vā dṛṣṭāḥ pradoṣe prathame tathā |
madhye madhyaphalāḥ sarvve cānte śīghraphalapradāḥ ||065:055||
govisarge ca ye dṛṣṭāste tathā parikīrttitāḥ dṛṣṭvā svapnān śubhān yāgaṃ kuryyāniṣṭhānna kārayet ||065:056||
snānaṃ devārccanaṃ homaṃ japaṃ śāntiṃ samārabhet |
kṛtvā śubhaṃ bhavet sarvvaṃ tato maṇḍala mālikhet ||065:057||
caturhastaṃ samārabhya yāvaddhastaśataṃ bhavet |
maṇḍalaṃ tatra karttavyamata ūrddha na kārayet ||065:058||
vimalaṃ vijayaṃ bhadraṃ vimānaṃ śubhadaṃ śivam |
varddhamānañca devañca maṃdākṣaṃ kāmadāyakam ||065:059||
rūcakaṃ svastikākhyañca dvidaśañceti maṇḍalāḥ |
sityādi-haritāśca rajāḥ kāryyāḥ suśobhanāḥ ||065:060||
[daśa dvā iti maṃḍala ga]
śāli ṣaṣṭika kausumbharajanī haripatrajāḥ |
maṇi vidruma rāgāśca bhasmanā abhimantritā ||065:061||
sita sarṣapa dhūpādyā rajaḥ kṛtvā tu pātayet |
astra rājaṃ nyasenmantrī sambhave'tipadaṃ pi vā ||065:062||
samotthānaṃ śubhaṃ kṛtvā gomayenopalepitam |
sa candana gurū karpūra kṣodadhūpādhivāsitam ||065:063||
bhūbhāgaṃ1 sumitaṃ siddhaṃ pūrvvapaścimacottaram |
sāmyaṃ svastika matsyādyaiḥ sūtraivaṇḍijapatrajaiḥ ||065:064||
padma patrāṣṭakaṃ madhye dviguṇaṃ triguṇaṃ pivā |
dvārāṇi samasūtrāṇi karṇikā keśarojjvalam ||065:065||
padmaṃ tathāvaśeṣāni svastikānyutpalāni ca |
savyāvalambahastastu rajaḥpātaṃ samācaret ||065:066||
madhyamānāmikāṅguṣṭhairupaviṣṭhā yathepsayā |
||065:067ab||
[upaceṣṭā sukhepptayā ka ga]
adhomukhāṅkuliṃ kṛtvā pātayet tu vicakṣaṇaḥ |
||065:067cd||
samārekhā tu karttavyā vicchinnā puñjavarjitā ||065:067ef||
aṅguṣṭhaparvva vaipulyā samā kāryyā vijānatā |
saṃsaktaṃ viṣamaṃ sthūlaṃ vicchinnakṛṣarāvṛtam ||065:068||
paryyanta sahitaṃ hrasvamālikhedvā kadācana |
saṃsakte kalahaṃ vidyādvakrarerave tu vigraham ||065:069||
[bahurerkha tu ka ga]
atisthūle bhavedvyādhirnityaṃ pīḍā vimiśrite |
vindubhirbhayamāpnoti śatrupakṣānnala saṃśayaḥ ||065:070||
â
kṛśāyāñcārthahāniḥ syād vicchinne maraṇaṃ dhruvam |
||065:071ab||
viprayogo bhavet tasya iṣṭaṃ dravyasutasya vā |
||065:071cd||
aviditvā likhedyasya maṇḍalantu yathepsayā ||065:071ef||
sarvvadoṣānavāpnoti ye doṣāḥ pūrvvabhāṣitāḥ |
caturasraṃ caturdvāraṃ likhenmaṇḍalamuttamam ||065:072||
maṇḍalasya pramāṇena padmaṃ dvārān samālikhet |
hastornonnata karttavyaṃ padmaṃ vipra kadācana ||065:073||
nādhika caturūrddhantu likhitavyaṃ vijānatā |
pratāpāyu striyo dharmmo rājyaṃ śrīrūpaśāntatā ||065:074||
yogāptirarthalābhaśca pūrvvadvāre tu maṇḍale |
siddhirmedhā yaśaḥ saukhya mārogyaṃ janavallabham ||065:075||
sarvvakāmārtha siddhiśca uttare dvāramaṇḍale |
putramāyurvalañcaiva saubhāgyaṃ ripumarddanam ||065:076||
yajñakarmābhivṛddhiśca paścimadvāri maṃḍale |
tasya madhye punaḥ padmamaṣṭapatraṃ sakarṇikam ||065:077||
caturvitastikaṃ vipre rājanye trivitastikam |
padmasyaivānupūrveṇa nālaṃ tadanupūrvaśaḥ(EN) ||065:078||
[kha pustake nāsti |
]
vāruṇīṃ diśamāśritya nālantu parikalpayet |
saptapātāla saunālaṃ bhuvanāntāḥ prakīrttitā ||065:079||
īdṛśaṃ kalpitaṃ padmaṃ devadevena śambhunā |
dhvajatoraṇa saṃyuktaṃ patākābhiralaṅkṛtam ||065:080||
karṇikā tu bhavenmerūrvījairgrahagaṇāḥ sthitāḥ |
keśarāstu bhavennadyaḥ kaṇṭake parvvatā sthitāḥ ||065:080||
aṣṭau dalā diśaḥ proktā ekaḥ padmaḥ pratiṣṭhitaḥ |
saptapātāla bhūrloke nālantu parikīrttitam ||065:082||
bhūrlokrastu dalā jñeyo digātmā śūnyagocarā |
||065:083ab||
sarvalokaḥ karṇikākhyātāstrailokyaṃ padmasaṃjñitam ||065:083cd||
karṇikāyāṃ nyaseddevaṃ pūjākāle maheśvaram ||065:083ef||
mātarā grahanāgāśca yakṣā rakṣā divaukaśaḥ |
vasavo munilokeśāḥ sarūdrā bhuvanādhipāḥ ||065:084||
lavāḥ kāṣṭhāḥ kṣaṇā yāmā rātryahāḥ sasitāḥ sitāḥ |
pakṣā māsā ṛrtumārgo samā yugayugāntarāḥ ||065:085||
kalpāntāśca mahākalpāḥ padme caivaṃ samālikhet |
||065:086ab||
prathame maṇḍale devaṃ śivaṃ vidyeśa saṃyutam |
| ||065:086cd||
gaṇanāyaka saṃyuktaṃ dvitīyāvaraṇe yajet ||065:086ef||
sagrahaṃ bhāskaraṃ prācayāṃmaiśānyāntu pinākinam |
saumyāsyaṃ keśavaṃ rakṣe paścimasyāṃ pitāmaham ||065:087||
tṛtīye maṇḍalāraṇye bhedinyāmupakalpite |
nānāratnākarākīrṇe bhūyo devān samālikhet ||065:088||
purohito yathāsthānaṃ nāgān yakṣān pitṛn surān |
gandharvvāpsarasaścaiva munīn siddhān nidhāpayet ||065:089||
grahāśca grahanakṣatraiḥ sarudrāścaiva mātaraḥ |
skandaṃ viṣṇuṃ viśākhañca lokapālān surastriyaḥ ||065:090||
varṇakai rvividhaiḥ kṛtvā kṛtyairgandhaguṇānvitaiḥ |
yathā sampūjayedvidvān gandhamālyānulepanaiḥ ||065:091||
bhakṣ ryeranekairvividhaiḥ phalamūlāmiṣaistathā |
pānaistu vividhairhṛdyaiḥ surākṣīrāsavādibhiḥ ||065:092||
viśeṣādvihitā pūjā grahayajñe mayā purā |
mātarāṇāṃ surāṇāñca sāpyatraivopakalpyate ||065:093||
piśācān dānavān rakṣān māṃsamadyaiḥprapūjayet |
abhyañjanāñjana tilairmāsena pitarastathā ||065:094||
munayaḥ sāmayajubhiḥ ṛá¹ggandhairdhūpamālyakaiḥ |
trimadhureṇa ca nāgānaśeṣairvarṇa kaistathā ||065:095||
[ghūpādhyāhutipānaiśca ga]
dhūpājyāhutidānaiśca devān ratnadakṣiṇaiḥ |
gandharvāpsaraso gandhairmālyaiśca sumanaistathā ||065:096||
śeṣāstu sārvvavarṇike valigandhaiśca pūjayet |
pratisarāṇi patākāśca vastrāpyābharaṇani ca ||065:097||
sarvveṣāṃ ca pradeyāni sayajñopavītāni ca |
dakṣiṇe paścime caiva vāyavyāṃ maṇḍalasya vā ||065:098||
grahayajñavidhānena homaṃ mātṛmakhoditam |
kṛtvā dravyairimairvatsa yathoktairlakṣaṇānvitaiḥ ||065:099||
lājākṣata ghṛtaṃ kṣaudraṃ dadhi kṣīraṃ sarīsṛpāḥ |
siddhārthāḥ sumanogandha dhūpāśca sasitotkaṭāḥ ||065:100||
[kṣīraṃ tu sarpadā]
gorocanā tilā darbhāḥ svarttujāni phalāni ca |

ghṛta pāyasa pūrṇāśca rāgavān vinivedayet ||065:101||
paścimāyāntu vedyāyāṃ pūjeyaṃ snānikī bhavet |
kalaśān sudṛḍhān kuryyāllakṣaṇena vadāmi te ||065:102||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe puṣpābhiṣeke cintā nāma pañcaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye puṣpābhiṣeka maṇḍalā ciṃtā ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 066
ṣaṭṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

utpattiṃ lakṣaṇaṃ mānaṃ kathayāmi mahāmune |
bādhakaḥ kalaśaścaiva yena loke prakīrtitaḥ ||066:001||
[vācaka ga]
amṛte mathyamāne tu sarvvadevaiḥ sadānavaiḥ |
manthānaṃ  mandaraṃ kṛtvā netraṃ kṛtvā tu vāsukim ||066:002||
[saṃsthānāṃ ga]
utpannamamṛtaṃ tatra mahāvīryyaṃ parākramam |
tasyāyaṃ dhāraṇārthāya kalaśaḥ parikīrtitaḥ ||066:003||
kalāṃ kalāṃ gṛhītvā vai devānāṃ viśvakarmmaṇāma |
nirmmito'yaṃ surairyasmāt kalaśastena ucyate ||066:004||
kalaśasya mukhe brahmā grīvāyāntu maheśvaraḥ |
mūle tu saṃsthito viṣṇurmadhye mātṛgaṇāḥ sthitāḥ ||066:005||
śeṣāstu devatāḥ sarvā veṣṭayanti caturddiśam |
kukṣau tu sāgarāḥ sapta saptadvīpāstu saṃśritāḥ ||066:006||
nakṣatrāṇi grahāḥ sarve tathaiva kulaparvvatāḥ |
himavān hemakūṭaśca viṣadho merureva ca ||066:007||
rohito mālyavantaśca sūryyakāntiśca parvvatāḥ |
gaṅgā sarasvatī sindhu subhagā yamunā nadī ||066:008||
erāvatī śatahṛdā tathā vaitaraṇī nadī |
godāvarī narmmadā ca mahī nāma mahānadī ||066:009||
kurūkṣetraṃ prayāgañca ekahaṃsaṃ pṛthūdakam |
amareśvaraṃ puṇḍarīkaṃ gaṅgāsāgarameva ca ||066:010||
[ekahastam ga; aśvamedham kha]
pṛthivyāṃ yāni tīrthāni kalaśe nivasanti te |
grahaśāntiśca puṣṭiśca prīti gāyatrireva ca ||066:011||
ṛgvedo'tha yajurvedaḥ sāmavedastathaiva ca |
atharvvavedasahitāḥ sarvve kalaśe saṃsthitāḥ ||066:012||
na caiva kalaśāḥ puṇyāḥ śambhūmūrtti samudbhavā |
gotyopagobhyo marutaḥ samudaśca tathāpare ||066:013||
manoharaḥ khalubhadraḥ pañcamaḥ parikīrttitaḥ |
virajastanudūṣaśca ṣaṣṭhasaptamakāvubhau ||066:014||
[talaiṣaṣṭa ga]

â
aṣṭamastvindriyopeto navamo vijayaḥ smṛtaḥ |
navaiva kalaśāḥ khyātā adhidevaṃ nivodhata ||066:015||
navamo yaḥ samākhyāto vijayo nāma nāmataḥ |
śivastatra sthitaḥ sākṣāt sarvvapāpaharaḥ śubhaḥ ||066:016||
sa tu pañcamukhaḥ khyāto loke sarvvārthasādhakaḥ |
pañcavrahmātmako yasmāt tena pañcamukhaḥ smṛtaḥ ||066:017||
paścime tu mukhe sadyo vāmadevastathottare |
pūrvve tatpurūṣaṃ vidyādaghorañcāpi dakṣiṇe ||066:018||
īśānaḥ pañcamo madhye sarvveṣāmupari sthitaḥ |
ete pañcamukhā vatsa pāpaghnā grahanāśanāḥ ||066:019||
sadyojātaṃ bhavecchuklaṃ vāmadevantu pītakam |
raktastat puruṣo jñeyo aghoraḥ kṛṣṇa eva ca ||066:020||
īśānaḥ paścimasteṣāṃ sarvvavarṇa samanvitaḥ |
kāmadaḥ kāmarūpī syād jñānādhāraḥ śivātmakaḥ ||066:021||
kṣitīndro jyeṣṭhakalaśo dvitīyo jalasambhavaḥ |
tṛtīya pavanaścaiva caturthastu hutāśanaḥ ||066:022||
pañcamo yajamānastu ṣaṣṭhaścākāśa sambhavaḥ |
somastu saptamaḥ provata ādityaśca tathāṣṭamaḥ ||066:023||
ete cotpāditā devyā śivenādhiṣṭhitāḥ purā |
indrasya mūrttayaścāṣṭau sūryyāntāstanavaḥ śivaḥ ||066:024||
kṣitīndraḥ pūrvvato nyāsyaḥ paścime jala sambhavaḥ |
vāyavye vāyavo nyāsya āgneye agnisambhavaḥ ||066:025||
saumyamuttarato yojyaṃ sauraṃ dakṣiṇato nyaset |
||066:026ab||
nyasyaivaṃ kalaśānāntu pūrvvarūpaṃ vicintayet |
||066:026cd||
kalaśānāṃ mukhe brahmā grīvāyāṃ viṣṇurevahi ||066:026ef||
[kṛṣṇa eva ga]
madhye mātṛgaṇāḥ sarvve sendrā devāśca pannagāḥ |
kukṣau tu sāgarāsteṣāṃ saptadvīpā ca medinī ||066:027||
śriyā caiva tayomā ca gandharvvā ṛṣayastathā |
pañcabhūtāstathā dhārāsteṣāmadharataḥ sthitāḥ ||066:028||
pūrṇāḥ pūtena toyena siddhāstvekāntatojjvalā |
saritsaraḥ sakhātena taḍāgena jalena vā ||066:029||
vāpīkūpau ca divyena sāmudreṇa sukhāvahāḥ |
sarvvamaṅgala maṅgalyāḥ sarvvakilviṣanāśakāḥ ||066:030||
abhiṣeke sadā grāhyāḥ kalaśā īdṛśāḥ śubhāḥ |
yātrāvivāha kāle vā pratiṣṭhāyajñakarmmaṇi ||066:031||
yojanīyā viśeṣeṇa sarvvakāma prasādhakāḥ |
mṛtāpatyā tu yā nārī yā ca vandhyā prakīrtitā ||066:032||
mūḍhagarbhā agarbhā ca durbhagā vyādhipīḍitā |
etāsāntu sadā kāryyaṃ snāpanaṃ puṣpamaṇḍale ||066:033||
â
sarvvaratnauṣadhī gandha-phala-puṣpa-samanvitāḥ |
grahadoṣe prayoktavyāḥ kalyāṇe maṅgale tathā ||066:034||
grahān dhārayate yasmānmātarā vividhāstathā |
duritāṃśca mahāghorastena te dhārakāḥ smṛtāḥ ||066:035||
[vācakāḥ ga]
ekaikāntu kalāṃ mūrtto kṣityādīnāṃ yathākramam |
saṃhṛtya saṃsthitā yasmāt tena te kalaśāḥ smṛtāḥ ||066:036||
haimarājata tāmrā vā mṛṇmayā lakṣaṇānvitāḥ |
pañcāṅgula vaipulyamutasedhaḥ ṣoḍaśāṅgulān ||066:037||
kalaśānāṃ pramāṇantu mukhamaṣṭāṅgulaṃ bhavet |
aṣṭamūrttisthito yo'sau sa śivaḥ padmasaṃsthitaḥ ||066:038||
[saptamūrtti ga]
mūrttayo'ṣṭau gaṇāstasya karṇikāyāṃ śivaḥ sthitaḥ |
ye gaṇāste dalā nāge ye nāgā kalaśāśca te ||066:039||
kalaśāśca grahāḥ proktā lokapālā diśaśca te |
etaiḥ sarvvamidaṃ vyāptamābrahma bhuvanaṃ jagat ||066:040||
durādharṣai rmahāsattvaiḥ sarvvapāpa viśodhakaiḥ ||066:041||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe kalaśotpatti niveśādhidevalakṣaṇakīrttanaṃ nāma ṣaṭṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādhe kalaśotpatti niveṣanādhi devalakṣaṇam ga]
%%%%

%%% Chapter 067
saptaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

ratnāni bīja puṣpāṇi phalāni kalaśe kṣipet |
puṣpamālyāśca vastrānte sitacandanacarccitāḥ ||067:001||
vajramauktika vaidūryyamahāpadmendrasphāṭikaiḥ |
sarvvadhātu phala bilvanāraṅgoḍumvaraistathā ||067:002||
vījapūraka jambīra āmrāamrāta dāḍimaiḥ |
yavaśālinīvāraiśca godhūmasita sarṣapaiḥ ||067:003||
[sāmra sāmrāta ga]
kuṅkumāgurukarpūramadarocanacandanam |
māṃselā kuṣṭha karpūra yatra caṇḍāmvarāñjanam ||067:004||
[mātsyenāṣṭi karpūra patra paṃḍā surājalam ga]
jātī patrakaṇagandha pṛkkāgaurī saparṇakam |
vacārātri samañjiṣṭhā turūṣkaṃ maṅgalāṣṭakam ||067:005||
[nirmāsāṃ vudaśele yajñajudevanaṃ phalam kha ka pustake nāsti]
dūrvvā mohanimṛṅgāṅka śatamūlī śatāvarī |
valā nāgavalā devī sahadevā gajadhvarā ||067:006||
[bhagāṃgaṃ ga; sahadevīmajākṣamā ga]
pūrṇakośā sitā pāṭhā guñjā surasikā latām |
vyāpakaṃ gajadantu śatapuṣpā punarnavā ||067:007||
brāhmī devī śivā rudrā sarvvagandhāni kāñcanam |
samāhṛtya śubhānyetān kalaśeṣu nidhāpayet ||067:008||
kalyāṇaṃ vijayaṃ dhūpau candrodaye samaṅgalam |
sarvaratnamalaṃkāraṃ rocanākhyaṃ tu paṭṭakama ||067:009||
budhyā dvayaṃgulamaṃgulyā ṣaḍviṃśāṃgulayāvadhī |
nottamaṃ caturasraṃ vā padmacandrikagarmikam ||067:010||
vāme sapadmamatsye bhāgā svastikavināyakaiḥ |
śrī śrī vṛkṣavarāhema amīdevī śubhānvitam(FN) ||067:011||
[kha pustake na santi]
sarvvaratnamalaṅkāraṃ paṭṭaṃ kāryya dvihastakam |
hastavistāra ucchrāyaṃ taśāṅgulyaṃ suśobhanam ||067:012||
snānākhyaṃ sārddhahastantu paṭṭaṃ vṛttāsanānvitam |
śayyākhyaṃ dviguṇaṃ dairdhyāddhanurmānaṃ sapīṭhakam ||067:013||
gaja sihaṃ kṛtāṭopaṃ hemaratnavibhūṣitam |
siṃhākhyaṃ sārddha vistārā kuṇḍāsanamathāpi vā ||067:014||
samapādaṃ grahākhyaṃ vā hema patra vibhūṣitam |
vajrendra nīla rūdrākhyaṃ mahārghamaṇi carccitam ||067:015||
catuṣpādo'tha vā kāryyastrimaṇḍala samo'pivā |
vyādhracitrakaraṭṭevā upadhānāni kārayet ||067:016||
anyairvā rañjitaiścammairmṛdutūlaka pūritāma |
śayyāṃ dairdhyārddha vistīrṇā caturhastāṃ sulakṣaṇām ||067:017||
vitastādhikamicchanti nṛpeśa kurūvidyayā |
padmapādātha pādā vā gajasiṃha padāthavā ||067:018||
dantidanta vicitrā vā hemaratna vibhūṣitā |
śubha paṭṭottarā vā dhātrā kariṇyā hastamucchritāḥ ||067:019||
kinnarādyāḥ prakarttavyāḥ sarvvaśobhā samanvitāḥ |
śubhavandhasamopetāḥ sakumbhā atha sagrahāḥ ||067:020||
[saṃgrahā ga]
śivopalasamaṃ mānaṃ kāryyaṃ vaṃ śivavāraṇam |
padmasvastika saṅghaṭṭa utpalaṃ vihagānvitam ||067:021||
[śivopayā samamānaṃ kārya vai śivadhāraṇam ga]
yatra vallīkṛtāpīḍa hemadantaṃ susañcitam |
vajrapadmamahāpadma rāgavaidūryya bhūṣitam ||067:022||
gajakumbha samākāramarddha candrakṛtāpi vā |
sahasrakinnarī mānaṃ saptamañca śataiḥ pivā ||067:023||
nṛveśaṃ sarvvalokānāṃ triśataṃ dvigataṃ pivā |
tūṇau śayyā samā kāryyā mṛdukauṣṭhaka pūrakaiḥ ||067:024||
upadhānaṃ vicitrantu kanakaṃ mṛdu varttulam |
vṛttaśṛṅgāṭakākārān śravaṇākhyāya kaṇḍukān ||067:025||
yānaṃ śayyākṛti kāryyaṃ vṛttapādaṃ suśobhanam |
vitastirūcchritā kāryyā śivapādārkṣā mṛttikā ||067:026||
evaṃ samastaṃ pratyagraṃ kṛtvā śayyāsanādikam |
vastrālaṅkāra śobhāḍhyamabhiṣekaṃ samārabhet ||067:027||
tato dhūpasya vaiśyasya carmma rohitamakṣatam |
siṃhasyātha tṛtīyasya vyāghrasya cra tataḥ param ||067:028||
[vṛṣasya ga]
catvāri tāni carmmāṇi tasyā vedyā upastaret |
śubhe muhūrte saṃprāpte puṣyayuvate niśākare ||067:029||
hemaṃ vā rājataṃ tāmraṃ kṣīravṛkṣamayaṃ pivā |
bhadrāsanaṃ prakarttavyaṃ sārddhahasta samucchritam ||067:030||
sapādahastamānantu rājñā maṇḍalikāntarā |
susaṃhṛṣṭamanā rājā haimante dīpaṃ saṃviśet ||067:031||
daivajñāmātya kañcukivandi paura suhadvṛtaḥ |
dvija vedadhvani gīta paṭu vādya ravānvitaḥ ||067:032||
mṛdaṅga śaṅkha tūryyaiśca śubha śabdairhatā śubham |
ahatakṣaumāni nivasaṃ nṛpaṃ kamvalachāditam ||067:033||
kalaśairvali puṣpāḍhyaiḥsarpipūrṇaiṃścasnāpayeta |
||067:034ab||
aṣṭa-ṣoḍaśa-viśāṃṣṭaśatamaṣṭādhikaṃ pivā |
||067:034cd||
kalaśānāṃ samākhyātamadhikānāmuttarottaram ||067:034ef||
kalyāṇairna mantreṇa maṅgalena japena vā |
devī śambhu bhavenātha snāpyājyena athāpivā ||067:035||
ājyaṃ tejaḥ samuddhiṣṭamājyaṃ pāpaharaṃ param |
ājyaṃ surāṇāmāhāramājye lokāḥ pratiṣṭhitāḥ ||067:036||
bhaumāntarīkṣa divyaṃ vā yattu kalmaṣamāgatam |
sarvvaṃ tadājyasaṃsparśāt praṇāśamupagacchati ||067:037||
tataḥ kamvalamupanīya puṣpasnāmvupūritaiḥ |
kalaśaiḥ snāpayedrājannārccayo'nena mantreṇa ||067:038||
surāstvāmabhiṣiñcantu ye ca siddhāḥ purātanāḥ |
brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśca sādhyāśca samarudgaṇāḥ ||067:039||
ādityā vasavo rudrā aśvinau ca bhiṣag varau |
aditirdeva mātā ca svāhā siddhiḥ sarasvatī ||067:040||
kīrtilakṣmīrdyutiḥ śrīśca sinīvālī kuhūstathā |
ditiśca surasā caiva vinatā kadrureva ca ||067:041||
devapatnyaśca yā proktā deva mātara eva ca |
sarvvāstvāmabhiṣiñcantu śubhāścāpsarasāṃ gaṇāḥ ||067:042||
nakṣatrāṇi muhūrttāśca pakṣā'horātri sandhayaḥ |
||067:043ab||
saṃvatsarā dineśāśca kalāḥ kāṣṭā kṣaṇā lavāḥ |
| ||067:043cd||
sarvve tvāmabhiṣiñcantu kālasyāvayavāḥ śubhāḥ ||067:043ef||
vaimānikāḥ suragaṇāḥ mānavāḥ sāgaraiḥ saha |
saritaśca mahābhāgā nāgāḥ kimpuruṣāstathā ||067:044||
vairavānasā mahābhāgā dvijā vaihāyasāśca ye |
saptarṣayaḥ sadārāśca dhruvasthānāni yāni ca ||067:045||
marīciratriḥ pulahaḥ pulastyaḥ kraturaṅgirāḥ |
bhṛguḥ sanatkumāraśca sanako'tha sanandakaḥ ||067:046||
sanātanaśca takṣaśca jaigīṣavyo'tha nandanaḥ |
||067:047ab||
ekataśca dvitaścaiva trito jāvāli-kaśyapau |
| ||067:047cd||
durayo durvinītaśca kaṇvaḥ kātyāyanastathā ||067:047ef||
[durvāsā ga]
mārkaṇḍeyo dīrghatapā śunaḥ śepo vidūrathaḥ |
dvaurtnaḥ saṃvarttakaścaiva cyavano'tri parāśaraḥ ||067:048||
dvaipāyano yavakrīto devarātaḥ sahānujaḥ |
ete cānye ca munayo vedavrata parāyaṇāḥ ||067:049||
saśiṣyāste'bhiṣiñcantu sadārāśca tapoghanāḥ |
parvvatāstaravo vandyāḥ puṇyānyāyatanāni ca ||067:050||
prajāpati ditiścaiva gāvo viśvasya mātaraḥ |
vāhanāni ca divyāni sarvvalokāścarācarāḥ ||067:051||
agnaya pitarastārā jībhūtāḥ khaṃ diśo jalam |
||067:052ab||
ete cānye ca vahavaḥ puṇyaiḥ saṅkīrttanāśubhaiḥ |
|||067:052cd||
toyaistvāmabhiṣiñcantu sarvvotpātanivarhaṇaiḥ ||067:052ef||
ityevaṃ śubhadairaitairmantrairdivyaistathāparaiḥ |
||067:053ab||
śaivai rnārāyaṇaiḥ raudrai rvrahmaśakra samudbhavaiḥ |
||067:053cd||
āpohiṣṭhā hiraṇyeti śambhaveti tathaiva ca ||067:053ef||
sarvvamaṅgala maṅgalyairvastraṃ kārpāsikaṃ dhriyāt |
śaṅkha veṇuravaistūryyai rācānto maṅgalairnṛpaḥ ||067:054||
tataḥ sampūjayeddevān gurun viprān dhvajāyudhān |
chatraṃ vādyaṃ gajānaśvān parijaptāni dhārayet ||067:055||
devena vijayenāḍhyamalaṅkārāṇi pārthivaḥ |
dvitīyāyāṃ tato vedyāṃ gatvāhūya hutāśanam ||067:056||
devānāṃ vadanaṃ sthānaṃ nimittāni tu lakṣayet |
svāhā rudrāya cendrāya viṣṇave brahmaṇe śive ||067:057||
prājāpatye kumārāya vighnahāya vināyake |
sūryyāya graharājāya varāhāya trivikrame ||067:058||
mātṛṇāṃ varade mātre cāmuṇḍāyai svadheti ca |
nāgarājāyānantāya tato rājā samāharet ||067:059||
krameṇa saṃsthite carmmaṇyupaviśennarādhipaḥ |
vṛṣasya vṛṣadaṃśasya rurośca pṛṣatasya ca ||067:060||
teṣāmupari siṃhasya vyāghrasya ca tataḥ param |
upaviṣṭe punarhomaṃ tairmantraiḥ saghṛtaistilaiḥ ||067:061||
kṛtvā śeṣaṃ samāptiṃ sa prāñjaliḥ saṃsthito vadet |
yāntu deva gaṇāḥ sarve pūjāmādāya pārthivīm ||067:062||
siddhiṃ dattvā suvipulāṃ punarāgamanāya vai |
nṛpatirato daivajñān purodhāmÌśca dvijānarccayet ||067:063||
gobhūhiraṇya ratnaiśca anyānapi kramāgatān ||067:064||
sthala devān purodevīn nadīkala catuṣpathān |
abhayañca jane deyaṃ gaṅgotsaṅgaṃ samācaret ||067:065||
alaṅkṛtya yathānyāyaṃ sitau tau vastubhūṣitau |
devadevīti vijñāya vandhanasthāṃśca mocayet ||067:066||
namo vicitrāṅga saduṣṭān punastān kṛtāgasān |
vibhavānurūpa bhāvaiśca pure pūjāṃ samārabhet ||067:067||
siṃhāsanaṃ samāsthāya catuske ghṛtadyotitaiḥ |
dīpaiḥ rajatapatrasthaiḥ toyārghamṛtavaṃditaiḥ ||067:068||
rocanādikaṃ paśyed darpaṇaṃ maṃgalāni ca |
evaṃ puṣye avāpnoti karttā rājyāyuḥ sampadaḥ ||067:069||
vināpi vardhe phaladaṃ puṣṭaṃ puṣyābhiṣecane |
rāṣṭrotpāto'yaseṣu dhūmaketośca darśanam ||067:070||
grahāvamardanaṃ caiva puṣyasnānaṃ samācaret |
| nāsti loke sa utpāto yo hyanena na śāmyati ||067:071||
maṅgalañcāparaṃ nāsti yadasmādatiricyate |
adhirājyārthino rājñaḥ putrajanmābhikāṃkṣayāḥ ||067:072||
[kha pustake na santi; kāṃkṣiṇaḥ ga]
tat pūrvvamabhiṣekeṇa vidhireṣa praśasyate |
devena brahmaṇe dattaṃ tenāpyuśanase punaḥ ||067:073||
uśanācca guroḥ prāptaṃ tato devaḥ sa te gatam |
mahendrārthamuvācedaṃ vṛhatkīrtti rbṛhaspatiḥ ||067:074||
sthānamāyuḥ prajāvṛddhiḥ saubhāgyakaramuttamam |
anenaiva ca toyena hastyaśvaṃ snāpayet tu yaḥ ||067:075||
tasyābhaya vinirmmuktaṃ parāṃ vṛddhimavāpnuyāt |
pratisaṃvatsaraṃ kāryyamabhiṣekantu pārthiva ||067:076||
māṇḍalīkanarendrāṇāṃ sāmantādhipateḥ pivā |
sāmantānāṃ sadā kāryyaṃ vighneśvara makhaṃ śubham ||067:077||
[viśveśvaraya ga]
striyā vā lakṣaṇopetā yasya vā labhate'sukham |
tasyedaṃ kārayet snānaṃ sarvvakāmaprasādhakam ||067:078||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe puṣyābhiṣeko nāma saptaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye trailokyābhyudayapāde puṣpābhiṣekaḥ samāptaḥ ga]
%%%%

%%% Chapter 068
aṣṭaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

gotīrthe putrakāmāya dhanakāmāya saṅgame |
mātṛsthāneṣu saubhāgyaṃ śmaśāne mṛtaputrikām ||068:001||
jīrṇe kūpe kākavandhyāṃ puṣkariṇītaṭe śubhe |
nityaṃ vināyakasthāne snāpayettu kumārikām ||068:002||
raktavāsottarīyāntu yasyā notpādyate naraḥ |
nadyāstu paścime kūle lekhyastīrtheṣu cāgrataḥ ||068:003||
mātṛṇāṃ vāmabhāge tu yajñasyāgneyatā diśi |
tale tu eka vṛkṣasya madhye caiva catuṣpathe ||068:004||
likhet pūrvveṇaiva raṇe śmaśāne nairṛte likhet |
jīrṇa kūpe yathecchantu parvvatasyotta reṇa tu ||068:005||
aiśānyāmekaliṅge tu yāmyāṃ vana ārāmayoḥ |
trikūṭasyottare bhāge ādhārasyāṣṭapade likhet ||068:006||
pustake nairṛte lekhyamāyataneṣu pṛṣṭhataḥ |
vāyavyāṃ vāruṇīmadhye goṣṭhe caiva yathepsayā ||068:007||
nairṛá¹tyāṃ yāmyamadhye tu pulinetu samālikhet |
kauverī aiśānīmadhye saṅgame ca samālikhet ||068:008||
taḍāgāt pada rātenaiva likheddikṣu yathepsayā |
ete sthānā mayākhyātā sthāna śreṣṭhāśca doṣajāḥ ||068:009||
bhayaṃ mṛtyuṃ kariṣyanti gotrotsādaṃ daridratām |
mantrasiddhirna jāyeta sutaścaiva vinaśyati ||068:010||
kulakṣayamato yāti sabhṛtyapaśuvāndhavaiḥ |
ādau bhūmiṃ parīkṣeta paścāt kurvīta maṇḍalam ||068:011||
saśalyāmuṣarāṃ caiva sphuṭitāṃ viṣamāṃ tathā |
| valmīkaṃ grāmadhānañca aśubhāṃ tāṃ vivarjjayet ||068:012||
saśalyānte keśavahulā ūṣare tu dhanakṣayaḥ |
||068:013ab||
sphuṭite maraṇaṃ jñeyaṃ viṣame śastrato bhayam |
||068:013cd||
valmīke anapatyārtha grāme dhāne tvanirvvṛtam ||068:013ef||
suṣamāṃ śādvalāṃ bhūmiṃ kūrmmapṛṣṭhonnatāṃ tathā |
pūrvvaplavā vṛddhikarī narāṇāñca śubhapradā ||068:014||
dakṣiṇato mṛtyobharyamarthakṣayaṃ paścimataḥ |
valaṃ dadatyuttarataḥ |
| ||068:015||
nairṛte śastrādbhayamāgneyyāmagnidāhaśca ||068:015||
aiśānyāṃ kāmadā mahī vāyavyāṃ śastrato bhayam |
aṣṭau dig bhāgāḥ mayākhyātāstataḥ karmma samārabhet ||068:016||
[kauveryyā ga]
grahān pāpān hanecddheto rakto'pi ca gaṇān hanet |
kṛṣṇaḥ sarvvāsurān hanti pītakantu vināyakān ||068:017||
piśācān rākṣasāṃścaiva harate harito rajaḥ |
rudro brahmā harirddevī sarvva devantu pañcamam ||068:018||
ākāśāt kṛṣṇakī jātaḥ pṛthivīṃ haritāṃ viduḥ |

iti śrī devīpurāṇe kāmyasnāna sthānanirūpaṇaṃ nāmāṣṭaṣaṣṭitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[nāsti ga pustake]
