%%% Chapter 069
ekonasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

sarvvakāmapradaṃ puṇyaṃ gaṇayāgaṃ vadāmi te |
hitāya sarvvalokānāṃ pārthivānāṃ viśeṣataḥ |
||069:001||
vināyakaḥ karmmavighna siddhyartha viniyojitaḥ |
gaṇanāmādhipatye ca rudreṇa brahmaṇā purā ||069:002||
tenopalakṣitaṃ karmma lakṣaṇāni nivodhata |
svapne'vagāhate'tyarthaṃ jalaṃ muṇḍañca paśyati ||069:003||
kāṣāyavāsasaścaiva kravyādāṃścāvarohati |
antyajairgardabhairuṣṭraiḥ sahaikatrāvatiṣṭhati ||069:004||
brajamānaṃ tathātmānaṃ manyate'nugataṃ paraiḥ |
vimanā viphalārambhaḥ saṃsīdatyanimittataḥ ||069:005||
tenopadhṛṣṭo labhate na rājyaṃ rājanandanaḥ |
kumārī na ca bharttāramapatyaṃ garbhiṇī tathā ||069:006||
ācāryyatvaṃ śrotriyaśca śiṣyo nādhyayanaṃ tathā |
vaṇiglābhaṃ na cāpnoti kṛṣīñcaiva kṛṣīvalaḥ ||069:007||
snapanaṃ tasya karttavyaṃ puṇye'hni vidhipūrvvakam |
gaurasarṣapa kakkola sadyo notsāditasya ca ||069:008||
sarvvauṣadhaiḥ sarvvagandhai rviliptaśirasaistathā |
bhadrāsanopaviṣṭasya svastivācyān dvijān śubhān ||069:009||
aśvasthānāda gajasthānād valmīkāt saṅgamād hradāt |
mṛttikāṃ rocanāṃ gaṃdhān gugulūñcāpsu nikṣipet ||069:010||
yadā kṛtaṃ hyekavarṇaiścaturbhiḥ kalaśairhradāt |
carmmaṇyupānahe rakte sthāpyaṃ bhadrāsanaṃ tathā ||069:011||
sahasrākṣaṃ śatadhāramṛṣibhiḥ pāvanaṃ kṛtam |
tena tvāmabhiṣiñcāmi pāvamānyaḥ punantu te ||069:012||
bhagaṃ te varuṇo rājā bhagaṃ sūryyavṛhaspatī |
bhagaṃ mitraśca vāyuśca bhagaṃ saptarṣayo viduḥ ||069:013||
yat te keśeṣu daurbhāgyaṃ sīmante pañcamūrddhani |
lalāṭe karṇayorakṣvorāpastad dhnantu te sadā ||069:014||
snātasya sārṣapaṃ tailaṃ sruveṇauḍumvareṇa tu |
juhuyānmūrddhani kuśān savyena parigṛhyate ||069:015||
sitaśca sanmitaścaiva tathā śālakaṭaṅkaṭāḥ |
kūṣmāṇḍarāja putrāṃśca yajet svāhāsamanvitam ||069:016||
nāmabhirvalimantraiśca namaskārasamanvitaiḥ |
dadyāt catuṣpathe sūpaṃ kuśānāstīryya sarvvataḥ ||069:017||
kṛtvā kṛtāṃstaṇḍulāṃśca palalaudanameva ca |
matsyān pakvāṃstathā vāmān māṃsāni vividhāni ca ||069:018||
puṣpāṃścitrān sugandhāṃśca surāñca trividhāmapi |
mūlakaṃ pūrikāpūpāṃstathaivoṇḍairaka srajaḥ ||069:019||
dadhipāyasamantrañca guḍaveṣṭita modakān |
vināyakasya jananīmupatiṣṭhet tato'mbikām ||069:020||
dūrvvāsarṣapa puṣpāṇāṃ kṛtvārdhya puṣpamañjalim |
rūpaṃ dehi yaśo dehi bhāgyaṃ bhagavati dehi me ||069:021||
tataḥ śuklāmbaradharaḥ puṣpagandhānulepanaḥ |
brāhmaṇān bhojanaṃ dadyād vastra yugmaṃ gurorapi ||069:022||
evaṃ vināyakaṃ pūjyaṃ grahān pūrvvavidhānataḥ |
asādhyena prasādena gurudevadvijārccanam ||069:023||
karmmaṇāṃ phalamāpnoti śriyañcāpnotyanuttamām ||069:024||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe vināyakamaṇḍalapūjāsnānavidhi nāmaikonasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ||
[adhivināyaka maṃtrapūjāsthāpana vidhiḥ ga]
