%%% Chapter 070
saptatitimo'dhyāyaḥ
auṃ vināyakāya gauṃ namaḥ |
gāṃ hṛdayāya namaḥ |
śrīṃ śiraḥ |
gūṃ śikhā |
gaiṃ netre |
gauṃ kavacam |
gaḥ astram ||070:001||
etaiḥ sarveṃ prakarttavyaṃ maṇḍalaiḥ sopapātakaiḥ |
ghātāgniśatru toyāgni dinarātryarddhagāmi tu ||070:002||
evaṃ maṇḍala vinyāsairhaimarājata bhāskaraiḥ |
paṭe vā likhitā bhūrje mantrā āyuḥ pradāyakāḥ ||070:003||
narāṇāṃ vāṇayodhānāṃ turagebhavṛṣoṣṭrayoḥ |
nāmādyakṣarasaṃrūddhā hemalekhāni nādarāt ||070:004||
madakuṅkuma karpūra rocanārasa lekhitāḥ |
gomayena savatsāyā bhūmau ca patitena tu ||070:005||
parasthaṃ mātṛmadhyasthaṃ ṣoḍaśānāntu rudragam |
dviguṇasthaṃ guṇāntasthaṃ maṇḍalānugataṃ kṛtam ||070:006||
pāṇau kaṇṭhakaṭivastraṃ rurūdevādpaṭṭagam |
mattavāraṇa saṃrūḍhaṃ pūjitaṃ dhanaputradam ||070:007||
vastrahema maṇi mālyagandhakarpūra candanaiḥ ||070:008||
phalainīrasanirmāṃsaṃ madhyasthaṃ dhanadhātyadam |
jātīcampakośīraṃ pūjitaṃ ghṛtamadhyagam ||070:009||
sitabhāvopacāreṇa ārogyāyuḥ pravarddhanam ||070:010||
raktapītā sitā nīlā kāmastambhana mohajaiḥ |
karttavyaṃ sarvvakāryyeṣu kālañcātra samṛddhe ||070:011||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe rakṣāvidhānaṃ nāma saptadatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[rakṣāvidhānam ga]

â
ekasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ
manuruvāca |

pārthivāt tu kṛtā rakṣā vahudhā rudralāñchitā |
tadvarṇavadasaṃkhyātā gajakumbhasthamāhave ||071:001||
[śakralāñchitā ka]
parasainya vināśāya pīta puṣpādi pūjitā |
sarvvakāmapradā rakṣā ādyavarṇopa lāñchitā ||071:002||
aṣṭavarga kṛtāntasthā candramadhyagatā punaḥ |
sitapuṣpopacāreṇa jvaradā ca śramāpahā ||071:003||
[kṛtā ga]
tejovarṇagatā rakṣā tanmaṇḍala kṛtānugā |
nāgāvirūpasampūrṇā viṣabhūta jvarāpahā ||071:004||
vāyu vīja kṛtā pīḍā sapatākā sitāñcitā |
cālane parasainyasya vidhinānena kalpitā ||071:005||
vaṭakāṣṭhotthaphalake vahṇistambhena vā mune |
rakṣeyaṃ tāmraphalake jvaraśīta nivāraṇī ||071:006||
kṣīracandraghṛtāntasthā dāhatāpaśame matā |
phala homāya vā mantrā phaladā ghṛtatarpaṇā ||071:007||
puṣpahomā jayaṃ dadyādāyurārogya sampadāḥ |
tarpaṇāyasakuṣṭhādi sarvvakāma phalapradā ||071:008||
ādityasya ca varṇena kālavarṇena vā mune |
rudradevena devasya tarpaṇaṃ vihitaṃ mune ||071:009||
catūrvyūhasamāyuktaḥ pūjito madhusūdanaḥ ||071:010||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe rakṣātrimūrtti sūryya tattva bheda pūjā nāmaika saptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

%%%%
%%% Chapter 072

dvisaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

vaśiṣṭha uvāca |

durgāṇāñca purāṇāñca pramāṇāyāmasaṃsthitim |
yathāvacchrotumicchāmi sarvvaloke sukhāvahām ||072:001||
[hitāvahā m ka ga]
bṛhaspatirūvāca |

sṛṣṭyādau kathitā brahman brahmaṇāmita tejasā |
svarbhūrloka vibhāgaśca pātālatalavāsinām ||072:002||
jambūdvīpe yathā lokā nivasanti sukhārthinaḥ |
tathāhaṃ sapravakṣyāmi yathā śambhuḥ purā'bravīt ||072:003||
sarvveṣāṃ surakaṅghānāṃ yathā brahmā uvāca ha |
pūrvvaṃ nikāmacāriṇyo hyaniketā athāvasan ||072:004||
prajāḥ sarvvāḥ suhṛṣṭātmā bhaya dvandvavivarjjitāḥ |
pṛthuḥ śāsadimāṃ pṛthvīṃ dharmmavartmavyavasthitaḥ ||072:005||
prajā lobhaṃ gatā vipra krāmakrodha valena ca |
kāmaṃ strīṣu pravṛttāsu niśumbhavaśagā yadā ||072:006||
tadā sadābhavat siddhiḥ kalpavṛkṣasamudbhavā |
devāpi merumācchannā durgaṃ dānavaśaṅkayā ||072:007||
tato brahmā samādhāya viśvakarmmā mahāmatiḥ |
gṛhāṇi cakrire tāsu prajāsu sukhahe tave ||072:008||
[kriyāsu ga]
jalaśītātapādīnāṃ pratighātāya cakrire |
yathā prītiryathā yogaṃ niketāni pṛthak pṛthak ||072:009||
marudhanvasu nimneṣu parvvateṣu nadīṣu ca |
saṃprayānti ca durgāṇi dhānyaṃ pārvvatamaudakam ||072:010||
yathā kālaṃ yathā deśaṃ sameṣu viṣameṣu ca |
nagaraṃ sanniveśāni durgāṇāñca yathāvidhi ||072:011||
tatastu māpayāmāsa sakheṭakāni purāṇi ca |
grāmāṇi ca yathābhāgaṃ tathevāntaḥ purāṇi ca ||072:012||
teṣāmāyāmaviṣkammān sanniveśāntarāṇi ca |
cakrustato yathāprajñaṃ mitvā mitvātmano'ṅgulaiḥ ||072:013||
mānārthāni pramāṇāni tadā prabhṛti cakrire |
bhānuṃ reṇuṃ kacaṃ likṣā yūkā yavakramāṣṭadhā ||072:014||
guṇitā hyaṅgulaṃ vipra yavāṣṭakamudāhṛtam |
devāṅgulaṃ samākhyātaṃ svaṃ svaṃ sarveṣu cāṅgulam ||072:015||

â
yavāṅgula pradeśāstu hastakiṃṣkadhanūṃṣi ca |
daśa tvaṅgulaparvvāṃṇi prādeśa iti saṃjñitaḥ ||072:016||
[athavāṅgula ka]
aṅguṣṭhasya pradeśinyā vyāsaḥ prādeśa ucyate |
tālaḥ smṛto madhyamayā gokarṇaścāpyanāmayā ||072:017||
kaniṣṭhayā vivastistu dvādaśāṅgula iṣyate |
araritnairaṅgulānyuktaḥ saṃkhyayā tvekaviṃśatiḥ ||072:018||
catvāri viṃśatiścaiva hastapādāṅgulāni tu |
kaṣkuḥ smṛto dviratnistu dvicatvāriṃśadaṅgulaiḥ ||072:019||
caturhasto dhanurdaṇḍo nālikā yugameva ca |
dhanuḥ sahasre dve kroṇe ganyūtirdviguṇaṃ matam ||072:020||
aṣṭau dhanuḥ sahasrāṇi yojanaṃ bhavate nṛṇām |
evaṃ māna vibhāgena vyavahāraḥ sthito bhuvi ||072:021||
aindrottaraplave bhūmau puraṃ durgañca śasyate |
caturasramathāvṛttaṃ tryasraṃ dīrghamathāpi vā ||072:022||
[tantrottara ga]
puraṃ yathākramāt śreṣṭhaṃ madhyamottamakanīyasam |
samantād yojanānyaṣṭāvaindraṃ devapuraṃ matam ||072:023||
daśa dve vaiṣṇavaṃ prāhuḥ ṣaṣṭimānantu śāṅkaram |
daśabrāhmaṃ tathā pañca sāmānyaṃ sārvvabhaumikam ||072:024||
yojanāddhi ca mānāni purāṇi sanniveśayet |
madhye rājagṛhaṃ kāryyaṃ viprāṇāñcottarāditaḥ ||072:025||
kramāccheṣāṇi kāryyāṇi prakṛtivāhyataḥ purāt |
vaseyuranyathā doṣo varṇaśaṅkarajo mahān ||072:026||
[vasedharaṇyapathyadoṣo ga]
kṛtrimeṣu ca durgeṣu ceṣṭaprākārakalpanā |
catuḥ pañcakamānena kalpayed vidhinā mune ||072:027||
khātikyaracitaṃ kāryyaṃ praṇālibhiḥ samanvitam |
catvāryyaṣṭa vāthavā trīṇi dvau vā bhūmi vaśād bhavet ||072:028||
navadurgā sametañca saśivaṃ bhujagānvitam |
nagaraṃ sarvvatobhadraṃ karttavyaṃ rucakaṃ pivā ||072:029||
svastikaṃ madhyamaṃ kāryyaṃ kumārīpurameva ca |
catuṣpathe caturyuktaṃ sarvvakāma sukhāvaham ||072:030||
chinnakarṇaṃ vināsañca dusthitaṃ kuśadurvvalam |
nagaraṃ na praśaṃsanti garttaṃ viddhaṃ vibheditam ||072:031||
agrataḥ svalpaprāsādaṃ chinnaghrāṇaṃ vidurvudhāḥ |
dvimukhaṃ karṇahīnantu kṛśaṃ madhye kṛśaṃ viduḥ ||072:032||
dusthitaṃ nimnaṃ yāmyantu nairṛtaṃ dhanadurvvalam |
saumyaṃ sarvvasukhācchādi pūritaṃ vārūṇaṃ vaśam ||072:033||
yāmyamāyuḥpradaṃ pūrṇaṃ nagaraṃ prītivarddhanam |
sarvavastu saṃpūrṇaṃ ca sarvvārogya sukhapradam ||072:034||
matryaṃ catuṣpathopetaṃ na ca taṃ pīḍayet kvacit |
vrahmasthānaṃ hitaṃ vipra śivastatra sadā sthitaḥ ||072:03||
caturviśitādyastu hastānaṣṭagataṃ param |
atra madhyaṃ praśaṃsanti hṛsvotkṛṣṭa vivarjitam ||072:036||
atha kiṣkuśatānyaṣṭau prāhurmukhyaṃ niveśanam |
nagarārddhañca viṣkambhaṃ kheṭaṃ grāmaṃ tatorddhataḥ ||072:037||
[śrīmān tatādrutaḥ ga]
nagarād yojanaṃ kheṭaṃ kheṭād grāmārddha yojanam |
dvikrośaṃ paramā sīmā kṣetra sīmā caturdhanuḥ ||072:038||
triṃśaddhanurgrāmamāhuḥ sīmāmārgo daśaiva tu |
||072:039ab||
[diśāmārgo ga]
viṃśaddhanuḥ grāmamārga sīmāmārgo daśaivatu |
|||072:039cd||
dhanūmÌṣi daśa vistīrṇaḥ śrīmān rājapathaḥ kṛtaḥ ||072:039ef||
nṛvājirathanāgānāmasamvādhaṃ susañcaraḥ |
dhanūmÌṣi caiva catvāri śākhārathyāstu nirmmitāḥ ||072:040||
trikarāstvuparathyāstu dvikarāpyuparathyakā |
jaṅghāpathaśca catuṣpādaḥ tripadaṃ syādgṛhāntaram ||072:041||
vyatīpādastvarddhapādaṃ prāgvaṃśaḥ padikaḥ smṛtaḥ |
avakaraḥ parivāraḥ pādamātra samantataḥ ||072:042||
prāvṛṭakāle tu sāvitrī karttavyā anyathā nahi |
ādye kāryyā purā vipra aṣṭa lokavivarjitāḥ ||072:043||
[sāvṛttā ga; rājye ga]
na viśecchaukaraṃ vaktraṃ tasmin pālo bhavedamī |
evaṃ nagare'ṣṭake siddhe pureṣu ca mahāmune ||072:044||
tato medhākṛtiṃ durgaṃ kalpayanti nṛpottamāḥ ||072:045||
sahajaṃ giridurgañca kailāsaṃ śāṅkaraṃ yathā |
tathā cārdrāpi draṣṭavyaṃ bahutoyagṛhānvitam ||072:046||
ākhyātaṃ divyasampannaṃ vinā devajalaṃ śubham |
sārddhayojanamānantu samaṃ dīrghamathāpi vā ||072:047||
[vinādairajanam ga]
śreṣṭhaṃ madhyaṃ bhaveddhanvaṃ pādāṃta kalpasaṃ bhavet |
| krośaṃ krośārdhamaṃ durgaṃ śreṣṭhamāhurmanīṣiṇaḥ ||072:048||
iṣurna carate yatra adhastāt prerito mune |
pathastena dhanuṣmatā tatra saṃskāramārabhet ||072:049||
caturddikṣu svadeśāntadurgaṃ daivakṛtaṃ nṛpaḥ |
kārayed yuddhayogyantu sapta grāma śatāvṛtam ||072:050||
durge kṛte caturddikṣu maṇḍalaṃ na viśatyariḥ |
vīravāsāvasaṃrodhāt pārṣṇigrāhabhayādapi ||072:051||
durgaṃ caturvvidhaṃ jñeyamāpatsvāśrayakāraṇam |
audakaṃ pārvvatañcaiva dhānvanaṃ vanajaṃ. tathā ||072:052||
â
catvāro mūladurge tu dvibhedāḥ parikīrtitāḥ |
antardvīpaṃ sthalañcaiva guhāprāntarameva ca ||072:053||
[antarīya ka]
proktaṃ nirudakaṃ stamvamiriṇākhyaṃ tathaiva ca |
khāñjanaṃ caiva vijñeyaṃ stamvagahanamaṣṭamam |
||072:054||
āpo dvidhā gatā yatra tadantardvīpamucyate |
vijñeyaṃ tu nadīdurgamityuvācośanā svayam ||072:055||
sthūlamunnata deśaḥ syādagādha salilāvṛtam |
jaladurgaṃ dvitīyaṃ syāt taḍāgaṃ sarasaśca yat ||072:056||
[tṛtīyam ga]
girīṇāmantarālaṃ yaddevadvāraṃ sudurgamam |
guhākhyaṃ parvvataṃ durga pravadanti manīṣiṇaḥ ||072:057||
prontuṅgaṭaṅka vicchinnaṃ sopasāraṃ susaṃskṛtam |
prāstaraṃ giridurgaṃ syāt sarvva durga sulakṣaṇam ||072:058||
[navadurgaṃ prakīrtitam ga |
vanadurgaṃ ka ]there is no ref. no in the text portion.
vahirniḥsalilaṃ durgaṃ tṛṇavṛkṣavivarjitam |
jñeyaṃ nirudakaṃ stambaṃ sadā durga vidhāyakaiḥ ||072:059||
etadekañca vijñeyabhiriṇaṃ soṣaraṃ vudhaiḥ |
svalpakṣārajalopetaṃ dvitīyaṃ soṣaraṃ smṛtam ||072:060||
[dhānvanaṃ ga]
etāvāṃstu viśeṣaḥ syāddhānvanaṃ dvividhaṃ punaḥ |
khañjanākhyaṃ punarjñeyaṃ sajalādhārakardamam ||072:061||
stokavṛkṣa samāyuktaṃ stambākhyaṃ gahanaṃ viduḥ1 ||072:062||
vanadurgaṃ dvitīyantu pravadanti manīṣiṇaḥ |
nadī parvvata durgeṣu caturaḥ pārthiva āvaset ||072:063||
varṇottamahite te dve sarvvakāma prasādhake |
dhānvanaṃ vanadurgañca āṭavyaṃ tat prakīrtitam ||072:064||
vasanti svena vidhinā yathoddiṣṭena te mune ||072:065||
anye'pi ca bhaviṣyanti durgāśrayasamāśritāḥ |
te'pi teṣu yathā yogaṃ hitakāryyaratāḥ sadā ||072:066||
khaṇḍasphoṭita saṃskāraṃ dravyāṇāṃ nicayāṃstathā |
rakṣāñceva yathāśāstraṃ kuryyād durgeṣvatandritaḥ ||072:067||
durgotpatteścaturthāśaṃ durgeṣvevopayojayet ||072:068||
khaṇḍasphoṭita saṃskāraṃ kriyādau nityakarmmaṇi |
karttavyaṃ poṣaṇe pādaṃ koṣamarddha praveśayet ||072:069||
â
deśakāla vaśādvāpi kalpanīyau vyayāvyayau |
prākāraparikhādīnāṃ kalpayed vā pṛthk pṛthak ||072:070||
dravyāṇāṃ nicayārthañca sagrāmān maharddhikān |
parikhākhananaṃ nityaṃ nityaṃ vapravivarddhanam ||072:071||
prākāropacayaṃ nityaṃ nityaṃ dhānyādisaṃgrahaḥ |
śarīrasya śarīro vā poto potasya vā yathā ||072:072||
tathā durgasya kāryyeṣu durgācārahito bhavet ||072:073||
āpadaḥ sulabhā rājñāṃ teṣāṃ durgaḥ pratikriyā |
durgeṣu matimāṃstasmānna pramādyeta karhicit ||072:074||
suprabhūnārivadhyānāṃ sarvvalokopakāriṇāma |
svāmyādīnāmanucchittāvekaṃ durgaṃ balaṃ viduḥ ||072:075||
[sarvaśoka prakāriṇām ga]
kṛto'pyāpat pratīkāro mohādeva pramādataḥ ||072:076||
taskarāḥ khaṇḍayantyeva naraṃ nidrālukāmikam |
anarghya nicayopetaṃ sāpasāraṃ surakṣitam ||072:077||
[ātmasya kha]
durgaṃ durgaguṇīpetaṃ yasya rājñaḥ susaṃbhṛtam |
anucchedyaḥ sa śatrūṇāṃ yāti mitrāṇāṃ cāpadi ||072:078||
adurgastu punaḥ śīghramabhiyukto valīyasā |
utsedha-vadha-vandhānāmekamāpnotyasaśaṃyam ||072:079||
tasmāt sukṛtarakṣeṣu dīrghakālaḥ sahiṣṇavaḥ |
durgeṣu nicayāḥ kāryyā dviguṇā dvādaśāvdikāḥ ||072:080||
aśeṣasneha dhānyādi bhaiṣajya lavaṇāni ca |
||072:081ab||
śuṣkaśākādika vallūraṃ kṣāragandhastṛṇāni ca |
|||072:081cd||
aṅgārāyavasaṃ kāṣṭha soradārūṇi veṇavaḥ ||072:081ef||
snāyulohāśma carmmāṇi valkāraṇyā viṣāṇi ca |
śastrabhāvagataṃ yantraṃ viṣāṇānyagni muktayaḥ ||072:082||
śarā dhanūmÌṣi prāsāśca kṛtāryyaḥ kāṇḍakalpanāḥ |
kacagrāhiṇyakruddhānāṃ varatrā śaṇarajjavaḥ ||072:083||
dātrīkā dūtayaḥ kuṇḍā bhūṣuṇḍayo dṛṣadastathā |
vayāghrī śataghnī roṣaṇyo jalayantrāṇi mudgarāḥ ||072:084||
ityevamāḍhyā kāryyā nicayā durgacintakaiḥ |
purāṇāmiti yaddravyaṃ kīṭādyupahatañca yat ||072:085||
evaṃ prakṣipya tāvat tad vyayaṃ tasyaiva kārayet |
tāvatā hi vyayābhāve dṛṣṭvā kāla sahiṣṇutām ||072:086||
navānāṃ parivartena kṣipejjanapadeṣu vā |
rakṣet śatakulīmekastā rakṣecchatiko daśa ||072:087||
daśaitāścintayedekaṃ caturthāśaṃ purasya vā |
samāgamaṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ nimittaṃ sthānameva ca ||072:088||
kālamarthapramāṇañca vidyāddaśakulādhipaḥ |
mānuṣāgraṃ kuṭumbasya vibhave yāti jīvake ||072:089||
vyayaṃ vivāha sambaṃdhaṃ dāyagrāhañca tatvataḥ |
nāpṛṣṭvā praviśet kaścidāyāntaṃ vā praveśayet ||072:090||
kāraṇaṃ mokṣakālañca vijānīyād dvayorapi |
abhyāgato'nya deśīyo naikarātrāt paraṃ vaset ||072:091||
[jñepakālañca ka ga]
susthavṛtte'nyadā tasya praveśābhāva eva ca |
anyadeśāgataṃ paṇyaṃ praveśyantaṃ nivāsibhiḥ ||072:092||
dātavyaṃ pratipaṇyañca taireva hi viniḥsṛtam |
durgopayogi yaddravyaṃ dhānyaṃ vā valkalādikam ||072:093||
tasya kuryyādanirvvāhaṃ kīṭādyupahatādṛte |
nānivaddho vaset kaścinna liṅgī na ca bhikṣukaḥ ||072:094||
na śastriṇāṃ na conmatto na vāgmī na kuśīlavau |
praveśayenna cājñātān prākpraviṣṭāṃśca śodhayet ||072:095||
āyudhīyairaśūnyāni sadā dvārāṇi kārayet |
ākāmināñca nāryānā mupabhogāya kalpayet ||072:096||
[agāmināṃ ca sādhanām ga. sarvāṇāṃ ka]
vikrayaṃ sarvvapaṇyānāṃ bahiḥ sūnāsugāsu ca |
advāreṇa praviṣṭasya dvāreṇāṃsamaye'pi vā ||072:097||
dvipādagniniṣedhārthaṃ sātatyādavaghoṣaṇam ||072:098||
prakṣepya paṭalebhyaśca tṛṇajātaṃ dhanātyaye |
nopahanyādamedhyena na gartairnāpyapaskaraiḥ ||072:099||
gṛhakāṣṭhatṛṇairvāpi viṭamārga na rodhayet |
anyonyāloki karttavyaṃ sthānakaṃ sthānakāntarāt ||072:100||
[ghaṭanāṃkena vodhayet ka ga |
dhaṭamārga nibodhayet ga]
prākāravāhumekaikaṃ careyurniśi rakṣiṇaḥ |
tānyeva bhayaśaṅkāyāṃ rājñi dūragate'pi vā ||072:101||
nirantarāṇi kurvvīta sthānakāni prayatnavān |
vyāmiśrāste'pi karttavyāḥ sainikaiḥ puravāsibhiḥ ||072:102||
lekhyakā vatsatajjāti gotra saṃkhyādilakṣitāḥ |
prākārādhiṣṭhitaṃ pādaṃ pādaṃ sarvvatracāriṇam ||072:103||
āvaddhakavacaṃ madhye valasyārddhaṃ niveśayet |
uṣṭrāśvāśvatarāruḍhaiḥ śīghradūra prayāyibhiḥ ||072:104||
saṃśodhya parito bhūmiṃ durgasya daśayojanāt |
yato yato bhayāśaṅkā tatra tatra mahāmatiḥ ||072:105||
carairvijñāya vṛttāntaṃ tasya yogyaṃ samācaret |
bhāṇḍāgāreṣu yatnena koṣṭhāgāreṣu nityaśaḥ ||072:106||
jalaśālāsu codyuktāḥ prayojyāḥ kulajāḥ sthirāḥ |
bhītā lubdhāstathā trastāḥ bhṛtyā vyasaninaḥ śaṭhā ||072:107||
dyūtamadyaratā durge na kāryyāstvadhikāriṇaḥ |
nityaṃ mantrijanopetaṃ bhiṣaksāṃvatsarānvitam ||072:108||
viṣabhūtopahārāṃśca gārūḍikādikāmÌstathā |
||072:110ab||
dvijān vedavidaścaiva kārayet sannidhau nṛpaḥ |
||072:110cd||
śvaśṛgālān mahādurge gopurādiṣu varjjayet ||072:110ef||
evaṃ kṛte sadā vipra puṣkalāṃ labhate śriyam |
pātigāṃ sabalopetāṃ nirāvādhāṃ sukhena ca ||072:111||
vasiṣṭha uvāca |

gopurasya pramāṇantu śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ |
kīdṛṅmānaṃ prakarttavyaṃ dina ṛkṣeṣu keṣu ca ||072:112||
vṛhaspatiruvāca |

pūrvādīn kārayeddvārān mahādurgeṣu cottamān |
dvātriṃśat karakotsedhamarddhenaiva tu vistaram ||072:113||
dvitīyaṃ madhyamaṃ kāryyaṃ karaṣoḍaśakocchrayam ||072:110||
tasya cārddhena vistāraṃ tṛtīyaṃ manumānagam |
caturthaṃ bhānumānantu rudrabhānantu pañcamam ||072:115||
ṣaṣṭhaṃ daśakaraṃ kāryya saptamaṃ grahamānitam |
vasumānaṃ bhavedvipra dvārataścāṣṭamaṃ matam ||072:116||
ucchrāyāccārddha vistārān dvārān kurvvīta buddhimān |
śailāni dṛḍha koṣṭhāni nānā hetiyutāni ca ||072:117||
ūrdhvamaṇḍapa yuktāni vīthikopavanādibhiḥ |
rājasthāna samāyuktān vātāyana samanvitān ||072:118||
matavāraṇavidyādyān dhvajakairupaśobhitān |
gaja vyāla kṛtāpīḍān padmapatramanoharān ||072:119||
kārayedvividhān dvārān yathāśobhaṃ yathākramam |
madhyamaṃ ṣoḍaśamānañcārthamānamathāpi vā ||072:120||
dvāraṃ sarvveṣu durgeṣu pravadanti manīṣiṇaḥ |
sakapāṭārgalopetaṃ sakīlakamathāpi vā ||072:121||
bhujagena sayantrādyān nāgavandha susañcitān |
āyasānyaṣṭakīlāni yathābhāgagatāni ca ||072:122||
[bhujākula ga]
kārayed dvārasaṃsthāni dvāre dvārāntarāṇi ca |
maṇḍapaṃ vīthikā cātha yatra śastrabhṛto narāḥ ||072:123||
tiṣṭhanti dvārapālāśca nityaṃ sannihitāyudhāḥ |
durgeṣu kārayed durgāṃ mahiṣāsuraghātinīm ||072:124||
dvārasthaṃ gajavaktraṃ vā dhanadaṃ vātha padmajam |
triṣūttarāsu rohiṇyāṃ devaṛkṣeṣu cāthavā ||072:125||
kārayet puradvārādi sulagne grahavarjjite |
yathā śukrayute vātha dṛṣṭe vā cocchraye'thavā ||072:126||
[sādhayet ga] reference no. not found in the text portion;  is this correct place?
śilānyāse valiḥ kāryyaḥ prāsādokto yathāvidhi |
hemaṃ kumbhaṃ saratnaṃ vā śākhādhaḥ sanniveśayet ||072:127||
pūtanā śakunī tatra jambhādīn pūjayed grahān |
devān yajñān grahān nāgān pūjayitvā yathāvidhi ||072:128||
daivajñān sūtradhārāṃśca vastrahoma sragādibhiḥ |
brāhmaṇān svastivācyāṃśca paśuṃ śāntau nipātayet ||072:129||
dadhyakṣatasrajaḥ kumbhaṃ bhakṣya bhojyaṃ caturvidham |
kārayet sarvvalokādimutsavaṃ vividhaṃ pure ||072:130||
śaṅkha bherīninādena kuryyāccotsavādikam |
śākhocchrayaṃ tathā kāryyaṃ chatraṃ śveta patākikam ||072:131||
evaṃ samucchrayecchāravāḥ sarvvadvāreṣu vuddhimān |
pūrvvāśaṃ śodhayeccāsya svātī puṣyasamudgame ||072:132||
tena parāpi saṃsiddhāḥ śeṣāḥ siddhāḥ parā mune |
diṅbhrāntaiḥ sumahaddoṣo nṛpasya tannivāsinām ||072:133||
uḍumvaraṃ samaṃ kāryyañcordhvaṃḍimvarakaṃ pivā |
sārddha hastantu vistīrṇamucchrayaṃ hastamānitam ||072:134||
śākhāṃ viśāmahīnāntu ṣoḍaśāṃśāmathāpivā |
triśākhamapi karttavyaṃ madhyadvāraṃ vipaścitā ||072:135||
stambhā vṛttāśca dvātriṃśat ṣoḍaśāṣṭāṣṭameva ca |
caturasrātha karttavyā yathāśobhaṃ yathā puram ||072:136||
[ga pustake padyadvayaṃ nāsti]
vicintyārthaṃ tathā śāstraṃ durgadvāraṃ niveśayet |
ṛddhimāpnoti yenāsu bhayaśoka vivarjitam ||072:137||
rājā prajāśca nandanti samyagdvāre kṛte mune |
sāmānyaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ tāsāṃ sautraṃ sarvvatra śasyate ||072:138||
[śaukra ga]
puradurgeṣu karttavyaṃ yathāvat tannibodhata |
nāgottama samārūḍha sacchatro viśate yathā ||072:139||
[yathāvṛkṣaṃ ka ga]
tathā pratolyaḥ karttavyā durge dharmmārthakāmadāḥ |
athavā āyasaṃ śuddhāḥ śṛṇu vistarataḥ phalam ||072:140||
nacorddhaṃ pañcavistārāḥ pūrvvādeva vivaharddhitāḥ |
||072:141ab||
[vivarjitā ka ga]
narākṣyā pañcavistīrṇā yadvṛddhā dakṣiṇā matāḥ ||072:141cd||
sapta sapta hatā toyā pañcasaptahatottarā ||072:141ef||
pañcāṅgulasya vṛddhayā vā sadā kāryyāstu gopurāḥ |
āyamāna vihīṃnāstu durgā rājño bhayāvahāḥ ||072:142||
nityodvega bhayatrasta tannivāsijanāntarāḥ |
sampūrṇamāna vāstvaṅga sukhadā gopurāḥ sadā ||072:143||
[jalāntaṭāḥ ka ga]
tāsāṃ nāmāni vakṣyāmi yathā vā parikīrtitāḥ ||072:144||
śriyā kāntid ryutirlaṃkṣmīrjaṃyābhadrāparājitā |
anantā śobhanā durgāḥ pūrvveṇa parikīrttitāḥ ||072:145||
śānti vṛddhirbhavā devī kālī ghorā vimohinī |
vimalā ceti yāmyena pratolyaḥ śubhadāyikāḥ ||072:146||
rocanā maṅgalā raudrī ugrā caṇḍā yaśovatī |
prāpti rdīptīti vāruṇyāṃ vīthikāḥ sarvvakāmadāḥ ||072:147||
icchā prītiḥ śubhā mātā yaśodā dhanadā umā |
śaraṇyā ceti saumyena durge gopurikā matā ||072:148||
susthitā suṣamā kāryyā aviddhā sumanoharā |
sarvvalakṣaṇasmapūrṇā pañcasaptātha bhūmikā ||072:149||
[suvidrā ga]
mūlādvā daśahīnāni mālā dvārāṇi kalpayet |
śailāni kāṣṭha veṣṭhāni vajrasaudhāni kārayet ||072:150||
[mānā]
lepāni sarvvagandhāni prāsādavibhavāni ca |
evaṃ lakṣaṇasampannaṃ durgaṃ yasya mahīpateḥ ||072:151||
sa pātīha bhayāt sarvvān lokān koṣasamanvitān |
padma svastika gomūtra vastu nyāsagate'pivā ||072:152||
madhyāmadhyagatairgehaiḥ paṅkivṛttagataiḥ pivā |
puraṃ durgaṃ pivā kāryyaṃ prāsādagṛhabhūṣitam ||072:153||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe gopuradvāralakṣaṇaṃ nāma dvisaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |
