trisaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi adhodurganiveśanam |
yathā yasya prakarttavyaṃ nṛpaloka sukhāvaham ||073:001||
yasmin viśvaṃ bhaveccorddhaṃ durgaṃ durgaviśāradaḥ |
tadadhobhāgavāsantu kuryyāt sarvvasukhāvaham ||073:002||
[nimnam ka ga]
pūrvva nimnaṃ śubhaṃ durgaṃ sarvveṣāṃ puravāsinām |
āgneyyāmagnidāhastu yāmye taskarajaṃ bhayam ||073:003||
nairṛá¹te nirdhanā lokā bhavanti tannivāsinaḥ |
nirdhanā dhanahīnāstu aparā mānate janāḥ ||073:004||
nityodvegaparā vatsa vāyavyāṃ sannate girau |
muditāḥ sarvvalokāśca durge saumyāṃśanāmite ||073:005||
aiśānyāṃ dharmmaniratā dhanadhānyasamākulāḥ |
bhavanti tannivāsino durge nimnagate mune ||073:006||
pūrvvabhāge nṛpaścādho vasennimnaṃ yadā bhavet |
āgneye tejasā viprāḥ sukhadā bhayadāstathā ||073:007||
yāmye antyajanā bāsyā nairṛte śastrakāriṇaḥ |
vāruṇe jaladravyādi tathā śūdrajanādayaḥ ||073:008||
gandhagandharvvaniratā vāyavye nadate janāḥ |
saumye haṭṭajalaṃ kāryyamaiśānyāṃ devatādikam ||073:009||
viparīte mahān doṣaḥ pūrvve haṭṭaṃ nṛpāntakam |
bhavate sukhadaṃ vatsa yathā saṃsthāna vāsinām ||073:010||
durgaṃ purañca nagaraṃ karttavyaṃ maṅgalāyutam |
na ca śūnyāni vāsāni dhārayeddevatādiṣu ||073:011||
na gṛhaṃ vīthikā durgaṃ pure śīrṇaṃ vidhārayet |
rājabhāgaṃ bhavet tacca devatādiṣu vinyaset ||073:012||
devaśca śaṅkaraḥ kāryyaḥ sagaṇo maṅgalāyutaḥ |
tasmin nityotsavāḥ sarvve gṛhaprāsāda bhūṣitāḥ ||073:013||
vaseyururddhagā lokā bādhā śāśvatavarjitāḥ |
aṭavyādiṣu durgeṣu adhovāsaṃ na kārayet ||073:014||
vasaṃstṛṇādigeheṣu bhayādi parivarjjitāḥ |
adhobhāgena meghādīn dhārayenmunisattamaḥ ||073:015||
dhārayan mahadāpnoti bhayaṃ rājā arātijam |
rāṣṭraṃ ripuvale naiva rājā ca paripīḍyate ||073:016||
[viprabalenaiva ga]
tasmād durgaṃ vivṛddhayarthañcordhvavāso vidhīyate |
urddharvaṃ subhṛtāvāsyāḥ kubhṛtāstu nivāsayet ||073:017||
mattonmattān pramattāṃśca durge na vāsayennarān |
naike kuryyāt prabhutvantu na śūdre na kuśīlave ||073:018||
na ca vandhakine kuryyānna co'yasi niyantrite |
kuryyād durgaṃ viśīryet yathā gehaṃ śirohatam ||073:019||
aindreśastu śivo durge adhorddhe tannipīḍayet |
svakāyapīḍanāddoṣaṃ śive svāmī vinaśyati ||073:020||
jalaje giridurge ca vādho vāso bhayāvahaḥ |
aṭavye tu viśeṣeṇa śāśvataṃ varjjayedadhaḥ ||073:021||
[rājye ga]
araṇyeṣu ca durgeṣu ūṣareṣu viśeṣataḥ |
vāhye vāsaṃ na kurvvīṃta araṇyeṣu tathaiva ca ||073:022||
[rājye ka ga; aṭavyeṣu ga]
araṇye dharmmahāniḥ syādūṣare'pi tathaiva ca |
aṭavye śatrujā śaṅkā tasmādvāsamadhastyajet ||073:023||
kṛṣikarmmātu carmmādi lohitantu gaṇāyasam |
śarayantrauṣadhādīnāṃ saṃgrahāya adho vaset ||073:024||
vaṇigvīthinivāsinyo dhānyameyā hiraṇyena |
urdhve cāsyā vaśīkṛtya rājñā durgahitaiṣiṇā ||073:025||
paṅkalaṃ kheṭakaṃ parṇaṃ durgādhaḥ karṣayet sadā |
tannivāsijanā sevane kāryyāḥ savalāḥ sadā ||073:026||
evaṃ na kṣīyate durgaṃ dhanadhānyena saṃbhṛtam |
varddhate ca janaḥ koṣo rājā ca sukhamedhate ||073:027||
yathā yathā vivardhante daivaukāni giraupari |
tathā tathā vivarddhante rājño dharmmayaśaśriyaḥ ||073:028||
yathāraṇyavāsināñca dharmmo bhavati dehinām |
evaṃ rājñaḥ śriyā dharmmo durge kālavaśād bhavet ||073:029||
durgādhaḥ kṛtrimaṃ durgaṃ kiñcit kālaṃ vivakṣayā |
vijayārthe prakarttavyaṃ yathāvat tānnibodha me ||073:030||
durgāśrayaṃ samālakṣya ūrdhrvaṃ durgaṃ valaṃ tathā |
||073:031ab||
jalendhanañca dhānyañca yavasamāyudhādikam |
|||073:031cd||
tathā kuryyānmahāvāho kṛtrimaṃ vijayottamam ||073:031ef||
kāṣṭheṣṭamathavā śailaṃ khātikāracitaṃ tathā |
drumavallīlatopetaṃ garbhaṃ toyasamanvitam ||073:032||
vāhyatoyaṃ surakṣyaṃ vā durgayantropalādibhiḥ |
karttavyaṃ gṛhaprākāraistoraṇairupaśobhitam ||073:033||
vīthī pūrakasaṃyuktamathavā maṇḍapānvitam |
maṇḍapaṃ śatadaṇḍena dviguṇaṃ triguṇaṃ pivā ||073:034||
mānādavṛttamatha tryasramāyatendu yathāśubham |
aneka garbhagarbhāḍhyaṃ devatā mātarānvitam ||073:035||
sudurgaṃ nāyakaṃ kāryaṃ nāgayajñaṃ umānvitam |
||073:036ab||
aneka māṇḍameyādibhṛtaṃ kūpaprapānvitam |
||073:036cd||
sūryyāgnī dharmmato deyau śubhe cāpādi varjjite ||073:036ef||
evaṃ kālavaśāt kuryyād vijayākhyaṃ mahāpuram |
nīcocca vidhisaṃsthānaṃ lakṣayitvā gṛhaṃ valam ||073:037||
puraṃ durgaṃ prakarttavyaṃ maharddhiphalakāṅkṣayā |
tritrikaṃ garbhagarbhantu daṇḍaiścāndrādibheditaiḥ ||073:038||
[vanam ga]
pūrvvādideśaṛkṣantu dvigarbhantu dviraṣṭakam |
vāhye dvādaśakaṃ deyaṃ tatra vidyād balāvalam ||073:039||
praveśe bhayadāḥ krūrāḥ saumyāḥ saumyaphalapradāḥ |
niṣkāśe śubhadāḥ sarvve pure durge ca kīrtitāḥ ||073:040||
ekaṃ patnī vināśāya dve ca mitradhanāpahe |
trīṇi jyeṣṭhasutaṃ hanyurnīcasthānasthitā grahāḥ ||073:041||
na bhānau nīcage kuryāt puraprāsādakalpanām |
svāmī nāśamavāpnoti tat puraṃ naiva sidhyati ||073:042||
saumyaiścoccasthitaiḥ kuryyād dravyārthaṃ vijayaṃ puram |
durgaṃ krūraiḥ prakarttarvyaṃ śatrunāśāya vuddhimān ||073:043||
valaṃ candrārkalagnānāṃ vuddhāvāsaṃ samaṃ samam |
āyurdā yaśadā pākarājayogāṣṭavargakam ||073:044||
candra dṛṣṭivalaṃ karmma sadakhyā praśnasambhavān |
sotpāta daiva sattvotthaṃ jñātvā durge śubhāśubham ||073:045||
rājayogaṃ samāveśaṃ saṃvatsaramataṃ sphuṭam |
kriyāsādhana siddhyarthaṃ cārabhedagrahasaṃśrayam ||073:046||
sthāna kāla svabhāvākhyaṃ valaṃ mitragṛhāśritam |
raśmijañca tathā cānyadvalānāṃ pravaraṃ valam ||073:047||
vakraiḥ saumyaśataiḥ kuryyād grahai durgapurādikam |
nityañca te grahā dadyurṛá¹ddhiṃ svāmijanasya ca ||073:048||
drekkāṇāśaśiveśa ca navāṃśamudaye śubhe |
triṃśaddvādaśabhāge ca kārayet purakalpanām ||073:049||
krūraḥ krūraṃ vijānīyāt saumyaiḥ saumyaṃ vidhīyate |
tavādi vigrahairvatsa ripumitravivarjjitaiḥ ||073:050||
atītairastulagnaiśca na kuryyāt sanniveśanam ||073:051||
na kīṭāraṇyalagneṣu na ca sandhyāgatai rgrahaiḥ |
puraṃ durgaṃ prakarttavyaṃ śatrukṣetrasamāśritaiḥ ||073:052||
mitrarkṣa mitra sampannaiḥ puṣṭairuccābhilāṣibhiḥ |
svakṣetresvatrikoṇeṣu sthitaiḥ kāryya sadāpuram ||073:053||
durgaṃ durgaṃ samīpasthaṃ tasya mitratrikoṇajaiḥ |
grahaiścandravalopetaiḥ kāryyaṃ sarvvaṃ śubhāvaham ||073:054||
saumye dharmmārthakāmāni śeṣāḥ sthāna samāgatāḥ |
agnidāhaṃ bhayaṃ hāniṃ ripupīḍāṃ sadāratim ||073:055||
āgneyādi vijānīyāt pūrvvadurgo kṛte pure |
nandate pūrvvabhāgasthe īśe dharmmo vivarddhate ||073:056||
sarvvakāmānavāpnoti pūrvveśānottareṇa tu |
saritpūrvvai valopetaiḥ śubhā yāmyena sārataḥ ||073:057||
taḍāgaṃ savanaṃ paścāt saumye cendīvaraṃ dalam |
||073:058ab||
pūjayitvā haraṃ durgāṃ grahān mātṛ vināyakān |
| ||073:058cd||
prāsādoktavidhanena valiṃ datvā kuru puram ||073:058ef||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe puradurgacintājātakriyā nāma trisaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

