%%% Chapter 074
catuḥ saptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

nityo vibhuḥ sthitaḥ kālo avasthā tasya hetunā |
naimittādi viśeṣaistu loke puṇyaphalapradāḥ ||074:001||
saṃkāntyākhya purākhyātaṃ puṇyaṃ dhārā śubhā mune |
grahaṇādiphalaṃ puṃsāṃ tīrthabhedaṃ śṛṇuṣva tat ||074:002||
gaṅgādvāraṃ kurūkṣetraṃ narmmadāmarakaṇṭakam |
yamunāsaṅgamaṃ puṇyaṃ vetravatī vipāśānvitā ||074:003||
sarayuḥ kauśikī vindhyā gaṇḍakī ca sarasvatī |
candrabhāgā mahāpuṇyā nadī godāvarī tathā ||074:004||
kāverī gomatī tāpi devikā varūṇāparā |
etāḥ puṇyatamā nadyo grahaṇādiṣu kīrttitāḥ ||074:005||
anyāśca vahavaḥ puṇyā anyakāle ca kāmadāḥ |
ayane viṣuve khyātī vyatīpāte tathaiva ca |
||074:006||
dinacchidre amāvasyāṃ grahāṇāṃ saṅgameṣu ca |
sanmoheṣu samājeṣu ekarkṣa saptapañcadhā ||074:007||
evaṃvidheṣu parvveṣu candre sarvvakalābhṛte |
tṛtīyāyāñca vaiśākhe aṣṭamyāṃ kujavāsare ||074:008||
caturdaśyacāñca kṛṣṇāyāṃ bhaumāhe pitṛtarpaṇam |
karttavyaṃ sarvvakāmānāṃ pūraṇāya narottamaiḥ ||074:009||
amāvasyāntu saṃkrāntau śivādityantu yo naraḥ |
yajate bhaktimān pūtaḥ sa pūto bhavate mune ||074:010||
[anta ka] there is no reference no. in the text portion, check it.
kārttike grahaṇaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ gaṅgā yamunā saṅgame |
mārgetu grahaṇaṃ puṇyaṃ devikāyāṃ mahāmune ||074:011||
puṣyetu narmmadā puṇyā māghe sannihitā śubhā |
phālgune varūṇā khyātā caitre puṇyā sarasvatī ||074:012||
vaiśākhe ca mahāpuṇyā candrabhāgā saridvarā |
jyeṣṭhe tu kauśikī puṇyā āṣāḍhe bhāvikā nadī ||074:013||
śrāvaṇo sindhunāmāca proṣṭhe śreṣṭhā tu gaṇḍakī |
aśvine sarayuḥ śreṣṭhā bhūyaḥ puṇyā tu narmadā ||074:014||
godāvarī mahāpuṇyā candre rāhusamanvite ||074:015||
sūryye ca śaśinā graste tamorūpe mahāmune |
narmmadā toyasaṃsparśāt kṛtakṛtyā bhavanti te ||074:016||
ye sūryye sehikeyena graste vairājanaṃ narāḥ |
spṛśanti avagāhanti na te prākṛtamānuṣāḥ ||074:017||
snātvā rājakratuṃ lebhe dṛṣṭvā godānajaṃ phalam |
spṛṣṭvā gomedhatulyantu pītvā sautrāmaṇiṃ labhet |
||074:018a-d||
snātvā vājimakhaṃ puṇyaṃ prāpnuyādavicāraṇāt ||074:018ef||
ravicandroparāge tu ayane cottare tathā |
evaṃ gaṅgāpi draṣṭavyā tadvaddevī sarasvatī ||074:019||
śivādityaphalaṃ yacca maṇḍale samudāhṛtam |
sagrahe maṅgalāyoge tadapi prāpnuyānnaraḥ ||074:020||
ūṣarāraṇya-kṣetreṣu puṇyaṃ yat samudāhṛtam |
tadatra kāla māhātmyāduparāge samādhikam ||074:021||
yo vā āhṛtya toyena vidhinā abhiṣecanam |
samantreṇaiva pūtena tasya puṇyaṃ tato'dhikam ||074:022||
ātma vittānusāreṇa pātraistaijasa pārthivaiḥ |
vārkṣaiḥ śailairatha vipra phalaṃ prāpnotyaninditam ||074:023||
ye vā vai mṛttikāṃ tasmiṃstīrthe āhṛtya ca mune |
prātaḥ prātaḥ samutthāya vandayanti narottamāḥ |
||074:024a-d||
te sarvve pāpanirmmuktā bhavanti vigatāmayāḥ ||074:024ef||
phala puṣpopahāreṇa yo vā tasmin ravīśvaram |
snātvā saṃpūjayed vipra sa bhavedvigatāmayaḥ ||074:025||
mantrapūtena toyena kumbhaiḥ puṣpaphalānvitaiḥ |
saphalairvidhinā snātaḥ sarvvakāmāmÌllabheta saḥ ||074:026||
yadevaṃ kathitaṃ puṇyaṃ mayā vrahmamukhācchrutam |
tat samagraṃ bhavet tasya araṇyeṣūṣareṣu ca ||074:027||
araṇyāṇi pravakṣyāmi yathā caivoṣarāṇi ca saindhavaṃ daṇḍakāraṇyaṃ naimiṣaṃ kurūjāṅgalam ||074:028||
upalāvṛtamāraṇyaṃ jambūmārgo'tha puṣkaram |
himavāsastato'raṇye uttamaḥ parikīrttitaḥ ||074:029||
navasveteṣvaraṇyeṣu yastu prāṇān parityajet |
vrahmalokātithirbhūtvā sa yāti paramaṃ padam ||074:030||
karṇiko śiva cākhyeti kālikāgaṇayo śive |
kālañjare mahākāle tulyañcaitiṣu yat phalam ||074:031||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe grahaṇānadyaraṇyayoṣara praśaṃsā nāma catu saptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

