%%%%
%%% Chapter 075
pañcasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

himavaddhemakūṭe ca vindhye mahendra parvvate |
vaidiśe ujjayinye vā mahāsene'tha bhūbhṛte ||075:001||
gopagirau mahāpuṇye citrakūṭe'thavā mune |
kālañjare'thavā kāśyāṃ puṣpākhye veda parvvate ||075:002||
ujjayinyāmayodhyāyāṃ dāpayedatha maheśvare |
eteṣu puṇyadeśeṣu viṣuvāyaṇasaṅgame ||075:003||
puṣkare naimiṣe vatsa deyā pañcamukhe'kṣaye |
girau dhārā pradānena grahapīḍā na jāyate ||075:004||
bahuvakragate dehe vatsavanna bhayaṃ bhavet |
janmādhānarkṣapīḍā vā dattā dhārā vyapohate ||075:005||
[vahni ka ga]
jamvūmārge sadā pūjā dhārāpātaṃ viśiṣyate |
sarvvakāmānavāpnoti narmmadāyāṃ mahāmune ||075:006||
dhārādānena gaṅgāyāṃ kālindyāñca mahāhrade |
dattvā vidhānavihitāṃ na bhayaṃ jāyate kvacit ||075:007||
śanisūryyakṛtāṃ pīḍāṃ gurubhaumāṃ vyapohate |
yathā pūjā vidhānena prati saṃvatsarotthitām ||075:008||
pīḍāṃ nivārayedvatsa saṃvatsaragrahodbhavām |
mantrajāpāt sadā vatsa na bhayaṃ vidyate kvacit ||075:009||
ekānte duṣṭarahite pāpajantu vivarjite |
dhārā homaṃ prakarttavyaṃ yathoktaṃ śriyamicchatā ||075:0010||
jihvāyāṃ pātayeddhārāṃ na drutāṃ na vilamvitām |
sāvadhānena manasā mṛtyuñjaya niyāmitām ||075:011||
mantrayogādbhavet siddhirdṛṣṭādṛṣṭa prasādhikā |
grahapūjā haret pīḍāṃ trividhāmapi utthitām ||075:012||
grahāśca trividhāḥ proktāḥ teṣāṃ mantrāstridhāmatāḥ |
aṅgajā mūlamantrāśca piṇḍāḥ padagatāstathā ||075:013||
homakāle prayoktavyāḥ pūjākāle tathaiva ca |
evaṃ siddhimavāpnoti iha svargāvargikīm ||075:014||
bhāvakāle kriyāyogāddhārāyāṃ labhyate mune ||075:015||
dhārādānaṃ prakarttavyaṃ yantrapātra ghaṭādibhiḥ |
naimitte nityahome ca pūrvaiśca kathito vidhiḥ ||075:016||
iti śrī devī purāṇe nimittadhārāparicchedo nāma pañca saptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[nimitta dhārāparicchedaḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 076
ṣaṭsaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

nārada uvāca |

narmmadāyāṃ mayā tāta śrutaṃ snānaphalodayam |
tīrthayātrā prasaṅgena mārkaṇḍeya-tapāśramam ||076:001||
caturmmukhaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ tathā māheśvaraṃ varam |
āmarākaṃ giriśreṣṭhaṃ devanadyāḥ phalodayam ||076:002||
vāraṇākhyaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ tathā paścima sāgaram |
jaṭā śaile mahādevaṃ pañcamṛtyuvināśanam ||076:003||
gaṅgābhāgyodayaṃ nātha kedāraṃ parvvatottamam |
nandādevī gatandevaṃ mahādevī mahāphalam ||076:004||
naimiṣaṃ puṣkaraṃ devaṃ tathā sthāneśvaraṃ varam |
kurūkṣetraṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ sarvva pāpa praṇāśanam ||076:005||
ghaṭeśvaraṃ mahādevaṃ kaumāraṃ dakṣiṇārṇave |
rāmeśvaraṃ śivaṃ devaṃ vrahmahatyāvināśanam ||076:006||
avimuktañca kāśyākhyāṃ māyāpuryyāṃ sureśvaram |
eva tīrthāni deveśa mahāpuṇyaphalāni ca |
||076:007a-d
śrutāni aghanāśāya śataśo'tha sahasraśaḥ ||076:007ef||
abhiṣeka prasaṅgena kumārasya mahātmanaḥ |
kīrttitaṃ vaidiśe deśe bhṛṅgāraṃ divamuttamam ||076:008||
jambūdvīpasya caiśānyāṃ tasya paścima dakṣiṇe |
vaidiśe cottare bhāge saptagavyūti saṃsthitam |
||076:009a-d||
kuṇḍaṃ śailadvayāsthaṃ ca mahāpuṇyaṃ mahodayam ||076:009ef||
vināyakānāṃ śāntyarthaṃ śakrasya ca mahātmanaḥ |
puṇyābhiṣecanaṃ cakre puṣpadanto gaṇottamaḥ ||076:010||
nandine mṛtyunāśāya śatasāhasramuttamam |
laḍaḍukānāṃ dadau yatra tat tīrthaṃ kathaya prabho |
||076:011a-d||
lokānāṃ hitakāmāya kalau pāpapraṇāśanam ||076:011ef||
brahmovāca |

śṛṇu vatsa pravakṣyāmi yanmāṃ tvaṃ paripṛcchasi |
hitāya sarvvalokānāṃ sarvvapāpaśamāya ca ||076:012||
puṣpadanto gaṇopetastapastapyet sudārūṇam |
puṣpakāntaṃ giriṃ vatsa aṅgāreśasya jāyate ||076:013||
yatrāṇḍajaḥ purā magno gato devapuraṃ mune |
tasya nāmnā samākhyātaṃ tīrthaṃ pāpapraṇāśanam ||076:014||
tasmāduddhṛtya yastoyaṃ śivaliṅgābhiṣecanam |
karoti sa pumān vatsa sarvva kāmānavāpnuyāt ||076:015||
mayāpi tatra deveśaḥ sthāpitaścottareṇa tu |
viṣṇunā nirmmaleśastu paścime gurūṇā param ||076:016||
dakṣiṇena tathā devaṃ kujena īśagocare |
mātṛṇāṃ maṇḍalaṃ yatra nandinā pūjitaṃ purā ||076:017||
anye'pi ye mahādevaṃ carccikāṃ vā mahodayām ||076:018||
bhānuṃ nārāyaṇaṃ vatsa maṅgalāntena cāmbhasā |
snāpayanti mahābhāgā na te prākṛtamānuṣāḥ ||076:019||
ye punaścarccikāṃ kṛtvā prastarādi samudbhavān |
tathā ye cābhiṣiñcanti te labhante hitaṃ phalam ||076:020||
maṅgalā rūpiṇī devī mātṛbhiḥ parivāritā |
vrāhmādyā dakṣiṇe kāryyā vaiṣṇavyādyāstathottare ||076:021||
vrahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśca prabhāmaṇḍala saṃsthitāḥ |
kumāraṃ gaṇanāthañca grahān pīṭhādhaḥsaṃsthitān ||076:022||
evaṃ kṛtvā muniśreṣṭha yatra tatrejitā śivā |
prayacchati paraṃ lokaṃ puṣpāṅke ubhayātmakam ||076:023||
tatra bhāvānurupeṇa mṛccitrā dhātu vārkṣajāḥ |
kṛtvā yastena toyena snāpayet svāmātmanaḥ ||076:024||
jayahomarato dhyānī bhikṣāśī atha kṣīrathaḥ |
ekāntareṇa bhaktena upavāsa ayācitaiḥ ||076:025||
sa labheta hitān kāmān yadā gūḍhavrato bhavet vidyā japtena toyena ayutaṃ vā prayacchati ||076:026||
śivāyāḥ saṃbhaved vatsa sarvvapāpavivarjjitaḥ |
devyāḥ putraḥ sadā loke darśanāccāgha nāśanam ||076:027||
kalaśā hemadhātūtthā mṛnmayā vā sulakṣaṇāḥ loka kumbha caturthāṃśāḥ karttavyāḥ snāpanā śivāḥ ||076:028||
gṛhe ṣoḍaśabhāgena japadhyānaratasya ca |
āyāryyasya sadā vatsa homayuktiḥ prakīrttitā ||076:029||
nārada uvāca |

vidyāhaṃ śrotumicchāmi sarvvapāpa praṇāśinīm |
yathā snānaṃ prakarttavyaṃ devī devasya vā vibho ||076:030||
brahmovāca |

kathayāmi muniśreṣṭha na deyā adīkṣite kvacit |
vidyā mṛtyunjayā nāma daśāvaraṇasaṃstutā ||076:031||
vrāhmaṇaḥ ṣaṣṭha varṇena viṣṇunāḥ pacaṃma tathā |
vājyanāda vilomantu tena tat bhedayenmune ||076:032||
dvitīyaṃ bhavate varṇa viṣṇu varṇacaturthaṃ tathā |
vrahama paṃcamasaṃyuktaṃ tṛtīyaṃ parikīrtitam ||076:033||
vāyuvarṇa gata varṇa savisargantu paṃcamam |
caturthaḥ kīrtitaṃ vatsa sarvvakāma samṛddhaye ||076:034||
[pravūrdhine ga]
vedāḍhyo matimantrasthā vidyā sāvākhyarā mune |
sakṛduccaritā vatsa mṛtyuhā vidhinā bhavet ||076:035||
anayā snāpitā devī sarvvakāmān prayacchati |
yāge vā rudrake yājyā padme vā grahanāśinī ||076:036||
pratyanugaṃ ṣaṭkaṃtu dvayakṣaraṃ prathamaṃ hṛdi |
homaṃ samastamuccārya kāryaṃ svāhāṃtikaṃ sadā ||076:037||
[saṃjñaku ka]
nārada uvāca |

kalaśānāṃ pramāṇantu japahomena kīrtitam |
dineṣu keṣu karttavyaṃ kathayasva prasādataḥ ||076:038||
mārkanḍeya muniśreṣṭha purāṇe samudāhṛtam |
narmaṃdāyāṃ sarasvatyāstairdānakṣe mune'tra tu ||076:039||
cartudaśyāmamāvaśyā8maṣṭamyāṃ navamī tathā |
dvādaśyāṃ paurṇamāsyānca saṃkrāntau grahaṇādiṣu ||076:040||
vyatīpāte dinacchidre caitrādiṣu ca parvvaṣu |
māsānte ṛtūvarṣānte gūrumandadineṣu ca ||076:041||
teṣāṃ saptamayogeṣu kratuvede karoti vā |
saptamyāṃ sopavāsena aṣṭamyāṃ pūjanaṃ mahat ||076:042||
japahomaṃ prakarttavyaṃ pūjayitvā tu maṃgalām |
kṣīrasnānantu yaḥ kṛtvā kunḍatoyena snāpayet ||076:043||
kūmkumāgūrukarpūramadena ca vilepayet |
sugandhadhūpanaivedya vāsāṃsi srajadarpaṇam ||076:044||
dattā devyāstataḥ pūjāṃ sarvvakāmānavāpnuyāt |
īhaloke bhaveddhanyo dhanapūtrāyu saṃyuta ||076:045||
dehānte śivaloke tu modate cottamaṃ sukham |
evaṃ ca vidhinā devīṃ mantra pūtena vāriṇā ||076:046||
snātvā snāpayate vipra sa bhavedamaravallabhaḥ |
yathā vayaṃ yathā viṣṇuryathā devo maheśvaraḥ ||076:047||
tathā saṃpūjanīyaste avicāreṇa bhāvitaḥ |
tatrastā devatāḥ sarvā kunḍe santarpitā surāḥ ||076:048||
pitṛṇāṃ bhavate prītistajjabalane anuttamā |
yastatra kurūte śrāddhaṃ snātvā pātraviśeṣataḥ ||076:049||
sa kṛtvā daśa varṣāṇi tena santarpitā pitṛn |
datvā dānaṃ tathā koṭi guṇaṃ phalamavāpnuyāt ||076:050||
japa homa phalaṃ tatra anaṃtaṃ bhavate kṛtam gavyūtimātraṃ smṛtaṃ kṣetraṃ sarvapāpa praṇāśanam ||076:051||
athottaraṃ viśeṣena madīya śiva sannidhau yātrākāle purāvṛttamitihāsaṃ nivodhata ||076:052||
vetravatyāstaṭe ramye vaṭavṛkṣo mahāmune |
tatra kapota saṃghānāṃ rājā āsīnmahān dvijaḥ ||076:053||
vaidiśe vrahmahā vatsa suhṛt strī vālaghātakaḥ |
mahākarma vipākena duṣkṛtena ca āvṛtaḥ ||076:054||
nānāyonigataḥ pāpī kathaṃcit pāpaparyayāt |
mṛto dehaṃ gataṃ tasya dhātrī bhūtaṃ suparṇavata ||076:055||
tena pakṣī bhavedrājā sa kapota śatāvṛtā |
kālena sa gataḥ śrutvā puṣpākhyaṃ giri parvatam ||076:056||
tatra kunḍa gate vṛkṣaṃ samārūhya sakhīvṛtaḥ |
krīḍamāno'patat toye paṃcatvamupagatañca saḥ ||076:057||
vidhūta pāpamajjantu saṃbhūtaḥ sa śuko muniḥ ||076:058||
śukī garbhe mahāvāho sarvaṃśāstrārtha pāragaḥ |
devī pūjārato vatsa devasnānarataḥ sadā ||076:059||
karma yajña samāyogāddevalokaṃ gataśca saḥ |
śivaṃ lokaṃ samāsādya śivavanmodate sukhī ||076:060||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe kapotakīrttanaṃ nāma ṣaṭsaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye kapota kīrttanaṃ ka ga]


%%%%

%%% Chapter 077
saptasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

sarve śivāśramāḥ puṇyā sarvvapāpa praṇāśanāḥ |
sarvasnānopavāsādi phaladā bhavate nṛṇām ||077:001||
anārādhya nṛpaṃ yadvat bhūtiḥ puṣṭirnaṃ labhyate |
asaṃpūjya śivaṃ vipra tadvat puṇyaṃ na prāpyate ||077:002||
[puṃbhiḥ na prāpyate ga]
viśeṣeṇa kalau ghore kṛṣṇarūpe tamovṛte |
kiṃ dvijāḥ śivapotantu tena pāraṃ bhavārṇavāt ||077:003||
[paṃktiriyaṃ ka pustake nāsti]
gacchanti snāpakāḥ puṇyā laḍḍūkādi pradānataḥ |
yastu liṃgākṛtiṃ kṛtvā gṛhe vā bhāvanāyutaḥ ||077:004||
[gaṃḍukādi ga; bhāvanārataḥ kha]
laḍḍūkādi pradānaṃ tu karoti satataṃ dvijaḥ sa gacchati śivaṃ lokamanaupamyaṃ manoramam ||077:005||
[gaṃḍukādi ka]
sadā vibhava saṃpannaḥ sarvadvandva vivarjitaḥ |
tatrasthaḥ sukhasampannaḥ krīḍate vividhaiḥ suravaiḥ ||077:006||
devīrūpo haro vatsa viṣṇurdevā vayaṃ tathā |
sarvarūpī mahābhāgā sūryasya ripunāśinī ||077:007||
[devībhayaṃ ka ga]
nāgarājarūpiṇī devī gorūpā carcikāmbikā |
mātarā bhāvagā vatsa nārāyaṇī tathā matā ||077:008||
[nāga vā ga |
nāgara ḍū kha]
mahāśvetā mahādevī ripuhā sūryasannidhau |
sarvagā sarvadevānāṃ varadā sarvato jitā ||077:009||
[māheśvarī ka kha]
trimūrttistriguṇā devī trivedā tripadā dhṛtiḥ |
trikalā triśubhā śakti triśūlā śūlarūpiṇī ||077:010||
vyaktāvyaktākṛtiṃ kṛtvā hemarūpya mayī śubhām |
triśūle pūjayedvatsa snātvā kāpotavāriṇā ||077:011||
[śivām kha]
candanāgurū gandhāḍhyāṃ srajadhūpa sudhūpitām |
sakṛddṛṣṭvā śubhaṃ hanyāt sapta janma kṛtaṃ mune ||077:012||
[puṣyā ka]
pūrvoktā ye mahātīrthā teṣāmekatamo'pi vā |
māyā puryāñca vā kāśyāṃ jambumārge'tha naimiṣe ||077:013||
[mayā ka]
nivasan pūjayeddevīṃ sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt |
dvijo muṃḍī śikhī vāpi yatra tatra vyavasthitaḥ ||077:014||
maṃtra japyārccanāsakto homāt sarvamavāpnuyāt |
tilājyāhuti dānāni devī kuṃḍena bhāvataḥ ||077:015||
[padyamidaṃ kha pustake nāsti; bharataḥ ga]
hutaṃ hutaṃ payo vatsa satataṃ labhate phalam |
potaṃ na vāplavaṃ khyātaṃ pāpakarma śubhaṃ matam ||077:016||
[yota nā vāyu ga]
tatra vā bhārate lokān kapotantu na dhāvati |
|
[vātārate ga]
oṃm vyoma vyāpine vyomarūpāya |
om sarvavyāpine śivāya |

anantāya anāthāya anāśritāya bhavāya ca |
śāśvatāya yogapīṭhasaṃsthitāya nityaṃ yogine dhyānāhārāya |
|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya śarvāya bhavaśivāya namaḥ |
somamūrdhni tatpurūṣāya |
aghora hṛdayāya namaḥ |
|
vāmadevaguhyāya sadmo jātamūrttaye |
namo guhyāti guhyāya goptre nidhanāya namaḥ |
|
sarvavidyādhipati jyotirūpāya parameśvarāya namaḥ |
acetana acetana vyoma vyoma arūpa arūpa pramatha pramatha teja teja |

[prathama prathama reja reja kha]
jyoti jyoti anākṣa anākṣa cetana cetana nānā nānā dhū dhū dhū dhū |

[anadya anadya ka |
anātma anātma kha]
oṃ bhūrbhuvaḥ svaḥ
anidhana nidhane bhava śiva śarva paramātmane |
maheśvara mahādeva sat bhāveśvara mahātejaḥ |

[sarvva ka ga]
