|
sarvaṃsānnidhya-kara brahmaviṣṇu rudra para arcita |
asaṃstuta |
pūrvasthita pūrvasthita,
nākṣi nākṣi, kṣarū kṣarū, |
pataṃga pataṃga, piṃga piṃgā, saṃga saṃga, sūkṣma sūkṣma |

śiva sarvāya sarvapataye namaḥ |
oṃ namaḥ |
oṃ namo namaḥ ||077:017||
[śivāya ka ga]
śivāya oṃ namo namaḥ |
śiva bhaṭṭāraka āyāhi śiva sarvadā atra sannidhiṃ kurū |

tvidamaṃ adhiṣṭhāyādhiṣṭhāya śāntaṃ śāntatamam |
oṃ namo nama svāhā vyomavyāpī |
īśvarāya maṃtraḥ |

tataḥ paṃca brahmāṇi sarvātmā svaśivam |

[ataḥ paraṃ yadrahmāṇi ka]
jvālinī piṃgalāstraṃ aghorāstram |

[ka ga pustake nāsti]
śivāṃgāni vidyādhipati brahma śivā rudrāṇī puruṣṭutaṃ pāśupatāstram |

yoga vidyāṃgāni yoga vidyāṃgāni vibhurjñānī kriyācarī vāgeśī jvālinī vāmādyāḥ śaktayaḥ ||077:018||
vighneśvarā gaṇeśvarāḥ lokapālāḥ vajrādyastrāḥ |
anantādyāḥ nāgāḥ |
sūryādyā grahāḥ |

jambhādyāḥ bālagrahāḥ |
devādyā devagrahāḥ |

śivādyāścitrādyā viśvādyāḥ śiva uccārakaparivārāḥ ||077:019||
oṃ namo hiraṇyavarṇāya hiraṇyaretase namo namaḥ |
hiraṇya pataye namaḥ umāpataye namaḥ svāhā oṃm ||077:020||
eṣa maṃtraḥ |

daśātmā vyoma vyāpī oṃ āṃ īṃ ūṃ vyāṃ rāṃ lāṃ bāṃ kṣam |
paramadaśādyā vidyāṃga śivāṃgāśca parāparavikalpanāḥ |

[daśātmā kha]
mudrādarśanaṃ pūrvaṃ gaṃdhadhūpa puṣpanaivedyārgha japa homa vidhiḥ ||077:021||
maṃgalā nandinī bhadrā lakṣmīḥ kīrttiryaśasvinī |
sarvamaṃgalāyā maṃtrapūjāvidhānaṃ likhyate |

[śloko'yaṃ nāsti kha pustake]
puṣṭirmedhā śivā sādhvī yaśā śobhā jayā dhṛtiḥ ||077:022||
ānandā ca svanandā devyāḥ svoṃ'śa kīrttitaḥ |
ekaikena tu varṇena devyo mudrāśca darśayet ||077:023||
īśānyādīni deyāni svāyudhāni yathāvidhiḥ |
yonimudrā liṃgamudrā vyāpinī chatraṃ ghaṇṭāṃ madhum ||077:024||
kheṭakaṃ ca śūlacakṣuṃ pāśaṃ khaḍgaṃ śaraṃ dhanuḥ |
vīṇā padma śaṃkhamudrāstā ṣoḍaśakā bhavanti ||077:025||
maṃtrapadāni |

oṃ kāli kāli vajreśvari lauha daṇḍādye ṭhaṃ ṭhaṃ |
mūla maṃtraḥ ||077:026||
oṃ kāli kāli ṭhaṃ ṭhaṃ hṛdayam |
oṃ kāli kāli vajriṇiṃ śiraḥ |
oṃ kālīśvari śikhā |

oṃ kālī vajreśvari kavacam |
oṃ kāli kāli lauhadaṇḍāyai astram ||077:027||
mūla maṃtraṃ netraḥ
[ka pustake nāsti]
anena nyāsa |
paṃca brahmāṇī sarvamaṃgalamaṃgalyeti paścāt kṣamāpayet ||077:028||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyāyogavidhānaṃ nāma saptasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[trailokyābhyudaye devyā yogavidhānam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 078

aṣṭasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manurūvāca |

ataḥ paraṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ sarva kāma prasādhakam |
brahmaṇā sanakādīnāṃ bhaktyā pratipāditam ||078:001||
tadahaṃ saṃpravakṣyāmi vratānāṃ pravaraṃ vratam |
sarva lokopakārāpa śṛṇuṣvāvahito dvija ||078:002||
upavāsātparaṃ bhaikṣyaṃ bhaikṣyātparamayācitam |
ayācitātparaṃ naktaṃ tasmānnaktena varttayet ||078:003||
devaistu bhuktaṃ pūrvāhne madhyāhne ṛṣibhistathā |
aparāhne pitṛbhirbhuktaṃ saṃdhyāyāṃ guhyākādibhiḥ ||078:004||
sarvavelāmatikramya nakte bhuktamabhojanam |
vāmācāro mahādevo naktenordhvarate pumān ||078:005||
[vāmacārī mahādevī ka]
haviṣyaṃ bhojanaṃ snānaṃ satyamāhāralāghavam |
agnikāryamadhaḥ śayyā naktabhojī samāharet ||078:006||
[samācaret ka]
evaṃ vidhiḥ sadācāro devadevī prapūjakaḥ |
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ prayatnena kṛtvā naktaṃ vidhānataḥ ||078:007||
māsasya mārga śīrṣasya śaṃkaraṃ deva marcayet |
pītvā śaktyā ca gomūtramanāhāro niśi svapet ||078:008||
[hyevam kha; śāṃtvā ka]
atirātrasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet |
evaṃ pauṣe'pi saṃpūjya śaṃbhunāmānamīśvaram ||078:009||
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ ghṛtaṃ prāśya vājapeyāṣṭakaṃ labhet |
māghe maheśvaraṃ nāma kṛṣmāṣṭamyāṃ prapūjayet ||078:010||
niśi pītvā tu gokṣīraṃ gomedhāṣṭakamāpnuyāt |
phālgune ca mahādevaṃ sampūjya prāśayettilān ||078:011||
[ati maṃtrasya yajñasya kha]
rājasūyasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet |
caitre tu sthāṇunāmānaṃ kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ prapūjayet ||078:012||
yavāmÌśca bharjitānadyāt so'śvamedhaphalaṃ labhet |
vaiśākhe śivanāmānamiṣṭvā rātrau kuśodakam ||078:013||
[yāvāśca bhūrjitān ka]
pītvā puruṣamedhasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet |
jyeṣṭhe paśupatiṃ pūjya gavāṃ śṛṃgodakaṃ pivet ||078:014||
gavāṃ koṭipradānasya yatpuṇyaṃ tadavāpnuyāt |
āṣāḍhe cogranāmānaṃ paṃcagavyaṃ tu prāśayet ||078:015||
sautrāmaṇi sahasrasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet |
śrāvaṇe śarva nāmānamiṣṭvārkaṃ niśi bhakṣayet ||078:016||
[śloka catuṣṭayaṃ nāsti kha pustake]
varṣa koṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ rudraloke mahīyate |
māse bhādrapade'ṣṭamyāṃ tryambakaṃ nāma pūjayet ||078:017||
prāśanambilvapatrāṇāṃ maṃtradīkṣā phalaṃ labheta |
īśvaramāśvayuje māsi pūjyānte tanḍulodakam ||078:018||
[madva ka]
pauṇḍarīkasya yajñasyaphalamāṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet |
||078:019ab||
[yajñasya protumaṣṭāṃ ka]
kārttike rudranāmānaṃ saṃpūjya prāśayeddadhi |
||078:019cd||
agniṣṭomasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labheta ||078:019ef||
varṣānte bhojayedviprān kanyakā abalāstathā |
pāyasaṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktaṃ madhunā saṃpariplutam ||078:020||
śaktyā hiraṇyavāsānsi bhaktyā temyo nivedayet |
nivedayīta rudrāya gāñca kṛṣṇāṃ payasvinīm ||078:021||
varṣamekaṃ caredbhaktyā nairantaryeṇa yo naraḥ |
kṛṣṇāṣṭamī vrataṃ bhaktyā tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu ||078:022||
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ sarvaiśvarya samanvitaḥ |
vasecchivapure divyaṃ na cehāyāti karhicit ||078:023||
puṇyeṣveteṣu sarveṣu viṣuvad grahaṇādiṣu |
dānopavāsa homādyamakṣayaṃ jāyate kṛtam ||078:024||
iti śrī devī purāṇe kṛṣṇāṣṭamīvrataṃ nāmāṣṭasaptatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devīpurāṇe kṛṣṇāṣṭamībratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 079
ekonāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

gaurī kālī umā bhadrā durgā kāntiḥ sarasvatī |
maṃgalā vaiṣṇavī lakṣmīḥ śivā nārāyaṇī kramāt ||079:001||
mārgatṛtīyāmāramya pūrvoktaṃ labhate phalam |
||079:002ab|| ardhanārīśvaraṃ rudramathavā umāśaṃkaram |
||079:002cd||
pūjayedvidhivannārī na viyogamavāpnuyāt ||079:002ef||
athavā viṣṇurūpeṇa pūjayecceśvaraṃ sadā |
śaṃkaraṃ vāmabhāgasthaṃ sarvvakāmamavāpnuyāt ||079:003||
[śaṃkare ka]
mārgaśirādau keśava nārāyaṇa mādhavān pūjayet |
dhūpa sragdīpādyairupoṣya sampūjya dakṣiṇābhi rnāmabhiḥ ||079:004||
[umārdha śivādhāṃn ka ga]
aśvamedha nṛpasūyavājapeyamatirātra uktamathāgniṣṭhomo gavāṃmedhaḥ puruṣamedha sautrāmaṇi |

pañcayajñā hemagolakṣaṃ sarve makhā sthāpyante nityaṃ smaraṇārccanāt nāma dvādaśī ||079:005||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe nāmadvādaśī |

[ityādyena mahādaśī ka]
manuruvāca |

yadīcchati śubhaṃ nārī īhajanme paratra ca |
tadā kuryāddvija śreṣṭha viṣṇunā kathitaṃ bratam ||079:001||
[śubhān ga]
sarvvapāraharaṃ puṇyaṃ sarvvakāma phalapradam |
umāmaheśvaraṃ nāma karttavyaṃ vidhinā yathā ||079:002||
prauṣṭhāśvine'thavā māghe bhāgye mṛge'thavā mune |
maitre śākre'thavā kāryamaṣṭamyāṃ vātha śāṃkare ||079:003||
[māse mṛge kha; vakre kha]
pūrve'hani saptanīkaṃ dāmpatyaṃ sukhasaṃgatam |

ekabhāryaṃ naraṃ vatsa sarvadharmabratānvitam |
āmantryamamaromeśaṃ prātaḥ kāryamanugraham ||079:004||
mudānvitastadā kuryāt kali dvandva vivarjitaḥ |
madhu cānnena bhojyaṃ tu kṣīrejya yavaśālijam ||079:005||
sitaślakṣe tathā rakte śubhe kārye tu vāsasī |
na keśe sa deśe vatsa devadevīprasādake ||079:006||
[śubhamaṃgalam ga]
snātvā umeśvaraṃ pūjyaṃ sthaṇḍile pratimāsu vā |
hutvā diśo baliṃ dattvā vitānāvatha kārayet ||079:007||
caturasraṃ cat rdvāraṃ gomayenopalipyate |
catuṣkaṃ śāligodhūmai rvarṇakairupaśobhyate ||079:008||
dīpamālānvitaṃ kṛtvā dāmpatyaṃ bhojayet tataḥ |
śaṃkaromāṃ sadādhyāya śakrādyaṃ śubhacarcitam ||079:009||
[site śukle ga]
madacandana kāśmīra karpūrāgurudhūpitam |
jātī punnāgamandāra śatapatrekṣumālitam ||079:010||
kṣamāpya yugmaṃ saṃvītaṃ tridhā kṛtvā pradakṣiṇam |
sukhālāpena sampūjya dhyāyantī tamumeśvaram ||079:011||
ācamyārdhyapādyaṃ te dadayāt gaṃgodakaṃ tathā |
sahiraṇyaṃ saratnaṃ ca punardattvā kṣamāpayet ||079:012||
[pātraṃ ga; gaṃdhodakam ga]
prīyatāṃ me umeśaṃ tu sarvadevapatiṃ patim |
anena prāpnuyānnārī aviyogaṃ sureśvara ||079:013||
saubhāgyamihajanme'pi putra rājyasuravāni ca |
mṛtā yāti paraṃ sthānaṃ śaṃkaromā adhiṣṭhitam ||079:014||
[dhana ga]
tatra bhogān mahān bhuktvā cehāyātā mahākule |
samṛddhaṃ vṛddhisampanne patiṃ vindati śobhanam ||079:015||
lāvaṇyarupasampannā bhartuḥ śreṣṭhā sadā bhavet |
ślāghanīyā samastasya vibhavāntaḥ purasya ca ||079:016||
[bhāgya śreṣṭhā ka]
suputrā jīvavatsā ca ādhivyādhivivarjjitā |
bhuktvā yathepsitān kāmān vṛddhatve patipūrvikām ||079:017||
divaṃ yāti suraśreṣṭha śaṃkaromārccikā striyaḥ |
naro vānena vidhinā nārīnāṃ bhavate patiḥ ||079:018||
[nārāyaṇena ka]
samṛddhaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ patitvamupagacchati |
śaṃkaromāvrataṃ śakra lakṣmyā pūrvamanuṣṭhitam ||079:019||
ratyā devyā arundhatyā rohiṇyā surasattama |
kṛtamāsīt sukhārthantu tāśca bhuñjanti tatphalam ||079:020||
umāmantreṇa comeśaṃ īśamantreṇa śaṃkarīm |
pūjitā sarvvakāmāni prayacchatyavicāraṇāt ||079:021||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe umāmaheśvara vratam |

[umāmaheśvara v tam ka ga]
indra uvāca |

kathitaṃ śaṃkaromākhyaṃ brataṃ me manatuṣṭidam |
śrotumicchāmyahaṃ tāta viṣṇu śaṃkara saṃjñitam ||079:001||
manuruvāca |

yathā umeśvaraṃ tāta tathā kāryamidaṃ vratam |
kintu pītāni vāsāṃsi keśavāya prakalpayet ||079:002||
gandhaṃ puṣpaṃ tathā dhūpaṃ sugandhañca janārdane |
kāryaṃ pūjānusadbhāvaṃ laḍaḍūkā dadhipāyasam ||079:003||
[śaṃkaram ga]
evaṃ tau pūjayitvā tu pratimau sthaṇḍile'pi vā |
āhūya brāhmaṇau vatsa veda siddhāntapāragau ||079:004||
yatī vā vratasampannau jaṭā kāṣāyadhāriṇau |
pūjayitvā vidhānena śūlapāṇi-janārdanau ||079:005||
[bhojayedvidhānena ga]
kṣamāpya vidhinā vatsa sarvvakāmaprasādhakau |
hemaṃ tu dakṣiṇāṃ viṣṇo rmoktikaṃ śaṃkarāya ca ||079:006||
dattvā pravajato loko kramāddehakṣaye brajet |
||079:007ab||
[dattvā'nuprapatau ka]
bhuktvā bhogāmÌstathā śakra ihāyāto nṛpeśvaraḥ ||079:007cd||
kule bhavati bhūpālaḥ sukhaputrāyusaṃyutaḥ ||079:007ef||
pūrvabhāvād bhavedbhaktiḥ śivaviṣṇuprasādhakī |
yogaṃ prāpya paraṃ yāti yattu sthānamanāmayam ||079:008||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe śaṃkara nārāyaṇavratam |

[śaṃkara nārāyaṇa bratam ka ga]
anenaiva vidhinā kāryaṃ lakṣmī nārāyaṇabrataṃ |
||079:001ab||
[lakṣmīparṇāṃ v tama kha]
brahma gāyatryajaṃ tāta candrarohiṇyajaṃ pivā |
||079:001cd||
[sāvitrājaṃ kha]
bhāvavittānu rupeṇasattva mātraphalaṃ labhet ||079:001ef||
[satya ka ga]
śakra uvāca |

sammārjanaphalaṃ deva sūcitaṃ prakīrttitam |
tadahaṃ śrotumicchāmi mānavānāṃ hitāya vai ||079:002||
īśvara uvāca |

vārāhe tu purā kalpe mano raivatake tathā |
tasminnāsīt mahīpāla candra mitra nṛpottama ||079:003||
[kāle kha; candramindre nṛpottame kha ga]
patnī ca kuṃkumā nāma ayutaṃ traya cotta mā |
lāvaṇyarupasampannā candrakāntisamaprabhā ||079:004||
[śataprabhā ga]
sānudinaṃ sadā bhaktyā devyāḥ sammārjane ratā |
dvāra śobhāṃ pathiśobhāṃ devyāmuddiśya kārayet ||079:005||
saprapaccha tadārājñīṃ kimetaddevi tvaṃ sadā |
sammārjanaparā nityamanyakarma parāṅamukhā |
etanno brūhi tattvena rāja rupaṃ patipriyā ||079:006||
kuṃkumovāca |

na hi me'styaparā bhaktiryathā saṃmārjjane śṛṇu |
tathāhaṃ kathayiṣyāmi purākarmma kṛtaṃ mayā ||079:007||
pūrvamāsaṃ hyahaṃ vilvā patantī viyaccāriṇī |
tatrāhaṃ bhramamāṇā tu gatā kiṣkindhyaparvatam ||079:008||
tatra devī nirādhārā hyākāśe tiṣṭhate sadā |
kenāpi pūjane dattaṃ bhaktaṃ pātraṃ supūjitam (FN)||079:009||
[mahā ga; supūritam ka gapustakenāsti |
]
mayāpi kramamādāya gṛhītumudyamaḥ kṛtaḥ |
kramānnataṃ gṛhītantu pakṣaiḥ pāṃśu nivāritā ||079:010||
[bhūmamādāya ga]
pūrṇadattakramānneva grahītuṃ pāṃśu mārjjitā |
tāvat tasmin samāyātaḥ pūjako devalo dvijaḥ ||079:011||
vayaṃ naṣṭā bhayāt kālānmṛtā jātā vasorgṛhe |
candramitrasya tenaiva dattāhaṃ prathamā vadhūḥ ||079:012||
[vayaṃ vasumapā kālāt ka]
rājñī triṃśatsahasrānāmabhūdahaṃ tatprabhāvataḥ |
akāmā devatāgāre pakṣapātasya mārjjanāt ||079:013||
tena rājñī ceyaṃ yātā kāmān sammārjjanena kim |
phalaṃ bhavati yaddevyā tanna vedmi yathācyatām ||079:014||
evaṃ pūrvvaṃ kathecchambhu rbhārgavasya prapṛcchataḥ |
||079:015ab||
brahmaṇā devarājasya mayāpi ca tavākhilam ||079:015cd||
kathitaṃ jīrṇa saṃskāre sammārjanaphalaṃ nṛpa ||079:015ef||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe sammārjjanamāhātmyaṃ nāma ekonāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye sammārjana mahātyama ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 080
aśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

vidyeśvara uvāca |

[viśveśvara uvāca ka]
kathaṃ devyāḥ sadā pūjā tadbhaktai rgṛhapālakaiḥ |
karttavyā siddhimicchadbhiḥ dṛṣṭādṛṣṭaphalārthibhiḥ ||080:001||
agastya uvāca |

sādhvidaṃ yattvayā praśnaṃ kṛtaṃ vatseśvarapriyam (FN)| tadahaṃ nikhilaṃ vakṣye tava bhaktasya vidyayā ||080:002||
[ka pustake nāsti |
]
devyā bhaktaiḥ sadā devī sarvagā sarvasaṃśritā |
dṛṣṭavyā nāgagulmeṣu tṛṇapakṣisarīsṛpe ||080:003||
[sarvasaṃstutā ga]
dvija-anttyaja jātiṣu duḥkhiteṣu sukheṣu ca |
sūkṣmāsūkṣma viśiṣṭeṣu surabhīṣvasurabhīṣu ca(FN) ||080:004||
[ga pustake nāsti |
]
na kruṣṭaḥ krodhamāgacchenna ca pūjā sukṛṣyate |
tṛṇa hema viśeṣeṇa na lobho na ca kāmitā ||080:005||
paradāra parasvādervācyā manakarmabhiḥ |
yasya notsahate rājan tasya devī na dūrataḥ ||080:006||
bhūṣito'pi varaṃ devaṃ kiṃ vane nivasan nṛpaḥ |
sakāmenaiva siddhiḥ syānniṣkāmasya gṛhaṃ vanam ||080:007||
[gṛhe balam kha |
tṛṇaṃ dhanam ga |
]
yastu sarvvaprajāpālaḥ sarvavarṇāśramejyakaḥ |
svena vartmani varttteta sa durgāṃ śakyamījitum ||080:008||
[dharmani ga |
]
rājovāca |

yadyevaṃ varṇajātīnāṃ devī sarvatra saṃsthitā |
tadahaṃ śrotumicchāmi āśramāṇāṃ ca pālanam ||080:009||
[kānanam kha |
pelanam ga |
]
agastya uvāca |

pūrva devena brahmāya śūlinā kathitā kila |
śrutā te manudakṣādyai-rbhṛgumitro'tha kāśyapaiḥ ||080:010||
tathā mayāpi tebhyaśca yathā prāptā tathā tava |
kathayāmi mahārāja devyā bhaktiparo bhavān ||080:011||
yathā āsītpurā rājan mahākalpe narādhipaḥ |
tathā pālaya prajāḥ sarvvā sve sve dharme vyavasthitā ||080:012||
[surāḍ priyaḥ kha sudhādhipaḥ ga]
tasya rājasya devendraḥ pṛcchate garuḍadhvajam |
rakṣaṇāya samastasya divyasya sa hite rataḥ ||080:013||
praṇamya taṃ jagannāthaṃ viṣṇu kamalalocanam |
prapṛcchati samastasya brahmādyasya ci kāraṇam ||080:014||
śakra uvāca |

jayānantu mahābāho sarvadevanamaskṛta |
ekamūrttistrimūrttistu pītavāso jagatpriyaḥ ||080:015||
sarvvavyāpi mahākāya sthalabhāvānucārakaḥ |
parāvara parāvastu kāraṇātman namo namaḥ ||080:016||
[āmubhava ga]
prakṛtisthaṃ ca bhāveśa vikṛtikhyayaḥ prabhuḥ |
cintyācintyaprameyaśca kālakālanahetavaḥ ||080:017||
dharmādharmamahābhāga bhāvābhāvanamo namaḥ |
mahadādi guṇāvāsa sarvaguṇavivarjitaḥ ||080:018||
[mahāmāpa ga]
śrūyase stavase tvañca vedase vedako bhavān |
sampūjyase pūjako nātha sarvagaḥ sarvakṛtti bhūḥ ||080:019||
[sarvakṣatprabhu ga sarvakṛtprabhuḥ ka]
avināśa vināśitve pārthivādiprayojane |
tvaṃ bhavān kāraṇābhāva parāpara namostu te ||080:020||
hṛṣīkeśa gadādhārin mahādanukulāntaka |
mahāgadāsidhārāya pṛcchāmi jagaddhetave ||080:021||
[ga jahe tave ga]
evaṃ stutastadā rājan viṣṇuḥ provāca yācyatām |
yat te manasi vartteṃta dadāmi brūhi vāsava ||080:022||
śakra uvāca |

bhagavan rki parā bhaktiḥ kasya vā kriyate sadā |
kasmin dvīpe sthitau puṃbhiryaṣṭavyā sā parāparā ||080:023||
śrī bhagavānuvāca |

ekasmin me dine śakra brahmā yānti caturdaśa |
tisṛṇāṃ tvaṃ ca tatsaṃkhyā brahmāhena purandara ||080:024||
evaṃ varṣa śate pūrṇe yoganidrā parāparā |
tasmina līlayāmyahaṃ śakra punaretat sṛjāmi ca ||080:025||
evaṃ te ca dināḥ pakṣāḥ māsārttava tathāyane |
sa te kālaṃ ca kalpaṃ ca mahākalpaṃ tathaiva ca ||080:026||
bhavate sṛjate śakra yā sā paramakāriṇī |
yoganidrā mahāmāyā sarvādyā na vyavasthitā ||080:027||
[paramakāraṇa ka]
sthāpitā parameśena yasmin kāle taducyatām |
||080:028ab||
labdhaṃ triṃśat sahasrāṇāṃ śatāni nava eva ca |
| ||080:028cd||
tasya māṃ bhūtabhūtasya kālasya surasattama ||080:028ef||
tasmin sā pūjitā devī brahmaṇā manurupiṇā |
svāyaṃbhuvatanurbhūtvā jagataḥ sthitikāraṇe ||080:029||
tena jñātāni nāmāni te ca dvīpā saridvarā |
pātālasthitayaḥ śakra bhavanti ca brajanti ca ||080:030||
tathāpi māṃ kṛtā māyā mohanī surajantuṣu |
anekakālabhūtaṃ yadadyaiva pratibhāṣate ||080:031||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe devyavatāre kālabhāvavyavasthā nāmāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye devyavatāre kālabhāva vyavasthā ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 081
ekāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ
śakra uvāca |

bhagarvastava vākyānāṃ na tṛptirbhavate mama |
kālāgnipārthivaṃ mānaṃ śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ ||081:001||
bhagavānuvāca |

nahi pārthivadvīpeṣu merupṛṣṭhe'pi vāsava |
bhogāhlādakatā nṛṇāṃ yathā pātālavāsiṣu ||081:002||
yeṣu na kālarudrasya nānāstrīśatasaṃkulāḥ |
vicitraharmyavinyāsāḥ kūṭasya merupṛṣṭhataḥ ||081:003||
sā evaṃ kālarudrasya tanurupeṇa saṃsthitā |
sā parā śivabhāvena paramapadadāyikā ||081:004||
[tattvarūpeṇa ka]
tasya yugasahassrānte brahmādyānāṃ bhayaṃkaram |
taṃ viddhi kālarudreti saumyarūpaṃ sadā śivam ||081:005||
[tasya yuddhusahaṃ tejo brahmādyānāṃ kṣaya kāraṇam ka ga]
kālāgni dhāmanaṃ lakṣaṃ yojanānāṃ pramāṇataḥ |
ardhena ucchrayastasya pādāḥ pādena vāsava ||081:006||
siṃharūpā mahāghor mahānakrā mahābalā |
kālāgnirudrarūpo yo bahurudra samāvṛtaḥ ||081:007||
ananta padmarudraśca dhātāraḥ kāraṇīśvaraḥ ||081:008||
dāruṇo'gnirudraśca ca yamahantā bhayāntakaḥ |
lohitaḥ krūratejātmā ghano vṛṣṭibalāhakaḥ ||081:009||
vidyutaśca na śīghraśca prasannaḥ śāntisaumyadṛk |
sarvajño vividho buddhyā dyutimān dīptisuprabhaḥ ||081:010||
ete rudrā mahātmānaḥ kālikāśaktibṛṃhitā |
saṃharanti samastedaṃ brahmādyaṃ sacarācaram ||081:011||
kālagnibhuvanīśo'yaṃ śatakoṭibhirāvṛtam |
tasyā purasya vistāraḥ śatakoṭisuvartanam ||081:012||
[bahukoṭibhirāv taṃ ka ga; suvardhanam ka ga ]
devagandharvasiddhānāṃ tatra bhogāḥ sudurlabhāḥ |
pūrvvottaraparā bhaktiryāmyāntarasthitā parā ||081:013||
analānila vācyā ca nirṛá¹tāśā na cāparā |
eteṣāṃ madhyato rājan kālarudrastu śobhate ||081:014||
paṃktyākāraiḥ puraiḥ sarva kaṭakaṃ tasya saṃsthitam |
samantādiṣṭidhavalaṃ prākārāttolagopuraiḥ ||081:015||
[taṃ bhuvanaṃ ka ga]
vajrendranīla vaidūrya-prākāraiḥ sarvato'nvitam |
kālāgninarakānte tu puraṃ kālasya saṃsthitam ||081:016||
paṃcāśallakṣa vistāraṃ samantāt parivartulam |
jāmbunadamayairharmyaiḥ khacitaṃ ratnadhātubhi ||081:017||
pramadā jana saṃhṛṣṭaṃ nānāvarṇasamāvṛtam (FN)| kāmonmatta pramattaiśca tajjātījanasaṃkulam |

[kha pustake nāsti]
kālasya bhuvanaṃ divyaṃ vṛtākāraṃ manoharam ||081:018||
veṣṭitaṃ hemaprākārai-ryojanāyutamucchritam |
prākārā bahidaṇḍānte akṣayaṃ yojanāyatam ||081:019||
[antaraṃ ga]
agnijālaiśca niviḍairbhayadaiḥ kiṃśukaprabhaiḥ |
haritālanibhā jvālāḥ sindurā gairikaprabhāḥ ||081:020||
ata ūrdhva prajajvālāḥ suvātoddhūta bhāsvarāḥ |
vīcitaranga kallola jvālāmālākulānvaram ||081:021||
[suvā coddhūta ga]
pravistāra pramāṇena yojanadvayakoṭayaḥ |
aṣṭānavatilakṣāni jvālā ūrdhva tataḥ śilāḥ ||081:022||
[prav ttāstā ga]
vajrabhūtā mahātaptā tasya tejoniyāmikā |
catvāri koṭimānena kāraṇena tu sthāpitā ||081:023||
tasyordhvena bhavet kiṃsvit koṭayaścatvāri vāsava ||081:024||
evaṃ kāmāgnirudrasya māhātmyaṃ kīrttitaṃ mayā |
śravaṇāt sarvapāpāni śamante kālajānyāpi ||081:025||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe kālāgnirudramāhātmyaṃ nāmaikāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye devyavatāre kālāgni rudrapura kathanam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 082
dvāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

śakra uvāca |

kālāgnibhavanasyārdhe vajrapāṣāṇamūrdhani |
ye sthitāstatra deveśa tān kathayasva prasādataḥ ||082:001||
śrībhagavānuvāca |

yathā pṛcchati māṃ śakra ūrdhvaṃ kālapurasya tu |
tathā te kathayiṣyāmi śṛṇuṣva vadato mama ||082:002||
ūṣmodake narakāḥ śakra koṭyaḥ paṃcāśanmānataḥ |
catvāriṃśacchataṃ teṣāṃ pradhānaṃ tannibodhata ||082:003||
avīciḥ kṛmibhakṣyaśca tathā vaitaraṇī mahān |
kūṭaṃ śālmaligucchāsaṃ yuga parvvatarauravam ||082:004||
nirucddhāsaḥ pūtimāṃsaṃ taptalākṣāsthitañjanaḥ |
krakacchedastathā paṃkaḥ kaṇṭāyasasutāpitam ||082:005||
pūtipūrṇastathā bhedaḥ stambhaṃ ca rūdhiraṃ vasā |
tāmisramapatuṇḍaśca tīkṣṇāsiśca napuṃsakaḥ ||082:006||
lohitantu striyā bhīmā aṃgārarāśirivopari |
kumbhīpākaḥ kṣuramadhyaḥ sañjīvanasutāpakam ||082:007||
kālasūtraṃ magāpadmaṃ śītoṣṇaṃ kṣaturameva ca |
ambarīṣaṃ tathā ghoraṃ mahāraurava sampuram ||082:008||
[samyutam ka ga]
sūcīmukheṣu yantraśca tailataptatrapustathā |
asipatraṃ tathā pīnaṃ karapatraṃ ca vāsava ||082:009||
catvāriṃśat śataṃ ghoraṃ teṣāṃ trīṇi parān śṛṇu |
avīcīrauravakumbhīpākāḥ pacyanti pāpakān ||082:010||
devadvijagurudrohā bālastrīvadhavañcakāḥ |
sadvattamācaran śakra vighnakāḥ pācayanti te ||082:011||
devyā divaṃ tathā vastra-bhūmī-rājyāpahārakāḥ |
pācayante narakai hyetai varṇāśramavighātakāḥ ||082:012||
[vādyāpahā ka ga]
kūṣmāṇḍī sarvameteṣāṃ rakṣakaḥ sanniyojitaḥ |
pādena kālarudrasya tasyāśramasya saṃsthite ||082:013||
[tasya vā sakhyase sthitiḥ ga]
anantarūpaśobhāḍhyā vayaṃ mūrdhni vyavasthitāḥ |
pātālā pṛthivī śakra mama māleva mastagāḥ ||082:014||
vayaṃ kālagnirudrasya śatāṃśena pramāṇataḥ |
mamopari sthitāḥ sapta pātālā manakāmadāḥ ||082:015cd||
[malakāmodāḥ kha]
yatra nāgāḥ śūrāḥ rakṣāḥ tiṣṭhanti mama pūjakāḥ ||082:015ef||
rudrabhaktāstathā cānye brahmadevījyakāḥ pare |
paraṃ tattvamajānantaḥ pṛthagbhāvena bhāvitāḥ ||082:016||
anye sarvagatān sarvān devyāḥ śaktyāvalokitāḥ |
paśyante mama sadbhāvā mumukṣuḥ paragāminaḥ ||082:017||
yasmin ye saṃsthitāḥ śakra tānnibodha samāsataḥ |
ābhāsaṃ karatālaṃ ca śarkara ca gabhastimam ||082:018||
mahātālaṃ sutālaṃ ca saptamaṃ ca rasātalam |
sauvarṇamaṣṭakaṃ śakra na prasīdhyanti cāgamaiḥ  ||082:019||
devyā rudraparā lokā mantratantraviśāradāḥ |
svadehānte praviśanti nāgakanyāḥ ramanti ca ||082:020||
aṣṭamaṃ tadvijānīyād vasuratnopaśobhitam |
vibhūti krīḍaṃ saṃkṣepāt kathayāmi surādhipa ||082:021||
[sureśvaram ka ga]
prathamaṃ bhāsamānantu tatra hemamayī mahī |
nānāratnasamākīrṇaṃ prāsādaṃ sphaṭikojjvalam ||082:022||
ratnaiśca khacitāḥ stambhā dvārabandhāśca vāsava |
strīsahasrasamārkīrṇaṃ lakṣakoṭibhirekadhā ||082:023||
āvṛtaṃ koṭikoṭīnāṃ prādhānyāt kathayāmi te |
namūciḥ śaṃkukarṇaśca mahānādastṛtīyakaḥ ||082:024||
anantaḥ kūliko nāga elāpatraśca nāgakāḥ |
rākṣasāḥ śūladantaśca raktāḍhyo vikaṭastathā ||082:025||
sukhabhāg duḥkhasantaptā devyā bhaktisamanvitāḥ |
strīsahasramadairhṛṣṭā ābhāseṣu kṛtāḥ janāḥ ||082:026||
śatakoṭipravistārai varatāle nibodhata |
padmarāgamayī bhūmi ratnaiḥ khacitamandirāḥ ||082:027||
tatra harmyocchritā tuṃgā indranīlairvibhūṣitāḥ |
||082:028ab||
[tāta ka]
dvāre bandhāśca pravalā muktā rukmāśca toraṇāḥ |
| ||082:028cd||
[dvārabandhāstu prāvārāḥ ka ga]
anekakoṭayo yatra rākṣasāsurapannagāḥ ||082:028||
prahlādo agnijihvaśca anūhlādo'surāstrayaḥ |
vāsukiḥ śaṃkhapālaśca dhṛtarāṣṭrastrayoragā ||082:029||
vidyunmālī hiraṇyākṣo vidyujjihvaśca rākṣasāḥ |
calacakitavitastai rdhūpayakṣasu cāyataiḥ ||082:030||
tāsāṃ dṛṣṭinipātena savikārāmalena ca |
||082:031ab||
vissrambhālā pabhāvenavibhāsotphullitena ca ||082:031cd||
[citra mālāpabhātena ga]
smaro'pi smaraṇāccaitā gatāsūriva lakṣyate ||082:031ef||
śikhijhaṃkāraśabdena stokakairṇāditena ca |
alibhirgītaśabdena kokilā kūjitena ca |
| ||082:032cd||
uddīpayati cānaṃgaṃ vikhinna manacetasām ||082:032ef||
nānāmadyaviśeṣāṇi pivan pānāni vāsava |
asurānena bhāvena devīṃ pūjayate sadā ||082:033||
karatāle sthitā hyevaṃ śrītāle ca nibodhata |
tārākhya śiśupālaśca amayaścāsurāstrayaḥ ||082:034||
kambalastakṣakaḥ padmo nāgarākhyastrayastathā |
yamadantogradantaśca viśālākhyaśca rākṣasāḥ ||082:035||
[daṇḍogradaṇḍaśca ga]
caturtha sampravakṣyāmi daityāśca mahīṣopamāḥ |
tṛtīyaḥ kālapṛṣṭaśca nāgāḥ karkīṭa paṃkajāḥ ||082:036||
śaṃkukarṇastṛtīyaśca rākṣasāśca nibodhata |
mahādevaṃ mahākāyaṃ tṛtīyantu mahābhujam ||082:037||
[mahādevaṃ kha]
śarkare te vijānīyāḥ paṃcamantu nibodhata |
amaraḥ śaṃbhustāpākhyo asurāste trayaḥ smṛtāḥ ||082:038||
suparṇaḥ kūliko nāgastṛtīyaśca dhanaṃjayaḥ |
asthibhadro virupākhyo ugrarūpāśca rākṣasāḥ ||082:039||
gataste te samākhyātā pṛṣṭhe vairocane śṛṇu |
kālanemi rhiraṇyākhyo niśumbhaśca trayo'surāḥ ||082:040||
atraiva yat purāvṛttaṃ kathayāmi surottama |
dākṣiṇātye mahārāṣṭre kuladevastu brāhmaṇaḥ ||082:041||
tasya putraḥ samutpatno nāmnā taskaravallabhaḥ |
sa ca kālena mahatā nāmarūpaṃ pravarttitaḥ ||082:042||
mitra devadvijātīnāṃ mahaddravyāpahārakaḥ |
kadācit kālaparyante malaye parvvate gataḥ ||082:043||
tatra kanyābhidhānā tu bhavati jalasamvṛtā ||082:044||
[tatra kakṣābhidhānā tu bhavatī janasaṃskṛtā ga]
bahudravya susampūrṇā nagaradvārasaṃsthitā |
sa ca dyūtaṃ ramitvā tu nāmnā taskaravallabhaḥ ||082:045||
rātrau praviṣṭvāṃstasmin utsṛṣṭo dravya hārakaḥ |
yāvaddīpaḥ samaprāptastailastenābhavat kila ||082:046||
[tailachedāt ga]
tāvat tena tathā taile dravyānveṣaṇakāriṇe |
datte prabudhyavāmÌstatra devalo devipūjakaḥ ||082:047||
sa ca prāṇabhayānnaṣṭaḥ kālānmṛtyurabhūt punaḥ |
kāñcīrājādhipaḥ śakra nāmnā khaḍgakarodyataḥ ||082:048||
devī bhaktavaro nityaṃ madyamāṃsa â vasāpriyaḥ |
devabrāhmaṇadrohī ca devabhū-grāmahārakaḥ ||082:049||
kālena mṛtyumāpanno rocano rākṣasādhipaḥ |
piṃgākhyo daśakoṭīnāṃ mahābalaparākramaḥ ||082:050||
ajaro amaraḥ śakra brahmakalpāyujīvitaḥ |
tena dīpaprabhāvena śarkarādhipatirmahān ||082:051||
[śaṃkarādhipati kha]
duṣṭabhāvo'pi sañjātaḥ kiṃ punastatsamāśritāḥ |
bhavanti tatra rājendra brahma loka nivāsinaḥ ||082:052||
etatte sarvvamākhyātaṃ prasaṃgena surādhipa |
śeṣān nāgāmÌśca vakṣyāmi pātāle ye tu kīrttitāḥ ||082:053||
pauṇḍarīkañca duṣprekṣyaṃ śvetabhadraṃ vayoragāḥ |
piṃgākhyo meghanādaśca tathā ghoraśca rākṣasāḥ ||082:054||
rasātale jarāsandho vairocano valistathā |
koṭidhā yo mayā baddhastava kāryeṣu satvarī ||082:055||
[sattvadhī ga]
punaḥ svargaṃ gamiṣyāmi punastvaṃ śaṃsitā prabhuḥ |
airāvato mahānāgaḥ piṃgamaśvataraṃ tathā ||082:056||
mārīcaḥ kumbhakarṇaśca mālyavāmÌstraya rākṣasāḥ |
pātālāḥ sapta vikhyātāstriṣaṣṭibhuvaneśvarāḥ ||082:057||
vṛttākārāni pātālāḥ śata koṭipravistarāḥ |
vṛtta trayavibhaktāste daitya pannaga rākṣasāḥ ||082:058||
kalpe kalpe vinaśyanti tannāmāno bhavanti ca |
na hi saṃkhyā bhavecchakra mṛtā jātā punaḥ punaḥ ||082:059||
upapātālamaṣṭantu sauvarṇaṃ tu nibodhata |
yatrāsau bhagavān devo ardhanārīśvaraḥ prabhuḥ ||082:060||
vayaṃ ca tatra krīḍāmo brahmā vedavidāṃvaraḥ |
dvitīya iva kailāśe jayatra bhogā manoramāḥ ||082:061||
yatrāsau bhagavān devo varado hāṭakeśvaraḥ |
tatra hemamayī bhūmi rbajravaidūrya citritā ||082:062||
vicitrā dhātubhirbhāti devāsuramanoharā |
sarvva-vṛkṣasamākīrṇā sadārttavavanaspatiḥ ||082:063||
[sakārttavavanaspati ga]
sugandhaphalapuṣpāṇāṃ gandhadravyasamanvitā |
sugandhiḥ śītalo vāyurviharenmanatuṣṭidaḥ ||082:064||
[sarvadravya samanvitā ka ga]
hema prāsāda prākārāstaravodyānakānanāḥ |
saritsarvvataḍāgaiśca dīrghīkairupaśobhitam ||082:065||
sphaṭikeḥ śailasopānai rmuktāphalasamanvitam |
bhānti aṃbhāṃsi tāndraistu nīlaraktāmbujaiḥ sitaiḥ ||082:066||
kusumotpalasaṃcchannaṃ te ca kārttasvarāmbujā |
taṭe vṛkṣa latāgulma koṣotpalapakṣiṇaḥ ||082:067||
sarvve kārttasvarāḥ śakra pātālaṃ tena śobhitam |
tatrāṃganā madonmattāḥ krīḍantyudyān kandaraiḥ ||082:068||
vanopavanaudyānai dīrghikāsaramadhyagāḥ |
krīḍanti jala krīḍābhirdīlāndolanatatparāḥ ||082:069||
rati pramattā niśceṣṭā sarvaduḥkhavivarjitāḥ |
aśeṣa sukhatṛptāsu duḥkhaika smarakrīḍanam ||082:070||
[bahupramatta ka ga
vicaranti mahābhāgai sarvābharaṇabhūṣitāḥ |
vinyastakeśa bhārāstāḥ kavarīdhammillamuktakaiḥ ||082:071||
alaṃkārālayastāsāṃ pṛṣṭhagāḥ kusumantritāḥ |
mūrghṇi ca srajgatā bhānti saṃśitāgraiḥ pralambitāḥ ||082:072||
śākhāpatraviśeṣeṇa lalāṭatilakena ca |
yatrāparaviśeṣeṇa itdvarkeṇa virājate ||082:073||
[śikhi ka ga]
karṇo vinyastapatreṇa kuṇḍalairbhāti cāparā |
sitāsitārūpai dīrdhaistrasta bālamṛgā iva ||082:074||
yāsāṃ netrā virājante pure śrīhāṭakeśvare |
evaṃvidhaiḥ sadāstrīṃbhirnityaḥ smara nipīḍibhiḥ ||082:075||
[vibhāvyante ga]
ramanti suratā bhogāḥ sutṛptāḥ śivabhāvitāḥ ||082:076||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe hāṭakeśvarapuravarṇanaṃ nāma dvāśītitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ādye hāṭakeśvarapura varṇanam ka ga]
