%%% Chapter 089

ekonanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

śakra uvāca |

yenopāyena sarveṣāṃ devi sarvaphalapradā |
tadahaṃ śrotumicchāmi navamyāmāśritaṃ phalam ||089:001||
[vada ātmāśritaṃ phalaṃ kha]
brahmovāca |

āśvine vātha māghe ca caitre vā śrāvaṇe'pi vā |
kṛṣṇādārabhya karttavyaṃ vrataṃ śuklāvardhi hare ||089:002||
aṣṭamī cāśvine kṛṣṇā ekabhaktena kārayet |
maṃgalārūpiṇīṃ devīmathavā rurūghātinīm ||089:003||
pūjayennavabhedena gaṃdhamālyanivedanaiḥ |
kanyakāḥ bhojayedvatsa devībhaktāṃśca mānavān ||089:004||
[naramedena ka]
naktena navamī kāryāṃ ayācandaśamīṃ kṣapet |
upavāsamekādaśyāṃ punarevaṃ vidhirbhavet ||089:005||
yāvacchuklāṣṭamī śakra upavāsyā vidhānataḥ |
snānahomajapaṃ pūjā kanyābhojantu pratyaham ||089:006||
karttavyaṃ dvijadvandvena devyā bhaktiratena ca |
navamyāṃ paśughātantu mahiṣādi ajāvikam ||089:007||
[jitatattvena ka |
dvijavṛndeṇa ga; navadhā ka ga ]
karttavyaṃ bhūtavetāla na ca ātmanaḥ kāmyayā |
kanyāḥ alaṃkṛtāstatra dvijāḥ devyāḥ parāyaṇāḥ ||089:008||
[asaṃskṛtāstatra ka]
naṭanarttakaprekṣāśca rathayātrāṃ sajāgarām |
dānaṃ deyaṃ yathā śaktyā sarveṣāmapi bhaktinā ||089:009||
mahābhairavarūpāṇāṃ asthimālādharāḥ narāḥ |
pūjanīyā viśeṣeṇa vastraśobhādharādiṣu ||089:010||
karttavyā sarvakāmārtha prāpaṇāya surottama |
anena vidhinā śakra yadṛcchaṃ labhate phalam ||089:011||
maṃgalā bhairavī durgā vārāhī tridaśeśvarī |
umā haimavatī kanyā kapālī kaiṭabheśvarī ||089:012||
kālī brāhmī māheśī ca kaumārī madhusūdanī |
vārāhī vāsavī carccā nāmānyanyāni japennaraḥ ||089:013||
pūjayed bhojayet kanyāḥ śāstradṛṣṭena karmaṇā |
vastrālaṃkārakāñcayādi kaṭakāḥ kaṭisūtrakāḥ ||089:014||
dātavyā ātmanaḥ śaktyā devībhaktaiḥ sukhārthibhiḥ |
athavā nava rātrāṇi saptapaṃcatrirekadhā ||089:015||
ekabhaktena naktena ayācan upavāsanaiḥ |
kṣapayedāśvine śakra yāvacchuklā tu aṣṭamī ||089:016||
pūjayenmaṃgalā tatra maṇḍale vidhikalpite |
sarvasadbhāvasampanne sarvāvidhividhāyike ||089:017||
sarvakāmaprade śakra sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt |
arthakāmasya arthaṃ tu rājyakāmasya rājyadam ||089:018||
putra ārogyadaṃ vatsa mahāpātakanāśanam |
sarvavarṇaiśca karttavyaṃ puṃstrībāla napuṃsakaiḥ ||089:019||
sarvagā sarvadā devī yasmācchakra mahāphalā |
anayā vidhinā vatsa dadate avicāraṇāt ||089:020||
sarveṣāṃ bratayonīnāṃ sarvabratamahāphalam |
navamyākhyaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ tava samyak prakāśitam ||089:021||
[yogānāṃ kha ka]
nākhyeyaṃ bhaktihīnasya mūrkhasyāhetu vādine |
deyaṃ bhaktāya śāntāya śivaviṣṇuratāya ca ||089:022||
[bhaktimuktihīnasya ka]
devībhaktaḥ sadācāraḥ kanyāpūjārato naraḥ |
ihaiva sarvakāmāni labhate avicāraṇāt ||089:023||
nādhayo vyādhayastasya na ca śatrubhayaṃ bhavet |
saṅgare vijayo nityaṃ mahāneko'pi jāyate ||089:024||
śravaṇātsarvakāmāni labhate avicāraṇāt ||089:025||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe aṣṭamī navamī vrataṃ nāmaikonanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[aṣṭamī nabamī bratama ka |
maṃgalā aṣṭamī vratam ga |
]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 090

navatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

śakra uvāca |

yadyevaṃ sarvadevānāṃ paramā mātarā vibho |
tadahaṃ śrotumicchāmi teṣāñca vidhipūjanam ||090:001||
kāni puṣpāṇi dānāni bratāni niyamāstathā |
yena sampūjitā devyaḥ kṣipraṃ siddhi phalapradāḥ ||090:002||
[śīghraphalapradāḥ ga]
lokānāmupakārāya asmākaṃ ca viśeṣataḥ |
etadeva yathādeśaṃ kathaya naḥ prasādataḥ ||090:003||
evaṃ pūrva nṛpaśreṣṭha viṣṇuḥ śakreṇa pṛṣṭavān |
tat samājñāya śakrasya brahmaṇā kathitaṃ yathā ||090:004||
tathāhaṃ te pravakṣyāmi vidyātattvārthapāraga |

agastya uvāca |

pure vā yadi vā grāme nagare kheṭake'pi vā ||090:005||
dṛṣṭādṛṣṭaphalārthibhiḥ pūjanīyāstu mātaraḥ |
ekaliṃgai nadītīre drumaśaile vane'pi vā |
||090:006||
pūjitāḥ sarvavidyanāṃ sādhanāya phalapradāḥ |
gṛhe catvare haṭṭānte pūjitā dhanaputradāḥ ||090:007||
nagaradvāra pūrvādyā vṛddhirājya sukhārthadāḥ |
gaṃgātīre'thavā vindhye sarvakāmaphalapradāḥ ||090:008||
veda parvata śrīśaile kiṣkindhā parvatādiṣu |
mokṣadā divadā vatsa niṣkāmāḥ phalavāñchitāḥ ||090:009||
[arbudādiṣu ka ga]
ete sthānāḥ samākhyātā āśu phalasamīhakāḥ |
kālāntaraphalā devyaḥ sarvā sarvatrapūjitāḥ ||090:010||
[aśruphala ga]
kālāgniśivaparyantā yeṣāṃ vyāptimahātmanām |
tā yatra yatra pūjyante tatraiva phaladāyakāḥ ||090:011||
sarvadevanutā devyaḥ sarvadevaprasūtayaḥ |
śivādyā yābhirjāyante kastāḥ na pratipūjayet ||090:012||
yā sūte prathamaṃ śambhurbrahmaviṣṇuvivasvataḥ |
ādityavaruṇacandrārkaḥ kastāṃ na pratipūjayet ||090:013||
tāsāñca śubhaṛkṣāhe dārumānīya buddhimān |
maṇimauktikavaiḍūrya kāṣṭhacandana candanāḥ ||090:014||
madhūkapāthavilvāmra aśokatindukaśiṃśapāḥ |
śailapārthiva hemotthāstāvaddhātu śubhapradāḥ ||090:015||
[madhūkapārthaṃ vinnāmra ka; stave ṛkṣa ka]
tadvidairghaṭitā vatsa tadvedibhiḥ pratiṣṭhitāḥ |
tāścottarānanāḥ sthāpyāḥ sarvakāmaphalepsubhiḥ ||090:016||
sarvaśailaiṣṭakāṣṭotthaṃ gṛhaṃ vāstuvibhājitam |
valabhī maṇḍapaṃ vatsa maṭhaṃ vā sthāpane śubham ||090:017||
gandhaṃ naivedya dhūpena valimālyavibhūṣaṇaiḥ |
adhivāsana pūrvāstu sthāpanīyā yathā kramam ||090:018||
[tathā kāryā yathā kramam kha |
sthāpanīyāstu tadvidhaiḥ ga]
vedadhvani mahāghoṣaiḥ strīsaṃgītopaśobhitam |
karttavyaṃ sthāpanaṃ teṣāṃ vahuvāditranāditam ||090:019||
rātrau jāgaraṇaṃ tatra devyā pūjārthavṛdvaye |
ākhyānairmātarā śāstraiḥ rudrakrīḍākaraiḥ śubhaiḥ ||090:020||
[karttavyaṃ śubhamaṃgalai ga]
daśāvatārapūrvāstu kathā vācyā yathākramam |
evaṃ pratyūṣasi samprāpte baliṃ saṃdhyāsu dāpayet ||090:021||
[paṃktidvayaṃ khapustake nāsti]
yathā mātṛgaṇaṃ pūjyaṃ devabhairavarūpiṇam |
strīsaṃghāḥ kanyakā viprā pūjanīyāḥ svaśaktinā ||090:022||
maṭhañca kārayettatra devyāḥ pūjārthavṛddhaye |
sarvalakṣaṇasaṃpūrṇaṃ sarvopakaraṇānvitam ||090:023||
vāpīkūpaṃ taḍāgaṃ vā vāṭikāvana śobhitam |
veśyātūryopasampannaṃ dhvajachatra vibhūṣitam ||090:024||
ghaṇṭādarpaṇadīpādyaṃ deyaṃ dravyānurūpataḥ |
ghaṭikāyantrayaṣṭyādi dinasaṃkhyārthasiddhaye ||090:025||
karttavyānekamekaṃ vā yathākālaparicchade |
anena vidhinā vatsa mātarāḥ sthāpayennaraḥ ||090:026||
ihaiva pūjanīyāstu mṛto yāti parāṃ gatim ||090:027||
[ihātra ka ga]
ye tasya dāsakarmāṇi dāsyo veśyādikā gṛhe |
||090:027||
[kha śeṣe tasya svakarmānte kha]
te'pi yānti divaṃ vatsa kiṃ punastasya vāndhavāḥ ||090:027||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe mātṛpratiṣṭhā mahābhāgyaṃ nāma navatitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ityādye mātarāpratiṣṭhāmahābhāgyam ka ga]

%%%%
%%% Chapter 091
ekanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo vaiśyaḥ śūdro vā yadi vā striyaḥ |
pūjayenmātaro bhaktyā sa savāmÌllabhatepsitān ||091:001||
mṛṇmayīṃ pratimāṃ kṛtvā vindhye vā yastu pūjayet |
ātmavitānusāreṇa sa labhenmauktikaṃ phalam ||091:002||
[mauktikaṃ phalam ka ga]
ekāṃ vā yadi vā devī devaṃ vā vallakīkaram |
gajānanayutaṃ skandaṃ sarvakāmaphalapradam ||091:003||
[ekapra tpūṣasi prāpte vā ga]
brāhmī ca vaiṣṇavīṃ devīṃ kaumārīṃ śakradharmajām |
pūjyamāno avāpnoti aihikaṃ phalamuttamam ||091:004||
[padyamidaṃ ka pustake nāsti]
vṛṣārūḍhāṃ mahādevīṃ trinetrāṃ śūladhāriṇīm |
pūjyamāno labhedvatsa yadyatphalamīpsitam ||091:005||
yāṃ pūjya pūjyatāṃ yānti sarvalokasya vidyate |
tāṃ pūjaya sadā mātṛṃ brahmaviṣṇu namaskṛtām ||091:006||
brahmāpi pūjayate yāṃ viṣṇurdevastrilocanaḥ |
tāṃ pūjaya sadā devīṃ suraśatrunivarhiṇīm ||091:007||
devyāvatāra-śāstrāṇi rudraviṣṇubhavāni ca |
vājayat cintayan vatsa īpsitaṃ labhate phalam ||091:008||
yastu devyā gṛhe nityaṃ vidyādānaṃ pravarttayet |
sa bhavetsarvalokānāṃ pūjyaḥ pūjāpadaṃ brajet ||091:009||
mātarā purato yastu vasordhārāṃ prapātayet |
pṛthivyāmekarāḍ vatsa iha caiva bhavennaraḥ ||091:010||
chatraṃ vātha prapāṃ vahniṃ prāvṛḍgrīṣmahimāgame |
kārayenmātṛpurataḥ sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt ||091:011||
vidyādānaṃ pravakṣyāmi yena tuṣyanti mātaraḥ |
likhyate yena vidhinā dīyate tat śṛṇusva naḥ ||091:012||
siddhānta mokṣaśāstrāṇi vedān svargādisādhakān |
tadaṃgānītihāsāni deyā dharmavivṛddhaye ||091:013||
gāruḍaṃ bālatantraṃ ca bhūtatantrāṇi bhairavam |
śāstrāṇi paṭhanāddānāt mātaraḥ phaladā nṛṇām ||091:014||
jyotiṣaṃ vaidyaśāstrāṇi kalā kāvyaṃ śubhāgamān |
dānādārogyamāpnoti gāndharvaṃ phalate padam ||091:015||
[sutāgamāṃn ka]
vidyāmbho varttate loko dharmādharmaṃ ca vindate |
tasmād vidyā sadā deyā dṛṣṭādṛṣṭaphalārthibhiḥ ||091:016||
mahīdānaṃ ca godānaṃ hemavastratilā jalam |
dhānyadīpānnadānaṃ ca mahādānāni dānasu ||091:017||
iha prakṣīyate dānaṃ dīpadānaṃ narādhipa |
vidyā bṛddhimavāpnoti dīyamānāpi nityaśaḥ ||091:018||
[dīyamāna ka]
ekoccāreṇa bhūdānaṃ dattaṃ bhavati bhūmipa |
na hi tadvidyate bhūya dehapātādanantaram ||091:019||
vidyādānaṃ dadadvatsa ekadhā daśadhā bhavet |
śatadhā koṭidhā gacchedihāpi vidyāpāragaḥ ||091:020||
rājñā taskara dāyārderjala vahni sarisṛpaiḥ |
sarvadānāni kriyante vidyā kenāpi na kriyate ||091:021||
vidyādānena dānāni nahi tulyāni vuddhimān |
vidyā eva paraṃ manye yattat padamanuttamam ||091:022||
[annamayam ka]
śṛṇvannutpadyate bhaktirbhaktyā gurumupāsate |
sa ca vidyāgamān vakti vidyā granthāśritā nṛpa ||091:023||
vidyāvivekavodhena śubhāśubhavicāriṇaḥ |
vindate sarvakāmāpti tasmādvidyā parāgatā ||091:024||
vidyādānātparaṃ dānaṃ na bhūtaṃ na bhaviṣyati |
yena dattena cāpnoti śivaṃ paramakāraṇam ||091:025||
vidyāvicāratattvajño rājñaḥ sanmārgagāminaḥ |
bhuñjate'pi hi bhogāni gacchanti paramāṃ gatim ||091:026||
[tattvaṃ śāraddhi sanmārchakāriṇaḥ ka]
antyajā api yāṃ prāpya krīḍante graharākṣasaiḥ |
sā vidyā kena mīyeta yasyāḥ sarpāḥ na sarpiṇaḥ ||091:027||
yavena kuñjaraṃ hanti sarṣapena turaṃgamam |
makṣikāpadamātrasya viṣasya viṣamā gatiḥ ||091:028||
evaṃvidhaṃ viṣaṃ vatsa vidyāmantraprabhāvataḥ |
jīryate bhakṣitaṃ pumbhistasmādvidyā parāparā ||091:029||
na hi vidyā kulaṃ jātiṃ rūpaṃ pauruṣapātratām |
eṣā te sarva lokānāṃ paṭhitā upakārikā ||091:030||
bhūtairgrahītā vidhvastā daṣṭā vā mahāpannagaiḥ |
vidyā utthāpayedvatsa antyajasyāpi saṃsthitā ||091:031||
[hṛtsthitā ka]
sarveṣāmeva vṛddhānāṃ vidyā vṛddhe hi mānyatā |
vayovṛddho hi śūdrāṇāṃ viśānāṃ dhanadhānyataḥ |

kṣatriyāṇāṃ tu vīryeṇa viprāṇāṃ śāstrapāragaḥ ||091:032||
vittaṃ vandhurvayaścaiva tapo vidyā yathākramam |
pūjanīyā hi sarveṣāṃ vidyā teṣāṃ garīyasī ||091:033||
guru śuśrūṣayā vidyā puṣkalena dhanena vā |
vidyayā labhate vidyā caturthīṃ nopalabhyate ||091:034||
yaḥ kṛtsnāṃ tu mahīṃ dadyānmerutulyaṃ tu kāñcanam |
sa yadyanyāyataḥ pṛcchenna tasyopadiśet kvacit ||091:035||
[paṃktiriyaṃ ka pustake nāsti]
evaṃ vidho mahābhāga vidyāyāmupavarṇitaḥ |
saṃkṣepānna ca rvistārāt tasya dānaphalaṃ śṛṇu ||091:036||
śrītāḍa patraje saṃghe same patrasusaṃcite |
vicitra paṭṭikāpārśve carmaṇāṃ saṃpuṭīkṛte ||091:037||
[śrī tāḍīpatra jaināñca kha; karmikā pārśve ka ga]
raktena atha kṛṣṇena mṛdunā vardhitena ca |
dṛḍhasūtrasubaddhena evaṃ vidha kṛtena ca ||091:038||
[ragitena ca kha ga]
yastu dvādaśasāhastrīṃ saṃhitāmupalekhayet |
dadāti cābhiyuktāya sa yāti paramāṃ gatim ||091:039||
pūrvottaraplave deśe sarvabādhāvivarjite |
gomayena śubhe lipte kuryānmaṃḍalakaṃ budhaḥ ||091:040||
[śubhenaiva ka ga]
caturhastapramāṇena śubhaṃ tu caturasrakam |
tasya madhye likhet padmaṃ sitaraktarajādibhiḥ ||091:041||
sarvarttukaśubhaiḥ puṣpairbhūṣayetsarvatodiśam |
vitānaṃ dāpayenmūrdhni śubhacitravicitritam ||091:042||
pārśvataḥ sita vastraiśca samyakśobhāṃ prakalpayet |
kandukairūrdhvacandraiśca darpaṇaiścāmalai stathā ||091:043||
[cāmaraistathā ka]
ghaṇṭākiṃkiṇī śabdaiśca sarvatra upakalpayet |
tasya madhye likhed yaṃtraṃ nāgadantamayaṃ śubham ||091:044||
adhaḥ kasmin vivardhantu pārśvato haridantibhiḥ |
śobhitaṃ dṛḍhabandhena baddhaṃ sūtreṇa vuddhimān ||091:045||
tasyordhvaṃ vinyaset devyāḥ pustakaṃ likhitaṃ śubham |
ālekhyamapi tatraiva pūjayed vidhinā tataḥ ||091:046||
[vidyā kha]
nirudakaistathā puṣpaiḥ kṛmikīṭavivarjitaiḥ |
candanena sadarbheṇa bhasmanā cāvadhūnayet ||091:047||
dhūpaṃ ca guggulaṃ deyaṃ turuṣkāgurumiśritam |
dīpamālāṃ tathā cāgre naivedyaṃ vividhaṃ punaḥ ||091:048||
[tvāpamānāstathā ga]
khādyaṃ peyānvitaṃ lehyaṃ coṣyaṃ vāpi nivedayet |
pūjayechiśipālāmÌstu lokapālān yathākramam ||091:049||
kanyā striyastu saṃpūjya mātarāḥ kalpayecca tāḥ |
pustakaṃ devadevīñca viprāṇāṃ dakṣiṇā tathā ||091:050||
svaśaktyā caiva dātavyā nṛpaṃ paurāṃśca pūjayet |
tathā sampūjayedvatsa lekhakaṃ śāstrapāragam ||091:051||
[dharma mānakam ka]
chandolakṣaṇatadvaṃgaṃ satkaviṃ madhurasvaram |
praṇaṣṭaṃ smarate granthaṃ śreṣṭhaḥ pustakalekhakaḥ ||091:052||
[sahakāriṃ madhukṣaram ka]
nāptisantatavicchinnairna śuklaiḥ na ca karkaśaiḥ |
nandi nāgarakairvaṇaiḥ lekhayecchivapustakam ||091:053||
[ślakṣaiḥ ka]
prārambhe paṃcaślokāni punaḥ śāntiṃ tu kārayet |
rātrau jāgaraṇaṃ kuryāt sarvaprekṣāṃ prakalpayet ||091:054||
naṭacāraṇa lagnaiśca devyāḥ kathana sambhavaiḥ |
pratyūṣe pūjayellokāmÌstataḥ sarvāṃn visarjayet ||091:055||
[naṭacāraṇa nattaiśca ka]
ekānte sumanakṣeṇa visrabdhena dine dine |
niṣpādyaṃ vidhinānena śubharkṣe śubhavāsare ||091:056||
tataḥ pūrvoktavidhinā punaḥ pūjāṃ prakalpayet |
tathā vidyāvimānantu saptapaṃcatribhūmikam ||091:057||
vicitravastraśobhāḍhyaṃ śubhalakṣaṇalakṣitam |
kārayet sarvatobhadraṃ kiṃkiṇīkhavarānvitam ||091:058||
darpaṇairardhacandraiśca ghaṇṭācāmara maṇḍitam |
tasmin dhūpaṃ samutkṣipya sugandhaṃ candanāgurum ||091:059||
turuṣkaṃ guggulaṃ vatsa śarkarāmadhumiśritam |
pūrvavatpūjayet sarvān kanyāstrī dvijapauravān ||091:060||
tathā taṃ pustake vastre vinyased vidhipūjitam |
evaṃ kṛtvā tathā cintyā mātaraḥ priyatāṃmama ||091:061||
[priyatāṃ na mama ka]
yasyaiva śaṃke tacchāstraṃ pustake pravikalpayet |
tathā tapasvinaḥ pūjyāḥ sarvaśāstrārthapāragāḥ ||091:062||
śivabratadharā mukhyā viṣṇudharmaṃparāyaṇāḥ |
mahatā jana saṃghena rathasthaṃ dṛḍhavāhanaiḥ ||091:063||
pradhānairvāpi taṃ neyaṃ yasya devasya aṃśajam |
sāmānyaṃ śivatīrtheṣu mātarābhavaneṣu ca ||091:064||
[yuvā naiḥ kha]
tasmin pūjyaṃ tathā kṛtvā devadevasya śūlinaḥ |
samarpayetpraṇamyeśaṃ mātaraḥ prīyatāmiti ||091:065||
sadādhyayanayuktāya vidyādānaâratāya ca |
vidyāsaṃgrahayuktāya sarvaśāstrakṛtaśrame ||091:066||
tenaiva varttate yastu tasya taṃ vinivarttayet |
jagaddhitāya vai śāntiṃ sandhyāyāṃ vācayettathā ||091:067||
tena toyena dātāraṃ mūrdhni samabhiṣiṃcayet |
śivaṃ vadettataḥ sarvaṃmuṃccāryaṃ jagatastathā ||091:068||
evaṃ kṛte mahāśāntirdeśasya nagarasya tu |
jāyate nātrā sandeha sarvabādhāḥ śamanti ca ||091:068||
[paṃktiriyaṃ ka pustake nāsti]
anena vidhinā yastu vidyādānaṃ prayacchati |
sa bhavet sarvalokānāṃ darśanādaghanāśana ||091:070||
mṛto 'pi gacchate sthānaṃ brahmaviṣṇunamaskṛtam |
sapta pūrvāparānvaṃśān ātmanaḥ sapta eva ca ||091:071||
uddhṛtā pāpakalinā viṣṇuloke mahīyate |
yābattat patrasaṃkhyāni akṣarāṇi vidhīyate ||091:072||
tāvatsa viṣṇulokeṣu krīḍate vividhaiḥ sukhaiḥ |
tadā kṣitiṃ samāyāto devyā bhaktirato bhavet ||091:073||
samastaâbhogasaṃpanne vidvān sa jāyate kule |
vidyādānaprabhāveṇa yogaśāstraṃ dadedyadi ||091:074||
[sadā ka]
ātmavittānurupeṇa yaḥ prayacchati mānavaḥ |
aśāṭhyātphalamāpnoti āḍhyatulyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||091:075||
striyā vānena vidhinā vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet |
bhartturanujñayā dattaṃ vidhavā vā samuddiśan ||091:076||
[ka pustake nāsti]
vidyārthine sadā deyaṃ vastramabhyaṃga bhojanam |
chatrikā udakaṃ dīpaṃ yasmāt tena vinā nahi ||091:077||
lekhanī ghaṭanaṃ tīkṣṇaṃ masīpādantu lekhanīm |
dattvā tu labhate vatsa vidyādānamanuttamam ||091:078||
pustakāstaraṇaṃ dattvā tatpramāṇaṃ suśobhanam |
vidyādānamavāpnoti sūtrabaddhantu vuddhimān ||091:079||
yantrakamāsanaṃ caiva daṇḍāsanamathāpi vā |
vidyāvācanaśīlāya dattaṃ bhavati rājyadam ||091:080||
añjanaṃ netrapādānāṃ dattaṃ vidyāparāyaṇe |
bhūmigṛhantu kṣetrantu sarvarājyaphalapradam ||091:081||
[mūrdhavajyeka ka]
yasya bhūmyāṃ sthito nityaṃ vidyādānaṃ pravarttatte |
tasyāpi bhavate svargaṃ tatprabhāvānnarādhipa ||091:082||
tasmāt sarva prayatnena vidyā deyā sadā naraiḥ |
ihaiva kīrttimāpnoti mṛto yāti parāṃ gatim ||091:083||
