%%% Chapter 092
dvinavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

śakra uvāca |

tvameva paramo deva vedavedāntapūjitaḥ |
tvayāpi kathitā devī pūjitā śivaviṣṇunā ||092:001||
sā ca sarvaṃgatā śāntā śivakālāgnivyāpakā |
yatra yatra ca pūjyet tatra tatra phalapradā ||092:002||
kṛtaṃ divasasāmarthyaṃ tretāyāṃ yajña karmaṇā |
dvāpare yajanādhyayanāt sidhyante hyavicāraṇāt ||092:003||
[kṛtādi tapasāmapharna va ga]
evaṃ pūrva tvayā nātha sūcitaṃ na prakāśitam |
kalā ghore mahāprāpte yuge ca tamasāvṛte ||092:004||
viṣṇoḥ kṛṣṇatvamāpannai kathaṃ devī varapradā |
kasmin sthāne sthitā nityaṃ dvīpe vā pṛthivītale ||092:005||
etadākhyāhi me tāta prasīta surasattama ||092:006||
brahmovāca |

sādhu sādhu mahāprājña nigūḍhārtha vivecaka |
sandehavinivṛtyarthaṃ pṛṣṭhakaṃ śubhamicchatā ||092:007||
yathaiva bhavatā pṛṣṭaṃ devī sarvatragā śivā |
yathā ca nātra saṃdehastathaiva kathayāmi te ||092:008||
yā sā ghoravadhārthāyaâsarvaṃâdeva namaskṛtā |
vindhyādrau saṃsthitā devī sā ca pūjyā yathāvidhiḥ ||092:009||
mantrādravya kriyādhyānānmahāsiddhikarā nṛṇām |
strī bāla vikalāndhānāṃ sā bhavet sūkṣmasiddhidā ||092:010||
[vikalāṃgānāmabhāvāt kṣudra siddhidā ka]
sarvakāmapradā loke sarvaiṣāmapi vāsava |
himavatyacale nandā devī pratyakṣasiddhidā ||092:011||
sā ca saṃsmaraṇāt dhyānāt yātrāniyamakarmaṇi |
sidhyate yena vidhinā śivena kathitā purā ||092:012||
devyāyāṃ mama govinda ṛṣīṇāṃ paripṛcchatām |
tathā te kathayiṣyāmi śṛṇu tattvena vāsava ||092:013||
agastya uvāca |

evaṃ pṛṣṭaḥ purā brahma devarājena vidyapa |
mahābhāgyantu devyāyāḥ nandāyā yatphalaṃ punaḥ ||092:014||
[viprendra ka]
tīrthayātrāphalaṃ puṇyaṃ yathā devyā prapṛcchitam |
tatte'haṃ saṃpravakṣyāmi yathāvadanupūrvaśaḥ |
||092:015a-d||
sūryalokaṃ labhedrājan brahmaṇā kathitaṃ yathā ||092:015ef||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe devīmāhātmyaṃ nāma dvinavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye devyāmāhātmyam ka ga]
