%%% Chapter 093

trinavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

kailāśaśikhare ramye nānādhātuvicitrite |
anekāśiravarākīrṇe gaṇagandhasevite ||093:001||
[śivālaye tu kailāśe ka]
sahasrakiraṇopete taptakāñcana bhūṣite |
devatāṛá¹ṣibhiścaiva sadāsiddha niṣevite ||093:002||
vimāna koṭisaṃcchanne vitānadhvaja śobhite |
nṛtyanti tatra vai kecit kecidvadanti dundubhim ||093:003||
[vādanti vastubhiḥ ka]
gāyanti gaṇagandharvā nṛtyanti devayoṣitaḥ |
stotramudīrayantyanye anye vijayamaṃgalaiḥ ||093:004||
[devayonayaḥ ga]
stuvanti bhagavandevamṛṣayaśca mahātapāḥ |
candrādityagrahāścaiva tathā tārāgaṇā api ||093:005||
ye cānye tridaśāḥ siddhā yogasiddhā mahāmakhaiḥ |
śakrādyā lokapālāśca brahmaviṣṇumarūdgaṇāḥ ||093:006||
[mahābhairavai ka]
sarve basanti tatraiva divyaiśvaryasamanvitāḥ |
praṇamya prāñjalirdevī idaṃ vacanamabravīt ||093:007||
[namanti ga]
kautuhalaṃ mahādeva utpannaṃ me maheśvara |
marttyaloke mahādeva guptasthānāni kathyatām ||093:008||
kathayasva prasādena lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā |
anivarttakāni tīrthāni guhyasthānāni me prabho ||093:009||
tanme brūhi sureśāna yadyahaṃ tava vallabhā |
śrotumicchāmyahaṃ praśnaṃ nandādevyā mahātmanā ||093:010||
[mahāvibho ka]
kathaṃ deva praviṣamaṭo'sau himavaṃte mahāgirau |
tīrthayātrāphalaṃ deva kīdṛśaṃ bhavati prabho ||093:011||
anivarttakāni mārgāni kuṇḍapraveśameva ca |
prasīdati yathā devī sukṛteneha karmaṇā ||093:012||
[daṇḍapraveśam ga; janmanā ka kha]
narake pacyamānānāṃ narāṇāṃ parameśvara |
||093:013ab||
īśvara uvāca |

śṛṇudevi pravakṣyāmi yathā devī vyavasthitā ||093:013cd||
śṛṇvantu devatāḥsarvā ye cānye ca tapodhanāḥ |
kathyamānāṃ ca tīrthānāṃ yathā devyā pracoditam ||093:014||
evaṃ śrutvā tathā brahmā śivasya vacanaṃ śubham |
sarve caivāgatāstatra śivasya purataḥ sthitāḥ ||093:015||
ahopūrvāṇi kathyante sarve kautuhalānvitāḥ |
āgataste samīpe tu devāsuramahoragāḥ ||093:016||
[parvāṇi ka]
bhāvitātmānaśca te sarveṃ hṛṣṭaromā samudgatāḥ |
pārvatyāstu praśaṃsante yayedaṃ pṛcchitaḥ śivaḥ ||093:017||
[kṛṣṇaroma samudbhavāḥ ka ga ]
mātā devāsurāṇāñca vandyā ca parameśvarī |
paśūnāñca hitārthāya mokṣārthañca tapasvinām ||093:018||
pṛcchate ca tato devī nandāśāstraṃ sudurlabham |
kotuhalānvitā devyā śṛṇvantu śivabhāvitā ||093:019||
[nandāśabdaṃ ka kha:; śṛṇavanti śivabhāṣitāḥ ka]
kṛtāñjalipuṭāḥ sarve sarve praṇatamūrttayaḥ ||093:020||
īśvara uvāca |

himavatyacale ramye nānā siddhaniṣevite |
apsarogaṇasaṃkīrṇe nānāvṛkṣasamākule ||093:021||
[vidyādhara samākule ka]
kinnarīgaṇasaṅkīrṇe ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ |
nityaṃ sevanti tatsthānaṃ parvataṃ bhūdhareśamavaram ||093:022||
tasminpuṇyāni tīrthāni guhyasthānāni yāni ca |
anivarttakāni catvāri tāni śṛṇvantu devatāḥ ||093:023||
bhairavaṃ caiva kedāraṃ tathā rudraṃ mahālayam |
nandādevī caturthaṃ tu paṃcamaṃ nopalabhyate ||093:024||
śivatīrthāni guhyāni kathitāni mahītale |
adhunā sampravakṣyāmi nandātīrthasya yatphalam ||093:025||
yathā gaṃgā nadīnāntu uttamatvena saṃsthitā |
tadvadbhagavatī nandā uttamatve vyavasthitā ||093:026||
nagendrāṇāṃ yathā meruruttamo vai vyavasthitaḥ |
tārakāṇāṃ yathā candraḥ prabhutvena mahātape |
||093:027a-d||
tīrthānāñca tathā nandā prabhutvena vyavasthitā ||093:027ef||
grahānāñca yathā prabhutvena vyavasthitaḥ |
tadvat kṣetraṃ mahādevī nandāyāḥ parameśvari ||093:028||
khagendrāṇāṃ prabhuryadvat suparṇo acalātmaje |
tadvat tīrthaṃ mahādevī nandāyāḥ uttamaṃ priye ||093:029||
phaṇīndrāṇāṃ yathā rājā vāsukistridaśārcite |
tīrthānāmuttamaṃ tadvat naṃdākhyaṃ surasundari ||093:030||
[padyamidaṃ kha pustake nāsti]
ṛṣīṇāṃ ca yathā vandyaḥ kaśyapo bhṛgureva ca |
nandātīrthaṃ mahādevī vandyaṃ puṇyaṃ ca kīrttitam ||093:031||
[yathāgastyaḥ kāśyapo mṛgurevaca ga]
yoṣitānāṃ yathā bhadre rājñī tvaṃ suranāyaki |
devatānāmahaṃ devi nandātīrthaṃ tathā priye ||093:032||
[devatānāṃ mahā debi ka]
tasmāt kiṃ bahunoktena varṇitena punaḥ punaḥ |
mokṣasthānaṃ yathā devi anaupamyaṃ surārccite ||093:033||
anaupamyaṃ tathā tīrthaṃ nandākhyaṃ parameśvari |
pṛthivyāntu sthito vāpi nandādevīṃ prakīrttayet ||093:034||
mucyate sarvapāpebhyo yaḥ smaredbhāvitātmanaḥ |
nandāsthānaṃ narāḥ prāpya na te prākṛta mānuṣāḥ ||093:035||
[prakṛtimānavāḥ ka]
ye brajanti ca tatraiva anivarttaṃpathe sthitāḥ |
aśvamedhaphalaṃ teṣāṃ narāṇāṃ tu pade pade ||093:036||
ye mṛtāstu pathe devī kuṇḍe vā narapuṃgavāḥ |
na teṣāṃ vidyate martye punarāgamanaṃ priye ||093:037||
sarvatīrtheṣu yatpuṇyaṃ sarvayajñeṣu yatphalam |
sarvadāneṣu yatproktaṃ tapaścāndrāyaṇādibhiḥ ||093:038||
koṭi koṭi guṇaṃ kṛtvā yatpuṇyaṃ sakalaṃ bhavet |
nandā sandarśanāddevi bhavate suvicāraṇāt ||093:039||
[saphalam ka kha; hyavicāraṇāt ga]
devyuvāca |

aśvamedhaṃ mahāyajñaṃ tapaścāndrāyaṇādikam |
devyāḥ saṃdarśanenātha vyarthametattathāgamāḥ ||093:040||
parameśvara uvāca |

na bhayaṃ naiva lobho me sneho vā suravandite |
ajñatvaṃ vātha dīnatvaṃ yenāhamanṛto dhruvam ||093:041||
[ṛá¹ṣabho dhruvam kha]
tapoyajñeṣu devānāṃ santarpaṇavidhirmataḥ |
te ca brahmādayo bhadre taistu nandā pratiṣṭhitā ||093:042||
yo'sāvanādimadhyāntaḥ śivaḥ śaktimayaḥ paraḥ |
tasyeyaṃ paramā nandā sarvakilbiṣanāśinī ||093:043||
[nāśanam ka]
tatprabhāvena prāpnoti tapo yajñādikaṃ phalam |
maṃtrāṇāṃ devaśaktīnāṃ na vicāro varānane ||093:044||
kālikā hāsyavākyāni grahabhūtaviṣāpahāḥ |
evaṃ kaliyuge ghore yasmin dehāntarā narāḥ ||093:045||
[kaulikāhāsyavākyāni ka ga; deha; samānavaḥ ka]
bhuñjanti darśanātkanyā tasya kiṃ tapasādikam |
aśvamedhādikaṃ bhadre yena tvaṃ vismayaṃ gatā ||093:046||
[bhuñjate darśanāḥ kanyāḥ ka]
aṃguṣṭhodaramātreṇa boḍhuryanmaṇinā phalam |
na tatsahasrapāṣāṇān vahanaṃ prāpnoti mānava ||093:047||
[sundari ka ga]
veda evaṃ hi dharmāṇāṃ pravaro dharmadarśakaḥ |
tasmin sā pūjyate devī mānastoketi veda sā ||093:048||
devyuvāca |

lokānāṃ tu manojñānaṃ utdyotanaṃ prati prabho |
pūrvapakṣānyahaṃ nātha samyagyātrāṃ nibodhaya ||093:049||
parameśvara uvāca |

māse bhādrapade devi śuklapakṣe vrajetsadā |
tasyecchā śrāvaṇe'ṣāḍhe anyathā na kadācana ||093:050||
teṣāñca candranāgastu pīḍāṃ kuryāt sulocane |
na gacchanti surāḥ siddhāḥ kiṃ punarmānuṣādayaḥ ||093:051||
viṣavātahatāḥ keciddhimavātaprapīḍitāḥ |
vimucyante narā devi yānti devyā prasādataḥ ||093:052||
pāpakarmmā narā ye tu gaṇādhyakṣo nivārayet |
śeṣānvai candranāgastu nityaṃ rakṣati tadgataḥ ||093:053||
kapilaḥ piṃgalaścaiva dhūmaketurmahābalaḥ |
somakaścandranāmaśca rakṣanti baladarpitāḥ ||093:054||
nityaṃ rakṣanti tattīrthaṃ paṃcakoṭi samanvitāḥ ||093:055||
umovāca |

kiṃ purasya tu vistāraḥ kā siddhiḥ kā ca ramyatā |
ko vā vinyāso harmyāṇāṃ kena vā nirmitāni ca ||093:056||
[ṛdvi ka]
kimpramāṇantu kanyānāṃ ko veṣo varṇayauvanam |
udyānāḥ kīdṛśāścaiva dīrghikā vāpi kīdṛśī ||093:057||
kiṃ vā vadanti tāḥ kanyāḥ nandāyāḥ purataḥ sthitāḥ |
kāntasya ca kathaṃ prāptistāsāṃ vara sureśvara ||093:058||
[suravareśvara ga]
katareṇa tapenaiva marttyā bhuñjanti tāḥ striyaḥ |
kasmiṃstu pūjitā devī kṣipraṃ pratyakṣatāṃ vrajet ||093:059||
kasmin kṣetre drutā siddhirniyamena kena prabho |
liṃgānāṃ lakṣaṇaiścaiva yasmin sidhyanti sādhakāḥ ||093:060||
[lamyate mānuṣe śivā ka]
samayāśca kati proktā mantroddhāraśca kīdṛśaḥ |
kīdṛśaṃ yajanaṃ devyā rupakaṃ caiva kīdṛśam ||093:061a-d||
etatsarvaṃ yathānyāyaṃ kathayasva prasādataḥ ||093:061ef||
īśvara uvāca |

nandā devyā purī ramyā bhogādyā suravanditā |
vasanti tatra vai kanyā satataṃ madanāturāḥ ||093:062||
[surāṃjitā ka]
pādapadmaṃ sadā pūjyaṃ nandāyā varavarṇini |
śocayanti sadātmānaṃ nandāyā agrataḥ sthitāḥ ||093:063||
aśrupātajalaughena soṣṇena tu varāṃganāḥ |
nandāyā pādapadmau tu ajasraṃ kṣālayanti tāḥ ||093:064||
kanyakā ūcūḥ
[kanyā ūcūḥ ka]
kiṃ kāryaṃ jalakrīḍāyāṃ dolākrīḍanakena kim |
udyānakrīḍanairvāpi dyūtakrīḍanakena kim ||093:065||
[bhūta ka number is not given in the text portion.]
pustakavācanenāpi kāvyākhyāyikakrīḍayā |
vīṇā śāstreṇa kiṃ kāryaṃ citrapatraparicchadaiḥ ||093:066||
[bināśāstrena ka]
unmattaceṣṭitaṃ sarvaṃ patihīnaṃ mahātape |
mṛdaṃgapaṭahai śabdairvallakīpanavādibhiḥ ||093:067||
nṛtyavāditrakaṃ sarvaṃ patihīnaṃ na rājate |
veṇu vīṇāninādena vipaściddhvanināditaiḥ ||093:068||
kimvā lambūkavīṇāyāṃ kāryaṃ piñjalakena kim |
vyādhitasya yathākrandastadvat tartrordhvaniḥ smṛtā ||093:069||
[randhradhvaniḥ ka]
araṇyaruditaṃ sarva vidhavānāṃ sureśvari |
kiṃ vā rūpeṇa karttavyaṃ kāryaṃ yauvanena ca ||093:070||
makarīkarapatraiśca payodharakapolayoḥ |
lalāṭairtilakairvāpi vinyastaiḥ kiṃ prayojanam ||093:071||
[kapolajaḥ ka]
ko vā āgatya marttyo'smin yaḥ pariṣvajya marddayet |
vastrairvilepanairdivyaiḥ sragdāma bhramarākulaiḥ ||093:072||
[ka pustake nāsti]
mukuṭaiścuṭakairvāpi kimvā lalāṭapaṭṭikaiḥ |
yadvadbhittiṣu citrāṇāṃ maṇḍanaṃ tadvanniṣphalam ||093:073||
[cūtakaiḥ ga; bāṇanādda paṭṭakaiḥ ka; maṃḍalaṃ tattvaniṣphalam ga]
dayāṃ kuru surādhyakṣe nānyastrātā sureśvari |
evaṃ yācanti deveśi bharttāraṃ nandamandire ||093:074||
udyānadīrghikairvāpi pravālāṅkura śobhitaiḥ |
kvacitsphaṭikasopānaiḥ kvacinmarakata sañcitaiḥ ||093:075||
kvacidhāṭakasambhūtaiḥ indranīlamayaiḥ kvacit |
rajovarttamayairdivyaiḥ kvacidvajravinirmitaiḥ ||093:076||
[kha pustake nāsti]
tapanīyodbhavaiḥpadmaiḥ kvacidvidru masannibhaiḥ |
sitāsitaistathā raktaiḥ śrīmukhairmukharaistathā ||093:077||
haṃsasārasasaṃgītaiḥ jīvaṃ jīvakanāditaiḥ |
nānāpakṣigaṇaiḥ ramyaiḥ śobhante dīrghikāḥ sadā ||093:078||
kāntahīnā mahādevi vani ca puṣkariṇīva |
aśokaâbakulairnāgaiḥ śubhaistilakapañcakaiḥ ||093:079||
[nāditaiḥ ka]
punnāgaânāgaâbakulaiḥ panasairbrahmayaṣṭikai |
jarmbīraibījapūraiśca puṣkalairupaśobhitam ||093:080||
[jendrākṣajamburaiḥ ga]
evamādiphalaiḥ ramyai susvādairamṛtopamaiḥ |
lavalīphalaâkaṃkolaiḥ lavaṃgaâlakucaistathā ||093:081||
[nabanīpheṇa karaiḥ kālai ka]
tamālaâpatraâkarpūraiḥ jātīphala-sadāḍimaiḥ ||093:082||
surapādapaâsaṃkīrṇaṃ saralairddevadārubhiḥ |
nānāvallīsamākīrṇaṃ latāgulmaâmahoṣadhaiḥ ||093:083||
nānāpuṣpaphalopetaṃ nityaṃ munimanāpaham |
ambike nāthahīnantu paitryaṃ vāvarapādapam ||093:084||
[badhira pādapam ka |
dhāvatpādam kha]
tapanīyodbhavairhamyaiḥ stambhairvidrumasaṃprabhaiḥ |
kvacitsphāṭikakuṇḍaiśca rājapaṭṭairmayaiḥ dṛḍhaiḥ||093:085||
puṣparāgamayaiścānyaiḥ kvacidvajra susañcitaiḥ |
indranīlamayaiścānyaiḥ dvārairmeravalayojitaiḥ ||093:086||
kapāṭaiḥ padmarāgotthairmahānīlamayaiḥ kvacit |
dvāraiścevopadvāraiśca rājāsanasurañjitaiḥ ||093:087||
[paṃktitrayaṃ kha pustake nāsti]
vātāyanordhvamārgaiśca tathā sopānapaṃktibhiḥ |
vādyaharmyairmanoramyai rnityaṃ gandharvasaṅkulaiḥ ||093:088||
ghaṇṭācāmaravinyastaiḥ kiṃkiṇīâjālaâmaṇḍitaiḥ |
vinyasta vastrasaṃghātairātapatravitānakaiḥ ||093:089||
mauktikadāmamālābhiḥ kvacit sragdāmamaṇḍitaiḥ |
mandirairmandarākārairmayasadbhāva kalpitaiḥ ||093:090||
dvisaptabhūmikopetaiḥ suramyaiḥ saujjvarlairgrahaiḥ |
hemaprākāraracitā pratolī gajamaṇḍitā ||093:091||
[kiṃ kārya pretavatgṛhai kha]
dhvajamālākulā divyāḥ siṃhadvāraistu śobhitā |
viṭaṃkottpala gotuṃgāḥ svargādramyatarā purī ||093:092||
nāthahīnā mahādevī raudrā yamapurīriva |
varaṃ martyā ca vanitā patimāśritya saṃsthitā ||093:093||
patihīnā na śobhante ambike kalpajīvitā |
ayutaṃ yojanānāntu nandādevyāḥ purī priye ||093:094||
[paṃktitrayaṃ ga pustake nāsti]
koṭi koṭibhiḥ strīṇāntu samantāt pūritā purī |
citrāmbaradharāḥ sarvāścitragandhānulepanāḥ ||093:095||
citramālyadharāḥ nityaṃ citrābharaṇabhūṣitāḥ |
citravarṇadharāḥ sarvāḥ vicitragatigāmini ||093:096||
nānāvādyaratā nityaṃ nānāgandharvatatparāḥ |
nānākrīḍāpramattāstu nānālekhyaratāḥ sadā ||093:097||
[prasaktāstu ka ga]
nānā śāstrārtha saṃpannā nānālekhyaratāḥ striyaḥ |
akṣīṇayauvanāḥ sarvā jarāmṛtyuvivarjitāḥ ||093:098||
nandā puravare kanyāḥ madhyamādhamavarjitā ||093:099||
umovāca |

rūpātiśayasampanā nānāguṇasamanvitāḥ |
kimarthaṃ dukhitāḥ jātā kāntasaukhyavivarjitāḥ ||093:100||
īśvara uvāca |

damayantī yathā sītā rūpātiśayapāragā |
duḥkhitāstena saṃjātā kāntasaukhyaâvivarjitāḥ ||093:101||
ahalyā baṃdhakī jātā gotamasya tu yoṣitā |
rūpasya tu prabhāveṇa dāsī jātā tilottamā ||093:102||
[kapilasya ga; ka pustake nāsti]
tasmādrūpaṃñca necchanti lakṣaṇajñāstapodhanāḥ |
atirūpeṇa svalpāyuḥ puruṣo yoṣito'pi vā ||093:103||
athavā saumyahīnastu jāyate tu mahātape |
nandāpuravare devi kanyakānāntu ceṣṭitam ||093:104||
udāhṛtaṃ mayā bhadre yathā pṛṣṭhaṃ tvayā priye |
pūjāsthānāni vakṣyāmi yasmin sānnidhyatāṃ vrajet ||093:105||
liṃgasthāṃ pūjayeddevīṃ sthaṇḍilasthāṃ tathaiva ca |
pustakasthāṃ mahādevīṃ pāduke pratimāsu ca ||093:106||
citre ca triśikhe khaḍge jalasthāṃ vāpi pūjayet |
agnisthāṃ pūjayetprājño hṛdaye vā suśobhane ||093:107||
ebhiḥ sthānairmahādevī pūjitā varadā bhavet |
mama pārśve śrutaṃ yaistu jñātaṃ devi tapodhanaiḥ ||093:108||
te'pi vandyā ahaṃ yadvacchivadharmaparāyaṇāḥ |
talliṃgamāśrayenmantrī śukrādyairyatpratiṣṭhitam ||093:109||
kacādyairyat kṛtaṃ liṃgaṃ varjaṃnīyantu sādhakaiḥ |
kalpasaukhyapradaṃ proktaṃ vedamantraiḥ pratiṣṭhitam ||093:110||
[ghṛtaṃ ka ga]
sādhikāraṃ tu yalliṃgaṃ muktabhogaṃ tathaiva ca |
jñātavyaṃ sādhakendreṇa siddhidaṃ cāpyasiddhidam ||093:111||
[sādhikā varṇayalliṃga ga]
sādhikāraṃ tu yalliṃgaṃ vedamantraiḥ pratiṣṭhitam |
nivarttitavikārañca uktaṃ śaṃbhuṃ svayaṃbhuvam ||093:112||
[maṃtrahīnaṃ pratiṣṭhitam ka ga]
kurvanti bhakti vātsalyaṃ lokānāṃ vāsanātmakam |
durvijñeyamidaṃ jñānaṃ yogināmapyagocaram |
||093:113a-d||
marttyairjaḍadhiyainathi kathaṃ vijñāyate prabho ||093:113ef||
īśvara uvāca |

sādhu sādhu mahādevi rahasyamidamuttamam |
yattvayā coditaṃ bhadre tathaiva ca na cānyathā ||093:114||
durvijñeyaṃ suraiścāpi kiṃ punarmarttya jantubhiḥ |
ādhiṣṭo sādhakaṃ jñeyaṃ hṛdayānandakārakam ||093:115||
[marttyajanmabhi ka ga; ādhiṣya ga]
indriyāṇāṃ cautsukyaṃ dadāti liṃgadarśane |
sevyamānaṃ tato liṃgaṃ nityānandapradāyakam ||093:116||
[nityamānandadāyakam ka ga]
susvapno paśyate nityaṃ vimānasthāṃ varāṃganām |
bhairavaṃ paśyate nityaṃ krīḍantaṃ mātṛmaṇḍale ||093:117||
umāmaheśvaraṃ vāpi svapne paśyati sādhakaḥ |
anivartti tādhikārañca liṃgaṃ ca tribhuvaneśvaram ||093:118||
[tribhuvaneśvari ka ga]
ākrāmanti mahāvighnāḥ sadaityāḥ rākṣasādayaḥ |
śūnyāgāraṃ yathā devi ākrāmanti narāḥ priye ||093:119||
anarcitantu bhuñjanti tathā liṃgantu kaśmalāḥ |
pretaṃ tathā surādhyakṣe ākrāmanti piśācakāḥ |
||093:120a-d||
śūnyaṃ ca vāṃgaliṃgantu āśrayanti tathā priye ||093:120ef||
śrīdevyuvāca |

paryāptañca śrutenaiva tava vākyena śaṃkara |
viśeṣotpādito mahyaṃ sutarāṃ gahanaṃ kṛtam ||093:121||
sūkṣmarūpā yadā vighnāḥ rākṣasā bhūtanāyakāḥ |
īdṛśīṃ tanumāsthāya liṃgaṃ bhuñjanti vai sadā ||093:122||
tadā te'pi manoramyaṃ sthānaṃ kurvanti śaṃkara |
sādhakasya sadānandaṃ te'pi kurvanti nityaśaḥ ||093:123||
svapnāṃśca śobhanān devī sādhakasya dadanti ca |
pūjārthino mahāvīryāḥ prītiṃ kurvanti sādhake ||093:124||
prabhāvayanti duṣṭātmā vadanti varadā bhava |
tasya varṣaśatenāpi kutaḥ siddhiḥ prajāyate ||093:125||
[pratārayanti ga, pratyāpayanti ka]
īśvara uvāca |

mahācodyaṃ mahādevi anaupamyaṃ surārccite |
brahmādyairapi deveśai rīdṛśaṃ na pracoditam ||093:126||
[deveśi ga]
yathāvatkathayiṣyāmi mā viṣādaṃ kurū priye |
aghorāsraṃ nyaset tasmin svādakañca mahābalam ||093:127||
daṃṣṭraiḥ karakarāyantu jvalantaṃ vidiśairdiśaiḥ |
pakṣamekaṃ yathā devi yathāsthānaṃ sukhāvaham ||093:128||
arcyamānaṃ tu talliṃgaṃ svapnaṃ dadati pūrvavat |
sādhikāraṃ tu talliṃgamāśusiddhipradāyakam ||093:129||
[vadanti ka ga; savikāraṃ kha]
ajāvikakharoṣṭraiśca ārūḍhāṃ paśyate tanum |
udvegaḥ kalaho nityaṃ sakhāpānāntu jāyate ||093:130||
[sakhāpālantu kha, sakhāpānantu ka]
kṛṣṇāmbaradharāṃ nārīṃ rātrau paśyati sādhakaḥ |
tasmāt kimbahunoktena talliṃgaṃ rākṣasālayam ||093:131||
varjanīyaṃ prayatnena mṛtyurogabhayāvaham |
upāyaṃ sampravakṣyāmi mantrahīne pratiṣṭhite ||093:132||
svayantu paṭhyate loke na ca tathyena sundari |
uṣare tu yathādhānyaṃ sthāpitaṃ niṣphalaṃ bhavet ||093:133||
[ropitam ka ga]
liṅge mantravihīne tu pūjanaṃ niṣphalaṃ bhavet |
upāyaṃ sampravakṣyāmi tasyāpi mṛdubhāṣiṇi ||093:134||
[yajanaṃ ga]
prasannāṃ dhārayetprājña āveśaṃ vātha paṇḍitaḥ |
svayambhuḥ kalpitañcāpi kathitaṃ siddhibalābalam ||093:135||
[kārayet ka ga; praveśaṃ ka ga]
pavargāccaturthe varge viparītasulocane |
tasyāpi prathame varge ādibījaṃ tṛtīyakam ||093:136||
prasannā ca sadā devi īṣṭāniṣṭaprasūcanī |
kiṃ vahunoktena svayaṃ saṃkalpite priye ||093:137||
āśrayastatra kurvīta āśusiddhipradāyike |
duṣṭa sattvasamākīrṇe jane bhaktivivarjite ||093:138||
[iṣṭa kha]
na kuryādāśrayaṃ mantrī diṅmoho yatra jāyate |
na kuryādvidiśe tīrtha snānapānaṃ śivātmani ||093:139||
[śirāmbuni ka ga]
vāpīkūpataḍāgaṃ vā prāsādaṃ vā niketanam |
na kuryāt tṛtpikāmastu analānile nairṛte ||093:140||
āgneyyāṃ manasastāpye naiṛte krūrakarmakṛt |
agnidāhaṃ sadā kuryāt amānuṣacatuṣpadām ||093:141||
vāyavyāṃ calacittastu prīyamāṇe jale priye |
sthānasya pāvake bhāge vāpīkūpa taḍāgakam ||093:142||
[padyamidaṃ kha pustake nāsti]
nairṛte pīyamānastu ātmā na duḥkhito bhavet |
kanyāpi tajjalaṃ pītvā patiṃ gṛhṇāti kāmataḥ ||093:143||
prāsādasyottare devi vasanti naiva siddhidāḥ |
vidiśāsu ca sarvāsu chāyākrāntāpi no śubhām ||093:144||
dakṣiṇonnato yā kṣoṇī vāruṇī nairṛtonnatāḥ |
śubhā ca siddhidā nityaṃ sādhakasya janasya vā ||093:145||
dravyāmÌścaiva pravakṣyāmi yathā taiḥ pūjyate priye |
nandā bhagavatī devī siddhidā sādhakasya tu ||093:146||
maṇiratnamayā kāryā hemarūpya mayāpivā |
candanenāpi karttavyā pāduke pratimāpi vā ||093:147||
śrīparṇe śrīdrume cāpi devatārumayī parā |
ṣaḍaṃgulā ca sā kāryāṃ pāduke pūjayetsadā ||093:148||
paṭasya lakṣaṇaṃ vakṣye yathā sidhyanti sādhakāḥ |
granthikeśavihīṃne tu ajīrṇe samatantuke ||093:149||
asphāṭite arcchidre tu sthalenaiva samālikhet |
maṃgalārupiṇī kāryā jayādyaiḥ parivāritā ||093:150||
vīṇāhastā prasaktā tu nānālaṃkāraśobhitā |
jīrṇe tu bhavate vyādhiḥ sphoṭite maraṇaṃ bhavet ||093:151||
[paṃktitrayaṃca ka kha pustake nāsti]
keśaiḥ suśokadaṃ vidyāt granthibhiḥ skhalanaṃ bhavet |
chidreṇa utthito vāpi sādhakasya balābale ||093:152||
vṛddhaṃ ca vyādhidaṃ vyāṃgaṃ dīrghaṃ sthūlaṃ kṛśaṃ tathā |
vṛddhena bhavate vṛddho vyādhite vyādhito bhavet ||093:153||
kurūpeṇa kurupaṃ tu mūrkhena tu na pūjyate |
lekhakasya tu yadrūpaṃ citre bhavati tādṛśam ||093:154||
khaḍgasya lakṣaṇaṃ vakṣye triśikhasya ca sundari |
nānāśastrodbhavaṃ kāryaṃ mṛdulauhamayaṃ pivā ||093:155||
sphuṭitaṃ khaṇḍitaṃ hṛsvaṃ savraṇaṃ sandhitaṃ tathā |
mṛdulauhe apūjyastu sandhite maraṇaṃ bhavet ||093:156||
[sphāṭitam ka]
savraṇe'pi hi hṛdroge rekhayā pātakī bhavet |
bhāryā mātā tathā putrā mriyante khaṇḍitena tu ||093:157||
[kṛdroṇe ka]
hrasvena lāghavaṃ loke dīrgheṇāpi hyasiddhidam |
anyaśastrodbhavenāpi bhavate maraṇaṃ dhruvam ||093:158||
paṃcāśadaṃgulaṃ khaḍgaṃ triśikhaṃ ca sureśvari |
īdṛśaṃ kārayetprājña āśusiddhiphalapradam ||093:159||
kṛtvā tu pūrvavattyāgaṃ śāstradṛṣṭena karmaṇā |
ālabhetsarvadravyāṇi khaḍgādyān saptapaṃcadhā ||093:160||
[khaḍgādyā ka]
atha sarvairya jeddevīṃ nandāṃ tribhuvaneśvarīm |
śākayāvakapiṇyāka kṣīrāśī bhikṣādo'pivā ||093:161||
[atrārabhya ślokānāṃ śataṃtrayaṃ ga pustake nāsti]
kandamūlaphalāśī vā japaṃ kuryādvicakṣaṇaḥ |
antaritopavāsena atha naktena varjjayet ||093:162||
trirātreṇa tu vartteta atha cāndrāyaṇādibhiḥ |
homayellakṣamekantu ājyamiśrantu guggulam ||093:163||
athavā śrīphalairvāpi homaṃ kuryādvicakṣaṇaḥ |
trilakṣeṇa labhet khaḍgaṃ triśūlaṃ pāñcalakṣikam ||093:164||
khaḍgena bhavate rājā madhye khecara cāriṇām |
triśūlena sureśāno bhavate nātra saṃśayaḥ ||093:165||
[atrārabhya aṣṭanavati adhyāyaparyantaṃ ka pustake .api nāsti]
pūrvameva trayo lakṣān japaṃ kṛtvā samārabhet |
anyathā tu mahādevi homaṃ naiva tu kārayet ||093:166||
samayā sampravakṣyāmi yaistuṣṭidaṃ phalaṃ labhet |
śaivāna pāśupatānvāpi mahābratadharāṃ pivā ||093:167||
kumārikāśca taduktān bhojayet pūjayet sadā |
nādyāt strī nāyakān bhaktān na nārīṃ tāḍayet kvacrit ||093:168||
pratāḍayenna cākrośaṃ vivastraṃ naiva kārayet |
prasuptāṃ naiva paśyeta tāḍyamānāṃ nivārayet ||093:169||
mūtraṃ purīṃṣaṃ kurvantīṃ na paśyenna jugupsayet |
naiva tāṃ bhūṣayenmantrī yadīcchecchāśvataṃ padam ||093:170||
majjanti yoṣito yatra śaucaṃ kurvanti yatra vā |
udvahanti jalaṃ yatra tattīrthaṃ pūjayet sadā ||093:171||
mṛdbhasmadaṇḍakāṣṭhāni tasmin tīrthe niveśayet |
sukhapādāvācarantu tattīrthaṃ kārayed budhaḥ ||093:172||
anena tuṣyate devī nandā cānandacāriṇī |
vastraṃ patraṃ tathā bhakṣyaṃ phalaṃ puṣpaṃ vilepanam ||093:173||
nānālaṅkaraṇaṃ devi yatkiṃcijjaladāyikam |
nandāmuddiśya dātavyaṃ tuṣyate tena sā priye ||093:174||
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi siddhisthānāni yāni tu |
yasminnārādhitā devī kṣipraṃ bhavati siddhidā ||093:175||
mandāraṃ śataśṛṃgañca trikūṭaṃ parvataṃ tathā |
vindhye gaṃgāsarid yatra revatī yamunāpi vā ||093:176||
payoṣṇī aśvarathye tu athavā kuṇḍaleśvare |
śaṃkareśvara rāmeśe athavā amareśvare ||093:177||
sarasvatītaṭe puṇye sugandhāyatane'pi vā |
sthāneṣveṣu japaṃ kuryānnandā tadagatamānasaḥ ||093:178||
vetravatyātasṭe ramye hariścandre tathā priye |
bhairavaṃ śūlabhedañca caṇḍīśaṃ tripurāntakam ||093:179||
aṣṭacakrañca krauñceśaṃ kapālākṣāgranāmakam |
ajāvikakharoṣṭākhyaṃ sthānānyanyāni varjayet ||093:180||
brahmasyāpi bhavecchipramebhiḥ sthānairmahātapaiḥ |
ūrdhvagaḥ kalaho nityaṃ vratabhaṃgaṃ vināśakṛt ||093:181||
śubhābhidhānakaiḥ sthānaistatra sādhanamārabhet |
caturthīṃ cāṣṭamīṃ naiva navamī vā caturdaśī ||093:182||
śuklapakṣe tu karttavyaṃ devyā yajanamuttamam |
tato nandīśvaro gacchedahorātrantu kārayet ||093:183||
snātvā gaṃgānadī tīre kṛtvā ca udakakriyām |
nandādevīṃ namaskṛtya sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate ||093:184||
cūbhikāmagame snāyānmahāpātakanāśane |
piṇḍagaṃgā kuśaṃgaṃgā tatra snātvā tu mānavaḥ ||093:185||
devānāṃ tarpanaṃ kuryāt piṇḍaṃ pitṛṣu dāpayet |
ghṛtena madhuvā vāpi saktūn guḍavimiśritān ||093:186||
tilodakaṃ tato dattvā kuśodaka samanvitam ||093:187||
om pitṛbhyaḥ svāhā |
oṃ pitāmahebhyaḥ svāhā |
oṃ prapitāmahebhyaḥ svāhā |
oṃ mātāmahebhyaḥ svāhā |
||093:188a-d||
oṃ umāmaheśvara varebhyaḥ svāhā ||093:188ef||
piṇḍaṃ dattvā hemamantrai praṇipatya kṣamāpayet |
evaṃ devi vidhiṃ kṛtvā kulānāṃ tārayecchatam ||093:189||
nandāgaṃgāṃ punaḥ snātvā mucyate sarvakilviṣaiḥ |
tato vaitaraṇīṃ gatvā snānaṃ tatraiva dāpayet ||093:190||
devānāmudakaṃ dattvā piṇḍaṃ tatraiva dāpayet |
mahādevaṃ namaskṛtvā sa gaccheduttarāṃ diśam ||093:191||
mahāgaṇapatiṃ dṛṣṭvā pūjāṃ kṛtvā vidhānavit |
gacchedāyatanaṃ divyaṃ devyā bhavanamuttamam ||093:192||
pūjāṃ kṛtvā vidhānajño yāvat praṇatavigrahaḥ |
tāvat taṃ gagane devī vimānasthā savāsavā ||093:193||
abhinandate taṃ dhanyaṃ narendra puṇyabhājanam |
nandādevyāścaraṇābjaṃ yena dṛṣṭaṃ sudurlabham ||093:194||
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ śāśvataṃ bhuvanottamam |
anenaiva tu dehena devyāḥ putrantu jāyate ||093:195||
kārttikeyasamo bhūtvā mahāvīryaparākramaḥ |
rtiṣṭhate sūcitaṃ kālaṃ matprasādāna suvrataḥ ||093:196||
tadante vrajate mokṣaṃ bhuktvā bhogān yathepsitān |
devyā dakṣiṇamukho bhūtvā mūlamaṃtraṃ japed vudhaḥ ||093:197||
darśanaṃ jāyate tasya sādhakasya na saṃśayaḥ |
śuklāmvaradharāṃ nārīṃ rātrau paśyati sādhakaḥ ||093:198||
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā jāyate siddhiraṇimādiguṇāṣṭakam |
devyāḥ pradakṣiṇāṃ kṛtvā kuṇḍasya ca viśeṣataḥ ||093:199||
dhyātvā devīṃ tataḥ kuṇḍe praviśenmatsyavajjale |
pauruṣatvaṃ jale tatra trāsaṃ naiva tu kārayet ||093:200||
paśyate kṣaṇamātreṇa strīmukhaṃ dvāramuttamam |
nānāratnamayaṃ divyaṃ hemaprākāra toraṇam ||093:201a-d||
maṇḍape tiṣṭhate devī dvārasyāgre suśobhane ||093:201ef||
pūrṇakumbhāśca sauvarṇāśca jalapallava maṇḍitāḥ |
nirmitā viśvakarmeṇa sarvaratnamayāḥ śubhāḥ ||093:202||
maṇihemamayaiḥ stambhairvimānairdhvaja śobhitaiḥ |
mauktikadāma mālābhi rmaṇimālābhirmālitam ||093:203||
ghaṇṭācāmara śobhāḍhyamātapatrai virbhūṣitam |
sauvarṇā murajāstatra tiṣṭhante meghanisvanāḥ ||093:204||
indranīlaparicchannaṃ vicitramaṇi carcitam |
śālabhañjika puṣpaiśca ratnapaṃkaja śobhitam ||093:205||
parijātaka mālābhiḥ samantāt parivāritam |
nandā bhagavatī devī pratimārūpa dhāriṇī ||093:206||
tiṣṭhate maṇḍapadvāre sahasrabhujabhūṣitā |
sarvāyudhadharā saumyā puṣpamālā vibhūṣitā ||093:207||
divyagaṃdhānuliptāṃgī kuṃkumāruṇavigrahā |
kuṇḍalaiḥ kaṭakaiyūrairmukuṭādivibhūṣitā ||093:208||
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā tu mahādevī pratimārupadhāriṇīm |
tasyā pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā praṇipatya śivena tu ||093:209||
tasyāgre tiṣṭhate cānyā jayā ca pratihārikā |
dṛṣṭvā tu sādhakaṃ vīraṃ iṣṭastuṣṭo prabhāṣate ||093:210||
svāgataṃ te mahāvīra puṇyabhājo mahātapāḥ |
tiṣṭhantu sādhakā atra yāvatpratyāgamamaham ||093:211||
pṛcchāmi bhagavatīṃ devī tubhyañcaiva praveśanam |
evantu vadate devī jayā dvārasya pālikā ||093:212||
gatā śīghrantu devyāyāḥ samīpaṃ varavarṇinī |
jānubhyāṃ dharaṇīṃ gatvā jayā vadati harṣitā ||093:213||
jayovāca |

āgato marttyo loke'smin dvāre tiṣṭhati sādhakaḥ |
kriyate sāmprataṃ kintu ādeśaṃ vada ambike |
||093:214a-d||
vihasya bhagavatī na ndā idaṃ vacanamabravīt ||093:214ef||
devyuvāca |

yathā tai pādapadmantu madīyaṃ hṛdaye kṛtam |
mamāpi ca tathā bhadre sādhakā hṛdaye sthitāḥ ||093:215||
mā vidhāraya tān dvāre tvaritantu praveśaya |
iṣṭātuṣṭamanā devi jayā tvaritamāgatā ||093:216a-d||
āgatya sādhakasya tu samīpasthā prabhāṣate ||093:216ef||
jayovāca |

bho bho vīra mahāsattva devī varapradā |
tatastu viditaṃ vīra apsarairbhaktavatsalaiḥ ||093:217||
īṣṭātuṣṭamanāḥ sarvāḥ nirgatāśca varāṃganāḥ |
cāmaraiḥ kanakadaṇḍaiśca chatrairmaṇivibhūṣitaiḥ ||093:218||
ardhyahastāstathā cānyāḥ puṣpahastāstathā parāḥ |
āgacchanti tataḥ kanyā divyālaṃkārabhūṣitāḥ ||093:219||
kuṃkumāgurūgandhaiśca liptāṃgāḥ sumanoharāḥ |
tilakairardhacandraiśca hemaratnavibhūṣitāḥ ||093:220||
nānālaṃkārasampannāḥ sarvāḥ pīnapayodharāḥ |
padmāṃkavapuṣaḥ sarvāḥ priyaṃgu campakādayaḥ ||093:221||
nīlotpaladalaśyāmā anyā vidyutsamaprabhāḥ |
kāmarūpāstathā cānyā gajendra gativikramāḥ ||093:222||
pūrṇacandrānanāḥ sarvāḥ sarvāstāmṛtasambhavāḥ |
ardhyaṃ pādyaṃ tato dattvā bhāṣyotphullalocanāḥ |
||093:223a-d||
svāgataṃ te mahāvīra ehi gacchāma sādhaka ||093:223ef||
evamuktvā tataḥ kanyā praviśanti purottamam |
hemaprākāradīptaṃ taṃ maṇitoraṇanupuram ||093:224||
divyagandharvagānāḍhyaṃ divyavādyasamākulam |
indranīlaparicchannaṃ bālākāryutasaṃprabham ||093:225||
dhvajamālākulaṃ sarvaṃ mayūracchatrabhūṣitam |
padmarāgamayai stambhaiḥ kvacit sphāṭikamayaiḥ śubhaiḥ ||093:226||
vidrumāḍhyaistathā cānyai nānāratnamayaistathā |
muraja vādyaśabdaiśca śaṃkhakāhalaniḥsvanaiḥ ||093:227||
geyaiśca madhurairdivyaiḥ śrotrendriya manoharaiḥ |
kanyānāṃ gītaśabdena nityaṃ pramuditaṃ param ||093:228a-d||
dṛśyate maṇḍapaṃ ramyaṃ nāgadaṇḍa vibhūṣitam ||093:228ef||
padmarāgaparicchannaṃ cāmarairupaśobhitam |
siṃhāsanantu devyāyā nyastaṃ hemamayaṃ śubham ||093:229||
darpaṇairardha candraiśca mauktikāhārabhūṣitam |
anaupamyaṃ mahādevi ratnākaramivotthitam ||093:230||
īdṛśaṃ mandiraṃ divyaṃ nānādhātuvicitram |
tasmiṃstu maṇḍapaṃ prāpya kanyā vacanamavravīt ||093:231||
asmiṃstu maṇḍape vīra nimeṣaṃ tiṣṭha suvrata |
svayamāgacchate devī varaṃ tubhyaṃ prayacchati ||093:232||
evamukttvā tataḥ kanyāḥ praviśanti purottamam |
kṛtañjalipuṭāḥ sarvāḥ kanyāḥ vacanamabrūvan  ||093:233||
kanyakā ucuḥ |

āgatā marttyā loke'smin dvāre tiṣṭhanti sādhakāḥ |
śaraṇāgatā mahādevi jayādevyā praveśitāḥ ||093:234||
tāsāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā kanyakānāṃ sureśvari |
siṃhayuktaṃ rathaṃ divyaṃ svayamāruhya rnirgatāḥ ||093:235||
kanyākoṭi sahasrantu devyā saha vinirgatam |
kāścid gacchanti vai hṛṣṭāḥ kāścidvījanti cāmaraiḥ ||093:236||
nṛtyanti kanyakāḥ kāścid kāścitstotraṃ paṭhanti ca |
nānāvādyaratāḥ kāścit nānāgītaratāstathā ||093:237||
kāścijjayajayā śabdaiḥ stuvanti parameśvarīm |
parivāritāḥ kanyaiśca āgatā maṇḍape śubhe ||093:238||
praviṣṭo maṇḍape devyābhyantare bhuvaneśvarī |
siṃhāsanopaviṣṭastu śvetapadmoparisthitā ||093:239||
jaṭā mukuṭa vinyastā bhasmākulita vigrahā |
lalāṭanayanopetā śravaṇāyatalocanā ||093:240||
pūrṇacandrānanā devī payodharabharālasā |
sunitambā sumadhyā ca sarvāvayaśobhitā ||093:241||
bhūṣitā paṭṭamāṇikyai rdivyagandhānulepanā |
sitasragdāmavastraiśca śobhāḍhyā mṛdubhāṣiṇī ||093:242||
svakāntikirarṇaughena purīmudyotya saṃsthitā ||093:243||
śrīdevyuvāca |

praveśya sādhakān sarvānāsanaṃ caiva dīyatām |
devyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā apsarā nirgatā drutam ||093:244||
ehi vīra mahāsattva praviśābhyantare pure |
tuṣṭā tu te mahādevī varaṃ tubhyaṃ prayacchati ||093:245||
kanyānāṃ vacanaṃ śrutvā sādhakastiṣṭhate tataḥ |
kṛtāñjali puro bhūtvā praviśed bhuvanottamam ||093:246||
daṇḍavat patito bhūmyāṃ devyāgre ca vyavasthitaḥ |
sagadgadaṃ vadedvākyaṃ kiñcidākulitekṣaṇaḥ ||093:247||
sādhaka uvāca |

tvaṃ gatiḥ śaraṇaṃ devi tvaṃ mātā parameśvari |
ahaṃ janmāntare kṣīṇastvāmeva śaraṇaṃ gataḥ ||093:248||
devyuvāca |

svāgataṃ bhadra bhadraṃ te varaṃ me brūhi subrata |
evaṃ sambhāṣito devyā sādhakaḥ puṇyakarmakṛt ||093:249||
muktvā tu mānuṣaṃ dehaṃ vidyābharaṇa bhūṣitaḥ |
bālārkāṇāṃ sahasrasya kāntirvai dhārayati saḥ ||093:250||
surūpaḥ subhagaḥ saumyaḥ mahābalaparākramaḥ |
idaṃ ratnapurī divyā sarvaâkāmaâphalapradā ||093:251||
sādhaka tvaṃ prasādena krīḍayasva yathāsukham |
skandatulyabalo bhūtvā yāvadāhūtasaṃplavam ||093:252||
sādhaka uvāca |

tvanmuktaśca bhaviṣyāmi janmaduḥkhavivarjitaḥ ||093:253||
devyuvāca |

koṭimekantu kanyānāṃ tava dattantu sādhaka |
ayutadvayaṃ tu śeṣāṇāṃ kanyakānāntu kalpitam ||093:254||
devyāḥ pādāmbujaṃ vatsa sādhakaḥ puṇyakarmakṛt |
gato vai sādhakaiḥ sārdhaṃ stūyamānastu maṃgalaiḥ ||093:255||
varaṃ dattvā mahādevī sādhakasya maheśvarī |
praviśya bhavanaṃ divyaṃ yatsurairapi durlabham ||093:256||
tataḥ kalakalā śabdaiḥ kanyakānāṃ purottame |
na śrūyate pure kiñcinnānā vāditra niḥsvanaiḥ ||093:257||
pariṣvajanti tāḥ kanyā bhramarā iva paṃkajam |
nānākrīḍāsamāyuktā divyastrī parivāritāḥ ||093:258||
krīḍanti sādhakāstāvat yāvadāhūtasaṃplavam ||093:259||
īśvara uvāca |

kathayāmi mahādevi yathā bhuñjanti tāḥ striyaḥ |
nandāpādārcanasaktā nandāsmaraṇatatparāḥ ||093:260||
nandādhyānaratā dityaṃ nandābhakti samanvitāḥ |
nandāsmaraṇasantuṣṭā nandādānaikatatparāḥ ||093:261||
nandābhaktajane bhaktā nandāyātraikatatparāḥ |
nandāmantraratā nityaṃ bratayogaratāśca ye ||093:262||
patayaste bhaviṣyanti kanyakānāntu subrate |
jala prākāradurbhedyaṃ himaprākāra rakṣitam ||093:263||
candranāga pratīhāraṃ devyā ājñā mahallakam |
antaḥpurataraṃ divyamasureśvaradurlabham ||093:264||
nandābhaktajanairbhīgyaṃ nijamantaḥpuramiva |
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi mantroddhārasya lakṣaṇam ||093:265||
yajanañcaiva devīnāṃ rupakañca mahātape |
pavargāt paṃcame varge vājañcaiva tadantimam ||093:266||
uccareta prayatnena bhinnaṃ vaihāyasena tu |
punastu madhyamaṃ bījaṃ tṛtīyaṃ svarabheditam ||093:267||
punaḥ prathamaṃ dātavyaṃ bhinnā vaihāyasena tu |
ekādaśena sabhinnaṃ bījaṃ kuryādvarānane ||093:268||
tasyāpi paramaṃ devi uddharetprathamaṃ punaḥ |
tṛtīyaṃ bhūtaje naiva adhastho na tu yājayet ||093:269||
punardvitīyabhūtasthaṃ bhedayekādaśena tu |
tasyāpi paratare varge prathamantu samuddharet ||093:270||
punaścaturthabhūyasthaṃ bījaṃ yatnena uddharet |
kālakṣāntaṃ tato bījaṃ bheda ekādaśena tu ||093:271||
navākṣarā mahāvidyā nandāyā hṛdayaṃ priye |
sarvakāmaphalapradā nityaṃ vidyeyantu mahātape ||093:272||
akṣaraṃ yugmāyugmañca aṃgāni tu prakalpayet |
navamantu bhavedasraṃ kālākhyaṃ savisargajam ||093:273||
anayā japyamānasya kanyakāstu mahātape |
nityaṃ kurvanti ānandaṃ nandāyāstu purottame ||093:274||
animeṣe kṣaṇā nityaṃ ratnaṃ paśyanti sādhakāḥ |
darśanenotsukāḥ sarvāḥ kāmārttāḥ kāminīḥ priye ||093:275||
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi devyāyā yajanaṃ śubham |
sādhakānāṃ hitārthāya tanme nigadataḥ śṛṇu ||093:276||
anantamāsanaṃ kṛtvā dharmādīśca niveśayet |
tataḥ prakalpayet padmāsanaṃ praṇavena tu ||093:277||
anantādīni deveśe praṇavena prakalpayet |
tata āvāhayeddevīṃ mūlamantreṇa subrate ||093:278||
śuklāmbaradharāṃ saumyāṃ jaṭāmukuṭa maṇḍitām |
nānālaṃkāraśobhāḍhyāṃ sitabhasmāvaguṇṭhitām ||093:279||
abhayavarapradāṃ devī varahastāṃ caturbhujām |
nānāpuṣpaistathā bhakṣyai rlehyavoṣyaiśca īpsitaiḥ ||093:280||
pūjayet parayā bhaktyā mahābhogajigīṣayā |
aṃgāni pūjayet paścāt hṛdayaṃ vahnigocaraiḥ ||093:281||
āgneyāntu śiraḥ pūjya naiṛtyā pūjayet śikhām |
kavacaṃ parame bhāge aiśānye'straṃ prapūjayet ||093:282||
pūrvapatre jayā sthāpyā vijayāṃ dakṣiṇe nyaset |
ajitāṃ paścime patre uttare aparājitām ||093:283||
dvibhujāṃ bālarūpāntu raktāmbaradharāṃ sadā |
vīṇāgṛhītahastāṃ tu nānālaṃkārabhūṣitām ||093:284||
svābhidhānābhidheyāñca bhūtyāṃśaścaiva prapūjayet |
śuklāmbaradharā hṛṣṭā dakṣiṇe varavarṇinī ||093:285||
paścime pītarūpā tu uttarā vṛṣarupiṇī |
rūpayauvanasampannā divyābharaṇabhūṣitā ||093:286||
ājñāṃ prārthayamānastu devīnāṃ tadgatā priye |
pratibhūtvā sadā kuryāt kṛtāñjali purā sthitā ||093:287||
svanāmaiḥ pūjayeddevīṃ vedikādyairvyaṃvasthitām |
paścimāyāṃ jayāṃ devīṃ varadābhayapāṇinīm ||093:288||
nandānandakarī devī bhavate sādhakasya tu |
lokapālān svanāmaistu astrāṃścaiva prapūjayet ||093:289||
pratibhāvaṃ yadā mantrī mantreṇa saha kārayet |
phalaṃ na vidyate tasya prabhutvena yadā sthitaḥ ||093:290||
ātmānaṃ prākṛtaṃ manyet mantraṃ manyed yathā śivam |
vidhireṣa samākhyātaḥ kāryaścaiva tu sādhakaiḥ ||093:291||
divyaprākṛtabhāvena pūjyamānā mahādhipe |
hṛdaye bhava deveśi anyathā tu nāsiddhidaḥ ||093:292||
pūjākāle tu karttavyamadāne mantrarūpiṇam |
anyathā yattu deveśi vighnaiḥ sa paribhūyate ||093:293||
evaṃ kṛtvā mahāyāgaṃ sarvasiddhipradāyakam |
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi mudrālakṣaṇamuttamam ||093:294||
aṃgulāgrasthitāḥ sarvā aṃguṣṭheva tatopari |
namaskārā smṛtā mudrā devyāḥ sānnidhyakārikā |
||093:295a-d||
anayā vidhinā devi devyāḥ sānnidhyatāṃ vrajet ||093:295ef||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe nandāpraśaṃsānāma trinavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ
[ka ga pustake 160 yā tvadeva ślokāḥ santi]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 094

caturnavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

umovāca |

mandā devyāḥ purī deva śrutā me parameśavara |
adhunā śrotumicchāmi sunandāyāḥ purottamam ||094:001||
kiṃ pramāṇaṃ ca kanyānāṃ praveśañca purasya tu |
kena mārgeṇa gacchanti narā ye bhāvitātmanaḥ ||094:002||
kena vā tuṣyate devī kathaṃ pratyakṣatāṃ bhavet |
vidhireṣa samākhyāhi mama kautuhalaṃ prabho ||094:003||
īśvara uvāca |

sunandāyā purī ramyā anaupamyā sureśvari |
tathāpi kathayiṣyāmi tava kautuhalaṃ priye ||094:004||
nānāratnopaśobhāḍhyā nānābharaṇabhūṣitā |
nānā ratnījvalā devī nānāmekhalayojitā ||094:005||
ratnasopānapaṃktibhiḥ sucitrā tu virājate |
nānāśayyāsanākīrṇai rnānācāmaraśobhitaiḥ ||094:006||
nānāvastravitānaiśca nānāvimānasaṃkulā |
nānākavāṭa-vinyastā nānāstambhasamanvitā ||094:007||
nānādhvajocchritā ramyā nānāghaṇṭānināditā |
nānādarpaṇavinyastā nānāsragdāmabhūṣitā ||094:008||
nānāvarṇarajaiḥ kīrṇā ramyā hemavatī mahī |
na nimnā nonnatā cāpi sukhapādapracāradā ||094:009||
nānāsaritsamākīrṇā nānānirjharakāśritā |
nānāpakṣīgaṇājuṣṭā hemadrumalatākulā ||094:010||
nānāpuṣpaphalopetā sundarībhiralaṃkṛtā |
kāmakārmukasaṃghuṣṭā sāyakairvidhvastacetasaḥ ||094:011||
stanorasi ca bharākrāntā praskhalanti pade pade |
kāmena sahasālāpaṃ nityaṃ kurvanti yoṣitaḥ ||094:012||
kanyakā ūcūḥ |

pātālapurasundaryaḥ kiṃ prayuktāsrilocana |
yathā kāmaṃ dahasveti evaṃ vidhvaṃsi nirdaya ||094:013||
alpāni hīnasattvāni aṃganānāṃ manobhavaḥ |
mlecchāpi na praharanti muktvā tvāṃ makaradhvajam ||094:014||
kāntaṃ dhyātvā kṛśodaryaḥ ekamevābhigṛhnitāḥ |
bhavanti lajjitā bhūyo avasāne sureśvari ||094:015||
anena madanārttāstu sunandāyāḥ pure priye |
kathitā yādṛśī ārttiryoṣitānāntu sundari ||094:016||
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi devyā siddhiniṣevitam |
tāvadgacchenmahātīrthaṃ yatsurairapi durlabham ||094:017||
gaṅgātīre mahādevī paśyate marukeśvaram |
tatra gatvā tu medhāvī trirātraṃ kārayed budhaḥ ||094:018||
trirātre caiva sampūrṇe praṇipatya maheśvaram |
uttarābhimukho bhūtvā vrajedīśānagocaram ||094:019||
ūrdhvayānaṃ tataḥ paśyennadīvāme śiloccayāḥ |
pitṛṇāmudakaṃ dattvā kālakūṭaṃ vrajettataḥ ||094:020||
kalahaṃseśvaraṃ nāma śambhorāyatanaṃ mahat |
tatrādipūjāṃ kṛtvā tu praṇipatya punaḥ punaḥ ||094:021||
kauśikāyāṃ puraḥ snātvā mucyate naraḥ kilbiṣaḥ |
śūlabhedaṃ tato gacchet tatsurairapi durlabham ||094:022||
tatrāpi pūjāṃ kṛtvā tu ekacittastu sādhakaḥ |
tadvasanbhavanaṃ gacchet kedāraṃ yatra krīḍitam ||094:023||
lokadṛṣṭena mārgeṇa sa gacchet kārtikaṃ puram |
guhyeśvaraṃ namaskṛtvā gacchedvaiśravaṇaṃ puram ||094:024||
brajennaṃdeśvaraṃ devamahorātrantu kārayet |
bhāgaṃ catuṣṭayaṃ kṛtvā devāgni-guru-ātmani ||094:025||
bhakṣayitvā tataḥ prājño gacchet taduttarāṃ diśam |
tato vaitaraṇīṃ gatvā snātvā tu vidhivat kramāt ||094:026||
devānāmudakaṃ dattvā piṇḍaṃ pitṛṣu dāpayet |
mahāvināyakaṃ dattvā pūjāṃ tasya prakalpayet ||094:027||
devyāśramantu saṃprāpya namaskṛtya maheśvaram |
pūrvabhāge tu kuṇḍasya aiśānī diśamāśritaḥ ||094:028||
sunandāyā śilā tatra jalamadhye pratiṣṭhitā |
puṣpargandhaistathā dhūpaiḥ pūjayet parameśvarīm ||094:029||
nandā kuṇḍaṃ hradaṃ tatra praviśettatra sādhakaḥ |
nandādevīṃ namaskṛtya tato vijñāpayed vudhaḥ ||094:030||
anivarttapathaṃ devī dehī me parameśvari |
tataḥ samīpato gacched śivena pūrvacoditam ||094:031||
[khapustake 34 iti saṃkhyākaḥ ślokaḥ]
kṛtāñjalipuṭoḥ bhūtvā praviśeta vicakṣaṇaḥ |
dhanvantarapramāṇaṃ tu praviśenmatsyavatdrutam ||094:032||
praviśyābhyantare vīra aiśānīdiśamāśritaḥ |
dhanvantaratrayaṃ gatvā śrīmukhaṃ tatra paśyati ||094:033||
praviśet tajjatāntasthaṃ śrīmukhaṃ dvāramuttamam |
dhanvantaraśataṃ gatvā paśyedāmalakaṃ drumam ||094:034||
tatphalaṃ bhakṣayet prājño namaskṛtvā maheśvarīm |
tatphalaṃ bhakṣamātreṇa valipalita varjjitaḥ ||094:035||
balaṃ nāgasahasrasya tatkṣaṇādeva jāyate |
dhanvantaraśataṃ gatvā praviśeta tato'dhikam ||094:036||
dṛśyate maṇḍapaṃ ramyaṃ śuddhaṃ hemamayaṃ mahat |
śuddhasphāṭikastambhāḍhyaṃ caturdvāraṃ mahāpuram ||094:037||
padmarāgoparicchannaṃ patākairupaśobhitam |
svayaṃ tiṣṭhati tatraiva mahākālagaṇādhipaḥ ||094:038||
sādhakañcāgataṃ dṛṣṭvā svāgatantu vadatyasau |
athā nandī vadedvākyamupaveśāya sādhakam ||094:039||
pṛcchāmi ambikāṃ yāvat tāvat tiṣṭha mahātapaḥ |
tataḥ śīghraṃ gato nandī sunandāyāḥ samīpataḥ ||094:040||
nandī uvāca |

āgato marttyo loke'smin tava pārśve maheśvari ||094:041||
sunandā uvāca |

āgacchantu mahānandī mama bhaktiparāyaṇaḥ |
devyāyāḥ vacanaṃ śrutvā tato nandī samāsataḥ ||094:042||
[baṃgalā pustake padmamidaṃ 46 saṃkhyākaṃ barttate]
sādhakasyedaṃ vākyaṃ vadennandī subhāvitam |
dhanyo'si bho mahāvīra ehi gacchāma sādhaka ||094:043||
ardhyaṃ pādyaṃ tato gṛhya kanyā nirgatya veśmani |
keyūrābharaṇairdivyai rmaṇikuṇḍalabhūṣitā ||094:044||
campakākāravapuṣaḥ karṇānttāyatalocanāḥ |
nīlotpaladalaśyāmā nānālaṃkārabhūṣitāḥ ||094:045||
raktāmbaradharā kācicchuklāmvaradharāparāḥ |
pītāmvarādharā cānyā pūrṇacandranibhānanāḥ ||094:046||
sarvā yauvanasampannāḥ sarvāḥ pīnapayodharāḥ |
sarvāṃstāḥ kāmarūpiṇyaḥ sarvāṃstāmṛtasambhavāḥ ||094:047||
yāścānyāścāparāstatra nirgatāśca samantataḥ |
geyaiśca madhurairdivyai rmaṇḍalaiśca manoramaiḥ ||094:048||
cāmaraiḥ kanakadaṇḍaiśca maṇiratnamayaidṛḍhaiḥ |
cāmarahastātathā kācit puṣpahastāstathāparā ||094:049||
madārttā muditāḥ sarvāḥ īkṣanteha nimiṣekṣaṇāḥ |
pūjyante sādhakāstatra ardhyaṃpādyaiśca maṃgalaiḥ ||094:050||
īṣṭā tuṣṭamanāḥ sarvā avagūhana-tatparāḥ |
tatastu sādhakaṃ gṛhya praveśayanti tatpuram ||094:051||
vijñāpayet tato bhaktyā tvaṃ gatiḥ śaraṇaṃ mama |
tato devī vadedvākyaṃ prasanna vadanojjavalā ||094:052||
[mūlapustake 59 saṃkhyākaṃ padyamidaṃ varttate]
svāgataṃ te mahāvīra sādhakastvaṃ kṛto mayā |
evaṃ sambhāṣitā devyā sādhakāstu mahātmanaḥ ||094:053||
tatkṣaṇādeva jāyante sādhakā divyarupiṇaḥ |
iyaṃ divyapurī vatsa candravatyā samanvitā ||094:054||
krīḍasva matprasādena yāvaccandradivākarau |
tadante bhavate mokṣo matprasādena putraka ||094:055||
devānāntu yathā rudraṃ atiraskṛtaśāsanaḥ |
tathaiva bhavane mahyaṃ krīḍaya tvaṃ yathāsukham ||094:056||
evaṃ dattvā varaṃ devī sādhakasya sureśvari |
namaskṛtvā tato mantrī praviveśa surottamam ||094:057||
maṃgalaiḥ stūyamānastu gītavādyamanoramaiḥ |
cāmarairbījyamānastu skandatulya-parākramaḥ ||094:058||
puṣpayānaṃ samāruhya krīḍate bhavanottame |
yojanānāṃ sahasrantu bhavanasya ca vistaraḥ ||094:059||
sahasrakoṭikanyānāṃ samantāt pūritaṃ puram ||094:060||
[pustake ślokasaṃkhyā aṣṭaṣaṣṭiparimitā vartate]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe sunandāpraveśavidhirnāma caturnavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ka ga pustake adhyāya eṣa nāsti]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 095
paṃcanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

umovāca |

sunandāyāḥ puraṃ ramyaṃ śrutaṃ me parameśvara |
adhunā śrotumicchāmi kanyakāyāḥ kathaya prabho ||095:001||
īśvara uvāca |

kanyakāyāḥ pathaṃ devi kathayāmi samāsataḥ |
śāka-yāvaka-payo-vāyu-ladhvāhāro athāpi vā ||095:002||
homayellakṣamekantu padma-vilva-samanvitam |
tato gacchenmahāvīraḥ pūrvoktena pathena tu ||095:003||
adhunā mantrapadāni bhavanti |
om nanda ninanda kili kili svāhā ||095:004||
imāṃ vidyāṃ japaṃ kuryāt tataḥ siddhiḥ prajāyate |
pūrvoktena vidhānena nityaṃ prakalpayet ||095:005||
tatastu kārayeddhaumaṃ guḍikairguggulasya tu |
ayutamekaṃ mahādevi tataḥ siddhiḥ prajāyate ||095:006||
pūrvameva eṣo lakṣān japtvā homaṃ prakalpayet |
homānte darśanaṃ rātrau siddhistasya prajāyate ||095:007||
tato gacchet medhāvī sādhakaiḥ sahitaḥ pathi |
devyāśramapadaṃ prāpya caruṃ tatra prasādhayet ||095:008||
bhāgaṃ catuṣṭayaṃ kṛtvā devi agniśivātmani |
ātmabhāgaṃ tato mantrī sādhakaiḥ saha bhakṣayet ||095:009||
vijñāpayet tato devīṃ praṇipatya punaḥ punaḥ |
ahaṃ duḥkhāntare bhītastāmeva śaraṇaṃ gataḥ ||095:010||
[ekādaśa saṃkhyākaḥ śleko'yaṃ kha pustake asti]
dehi me tvaṃ pathaṃ devi avighnena maheśvari |
evaṃ vijñāpya deveśīṃ sa gaccheduttarāṃ diśam ||095:011||
śarakṣepatrayaṃ gatvā dṛśyate śailamuttamam |
śuddhasphaṭikasaṅkāśā pratimā tatra tiṣṭhati ||095:012||
namaskṛtvā tu gantavyamaiśānyāṃ diśi saṃsthitam |
dhanvantaraśataṃ gatvā ardhacandrākṛtiḥ śilā ||095:013||
tatra mātṛ gṛhasthaiva uttarā diśi tiṣṭhati |
namaskṛtvā tu gantavyaṃ yāvad dṛśyaṃ nabhaḥ sthalam ||095:014||
karavīravanaṃ tatra hemapuṣpaṃ sugandhi ca |
ṣaṭpadāravaramyāḍhyā divyabhūmyā vyavasthitā ||095:015||
pratimārūpadharā sā divyahemamayā śubhā |
nānāratnojjvalā ramyā sādhakānāṃ phalapradā ||095:016||
tasyāḥ pūrvottare bhāge vanaṃ gīrvāṇapādapam |
aśokabakulaiścaiva śubhaistilakacampakaiḥ ||095:017||
priyaṃgunāgapunnāgaiḥ nānāpādapasaṅakulaiḥ |
nānā gulmasamākīrṇaṃ nānāvallī samākulam ||095:018||
sadā puṣpaphalopetaṃ sadā ṣaṭpadanāditam |
kokilārāvaramyantu nānāpakṣiniṣevitam ||095:019||
asya madhye mahādevī devyā bhavanamuttamam |
nānāratnaiśca vinyastaṃ nānādhvaja samākulam ||095:020||
nānā līlāvatī ramyā nupūrārāvanisvanā |
dīrghikābhiḥ suramyābhiḥ śobhitābhiḥ saroruhaiḥ ||095:021||
tatra mānavakanyāstu devyāḥ pādaprapūjakāḥ |
yakṣiṇyaḥ kāmarūpāstu gandharvī kinnarī tathā ||095:022||
vidyādharya surūpāstu devīmārādhayanti tām |
kāmārttā vihvalā nityaṃ bharttāṃraṃ prārthayanti tāḥ ||095:023||
aneka siddhisaṃkīrṇaṃ devyāyāḥ sthānamuttamam |
devyā vimānamāruhya āgatā kanakeśvarī ||095:024||
jaṭāmukuṭa ratnāḍhyā bhasmīddhūlita vigrahā |
pañcamudrāsamopetā nānāratnavibhūṣitā |
||095:025a-d||
mahāvratadharā devī āgatā yatra sādhakāḥ ||095:025ef||
[asya ślokasya saṃkhyā triṃśat iti varttate kha pustake]
devyuvāca |

svāgataṃ te mahārāja vīrasattva mahātapaḥ |
madīyaṃ bhavanaṃ vatsa nānāsiddhi samākulam ||095:026||
vicitramaṇinā kīrṇa devānāmapi durlabham |
yadi tiṣṭhasi atraiva divyaiśvarya samākule ||095:027||
pātālayoṣito gṛhya yakṣiṇīṃ vātha rūpiṇīm |
kinnarīṃ vātha gṛhya vidyādharīmathāpi vā ||095:028||
khaḍgaṃ vā rocanāṃ vāpi guḍikāṃ vāpi pāduke |
aṣṭadhā divyasiddhināmekāṃ gṛhya yathepsayā ||095:029||
bhuktvā tu vipulān bhogān paścānmokṣo bhaviṣyati |
evaṃ dattvā varaṃ devyā sādhakasya tu sundari ||095:030||
gatā vimānamārūhya svaka yaṃ sthānamuttamam |
candrakāntamayīṃ nandāṃ pratimārūpadhāriṇīm ||095:031||
pūjayanti kṛśodarya kāntārthinyo gṛhe gṛhe |
muktāphalamayīṃ devīṃ sunandāyāḥ pure priye ||095:032||
gandhadhūpaiḥ supuṣpādyai strikālaṃ pūjayanti tāḥ |
sphāṭikāṃ śubhrarūpāntu kanakāḍhyāñca kāminīḥ ||095:033||
arccayanti sadākālaṃ mathitā manmathena tu |
svakīyairbhuvanairdivyaiḥ pūjāṃ kurvanti tā striyaḥ ||095:034||
pralaye tu samutpanne devyāḥ puravaraiḥ saha |
vidyate dve mahādevi tadā līyanti devatāḥ ||095:035||
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi sakhāyānāntu lakṣaṇam |
dharmaśīlāstapoyuktāḥ satyavādi-jitendriyāḥ ||095:036||
mātsaryena parityaktāḥ sarvasattvahite ratāḥ |
priyavādinaḥ sotsāhā marttyaloka jugupsakāḥ ||095:037||
paraspara susantuṣṭā anukūlā sādhakasya tu |
īdṛśaiḥ sādhanaṃ kuryāt susaravāyaiḥ sahaiva tu ||095:038||
[śloko'yaṃ 46 saṃkhyākaḥ varttate mūlapustake]
brahmovāca |

yā nandā sā śivaḥ sākṣānnandārūpadharaḥ śivaḥ |
ubhayorantaraṃ nāsti nandāyāstu śivasya ca ||095:039||
na nandāparamaṃ dhyānaṃ na nandāparamaṃ tapaḥ |
na nandāparamaṃ tīrthaṃ śivaḥ sākṣāt prabhāṣate ||095:040||
lekhye'pi tiṣṭhate yasya idaṃ dhyānaṃ mahātapaḥ |
tasyāpi prīyate devī kiṃ punarmantra pūjitā ||095:041||
īśvara uvāca |

nāstikāya na dātavyaṃ na śambhu-guru-nindake |
piśunāya na dātavyaṃ devyā bhaktivivarjite ||095:042||
guru-dvija-deva-viṣṇu-kanyā-go-nindakena ca |
dātavyantu mahādevi devyā bhaktiratasya ca ||095:043||
anyathā tu varārohe hīyate śāstrasantatiḥ |
snehāllobhāt pradānena narakaṃ yānti rauravam ||095:044||
trimantrāṃ paṭhate yastu nandābhaktiparāyaṇaḥ |
so'cireṇaiva kālena siddhimiṣṭāṃ labhennaraḥ ||095:045||
yathoktaścaiva karttavyamādeśaḥ parameśvari |
śravaṇādbhāvayuktasya sarvakāmān prayacchati ||095:046||
daśānāṃ rājasūyānāmagniṣṭomaśatasya ca |
bhāvitaḥ phalamāpnoti koṭikoṭi guṇottaram ||095:047||
putrārthīṃ labhate putraṃ dhanārthī dhanabhāgbhavet |
mucyate bandhanādvaddho rogī rogāt pramucyate ||095:048||
yān yān kāmān naro bhaktyā pūjayannabhikāṃkṣate |
tāṃstān sa labhate śakra ityevaṃ śiva abravīt ||095:049||
devena kathitaṃ devyā śakrasya tu pitāmahāt |
mayā tava nṛpavyāghra kiṃ bhūyaḥ paripṛcchasi ||095:050||
[adhyā ye'smin ślokānāṃ saṃkhyā ṣaṣṭiparimitā aṃkitāsti]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe nandāmahābhāgyaṃ nāma pañcanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ka ga pustake adhyāya eṣa nāsti]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 096
ṣaṇṇavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

nṛpavāhana uvāca |

kena kena prakāreṇa devyā varṇāśramairvibho |
pūjanīyā svavṛttasthairetadicchāmi veditum ||096:001||
agastya uvāca |

sādhu rājan yathā pṛṣṭaṃ varṇāśramavibhāgataḥ |
pālanaṃ pūjanaṃ devyā pravakṣyāmi hyaśeṣataḥ ||096:002||
veda eva dvijātīnāṃ niḥśreyasakaraḥ paraḥ |
dṛṣṭādṛṣṭārthamicchadbhiḥ sevanīyaḥ sadā dvijaiḥ ||096:003||
mātṛtaḥ pitṛtaḥ śuddhaḥ pañcasapta tathā dvijaḥ |
saṃskārairgarbhadhārī ca tadā tasya kriyā tataḥ ||096:004||
yathā hi madyabhāṇḍasya śuddhiḥ kenāpi na vidyate |
pañcagavyaṃ na tadyāti evaṃ prāyaṃ śruteḥ kriyā ||096:005||
jātisaṃskārahīnasya dravyasaṃkarakāriṇaḥ |
śūdrānnabhojino rājan na vedo dadate phalam ||096:006||
śūdrasya annamaśitvā vedaṃ yadi udīrate |
ucchiṣṭa bhojī varṇānāṃ narake paryupāsate ||096:007||
cāṇḍāla caṇḍakarme ca vṛṣalīpatisannidhau |
yadi udīrate vedaṃ tadā vipro'pi tatsamaḥ ||096:008||
vedamantrān yadā vipraḥ śūdradravyeṇa tarpate |
sarpiṣā yavagodhūma tilapiṣṭaka śālibhiḥ ||096:009||
yāvatī tasya dravyasya rajoreṇu vidhīyate |
tāvatīśca mahāghore narake paryupāsate ||096:010||
na hi vedaṃ samāsādya vidhiṃ jahyāt dvijottama |
tasya eva hi ājñā na laṃghanīyā kadācana ||096:011||
cakravṛttidharā viprā uñchakāpota vṛttinaḥ |
dantolūkhālikāhārā vedānāṃ labhate phalam ||096:012||
nadīsaṃgamagoṣṭheṣu vicitraṣu taṭeṣu ca |
vicitrabhūmideśeṣu darbhadūrvāvṛteṣu ca ||096:013||
gṛheṣu śubhalipteṣu viṣṇu-sūrya-gṛheṣu ca |
paṭhitavyaḥ sadā vedaḥ svaravarṇa sulakṣitaḥ ||096:014||
plutadīrghakramahrasva sānusvāra sulakṣitām |
ṛcamuccārayet prājño na drutāṃ na vilambitām ||096:015||
śuklamālyadharo nityaṃ sugandhaḥ sukhavāsasaḥ |
netrāñjanaṃ niṣeveta dantadhāvanapūrvakam ||096:016||
ṛjupathe sadācāro ṛjusevī jitendriyaḥ |
paṭhanājapanāsakto likhanā śravaṇā tathā ||096:017||
nityaṃ daivatapūjāyāmauṣadhādhāraneṣu ca |
japahomārccane sakto vindate sukhamuttamam ||096:018||
na gacchenmaithunaṃ parve na devagurusannidhau |
na kuryājjale nādantu na vedyairna ca vatsaraiḥ ||096:019||
na pradhānajanavādaṃ nṛpākṣepaṃ kadācana |
nṛpa-bandhu-gurvamātya-bhiṣag-jyoti-purohitaiḥ ||096:020||
virodhānīha duḥkhāni sukhaṃ prītyā avāpnuyāt ||096:021||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe ācārakīrttanaṃ nāma saptanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ka ga pustake adhyāyo'yaṃ nāsti]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 097
saptanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

śakra uvāca |

gomedho aśvamedhaśca paśumedhādayo makhāḥ |
teṣu prāṇivadhastāta te ca svargādisādhanāḥ |
||097:001||
evaṃ pūrvāṃparārtheṣu virodhaḥ sumahān bhavet |
chindhi me saṃśayaṃ nātha sarvaśāstrārthapāraga ||097:002||
brahmovāca |

yajñārthaṃ paśavaḥ sṛṣṭā yajñeṣveṣāṃ vadhaḥ smṛtaḥ |
anyatra ghātanāddoṣo vāṅ-manaḥ-kāya-karmabhiḥ ||097:003||
devārthe pitṛkāryeṣu manuṣyārthe purandara |
vadhayan na bhavedena anyathā mahākilviṣam ||097:004||
navakṛṣarapūpāni pāyasaṃ madhusarpiṣī |
vṛthā māṃsañca nāśnīyāddeva-pitṛ-aho-mitam ||097:005||
na vṛthā ceṣṭayet kiñcit trivargasya virodhayā |
na ca vācaṃ vaded duṣṭāṃ na dīnāṃ na ca karkaśām ||097:006||
nāsahāyo brajedrātrau na paṃke na catuṣpathe |
na śūnyāgāre tiṣṭheta na ca parvatamastake ||097:007||
na śmaśāne na devasya prāsādeṣu kadācana |
na ca gavi prasūtāyāṃ viśvaseta satrījaneṣu ca ||097:008||
na vṛkṣārohaṇaṃ kuryāt na ca kūpāvalokanam |
na godvijahutāśānnaṃ madhyena gamanaṃ kvacit ||097:009||
na vahṇau tāpayeta pādaṃ na ca tamamabhilaṃghayet |
na sūryamavaloketa udayāstamane kvacit ||097:010||
na mukhena dhamedagniṃ na ca khaḍgaṃ tu laṃghayet |
tathā caivāyudhān sarvān yatropaskara mārjanīḥ ||097:011||
na pramattajanākīrṇe na ca strīvālasevite |
gṛhe vāmagamaṃ kuryānna ca viśvāsa krīḍanam ||097:012||
na viṣaṃ bhakṣayet prājño na bhujaṃgaiśca krīḍayet |
na gurudvijavedāṃśca nindayenna ca ākṣipet ||097:013||
sarvaṃ bhadraṃ brūyāt sarvakālaṃ śubhānanaḥ |
śuklavāsā śuciḥ sragvī na ca keśanakhaḥ sukhī ||097:014||
śuklamālyadharo nityaṃ sugandhaḥ sukhavāsasaḥ |
netrāñjanaṃ niṣeveta dantadhāvanapūrvakam ||097:015||
ṛjupathe sadācāro ṛjusevī jitendriyaḥ |
paṭhanājapanāsakto likhanā śravaṇā tathā ||097:016||
nityaṃ daivatapūjāyāmauṣadhādhāraneṣu ca |
japahomārccane sakto vindate sukhamuttamam ||097:017||
na gacchenmaithunaṃ parve na devagurusannidhau |
na kuryājjale nādantu na vedyairna ca vatsaraiḥ ||097:018||
na pradhānajanavādaṃ nṛpākṣepaṃ kadācana |
nṛpa-bandhu-garvamātya-bhiṣag-jyoti-purohitaiḥ ||097:019||
virodhānīha duḥkhāni sukhaṃ prītyā avāpnuyāt ||097:020||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe ācārakīrttanaṃ nāma saptanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ka ga pustake adhyāyo'yaṃ nāsti]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 098
aṣṭanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

evamācārayuktātmā satataṃ carccikārataḥ |
āpnuyāt sarvakāmāṃstu yathepsitamano'nugān ||098:001||
śakra uvāca |

nityaṃ ye bhagavatībhaktāstairnarairdvijasattama |
kiṃ kāryaṃ kiṃ vā no kāryaṃ tadvada pṛcchato mama ||098:002||
brahmovāca |

sarvā sarvagatā devī sarvadeva namaskṛtā |
yaṣṭavyā śuddhabhāvena na bhinnā pṛthageva sā ||098:003||
nāmabhedād bhavedbhinnā na bhinnā paramārthataḥ |
śivā nārāyaṇī gaurī carccikā vimalā umā ||098:004||
tārā śvetā mahāśvetā amvikā śivaśāsanāt |
yāvad dravyaṃ bhavedahaṃ tāvaddevī vyavasthitā ||098:005||
sā vandyā pūjanīyā ca satataṃ nandabhāvitaiḥ vijayārthaṃ nṛpaiḥ khaṅge chūrikāpādukāpaṭe ||098:006||
cāmuṇḍā citrarūpā vā likhitā vātha pustake |
dhvaje vā kārayecchakra sa nṛpo vijayed dviṣam ||098:007||
viśeṣācchrābaṇārabhya tasyāḥ pūjāntu kārayet |
pavitrārohaṇaṃ vatsa sarvaśāstreṣu gīyate ||098:008||
agnerbrahmasya pārvatyā gajavaktramahoragām |
skanda-bhānu-gaṇā-mātṛ-durgā-dharmeśa-go-vṛṣām ||098:009||
viṣṇoḥ kāmasya devasya śakrasya ca dināṃśagām |
pūjanīyā tu cāmuṇḍā caṇḍapāpavināśinī ||098:010||
sarvakāryādinā dattā ebhirnāmaiḥ purandara |
athavāṣāḍhamāse tu śrāvaṇe vāpi kārayet ||098:011||
saptamyāṃ vā trayodaśyāmadhivāsaṃ surādhipa |
sarvopahārasampannaṃ nandāyāḥ bhaktimāśritaḥ ||098:012||
śuklatastumayaṃ kārya pavitraṃ bahutantubhiḥ |
granthibhiḥ suvicitrābhi racitañcaiva mauktikaiḥ ||098:013||
sudhautaṃ bakṣayet tantuṃ rocanā śaśikuṃkumaiḥ |
tathā sarvāṇi dravyāṇi puṣpagandhaphalāni ca ||098:014||
naivedyāni vicitrāṇi vastrānādyābharaṇāni ca |
hematāramayān puṣpān kuśāni mṛdavastathā ||098:015||
susnāto mantravidhinā agnikāryaṃ tathā kuru |
tathā ca pūjayeddevīṃ pratimāṃ sthaṇḍile'pi vā ||098:016||
pāduke vātha khaḍge ca chūrikādhanuṣostathā |
mantradhāvananapūrvantu pañcagavyaṃ carūṃ kurū ||098:017||
dattvā diśāṃ baliṃ vatsa tathā kuryādhivāsanam |
sadaśairvastrapatrairvā sthāpayet tat pavitrakam ||098:018||
kṛtvā satrābhimantrādyaṃ naivedyaṃ ca nivedayet |
rātrau tu jāgaraṃ kuryāt sarvaśobhāsamanvitam ||098:019||
naṭanartakaveśyānāṃ saṃghāni muditāni ca |
tiṣṭhantu vādyagītābhiniratāni purandara ||098:020||
prabhātasamaye vatsa prāpte dadyāt punarvalim |
pratyūṣe vidhivat snātvā tathā devī hutāśanam ||098:021||
japtvā hutvātha kanyāśca striyo bhojyā dvijāstathā |
pavitrārohena vṛtte dakṣiṇāmupapādayet ||098:022||
yathā śaktā bhavecchakra nityaṃ kāryakāriṇā |
rājñā nānāvidhā bhakti akṣakrīḍā mṛgāvadham ||098:023||
dvijācāryaiśca svādhyāyaṃ na kāryaṃ kṛṣigovṛṣaiḥ |
bālai srībhiśca ca ātmīyaṃ dināni daśa paṃcavā ||098:024||
devyā vyāpāranāmābhiḥ karttavyaṃ satataṃ hare |
tathā sampūrṇa karttavyaṃ punaḥ kuryāt pavitrakam ||098:025||
evaṃ yaḥ kārayedvatsa tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu |
sarva-yajña-vrata-dāna sarvatīthābhiṣecanam ||098:026||
prāpnuyānnātra sandeho yasmāt sarvagatā śivā |
nādhayo na ca duḥkhāni na pīḍā na ca vyādhayaḥ ||098:027||
na bhayaṃ śatrujaṃ tasya na grahaiḥ pīḍyate kvacit |
sidhyante sarvakāryāṇi api yāni mahāntyapi ||098:028||
nātaḥ parataraṃ vatsa manye puṇyavivṛddhaye |
narāṇāñca nṛpāṇāñca srīṇāñcāpi viśeṣataḥ ||098:029||
saubhāgyajananaṃ vatsa tava snehātprakāśitam |
mayāpi te nṛpaśreṣṭha yathāvadupapāditam ||098:030a-d||
śravaṇādapi puṇyāya kiṃ punaḥ kāraṇādvibho ||098:030ef||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe pavitrārohaṇaṃ nāmāṣṭanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ka ga pustake adhyāyo'yaṃ nāsti]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 099
navanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi sarvābhyudayavardhanam |
yatkṛtvā bhavate rājan sarvavarṇo'pi cānagha ||099:001||
nabhomāse tu samprāpte naktāhāro jitendriyaḥ |
prātaḥ snāyī sadādhyāyī agnikārya parāyaṇaḥ ||099:002||
devīṃ saṃpūjayedvatsa punnāgavilvacampakaiḥ |
dhūpantu guggulaṃ dadyānnaivedyaṃ ghṛtapācitam ||099:003||
[pāvitam ka]
kṣīrānnaṃ dadhibhaktañca athavā śākayāvakam |
japaṃ kuryāttu mantrasya sahasraṃ śatameva vā ||099:004||
devvāyāstraṃ samarpyeta yāvat pūrṇavrato bhavet |
pūrṇe vrate tato vatsa kanyācāryadvijān striyaḥ ||099:005||
bhojayet pūjayedbhaktyā hemabhūvastragovṛṣaiḥ |
abhāvāt maṃtrajāpantu nityaṃ kārya nṛpottama ||099:006||
[śaktyā ka ka; bhūgīvṛṣaiḥ ka ga; dvijottama ka]
yaḥ kuryāt satataṃ bhaktyā so'pi tatphalamāpnuyāt |
na ca vyādhirjarā mṛtyurna bhayaṃ cora -sambhavam ||099:007||
[tattulyamāpnuyāt ka; cārisambhavam ka ga]
bhavate nandābhaktasya ante ca padamavyayam ||099:008||
atha mantrapadāni bhavanti |
oṃ nande nandinī sarvārthasādhanī |

(mūlavidyā)
oṃ nuṃ nande hṛdayam |
oṃ tuṃ nandinī śiraḥ |
oṃ sarvāni śikhā |
oṃ arthasādhinī kavacam |

oṃ nuṃ netram |
oṃ namaḥ humÌphaṭ astram |
oṃ nandinī upacārahṛdayam ||099:009||
tṛtīyāmatha pañcamyāṃ caturthyāmaṣṭamīṣu ca |
navamyaṃ, paurṇamāsyāñca ekādaśyāñca dvādaśīm ||099:010||
ṣaṣṭhyāṃ caiva vidyeṣā pūjanīyā viśeṣataḥ |
nandāmuddiśya yo dadyācchrāvaṇe govṛṣaṃ sitam ||099:011||
[vighneśa ka ga]
sa labhediṣṭakāmāni ante lokañca śāśvatam |
navamyāṃ yaḥ samuddiśya dadyātgāṃ kācanaṃ pi vā ||099:012||
sa vrajed dhūtapātastu nandālokaṃ tanukṣaye |
āśvine navarātrāṇi upavāsa ayācitaiḥ ||099:013||
kṛtvā devīṃ prapūjyeta aṣṭamyāmapare'hani |
hema-vastra-maṇi-puṣpa-nānācitra-vibhūṣaṇaiḥ ||099:014||
dānaṃ ca kācanaṃ deyaṃ nandāśāstrārthapārage |
sa dhūtapāpasaṃghātaḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ ||099:015||
vimāne cāmarotkṣipte cārū cākṣaraśobhite |
gacchate nandalokantu yatra devī purārihā ||099:016||
[cāruvatsasuśobhitaḥ ka ga; surārihā ka ]
ramate kanyā koṭibhirapsarogaṇasevitaḥ |
tadante āgataścātra pṛthivyāmekarāḍ bhavet ||099:017||
[kalpakoṭibhi ka]
nandābhaktaḥ śive bhakte nandāyātraika tatparaḥ |
kārtike pūjayitvā tu devīṃ yāti gajāhvayaiḥ ||099:018||
annadānaṃ daded vipra kanyāyāṃ strījaneṣu ca |
śvetāni caiva vastrāṇi tathā deyāni dakṣiṇā ||099:019||
[anuyānaṃ ga]
mucyate sarvapāpaistu janmāntarakṛtairapi |
ihatraiva bhavedyogī paratra padamavyayam ||099:020||
mārgasya vidhivatsnātvā devīṃ pūjaya kuṃkumaiḥ |
naivedyaṃ pūṣpapūrṇāśca deyā kanyāśca brāhmaṇe ||099:021||
[puṣpavarṇāśca ka]
bhojayed dakṣayed vatsa vastraiḥ kīṭakulodbhavaiḥ |
prāpnuyāt sarvakāmāni sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate ||099:022||
pauṣe devīṃ samādhāya pūjayejjavajaiḥ srajaiḥ |
naivedyaṃ śālibhaktañca kanyā bhojayet bhakṣayet ||099:023||
pītairvastraistathā deyā śayyā devyā tulodbhavā |
anena vidhinā vatsa sākṣāddevī prasīdati ||099:024||
[tilodbhavā ka]
dadate kāmikān bhogān ante ca svapuraṃ nayet |
māghe tu pūjayeddevīṃ kundajairvidhiṃvat srajaiḥ ||099:025||
[surapura ka]
kuṃkumena sadarpeṇa tathā samupalepayet |
snāpitāṃ vidhivatpūrvaṃ tataḥ kanyāstu bhojayet ||099:026||
[tataḥ kanyāṃstu na bhojayet ka]
dvijāṃśca nandinī bhaktān vidhinā ghṛtapāyasaiḥ |
dakṣiṇāṃ tilahomaiśca yathāśaktyā pradāpayet ||099:027||
[caṇḍinibhaktān ka ga]
vidhūta-pāpa-kalilaḥ sarvabhoga-dhanānvitaḥ |
viśatrurbahuputraśca bhavate narasattamaḥ ||099:028||
dehānte nandinīlokaṃ sarvadevanamaskṛtam |
vrajate nātra sandeho anena vidhinā nṛpa ||099:029||
[sarvadevīnamaskṛtaḥ ka]
phālgunyāṃ pūjayeddevīṃ sahakārasrajaiḥ śubhaiḥ |
tathā naivedyabhakṣyāṇi śarkarāmadhunā saha ||099:030||
bhojayet kanyakā biprān dakṣiṇā sitavāsasī |
anena vidhinā bhogī devīlokaṃ ca gacchati ||099:031||
saṃprāpte caitramāse tu devīmijyād damanakaiḥ |
naivedyaṃ laḍḍukā deyāstathā kanyāśca bhojayet ||099:032||
[āmalakai ka]
striyaśca raktavastraiśca dakṣitavyā yathāvidhiḥ |
anena sarvavidhinā prāpnuyādavicāraṇāt ||099:033||
devīlokaṃ vrajedvatsa yatra bhogā nirantarāḥ |
vaiśākhe pūjayeddevīṃ karṇikārasrajaiḥ śubhaiḥ ||099:034||
naivedyaṃ saktavaḥ khaṃḍaṃ kanyāścaiva bhojayet |
śubhāni hemavastrāṇi deyāni dvijasattamaiḥ ||099:035||
devī suprītaye vatsa sarvadevamanuttamaiḥ |
kṛtavāmÌstu vidhireṣa tathā gandharva-kinnaraiḥ ||099:036||
jyeṣṭhe tu śaṃkarī pūjyā raktāśokakṛraṃṭakaiḥ |
tathā deyañca naivedyaṃ ghṛtapūrṇa ca kanyakāḥ ||099:037||
[jyeṣṭhayāṃ ka]
bhojanīyāstathā dakṣed gobhūdāna hiraṇyataḥ |
tathā deyāḥ jalakumbhāḥ sampūrṇā vāsitāḥ śubhāḥ ||099:038||
anena vāruṇān bhogān devī kṣipraṃ prayacchati |
āṣāḍhe pūjayeddevīṃ padmanīlotpalairdalaiḥ ||099:039||
naivedyaṃ śarkarābhaktaṃ sadadhi bhaktapāyasam |
kanyā dvijāḥ striyo bhojyāddakṣayecca tathā ca tān ||099:040||
nānā-hemāmvara-rāga-tila-bhū-aśva-mauktikaiḥ |
pūjyā bhagavatī bhaktyā sarvavarṇa-prasiddhaye ||099:041||
nandā sunandā kanakā umā durgā kṣamāvatī |
gaurī sarveśvarī śvetā nārāyaṇī sutārakā ||099:042||
ambikā ceti nāmāni śrāvaṇāderanukramāt |
ye ca kīrtyanti utthāya te narā dhūtakilviṣāḥ ||099:043||
bhavanti nṛpaśārdūṃlāḥ pṛthivyāṃ dhanasaṅkulāḥ |
etāni pathi-saṃgrāma-vṛddhipīḍāsu nityaśaḥ ||099:044||
[dhana sampadā ka]
smarrastarati ghorāṇi carciketi yaduttamam |
vratānāṃ pravaraṃ vatsa samāsārdha tu pādataḥ ||099:045||
[durgāṇi ka ga]
māsaṃ vāpi prakarttavyaṃ śrāvaṇādi krameṇa tu |
nāpuṇyaiḥ prāpyate vatsa narairnṛpavaraistathā ||099:046||
prāpyate bhagavatībhāvaṃ yasya tuṣṭā tu nandinī ||099:047||
[bhavatībhāvā kha, bhagavatī bhāvā ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe nandāvrataṃ nāma navanavatitamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye purāṇe devī nandāvratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 100
śatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

sarveṣāñcaiva pātrāṇāṃ devī pātrantu śaṃkarī |
tāntu pūjaya vidyaiṣā dṛṣṭā-dṛṣṭa-pradāyikā ||100:001||
brahmaśāstra vidhiḥ śakra kathitā vijayāvahā |
śakreti paurṇimā tāta śrāvaṇasya śubhā vahā ||100:002||
[bhāvitāvahā ka ga; mātā ka ga]
śakra uvāca |

vijayā yā samākhyātāsarvakāma prasiddhaye |
tāmahaṃ śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ surasattamaḥ ||100:003||
brahmovāca |

putrārthaṃ rājyavidyārthaṃ yaśaḥ saubhāgyato'pi vā |
vijayārogyakāmāya vijayāṃ kurvīta paurṇimām ||100:004||
[pūṇimām ka]
hemaṃ vā rājataṃ vāpi bhaikṣyaṃ khaḍgaṃ ca pāduke |
pratimāṃ vāpi kurvīta sarvalakṣaṇasaṃyutām ||100:005||
tāmādāya śubhe ṛkṣe śuklavastravibhūṣitām |
yavaśālyaṃkuropetāmātapatravibhūṣitām ||100:006||
devīṃ suśobhanāṃ vastraiḥ kalpayet tatra tāṃ nyaset |
hutvā hutāśanaṃ mantraistato devīṃ tu vinyaset ||100:007||
rocanā-candana-candrai rūpalipya prapūjayet |
nānāpuṣpaviśeṣaistu dhūpagandhānubhojanaiḥ ||100:008||
pūjayedvidhivaddevīṃ tathā bījāni āharet |
yavagodhūma mudgādi śāliyaṣṭika āḍhakī ||100:009||
[bedīm ? ]
tilamāṣāḥ pramāthī ca śyāmākā navavālakāḥ |
bilvāmradāḍimo coddhūmo ca kāpitthanāgarān ||100:010||
[nāraṃgā ka]
vadarān bījapūrāṃśca udumvara ākheṭakān |
dāpayeccaiva bhaktyā vai naivedyānyaparāni ca ||100:011||
phalārthantu phalā devyā jayārthaṃ yava aṃkurān |
puṣpaṃ saubhāgyakāmāya ratnānyāyurdhanāya ca ||100:012||
dhanuḥ śatruvināśāya priyamicchāya tat bhavān |
annaṃ sarvārthakāmāya yathālābhantu dāpayet ||100:013||
tataḥ kṣamāpayeddevī vidyāṃ gṛhyeva prārthitām |
putrārtha bhojayedvālān vijayāya striyo dvijān ||100:014||
[gṛhe ca ka]
dharmārtha ceva bhojyeta anayā vidyābhimantritām |
dakṣiṇāṃ ca gurvācārye kanyakā brāhmaṇeṣu ca ||100:015||
dāpayet yathāśaktyā tu tathā tamanugṛhya ca |
bhojyāgraṃ putrakāmena grāmaṃ vidyābhimantritam ||100:016||
bhoktavyaṃ pṛthakpātreṇa na ca kurvīta śaṃkaram |
anayā vidhipūrvaṃ tu mantramatraiva vidyate ||100:017||
[putraiṇa kha]
tadyaḥ pṛthivyāṃ retastāmeha dadatu yo māṃ bhakṣitāni |
vidyā prayacchannaṣṭau putrān janayate vedavedāṃgapāragān ||100:018||
[optaḥ ka]
yo'dhītya na prayacchet so'putro'puṃsako bhavati |
ahaṃ vīryenāhaṃ valena dhanena |
oṃ namo bhagavate akṣīṇaretase svāhā ||100:019||
ratikāle hi cintayed daivataṃ tridaśeśvaram |
yasya retena loko'yaṃ bhūṣitaḥ pāvano bhuvi ||100:020||
oṃ retāya mahāretāya sarvavīrya mahābale |
kāmāya kāmadevāya mama kāmān prayacchatu-ṭhaṃṭhaṃ ||100:021||
[mahātape ga]
anayābhi mantritaṃ śayanaṃ bhajet |

prayacchatyaṣṭau putrān yadi mohaṃ na gacchati |
evaṃ vidyāṃ gṛhītvātu devīṃ nityaṃ prapūjayet ||100:022||
bhavate sarvakāmānāṃ siddhimiṣṭāṃ parājitām |
yānīha phalapuṣpāṇi utpadyante tu prāvṛṣi ||100:023||
[yātīha ka ga]
devyā viprāya kanyāyāṃ gurave api dāpayet |
yathālābhaṃ śrutaṃ vatsa deyaṃ puṣpaṃ phalāni ca ||100:024||
śrāvaṇī navamī yā sā āśvinī kārtikī pi vā |
sthātavyamanena vidhinā avaśyaṃ siddhimicchatā ||100:025||
homena vratacaryeṇa carumantra-prasādanāt |
aputro labhate putraṃ dhanaṃ saubhāgya jīvitam ||100:026||
athavā anayā vidyā lakṣaṇā bṛhatī sitā |
rājapūrakavidyāni vaṭa śṛṅgādivādarāt ||100:027||
[bīja ka ga; vacasvargāṃniṃvāraṇāt kha]
nāgakeśarapuṣpāṇi tadante labhate phalam |
phalaṃ sarpiḥ jala dānāt phalaṃ prāpnoti vidyayā ||100:028||
[caraḥ ka ga]
ajayo bhavate loko vidyādhara-dharādhipaḥ |
etatte sarvamākhyātaṃ vijayākhyaṃ vratottamam ||100:029||
siddhidaṃ sarvalokānāṃ vidhinā tapasevanāt ||100:030||
[upasevanāt ka]
iti śrī devipurāṇe vijayāvrataṃ nāma śatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devyavatāre vijayā vratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 101
ekādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi rūpasaubhāgyakārakam |
nakṣatravidhinā vatsa yathā tuṣyati śaṃkarī ||101:001||
mārgādārabhya mūlena pādau jātimayaiḥ srajaiḥ |
pūjayetsopavāsastu nakṣatroktaṃ tu pāraṇam ||101:002||
[māghādārabhya ga]
yavānnaṃ haviṣā siddhaṃ brāhmane jaṃghe prapūjayet |
kahlārairmṛgarājaiśca tilamāṣānnabhojanam ||101:003||
tenaivaṃ prathamaṃ viprā aśvinyāṃ jānūni yajet |
kundaiḥ asitapuṣpaiśva bhojanaṃ dadhiśarkarā ||101:004||
[sugita kha]
āṣāḍhadvaye'pi tāṃ devīṃ vilvapatraiḥ prapūjayet |
nakṣatrāṃte tu bhuṃjīyāt brāhmaṇān tacca pāraṇam ||101:005||
[rupe'pi cāru ka ga]
yugmaṃ phālgunaṃ guhyaṃ tu pārayantyā prapūjayet |
dadhibhaktaṃ tu naivedyaṃ koṭiñca kṛtikairyajet ||101:006||
[puṣpa kānte'nyagṛhmaṃ tu uṣānatyā prapūjayet ga]
damanaiḥ sitapuṣpaiśca laḍḍūkā devī bhojane |
bhādrapade dvau ca pārśve pūjayetkusumaiḥ sitaiḥ ||101:007||
kṣīrānnaṃ devī viprāṇāṃ nakṣatrānte tu bhojanam |
pauṣyā kukṣigatā devyā sahakārasrajairyajet ||101:008||
[dadhi ka ga]
ghṛtamāṣānna bhojanaṃ tu anurādhā uro yajet |
karṇikārasrajaiḥ pītairbhojanaṃ ghṛtapācitam ||101:009||
[kṣīrapiṣṭaṃ sānnabhojyaṃ kha]
pṛṣṭhadeśaṃ dhaniṣṭhāsu hemapuṣpaiḥ prapūjayet |
karṇapatrañca naivedyaṃ devīṃ śākhāsu pūjayet ||101:010||
marupatraiḥ sugandhaiśca deyaṃ bhojyaṃ tu pāyasam |
karau kareṇa pūjyantu uśīratagarādibhiḥ ||101:011||
guḍaṃ kṣīraṃ tu naivedyaṃ mañjulāśca punarvasau |
kuṃkumena prapūjyeta deyaṃ bhojyantu ṣaṣṭhikam ||101:012||
[aṃgulīśca ka ga; pañcakam kha]
naravān bhujaṃgadaivatye punnāgādibhiḥ pūjayet |
bhojyantuḥ mārjjitā deyā grīvāṃ jyeṣṭhāsu pūjayet ||101:013||
sitamālābhirdevyāyāḥ deyaṃ bhojyaṃ ghṛtādikam |
rakta puṣpadalaiḥ karṇaiḥ pūjayet bhojayeddhaviḥ ||101:014||
[rambhā ka ga]
puṣye bhūyantu padmādyaiḥ śarkarānnaṃ tu bhojayet |
daśanān svātinā sevyā suraktaiḥ kuḍmalairyajet ||101:015||
hāsyantu śatabhiṣaijyā nāgakeśaracandanaiḥ |
kharjūraśarkarābhojyaṃ nāsikāsu maghāṃ yajet ||101:016||
yavapuṣpaistathā bhojyaṃ godhūmakṛtisaṃskṛtam |
mṛganetre tu devyāyāḥ sugandhaiḥ kusumairyajet ||101:017||
citrācitrasrajairdevyā lalāṭaṃ citrabhojanam |
bharaṇī śirasā devyāṃ campakādi srajairyajet ||101:018||
kṣīrānnabhojanaṃ deyamārdrakeśān prapūjayet |
jātyādi kusumairdevyāḥ sarvātmāni ca bhojanam ||101:019||
[sarvānnāni ka ga]
nakṣatramātarā hyetāḥ rūpaputrārthibhiḥ sadā |
śambhuṃ vāpyathavā viṣṇuṃ ghṛtahomānnadakṣiṇā ||101:020||
deyaṃ vastrayugaṃ vipre sapatnīke jitendriye |
devyāśāstrārthakuśale śivajñānaviśārade ||101:021||
sampūrṇa-candravadanā padma-patrāyatekṣaṇā |
śobhanā daśanā śubhrā karṇau cāpi sumāṃsalau ||101:022||
ṣaṭpadodaranibhaiḥ keśaistathā kokilanādinī |
tāmroṣṭhī padmapatrākṣī suhastā stananāmitā ||101:023||
[ṣaṭpadodarataiḥ ka ga; lalanāmitā kha]
nābhiḥ pradakṣiṇāvarttā rambhādalanibhoru ca |
suśroṇī mṛdumadhyā ca suśliṣṭāṃguliśobhanā ||101:024||
pramadā subhagā bhartturmanuṣyo'pi mahābhujaḥ |
pīnavakṣāḥ pṛthubhāvaḥ pūrṇacandranibhānanaḥ ||101:025||
sitadanto gajagāmī mahābalaparākramaḥ |
priyaḥ sarvasya lokasya padmapatrāyatekṣaṇaḥ ||101:026||
mṛduvākhāsyayuktaśca strīṇāṃ ca manohārakaḥ |
kāmatulyo mahāvipro vratenānena jāyate ||101:027||
[sarvaśāstrārthavettā ka ga]
nāriyogaśca iṣṭānāmarthānāñca śubhāgamaḥ |
nakṣatrākhyaṃ mahāpuṣyaṃ vratānāntu vratottamam ||101:028||
āpatsvapi na bhedaṃ tu priyaiḥ kāryaṃ yaducyate |
api doṣātmakairbhāvairna tyājyaṃ munisattama ||101:029||
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe nakṣatravrataṃ nāmaikādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devyāvatāre nakṣatravratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 102
dvyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

āṣāḍhe toyadhenūṃ yo ghṛtaṃ bhādrapade tathā |
māghe tu tiladhenūḥ syātsa dattvā labhate hitam ||102:001||
vidyādhara uvāca |

[vidyādhana ga]
kāni dānāni devyāyā deyāni munisattama |
kāni pātrāṇi deśaṃ vā kālaṃ dravyavidhiṃ vada ||102:002||
tānyahaṃ śrotumicchāmi kathayasva prasādataḥ |

agastya uvāca |

nyāyato yāni prāptāni śākānyapi nṛpottama ||102:003||
[śālānyapi ga]
tāni devyāni devyāyāḥ kanyakā yoṣitāṃ sadā |
tadbhakteṣu ca vipreṣu apareṣu ca nityaśaḥ ||102:004||
viśeṣāt prāvṛṣi vatsa devī kāmān prayacchati |
deśaṃ nandāgayāśailaṃ gaṃgānarmadāpuṣkaram ||102:005||
vārāṇasyāṃ kurukṣetraṃ prayāgaṃ jambukeśvaram |
kedāraṃ bhīmanādañca daṇḍakaṃ puṣkarāhvayam ||102:006||
[bhīmadānañca kha]
someśvaraṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ tathā amarakaṇṭakam |
kālañjaraṃ tathā vindhyaṃ yatra vāsaṃ guhasya tu ||102:007||
[gomeśvaram ka ga]
dravyaṃ bhū-hema-go-dhānyaṃ tilavastraghṛtādikam |
vidhinā upavāsena ekānnaṃ naktabhojanam ||102:008||
śucinā bhāvapūtena kṣānti-satya-vratādinā |
api sarṣapamātro'pi dātāraṃ tārayeddadat ||102:009||
yaḥ punarvidhinā vatsa devīmuddiśya prāvṛṣi |
vipreṣu viprakanyāsu tilādīn saṃprayacchati ||102:010||
tadā saṃtuṣyate devī acireṇa tu vidyayā |
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi nandā devyāḥ paraṃ vratam ||102:011||
yena saṃprīyate vatsa acireṇa mahātmanām |
hemotthaṃ pāduke kārye yathāśaktyā tu bhāvitaḥ ||102:012||
[homācca kha]
āmradūrvākṣatabilvapatraiḥ pūjitamantaḥ |
devīṃ sampūjayitvā tu sthaṃḍile pratimāsu vā ||102:013||
tadbhaktāya ca viprāya kanyāsu ca nivedayet |
mucyate sarvapāpebhyo svargalokaṃ ca gacchati ||102:014||
tanukṣaye mahāprājño vidyādharapatirbhavet |
kālena cehāyātaḥ pṛthivyā nṛpasattama ||102:015||
bhavate nātra sandeho brahmaṇedaṃ ca bhāṣitam |
prajāpatirvaśiṣṭhena kaśyapasya ca dakṣayoḥ ||102:016||
tathā tvamapi rājendra kuruṣvedaṃ padavratam |
mahadaiśvaryakāṃkṣāya devīpratyakṣakāriṇe ||102:017||
iti śrīdevī purāṇe padavrataṃ nāma dvyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |
|
[ityādye devyavatāre padavratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 103
tryadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

athātaḥ sampravakṣyāmi tava dānamanuttamam |
yena tuṣṭā purā devī śakrasya tu mahātmanaḥ ||103:001||
[śukrasya ka ga]
nīlāṃ vā yadi vā śvetāṃ pāṭalāṃ kapilāṃ pivā |
aduḥravāṃ vatsavālāñca sukhadohāṃ gavāṃ nṛpa ||103:002||
ādāya vidhivaddevīṃ pūjayet srajapaṃkajaiḥ |
dhūpañca pañcaniryāsaṃ saturuṣkāgurūcandanam ||103:003||
dattvā mantrapūjāntu devyā naivedyamupakalpayet |
pāyasaṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktaṃ kṣamāpayet tathā tu tām ||103:004||
[dugdhapunantu kha]
dvijāya śivabhaktāya nivedayet savatsagām |
sahemavastrakāñcayāñca mahatpuṇyamavāpnuyāt ||103:005||
yāvat yadromasaṃkhyānaṃ tāvaddevyāḥ pure vaset |
ihatra vigatapāpo jāyate nṛpasattamaḥ ||103:006||
manunāyaṃ vidhiṃ kṛtvā prāptaṃ lokamanuttamam |
ahaṃ te kathayiṣyāmi śṛṇu rājan yathāvidhi ||103:007||
[yamunāyā kha]
śubhāṃ hemamayīṃ gāvaṃ kārayedrajatakhurām |
tāṃ vastraprāvṛtāṃ kṛtvā pūjayed danudaryahām ||103:008||
[devīm ka ga; gandhadarpahām kha]
vicitra citrapuṣpaiśca gandhadhūpanivedanaiḥ |
tathā kṣamāpayeddevīṃ tāṃ gāṃ tatraivamānayet ||103:009||
devī tvadīya ādeśāt tava bhakteṣu dīyate |
punastāṃ viprarājāya dāpayet śivabhāvite ||103:010||
akṣayaphalakāmena prāyaścitaviśuddhaye |
manunā cīrṇamāsīcca vratamanyaiḥ nṛpottamaiḥ ||103:011||
[āpnoti; samādhāyāmṛtopam ka ga]
saptapūrvānparān vaṃśānapi kilviṣasaṃsthitān |
uddhṛtya nayate vatsa devīlokamanuttamam ||103:012||
[sātu kha, satya ka]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe hemagovrataṃ nāma tryadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devyavatāre hemagovratam ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 104
caturadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

mārge rasottamaṃ dadyāt ghṛtaṃ poṣe mahāphalam |
tilā māghe muniśreṣṭha dhānyāḥ saptātha phālgune ||104:001||
[bratam ka ga; citrā ka ga]
vicitrāṇi ca vastrāṇi caitre dadyāt dvijottamaḥ |
vaiśākhe yavagodhūmān jyeṣṭhe toyabhṛtān ghaṭān ||104:002||
āṣāḍhe candanaṃ deyaṃ karpūrañaca mahāphalam |
navanītaṃ nabho māsi caitra proṣṭha pade matam ||104:003||
guḍaśarkaraśaṃḍādyān laḍaḍūkānaśvine mune |
dīpadānaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ kārttike yaḥ prayacchati ||104:004||
sarvakāmānavāpnoti kramānmārgādudāhṛtān |
dhenūṃ pauṣe ghṛtāṃ dadyāt māghe tilamayīṃ tathā ||104:005||
jyeṣṭhe toyamayī dadyāt ghṛta vatsāṃ mahāphalām |
surūpāṃ śrāvaṇe dadyāt gāṃ mahāphaladāyikām ||104:006||
[mṛtavatsāṃ ga; arupo ga]
sarvahemamayaiḥ śṛṃgaiḥ raupyapādairudāhṛtām |
kāmÌsyapātrāṃ saghaṇṭāṃ tuḥ kiṃkiṇīrupaśobhitām ||104:007||
sayugāṃ sasrajāṃ vatsa dātavyā vidhinānayā |
devī brahmeśasūryaṃ vā viṣṇuṃ vātha yathāvidhi ||104:008||
[mayā ka ga]
svabhāvacitta sampanno pūjayitvā dvijottama |
dātavyā vītarāge tu kāmakrodhavivarjitam ||104:009||
[subhāva vittasampanno kha]
ayācake sadācāre vinīte niyamānvite |
go pradātā labhet kāmān svarge loke manoramān ||104:010||
agastya uvāca |

tiladhenūṃ pravakṣyāmi durgā yena prasīdati |
api duṣkṛta karmāṇi yāṃ dattvā nirmalo bhavet ||104:011||
pratyakṣā yena devī tu rājyaputrasuravāvahā |
bhavate tvacireṇaiva tāṃ śrṛṇuṣva nṛpottama ||104:012||
devadevīmanujñāpya snātvā caiva jitendriyaḥ |
pūjayet puṣpa-gaṃdhānna-dhūpa-dīpa-pavitrakaiḥ ||104:013||
[vicitrakai ga]
hutvā hutāśane devīṃ tathā droṇamayīṃ kuru |
āḍhakena bhavedvatsa sarvaratnavibhūṣitām ||104:014||
hemaśrṛṃgīṃ śaphaiḥ rupyai gaṃdhaghrāṇāṃ suśobhanām |
mukhaṃ guḍamayaṃ kāryaṃ jihvāmannamayī tathā ||104:015||
kambalaṃ śuklasūtrāṃ tu pādo ikṣumayāstathā |
tāmraṃ pṛṣṭhe bhavet tasyā īkṣaṇaṃ maṇimoktikaiḥ ||104:016||
[sūkṣmasūtram ka ga]
cārupatramayau kaṇau dantaiḥ phalamayaiḥ śubhaiḥ |
navanītastanāṃ kuryāt puṣpamālāmayaṃ kuru ||104:017||
puñchañca maṇimuktaistu phalai śuciṃ samarpayet |
śubhāṃ vastrayugacchannāṃ cāruchatravibhūṣitām ||104:018||
īdṛksaṃsthānasampannāṃ kṛtvā śraddhāsamanvitaḥ |
kāmÌsyopadohanaṃ dadyāt devyā me prīyatāmiti ||104:019||
mantrābhimantritaṃ kṛtvā tadbhaktāya nivedayet |
yāvanti tilavastrāṇi dhātumūlaphalasya ca ||104:020||
vidyante rajareṇūṃṣi tāvatsvarge vasennaraḥ |
pitṛn vigatapāpāmÌstu kṛtvādhastha gatānapi ||104:021||
[dhenugatāmapi kha]
prāpya devyāḥ śubhaṃ lokaṃ sthāpayedavicāraṇāt |
tasmin me ramate vatsa yāvadācandratārakam ||104:022||
tathā kālādihāyāto jāyate pṛthivīpatiḥ |
vinaya-teja-sampanno bahuputraḥ sukhānvitaḥ ||104:023||
[nirvaira kha]
punardevyāvrate nityaṃ pūjane vidhivattathā |
prāpya yogamaheśvaryaṃ prāpnoti padamavyayam ||104:024||
[rato ka ga]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe tilaghenurnāma caturadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devyavatāre tiladhenuḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 105pañcādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

tilābhāve pradātavyā sarpirdhenū vijānatā |
snāpayitvā bhavānīntu ghṛtakṣīrairyathāvidhiḥ ||105:001||
pūjayet srajamālābhi rnaivedyaiḥ sumanoramaiḥ |
āharetsarvadravyāṇi upakalpeta tatra tān ||105:002||
gavye sarpiṣi kumbhe tu puṣpamālāvibhūṣite |
kāṃsyapātraṃ tathā vastraischādayīta vijānatā ||105:003||
hiraṇyagarbhasahitaṃ maṇividrumamauktikaiḥ |
pādānikṣumayān kuryāt kuryādraupyāṃstathā śaphān ||105:004||
hema cakṣustathā śṛṃgo kṛṣṇāgurumayai śubhaiḥ |
saptadhānyāni tatpārśve patrorṇena ca kambalam ||105:005||
[saptadhānyau ca ga]
ghrāṇo tagarakarpūṃro stanāḥ phalamayā śubhāḥ |
mukhañca gurukṣīreṇa sitāṃ jihvāṃ prakalpayet ||105:006||
pucchaṃ kṣaumamayaṃ kāryaṃ romāṇi sitasarṣapaiḥ |
tāmraṃ pṛṣṭhaṃ vicitrantu sneharūpā manoramā ||105:007||
vidhinā ghṛtavatsaṃ ca kuryād lakṣaṇalakṣitam |
etau kṛtvā tathā nandāṃ pūjayitvā vidhānataḥ ||105:008||
[ghṛtaratnaṃ kha]
tadbhaktāya pradātavyā maṃgalāśāstrapārage |
mātre sadopakārāya gṛhna me'nugrahāya ca ||105:009||
[sāte manaupakārāya ka ga]
prīyatāṃ nandinī devī maṅgalā carcikā umā |
ityuktvā arcayeddhenūṃ kṛtvā nandāmanonugām ||105:010||
anena vidhinā deyā yavaśālīkṣūkalpitā |
hemaratnānnavastrā vā deyā gaurvidhinā nayā ||105:011||
mucyate sarvapāpebhyaḥ sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt |
yatra kṣīravahā nadyo yatra sarpirvahā hradāḥ ||105:012||
payasā kardamā yatra tasmin loke mahīyate |
teṣāṃ svāmitvamāpnoti mudayā parayā yutaḥ ||105:013||
diśāṃ pūrvāparāṃstāta ātmanastvekaviṃśatiḥ |
bhūyaḥ pṛthvī śatāmeti ihaloke samāgataḥ ||105:014||
[daśa pūrvā parāstatra kha; pṛthvīgatām kha]
sakāmānāmiyaṃ vyuṣṭiḥ tatastāvadudāhṛtā |
devyā lokamavāpnoti niṣkāmo ghṛtadhenudaḥ ||105:015||
[vuddhiḥ ga; dhenūbhiḥ kha]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe ghṛtadhenūrnāma pañcādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye devyavatāre ghṛtadhenūḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 106
ṣaḍdhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

agastya uvāca |

toyadhenūṃ śruṇu vatsa yathā devī prasīdati |
kumbhaṃ toyasamāpūrṇaṃ ratnavastrayugānvitam ||106:001||
[atra vatsa yugānvitam ka ga]
samastabījasaṃyuktaṃ dūrvāpallava śobhitam |
murābālamuśīraṃ ca kuṣṭāmalakacandanaiḥ ||106:002||
mālācchatramupānahaṃ tilapātraiścaturyutam |
dadhikṣaudraghṛtaṃ pātraṃ vidhānamupakalpayet ||106:003||
vatsakaṃ pūjayedvatsa kṛtaṃ havimayaṃ budhaḥ |
devīmambharcya vidhivat sopavāso ca naktavān ||106:004||
devyā bhakte pradātavyaṃ sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt |
jayārisūdanī devī devānāṃ bhayanāśinī ||106:005||
vedamāte vare durge sarvege śubhade namaḥ ||106:006||
[sarvāga ga]
anena vatsa mantreṇa tāṃ dānāyābhimantrayet |
devī me prīyatāṃ nityaṃ yathepsita phalā śivā ||106:007||
[rathe kha]
iti śrī devīpurāṇe jaladhenūrnāma ṣaḍadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[jaladhenūḥ ga]
