%%% Chapter 107
saptādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

svayambhureṣa bhagavān vedodgītaḥ purā tvayā |
śivādyāḥ ṛṣiparyantāḥ smārttā vāsthāna kārakāḥ ||107:001||
[smarttāro kārakā kha]
kathaṃ mātā bhaveddevī etatkautuhalaṃ mama ||107:002||
[mātā ka ga]
brahmovāca |

jñānaśaktiḥ kriyā dhenūrdevyārūpāḥ prakīrtitāḥ |
mātṛkā jñānaśaktistu kriyā sā tamarūpiṇī ||107:003||
vāmādyā sā tridhā bhūtvā jyeṣṭhā raudrā ṛjusthitā |
kuṃḍalī trikaṭākārā dvau dvau vindusamanvitā ||107:004||
sā prasūtāṣṭavargāṇi svarā vaso dvidhā punaḥ |
anunāsāṃśca ghoṣāṃśca ekonā śatamardditān ||107:005||
mātarā tasya vargasthāṃ dṛṣṭavyaḥ prathamaḥ śivaḥ |
ṣoḍaśāntavibhaktastu akāre saṃvyavasthitaḥ ||107:006||
akāre brahmarūpeṇa śivarūpeṇa cāpare |
viṣṇu-skanda-yama-śakra-carcikāntara-saṃsthitā ||107:007||
[kakāre ka ga]
vindau candrārkasūryau tu tataḥ sā śatadhā matā |
kriyārūpā bhaveddevī vedamātā śṛṇusva te ||107:008||
[ bindau bahnayarka sūryau tu ka]
oṃkārapraṇavā vedā gāyatrī vetasambhavā |
ṣaḍaṃgāste samākhyātā upāṃgāścaturo'pare ||107:006||
[vedī gāyatrī barṇa sampadā ka |
devī kha ]
chandolakṣaṇasaṃyuktā mātṛkā garbhajā viduḥ ||107:010||
manuruvāca |

kiṃ vedo rūpamānena upāṃgaṃ saṃkhyābhedataḥ |
bhaktaṃ kiṃ vedarūpantu tanme brūhi samāsataḥ ||107:011||
brahmovāca |

[ka ga pustake nāsti]
eka eva bhavedvedaścaturbhedaḥ punaḥ kṛtaḥ |
śākhārthamalpasattvānāṃ grahaṇā yātivistarāt ||107:012||
[grahāṇāma ka]
saṃvibhakto mayā vatsa ṛgyajuḥ sāmātharvaṇaḥ |
atra bhedāstu ṛgvede daśa caiva prakīrtitā ||107:013||
āśleṣāḥ saṃkhyā carcāśca śrāvakāścarcakāstathā |
śrāvaṇīya cakramā ca puṭakramavaṭakramāḥ ||107:014||
daṃḍaśceti samāsena punarekaiva pāragāḥ |
śākhāśca vividhā bhūyaḥ śākalā brahmamātṛkāḥ ||107:015||
[cākṣu māṃḍakā ka ga]
teṣāmadhyayanaṃ proktaṃ maṃḍalāścatuṣaṣṭikāḥ |
vargāṇāṃ parisaṃkhyātaṃ caturviśaśatāni ca ||107:016||
[catuḥ saptati ka ga]
ṛcāṃ daśasahasrāṇi ṛcāṃ pañcaśatāni ca |
ṛá¹cāmaśītipādañca tatra pāraṇamucyate ||107:017||
[mānamaśītapādañca kha]
ṛgvede tu bhavetsaṃkhyā yajurvedasya śrūyatām |
ṣaḍaśītivibhedena mayā bhinnaṃ śivājñayā ||107:018||
[ādye ka ga]
daśadhā carakā tatra kārakā vidradhiṣayā |
kaṭhāprācyaḥ kaṭhāścaiva kapiṣṭhalakaṭhāstathā ||107:019||
[haridravīyā ka ga]
cārāyaṇīyāḥ śvetāśca śvetātārā maitrāyaṇīyā |
punaḥ saptavibhedena maitrāyaṇyaḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||107:020||
mānava-dundubha-vārāhāśchāgeyāḥ hāridravīyāḥ |
sāmasāyanīyāśca teṣāmadhyayanamucyate ||107:021||
[sāmasīmāpanīyāśca ka]
aṣṭādaśasahasrāṇi paṭhan śākhāvido bhavet |
dviguṇaṃ padapāṭhī yastriguṇaṃ kramapāragaḥ ||107:022||
[viguṇam ka ga]
ṣaḍaṃgāni yadādhītya ṣaḍaṃgaviducyate |
śikṣā kalpo vyākaraṇaṃ niruktaṃ chando jyotiṣam ||107:023||
ṣaḍaṃgāni bhavantyetānyupāṃgāni śṛṇu kathyatām |
pratipadamantrapadaṃ chando bhāṣā mīmāṃsā ca ||107:024||
[anupadam ka]
nyāyatarkasamāyuktā upāṃgāḥ parikīrtitāḥ |
pariśiṣṭāśca saṃkhyātāḥ aṣṭādaśa śṛṇusva tat ||107:025||
yūpalakṣaṇapratiṣṭhā tu vākyaṃ saṃkhyā caraṇavyūhaḥ |
śrāddhakalpaśca sūktāni pāriṣadamṛgyajuśca ||107:026||
aṣṭakāpūraṇañcaiva pravarādhyāyāṃga ṣoḍaśa |
kratusaṃkhyābhigamyo yajña pārśvānugrahaśrautrikam ||107:027||
[śāstram kha]
vratañca paśavo homaṃ kūrmalakṣaṇasaṃyutāḥ |
kathitāḥ pariśiṣṭāstu ūnaviṃśā mahāmune ||107:028||
[vasavotthānam ka]
kaṭhānāṃ ca yūpānyāhuścatvāriṃśaccatuttarāḥ |
prācyodīcya niruktaṃ ca vājasaneyaśca paṃcadhā ||107:029||
daśabhedavibhinnāstu praṣṭavyā munipuṃgavā |
jābālā baudheyā kāṇvā mādhyandināśca śāraveyāḥ ||107:030||
[munipuṃgānāṃ ka]
sapāyināṃ kapālākhyā pauṇḍaravatsavārikaparāśarāḥ |
gauṇapā baudheyā ayodhyāyeyāśca teṣāmadhyayanāni ca ||107:031||
[svapāṭhināṃ ka; baulapā ka]
dve sahasre śate nyūne vedavājasaneyake |
ṛggaṇaḥ parisaṃkhyātastato'vyāni yajūmÌṣi ca ||107:032||
aṣṭau sahasrāṇi śatāni cāṣṭāśītiranyatrādhike |
yajūmÌṣi tatpramāṇāni yajuṣādi kevalam ||107:033||
śaśvatkriyaṃ parisaṃkhyātaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ ca caturguṇam |
etat tvañca vijānīyāt taittirādvividhā punaḥ ||107:034||
[saśukriyaṃ ka ga]
aukheyāḥ khaṃḍikeyāśca caṇḍikā paṃcadhā punaḥ |
kālakeyā bauddhāyanīyā hiraṇyakaśyāstathā pare ||107:035||
bhāradvājāpastambāśca teṣāṃ bhedāḥ prakīrtitāḥ |
adhyayanaṃ sauptikaṃ caiva pravacanīyaṃ tathāparam ||107:036||
sāmavedastu vistīrṇaḥ sahasrabhedaiḥ kīrtitaḥ |
anadhyāyeṣvadhīyante tadā indreṇa dhīmatā ||107:037||
[padyamidaṃ ka pustake nāsti]
vajreṇa nihatāḥ śeṣān vakṣyāmi śṛṇu bho dvija |
nārāyaṇīyāḥ kauthumāśca tatra bhedāḥ punaḥ śṛṇu ||107:038||
[rāṇāyaṇīyā ga]
nārāyaṇīyā saptaiva ugrādyā nayanāvarā vedamātā |
kālarayā mahākālarayālaṃghana vidyutā ||107:039||
[kha pustake eva kevalam; kālavayā mahākālavayānandanavidyutāḥ kha ga]
kauthumānāmapi sapta asurā bādarāyaṇā |
vaineyā baudheyā ayaudheyāśca teṣāmadhyayanāni ca ||107:040||
[kārttyamānām kha]
prāṃjalādvenabhṛtyāśca prācanayojyānīkāyanā |
adhyayanamapi teṣāṃ tu |
aṣṭau sāmasahasrāṇi sāmāni ca caturdaśa ||107:041||
[māsasahasrāṇi māsāni ka]
aṣṭau śatāni navatirdaśa sahasrāṇi bālikhilyāḥ |
sasuparṇāśca preṣyāśca etatsāmagaṇaṃ smṛtam ||107:042||
[sāmaguṇaṃ smṛtam ka ga]
atha atharvavedasya navabhedā bhavanti ca |
pippalādamodā modā ca bhūtāpanīyā ca tathā ||107:043||
[ka pustake paṃktidvayaṃ nāsti]
yāhano brahmavalo ca śaunako kunakho tathā |
deva darśiścāpi vidyāsteṣāmadhyayanaṃ śṛṇu ||107:044||
[devadarśāḥ ka ca]
pañcakalpā bhavanti |

nakṣatrakalpo vaitānaśca saṃhitāvidhiḥ āṃgirasaḥ |
śāntikalpaśca paṃcaite atharvasya bhavanti ca ||107:045||
sarveṣāmeva vedānāmupavedān śṛṇusva te |
ṛgvedasyāyurvedo yajurvedasya dhanustathā ||107:046||
sāmavedasya gāndharvamarthaśāstramatharvaṇaḥ |
ṛá¹gvedasyātreyaṃ gotraṃ sāmavedaṃ vidurmune ||107:047||
kāśyapaṃ yajurvedantu rudravedantu tatsmṛtam |
sāmavedo'pi gotreṇa bharadvāja purandaraḥ ||107:048||
adhidevaṃ vijānīyāt vaitānantu atharvaṇe |
brahmadevaṃ vijānāyāt rūpāṇyasmācchraṇusva te ||107:049||
[baitālam ka ga]
ṛgvedaḥ padmapatrākṣaḥ pralambajaṭharaḥ suvibhaktagrīvaḥ |
kuṃcitakeśaśmaśruḥ pramāṇenāpi vitastipañca ||107:050||
sa rājate mauktikavaro'tha pūjyo varaprado bhaktiyute dvijāya ||107:051||
yajurvedaḥ piṃgalākṣaḥ kṛṣamadhyaḥ sthūlagalaḥ kapolastāmrāyattavarṇaḥ kṛṣṇacaraṇaḥ ||107:052a-d||
prādeśāt ṣaḍdīrghatvena liṃgo'thavā citre pūjya sarvakāmānvāpnuyāt ||107:052e-h||
sāmavedo nityaṃ sragvī suvrataḥ śuciḥ śucīvāsasaḥ |
kṣamī dāntaścarma ca daṇḍī kāñcananayanaḥ ||107:053||
ādityavarṇo vaṇena ṣaḍ ratnamātrastathā |
tāmre'tha maṇi indrākhye pūjayan śubhado bhavet ||107:054||
atharvavedastīkṣṇaścaṇḍaḥ kṣāmarūpo viśvātmā viśvakṛt |
||107:055ab||
krūra ūrdhva jvālāvān kṣudrakarmā ca śāstra kṛtonnāmī |
||107:055cd||
[padyamidaṃ ga pustake nāsti]
nīlotpalavarṇo varṇena svadāratuṣṭaḥ parastriyārthaśca ||107:055ef||
sovarṇa padmarāge vā rudrākhye pūjayanmune |
sarvakāmānavāpnoti atharva vihitāni ca ||107:056||
[rūdrākṣe ka]
vedānāṃ caiva utpatti svaravarṇa samudbhavā |
śivabhakti sāmāyogāt tavākhyātā mayā mune ||107:057||
yaddevanāmarūpantu gotraṃ vedapramāṇajam |
varṇa varṇayate tāta tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu ||107:058||
yāvanti vedagītāni puṇyayajña vratāni ca |
tāvanti śravaṇādasya prāpnuyāt bhaktibhāvataḥ ||107:059||
aputro labhate putramadhano dhanamāpnuyāt |
avidvān vidyāṃ prāpnoti duḥkhād duḥkhī pramucyate ||107:060||
paṭhitvā sarvavedānāṃ sammato dvijavallabhaḥ |
bhavate nātra sandeho devī ca varadā sadā ||107:061||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe vedotpattismaraṇīya caraṇavyūha samāptirnāma saptādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye vedotpattismaraṇīyaṃ caraṇavyūhaṃ samāptam ka ga]
