%%% Chapter 108
aṣṭādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

manuruvāca |

ṣaḍaṃgānīha vedānāṃ mayā jñātāni pūrvaśaḥ |
cāturvaṇyahitārthāya upāṃgaṃ mama kathyatām ||108:001||
brahmovāca |

upāgāṃnāṃ ca aṃgāṃnāmāyurvedaṃ varaṃ viduḥ |
dharmārthakāmamokṣānāṃ sa cāpi phaladāyakaḥ ||108:002||
[paraṃ kha]
jyotiḥ śāstraṃ dvitīyantu dṛṣṭādṛṣṭaprasādhakam |
tasmāt taducyeta vipra saṃkṣepādavadhāraya ||108:003||
purā kailāśaśikhare bhagavantaṃ punarvasum |
upāsatāṃ maharṣīnāṃ prādurāsīdiyaṃ kathā ||108:004||
ātmendriyamano'rthānāṃ yo'yaṃ puruṣasaṃjñakaḥ |
śaśi vasyāmayānāñca prāgutpattiviniścaye ||108:005||
[kāśivasyām ga]
tadantaraṃ kāśipatirvāmako vākyamarthavat |
vyājahāra ṛṣimiti abhisṛtyābhivādya ca ||108:006||
[avravīt ga]
kiṃ nu bhoḥ puruṣo yajñasteja stasyāmayāḥ śubhā |
na cetyukte narendrena provācarṣīnu punarvasuḥ ||108:007||
[tajjās kha]
sarve evāmitajñānā jñānavicchinnasaṃśayāḥ |
bhavantaśchettumarhanti kāśirājasya saṃśayam ||108:008||
pārīkṣastat parīkṣyāgre maidgalyo vākyamabravīt |
ātmajaḥ puruṣogā śvātmajāḥ kāraṇaṃ hi saḥ ||108:009||
[rogāḥ kha]
sa cinotyupabhuṃkte ca karmaṃ karmaṃphalāni ca |
na smṛte cetanādhātoḥ pravṛttiḥ sukhaduḥkhayo ||108:010||
śaralomā tu netyāha na hyātmānamātmanā |
yojayed vyādhirbhirdukhaiḥ duḥkhadveṣī kadācana ||108:011||
[savalo mārute ga]
rajastamobhyāntu manaḥ parītaṃ sattvasaṃjñakam |
śarīrasya samutpattau vikārāṇāñca kāraṇam ||108:012||
vyādhayo vidastu netyāha na hyekaṃ kāraṇaṃ manaḥ |
nārttaśarīraṃ rogāṇāṃ narāṇāṃ manasaḥ sthitiḥ ||108:013||
[nāpocidastu ka; nakte śarīrācchārīrā rogānāṃ manasaḥ sthitiḥ ca]
rajasāni tu bhūtāni vyādhayaśca pṛthagvidhāḥ |
āpo hi rasavatyastāḥ smṛtā nirvṛttihetavaḥ ||108:014||
hiraṇyākṣastu netyāha na hyātmā rajasaḥ smṛtaḥ |
nātindriyaṃ manaḥ santi rogā śabdādijāstathā ||108:015||
ṣaḍdhātujastu puruṣo rogā ṣaḍdhātujāstathā |
rāśiḥ ṣaḍdhātujo hyeṣa sāṃkhyairādyaiḥparīkṣitaḥ ||108:016||
tathā bruvānaṃ kuśikamāha tameti śaunaka |
kasmāt mātāpitṛmyāṃ hi vinā ṣaḍdhātujo bhavet ||108:017||
puruṣaḥ puruṣāde rgorgorakhādaśvaḥ prajāyate |
paitryau mehādayaścoktā rogāstu eva kāraṇam ||108:018||
bhadrakāpyastu netyāha na śakto'śaktāt prajāyate |
mātrāpitrośca te pūrvamutpattirnopayadyate ||108:019||
karmajastu mato jantuḥ karmajāstasya cāmayāḥ |
na hyete karmaṇā janma rogānāṃ puruṣasya ca ||108:020||
bharadvājastu netyāha karttā pūrva hi karmaṇaḥ |
dṛṣṭaṃ na cākṛtaṃ karma yasya syāt puruṣaḥ phalam ||108:021||
bhāvahetuḥ svabhāvastu vyādhīnāṃ puruṣasya ca |
kharadruva calotpattvaṃ tejohantānāṃ yathaiva hi ||108:022||
kātyāyanastu netyāha na hyārambhaḥ phalaṃ bhavet |
bhavet svabhāvādbhāvānāmasiddhaḥ siddhireva vā ||108:023||
sraṣṭo tvamatisaṃkalpo vrahmāpatyaṃ prajāpatiḥ |
cetanā cetanasyāsya jagataḥ sukhaduḥkhayo ||108:024||
tannati bhikṣurātreyo na hyapatyaṃ prajāpatiḥ |
prajāhitaiṣī satataṃ dukhairyujyādasādhuvat ||108:025||
kālajastvena puruṣaḥ kālajāstasya cāmayā |
jagat kālavaśaṃ sarvaṃ kālaḥ sarvatra kāraṇam ||108:026||
[pṛṣṭatvām ga]
vivadatāmuvācedaṃ tatharṣīṇāṃ punarvasuḥ |
maivaṃ vocata tattvaṃ hi duṣprāpyaṃ pakṣasaṃśrayāt ||108:027||
vādān samprativādāṃśca vadanto niṣcitāniva |
pakṣāntaṃ naiva gacchati tilapīḍakavadagatau ||108:028||
muktvainaṃ vādasaṃcarṣamadhyātmamanucintyatām |
nāvidhūte tamakṣepe jñānametad pravarttate ||108:029||
[dūḥkhairdukhād asādhuvat ka ga; cāśayāḥ ka]
karma vācetano'mūrteḥ prakṛtamūrtte'sthacetana |
puruṣo'cetano'mūrtto rasādyāḥ sarvacetanāḥ ||108:030||
kālo nityodito'mūrttaḥ sa ca hetuḥ kathaṃ bhavet |
na hi ātmānaṃ duḥkhādyaiḥ prekṣāpūrvaṃ samācaret ||108:031||
1. na hi mātāpitṛbhyāṃ hi vināśitvā bhujo bhavet ka ga |

2. tatra kāvyastu netyāde na hyardho'rtha prajāyate ka ga |

3. caloṣṭhatvaṃ ga |

7. anucintitam ka
