[dāruṇam svanam ka ga]
niḥśaucāste'bhavan vatsa tatsthāḥ lokā na saṃśayaḥ |
grahāpasṛṣṭa vidviṣṭā yānti nāśaṃ mahānapi ||118:020||
tasmāt taṃ saṃskaredvatsa pūjārthaṃ cānyathā nyaset |
devaṃ devālayaṃ vāpi jīrṇājīrṇaṃ niyojayet ||118:021||
yathā sadā bhavetpūjā tathā kāryaṃ vipaścitā |
mūlamevāpnuyātpuṇyaṃ dravyāṃśena mahāmuniḥ ||118:022||
karttā śatādhikaṃ mūlādāpnuyādavicāraṇāt |
rājā ṣaṣṭhāṃśamāpnoti prajārāṣṭraṃ ca śudhyati ||118:023||
[vindati ka ga]
iti śrīdevīpurāṇe jīrṇadevatāpratīkāro nāmāṣṭādaśādhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye jīrṇasaṃskāra pratīkāravidhiḥ ka ga]
