%%% Chapter 120
viṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

naravāhana uvāca |

devyotpattividhānaṃ ca vratacaryā pṛthagvidhā |
vihitaṃ śrotumicchāmi tanuśuddhiṃ hutāśane ||120:001||
agastya uvāca |

japtvā tu caturaṣṭantu aṣṭāviṃśamathāpi vā |
śrūyate lakṣamātreṇa yadi brahmahano'pitu ||120:002||
[varṇacatuthaṃtu ka ga; śudhyate ka ga]
śākayāvakakṣīrāśī karamūlaphalāśanaḥ |
padamālāṃ japanvatsa tanuśuddhimavāpnuyāt ||120:003||
tritayaṃ vā japenmantraḥ gāyatrīṃ lakṣamanvitām |
mucyate sarvapāpaiśca yamaniyamopasevanāt ||120:004||
brahmacaryaṃ dayā kṣāntiḥ dhyānaṃ satyamakalkatā |
ahiṃsā satyamādhuryaṃ damaśceti yamāḥ smṛtāḥ ||120:005||
snānamaunopavāsejyā svādhyāyopastha nigrahaḥ |
niyamāt guruśuśrūṣā śauco'krodho'pramādatā ||120:006||
paṃcagavyaṃ tu gokṣīraṃ dadhi mūtraṃ śakṛd ghṛtam |
japtvā pare'dyū pavaset kṛcchraṃ sāṃtapanaṃ caran ||120:007||
pṛthaka kartā parṇadravyaiḥ ṣaḍahaḥ sopavāsakaḥ |
saptāhena tu kṛcchro'yaṃ mahāsāṃtapanaḥ smṛtaḥ ||120:008||
parṇoṃdumbara rājīvaḥ vilvapatra kuśodakaiḥ |
pratyekaṃ pratyahābhyastaiḥ parṇakṛcchraḥ udāhṛtaḥ ||120:009||
taptakṣīraghṛtāmbūnāṃ ekaikaḥ pratyahaṃ pibet |
ekarātropavāsaśca taptakṛcchrantu pāvanam ||120:010||
ekabhaktena naktena tathaivāyāsitena ca |
upavāsena caivāyaṃ pādakṛcchraḥ udāhṛtaḥ ||120:011||
yathākathacit triguṇaḥ prājāpatyo'yamucyate |
ayamevāti kṛcchraḥ syāt pāṇipurānnabhojanaiḥ ||120:012||
kṛcchrātikṛcchraṃ payasā divasānekarviśatim |
dvādaśāhopavāsena parākaḥ parikīrttitaḥ ||120:013||
vrīṇyekācāmatakrāmbu paśūnāṃ pratisāram |
ekarātropavāsaśca kṛcchraḥ saumyo'yamucyate ||120:014||
[paṇikaṃ vatakrātyu ca śatrūṇāṃ prativāsarai ka |
piṇyākaṃ vātakātyupasaktūnāṃ prativāsaraḥ ka ga |
]
eṣaṃ trirātramabhyāsādekaikaṃ pratyahaṃ pibet |
tulāpuruṣa ityeṣa jñeyaḥ pañca daśāhikaḥ ||120:015||
tithivṛddhau caret piṇḍānaśulke śikhaṇḍa sasthitān |
ekaikaṃ dāpayet kṛṣṇaḥ piṇḍaṃ cāndrāyaṇaṃ caret ||120:016||
[śikharesthitām ka]
yathā kathaṃcit piṇḍānāṃ catvāriṃśat śatadvayam |
māsena copayuñjīta cāndrāyaṇamathāparam ||120:017||
kuryāt triṣavaṇasnānaṃ kṛcchraṃ cāndrāyaṇaṃ caran |
pavitrāṇi japet piṇḍān hyamantrenābhimantritāna ||120:018||
anādiṣṭeṣu pātreṣu śuddhi cāndrāyaṇena tu |
dharmārtha yaścaret etaccandrasya yāti salokatām ||120:019||
kṛcchraṃ taddharmaṃ kāmāntu mahartī śriyamaśnute |
yathā śāstravidhānena phalaṃ homādavāpnuyāt ||120:020||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe yama-niyama śuddhirnāma rviśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ādye yama-niyama-tapa-siddhiḥ ka ga]
