%%% Chapter 121
ekaviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

vahnervidhānaṃ paramaṃ sarvakāmaprasādhakam |
kathayāmi suraśreṣṭha nāmaâbhedaâkriyādibhiḥ ||121:001||
agneḥ parigrahaḥ kāryaḥ sarvaśāstrārtha vedakaiḥ |
vāma-dakṣiṇa-siddhānta-vedānta-gṛhya-pāragaiḥ ||121:002||
kāryaḥ parigraho vahneḥ sarvasampatti vedibhiḥ |
anyathā antarāyastu bhavanti dhana-āyuṣau ||121:003||
nityaṃ vyādhiradhanyo vā sarvalokanamaskṛtaḥ |
aviditvā yadā vatsa jñātvā sarvaṃ bhaved budhaḥ ||121:004||
[uparanute ka]
tasmātsarvaprayatnena bahuvidye kriyā matā |
kuṇḍāṣṭakaṃ samākhyātaṃ tribhedantu mayā tava ||121:005||
bahuvahnividhānantu ekasyaivopacārataḥ |
strī-bāla-vṛddha-śūdraistu hotavyaṃ pratyahaṃ tathā ||121:006||
[murkhaistu ka ga]
maṭhe mahānase vāpi na kuṇḍe tu kadācana |
saṃskṛte nāmabhedaiśca rakṣayitvā hutāśanam ||121:007||
mahāvidyārthavettārai rhotavyaṃ phalakāṃkṣibhiḥ |
śrūyate ca purā vatsa aviditvā vasoḥ sutaḥ ||121:008||
saṃskṛte'havamānasya rājyabhraṃśamavāpnuyāt |
tathā vā anahotāramacirānmṛtyumavāpnuyāt ||121:009||
[avanihotāram ka ga]
tasmādasthiravahnau tu na hotavyamavedinā |
vedanantu pravakṣyāmi yena siddhiḥ prajāyate ||121:010||
vṛhaspatiruvāca |

agnicakravidhiṃ puṇyaṃ devatānāṃ ca sthāpanam |
śrotumicchāmyahaṃ tāta kathayasva prasādataḥ ||121:011||
brahmovāca |

catuṣkoṇe hyahaṃ vatsa maṇḍale madhusūdana |
dhanuṣākṛtiko rudraḥ sarvadeva namaskṛtaḥ ||121:012||
caturasne bhavedagnirmaṇḍale tu hutāśanaḥ |
ardhacandre'nalo hyagnirevaṃ yajñaḥ pratiṣṭhitaḥ ||121:013||
[ka ga pustake ga ita ārabhya dśa ślokā na santi]
dvijānāmÌ devatā sadya ācāryo yogavedanam |
udake varṇo devo darbheṣu ca mahāragāḥ ||121:014||
srucāyāntu mahādevī śruvo devastrilocanaḥ |
tatsaṃyogaparo devaḥ sarvadevanamaskṛtaḥ ||121:015||
praṇītā pṛthivī jñeyā svāhā kāre mahāmaravāḥ |
puṣpeṣu ṛtavo viddhi pātreṣu ca mahādadhiḥ ||121:016||
vedīmadhye tu gāyatrī somo abhyukṣaṇe sthitaḥ |
īndhane maṇibhadrastu śikhaṃ vajradharāyudhaḥ ||121:017||
hotārantu vijānīyāt camasādiṣu parvatāḥ |
ucchrave devatā rudrastālavṛnte tu vāsavaḥ ||121:018||
mantraṇeṣu gaṇāḥ sarvāḥ bhasme bhūyo'pi śaṃkaraḥ |
lokapālāstu koṇeṣu oṃkāre sarvadevatāḥ ||121:019||
mātaro homabhāge tu pūtanā viṣphuliṃgadā |
ādityādisthitā teje yo devo'paraḥ paraḥ ||121:020||
devānāṃ prāta rhomantu praharārdhena bhūtidam |
madhyānhetu manuṣyāṇāṃ homahetu priyādikam ||121:021||
aparāhne pitṛṇāñca sandhyāyāṃ grahabhautikam |
rātrau pāpavināśārthaṃ divyasiddhi prasādhakam ||121:022||
praharārdhena hotavyamardharātre ca āyudam |
śeṣe putrapradaṃ vatsa udaye sarva kāmadam ||121:023||
dakṣiṇā sarvakāmeṣu sarvaprāptipradāyakam |
kṣaṇādhi devatā deyā prathamācaraṇāhutiḥ ||121:024||
anyathā viphalaṃ vipra bhavate havanaṃ sadā |
vārkṣamṛṇmayatāmrādyaiḥ raupyahemamayodbhavaiḥ ||121:025||
daśadhā puṇyavṛddhistu havanasnāna bhojanaiḥ |
devāṃkaiḥ śūla padmāṃkaiḥ śaṃkhacakrahutāśanaiḥ ||121:026||
ghṛta-kṣīra-vasādīni grahītavyāni buddhimān |
devyāsnāpana yajñiyai rvasordhārā prabhāvitaiḥ ||121:027||
dravyairhīmaṃ prakarttavyamanyathā vā vidhānataḥ |
āpta vedeṣu sāmtṛptiṃ puṣṭā dāsyanti devatāḥ ||121:028||
velā hīneṣu surāṇāmadhidevabhujaṃ phalam |
evaṃ te kathita vatsa sarvalokasuravāvaham ||121:029||
hotāro mantrahīnāstu aśucirbhavate sadā |
tasmādasaṃskṛte vahnau na hotavyamavedakaiḥ ||121:030||
mantravidaśca hotāro āpyāyanti devatāḥ avedakastu hotāro naiva prīṇāti vai surān ||121:031||
[mantāvindaka hautārau ka ga]
homātsarvaphalāvāptiḥ sarveṣāmapi jāyate |
tasmānmantravidhānajñaḥ prātareva śubhapradaḥ ||121:032||
pūrvāgni devatā viṣṇurdakṣiṇena haraḥ sthitaḥ |
paścimena sthito brahmā ete agnistha devatāḥ ||121:033||
teje rudraṃ vijānīyājjvālāyāṃ cāpi carcikā |
trayāyuṣaṃ ca viprāṇāṃ lakṣmīstatrāpi devatāḥ ||121:034||
[kriyāyuṣam kha]
evaṃ pratiṣṭhitaṃ homaṃmagnayaśca trayastathā |
trayo devāstrayaḥ kālā trayogni gṛhamantritāḥ ||121:035||
gārhapatyaṃ dakṣiṇāgniḥ āhavanīyaśca te trayaḥ |
ekasyaiva samutpannā bahubhedā dvijottama ||121:036||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe triragnividhirnāma ekaviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyayaḥ |

[ādye devyavatāre triragnividhiḥ ka ga]
