%%% Chapter 122
dvāviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

vṛhaspatiruvāca |

ekastriguṇa ākhyātaḥ sarvadeva sukhāvahaḥ |
bahudhā tatkathaṃ karma yojayanti dvijottamā ||122:001||
dakṣiṇāgni vibhāgaṃ tu prasūtirbahudhā tathā |
nāmabhiḥ karmabhirddeva kathayasva samāsataḥ ||122:002||
[sthāpitāni ka ga I don't know the right place for FN ref. no.]
evamuktastu guruṇā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ |
uvāca madhurāṃ vāṇīṃ śṛṇuṣvāvahito dvija ||122:003||
brahmovāca |

purā kṛtayuge vipra eka eva hutāśana |
rudramūrtti sthito nityaṃ tejo nāma mahātmanaḥ ||122:004||
tretāyāṃ dakṣiṇeśo vai yajñārthaṃ visṛjanmahān |
gārhapatyaṃ tamo jātaṃ havanīyaṃ tato'bhavat ||122:005||
havanīya prasūtistu bharatādyā mahaujasaḥ |
ekapañcāśataṃ nāma carācaravidhāyakāḥ ||122:006||
teṣāṃ vai nāma karmāṇi bahudhā brūhi bho dvija |
sapta sapta vibhāgena teṣāṃ santatijātayaḥ ||122:007||
bharatī varamāṃgalye vibhuśca bala aṃgirāḥ |
samudbhavo jayo rudraḥ saṃyugaḥ kāliko bhavaḥ ||122:008||
[bhavato paramāṃgalye vibhāvacalasaṃjñakaḥ ga]
sūryo janaḥ śaśāṃkaśca viśvedevāḥ parāvasuḥ |
kalmāṣaḥ saṃcayo ghoro vaḍavāgni varāntakaḥ ||122:009||
[jjalaḥ ga]
dakṣo nidhīśvaraḥ kāmaḥ kālāntaka parāntakau |
bībhatso vijayo dhūmraḥ kṛṣṇavarṇo'thahāṭakaḥ ||122:010||
ajitaḥ śaṃkaraḥ śaṃkhaḥ śuddhido jayado guruḥ |
aparo'parājitaḥ kaśca pratāpo bahudaḥ śubhaḥ ||122:011||
[gahvaraḥ ga]
āraṇyaḥ sarvagaḥ śambhuḥ kāmiko ripuhā śivaḥ |
garbhādhānādisaṃskāraiḥ sa bhavet sarvadakāmadaḥ ||122:012||
parigrahānurūpeṇa tathā homavaśena ca |
laghvāhāro viśuddhaśca nityahotā prakīrttitaḥ ||122:013||
[avigrahānnarūpeṇa tta thā hotṛvaśena ca ga]
kṛtvā hutāśane paṃca karmāṇi bhavate sadā |
sarvasiddhi pradāyitvādanyathā havane caruḥ ||122:014||
ādhāne bhavate hyagnirbara puṃsavane sthitaḥ |
sīmante maṃgalo nāma jātakarma vibhuḥ smṛtaḥ ||122:015||
nāme balaḥsamākhyātaḥ prāśane aṃgirā mataḥ |
cūḍe samudbhavo vahnirjayo vratanibandhane ||122:016||
rudro godāniko nāma vivāhe saṃyugaḥ smṛtaḥ |
agniśca kāliko nāma agnihotre vidhīyate ||122:017||
āvasathye bhavo jñeyaḥ pitṛṇāṃ viśvadevakaḥ |
analo jaṭharo vahniḥ kalmāṣo'mṛtabhakṣaṇe ||122:018||
sūryo vahnirmahāhome jalo jalaniveśane |
śaśāṃkaḥ pūrṇimāhome kṣaye samvarttako mataḥ ||122:019||
[padyamirda ga pustake nāsti]
ghoraḥ kāṣṭha samṛddhaśca parānto veṇusambhavaḥ |
samudre vaḍavāgnistu dakṣaḥ pākavidho mataḥ ||122:020||
nidhīśo vasudhārāyāṃ kāmadevo'tha dhūmajaḥ |
tūṣajaḥ kāmahā tvagnau rathyāyānta parāntakaḥ ||122:021||
bībhatsu kṣutkaro vahnirvijayo nṛpagehajaḥ |
dhūmajo vṛkṣasamutthastu dīpe kṛṣṇapatho mataḥ ||122:022||
hemaṃ tāpe bhavedvādye ajito mātṛveśmajaḥ |
saṃgaro mlecchalokeṣu śaṃkho vai ceṣṭapākajaḥ ||122:023||
āditye śuddhiṃ vijānīyājjayaḥ śukraniveśane |
gurudīkṣāvidhau vahniraparo tiṇḍileṣu ca ||122:024||
[ślaukapaṃcakaṃ ga pustake nāsti]
kaṇṭhānukūlajo viddhi lakṣahoma parājitaḥ |
pratāpo nṛpadīkṣāyāṃ vahudānajaśoṇajaḥ ||122:025||
śubho grahavidhau hyagnirāraṇye araṇībhavaḥ |
sarvago vaidyuto vahniḥ śambhurmaṇisamudbhavaḥ ||122:026||
kāmikaḥ sādhakāgniśca ripuhā abhicārajaḥ |
koṭihome śivo vahniḥ sarvakāma prasādhakaḥ ||122:027||
śivatejodbhavo vipra kālāgniḥ sa ca kīrttitaḥ |
eko bahuprakāraistu nāma karmairyathāsthitaḥ ||122:028||
kathitaḥ pāvako vatsa kiṃ bhūyaḥ paripṛcchati ||122:029||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe vahnibhedonāma dvāviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

[ityādye vanhibhedaḥ ka ga]
%%%%
%%% Chapter 123
trayoviṃśatyadhikaśatatamodhyāyaḥ |

nṛpavāhana uvāca |

vahnikarmaphalaṃ vipra kathitañcāvadhāritam |
puṣpagandhaviśeṣantu śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ ||123:001||
agastya uvāca |

pātrāṇāṃ hemaraupyotthaiḥ yathā prokto nṛpottama |
ghṛtahome varaṃ yadvat tilāśca madalepane ||123:002||
candanāguru karpūra nakhaṃ dhūpe varaṃ matam |
mada karpūra kāśmīraṃ rocanā ca catuṣṭayam ||123:003||
etena lepayeddevyāḥ sarvakāmānāpnuyāt |
jātī kaṃkola-patrailā-kuṣṭakuṃkuma patrikā ||123:004||
jātīphalo latākhyā ca snānagandhā sadādharā |
nāga keśara karpūra surāmāṃsī sabālakāḥ ||123:005||
udvarttanāḥ samākhyātāḥ sadaiva mātarapriyāḥ |
dhūpaṃ kalyāṇa nāgantu nityaṃ devyā priyaṃ nṛpa ||123:006||
candrākhyaṃ lepanaṃ deyaṃ sarvasiddhipradāyakam |
maṇimauktika mālāśca vitānañca dukūlajam ||123:007||
ghaṇṭādi sarvadā dattvā hemapuṣpaphalaṃ labheta |
puṣpairvāraṇya sambhūtaiḥ patraivā girisambhavaiḥ ||123:008||
aparyuṣitānyacchidraiḥ prokṣitairjantuvarjitaiḥ |
ātmārāmodbhavairvāpi puṣpaiḥ sampūjayecchivām ||123:009||
puṣpajāti viśeṣeṇa bhavetpuṇyaṃ viśeṣataḥ |
tapaḥ śīlaguṇopete pātre vedasya pārage ||123:0010||
daśa dattvā suvarṇāni yatphalaṃ kusumeṣu tat |
mātarāṇāṃ sakṛddattvā labhate nṛpasattama ||123:0011||
tasmāt puṣpān pravakṣyāmi patrāśca surabhīścaye |
ketakīñcātimuktaśca baka-bandhū-bakulā ṛṣiḥ ||123:012||
kadambaḥ karṇikāraśca sindhuvāraḥ samṛddhaye |
punnāga campakaṃ kundraṃ yūthikā navamallikā ||123:013||
damanā padmapatraśca śatadhā puṇyavṛddhaye |
tārārjunamallī ca bṛhatī śatapatrikā ||123:014||
[ga pustake nāsti]
karavīra kusuma kahlāra bilvapāṭala mālatī |
javā vijo kilāśoko raktanīlotpalāḥ sitāḥ ||123:015||
paṃkajaḥ śatapatraśca daśadhā puṇyavṛddhaye |
etaistu arccayeddevīmāśusiddhiḥ prayacchati ||123:016||
drauṇapuṣpī śamī kṣīrī nīlāpamārga patrikāḥ |
surasā barvarā bhadrā surabhī karṇamallikā ||123:017||
kadambairarcayedrātrau mallikā ubhayoḥ samā |
divyaśeṣāṇi puṣpāṇi yathālābhena pūjayet ||123:018||
kīṭakeśopaviddhāni śīrṇaparyuṣitāni ca |
saṃpatitāni ca puṣpāṇi tyajedupahatāni ca ||123:019||
[ga pustake nāsti]
mukulairnārca yeddevyāḥ apakvaṃ na nivedayet |
phalaṃ kvathitaṃ viddhañca yatnāt pakvamapi tyajet ||123:020||
alābhena ca puṣpāṇāṃ patrāṇyapi nivedayet |
patrāṇāmapyalābhe tu phalānyapi nivedayet ||123:021||
phalānāmapyalābhe tu tṛṇagulmauṣadhānyapi |
auṣadhīnāmalābhe tu bhaktyā bhavati pūjitā ||123:022||
pratyekamuktarapuṣpeṣu daśasauvarṇikaṃ phalam |
sannibaddheṣu teṣveva dviguṇaṃ phalamucyate ||123:023||
yaḥ sugandhai raktapuṣpaiḥ samyagdevīṃ prapūjayet |
mālābhirvāpi sumanaiḥ so'nantaṃ phalāmāpnuyāt ||123:024||
bilvapatrairakhaṇdairyaḥ sakṛlliṃgaṃ prapūjayet |
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate ||123:025||
[kha pustake nāsti]
yaḥ kuryācca śivārāmamāmrabilvādi śobhitam |
jātī vijayaparājārkaâkaravīrābjaâkubjakaiḥ ||123:026||
punnāga nāga bakulai aśokotpala campakaiḥ |
kadalī hempuṣpādyaistasya dānaphalaṃ śṛṇu ||123:027||
yāvat tatpatra kusuma bījayuti phalāni ca |
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi devyāloke sa modate ||123:028||
iti śrī devīpurāṇe puṣpavidhirnāma trayoviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

