%%% Chapter 126
ṣaḍviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

nṛpavāhana uvāca |

japādhyayanayuktānāmantarāyā bhavanti ye |
teṣāṃ saṃśamanaṃ tāta śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ ||126:001||
agastya uvāca |

devyāḥ saṃsmaraṇaṃ vatsa sarvavighnavināśanam |
anekadhā samākhyātaṃ tathāpi kathayāmi te ||126:002||
japena cātmanaḥ śuddhiḥ agnikāryeṇa sampadaḥ |
sampadā ceha karmāṇi sidhyanti muktidāni ca ||126:003||
tasmājjapādi saṃśuddho agnikāryaṃ samārabhet |
āśrayaṃ sarvasiddhināmihāputra phalapradam ||126:004||
pūrvoktalakṣaṇe kuṇḍe pūrvanāmni hutāśane |
śruvadravyādisaṃsāra sampannastu tato'gnaye ||126:005||
prokṣayitvā purā prājñaḥ kuṇḍaṃ mantrodakena tu |
tatastu veṣṭayet paścāt kavacena yathākramam ||126:006||
punarullakhanaṃ kuryāt astra bījena bho nṛpa |
dakṣiṇottaravāruṇyāṃ madhye tisrastathottare ||126:007||
punarabhyukṣaṇaṃ paścāt kavacena vidhānavit |
vistaraṃ kuṇḍamadhye tu praṇavena punarnyeset ||126:008||
tataḥ śaktiṃ nyaset tasmin taḍitsahasra sannibhām |
kratumayīṃ viśālākṣīṃ satataṃ yonimudrayā ||125:009||
[bhānumatī ka |
ṛá¹tumatī ga]
yugakeśavasaṃ bhintaṃ dvitīyāśramasaṃmaṃ sthitam |
keśavāntarhito devo devī eṣā hutāśane ||126:010||
gaṃdhapuṣpārcitaṃ kṛtvā arpayitvā vidhānavit |
devyāḥ saṃtarpaṇārthāya tato vahniṃ prakalpayet ||126:011||
tenaiva sa vinirmukta veṣṭagaṃ niyojitaḥ |
sa eva parasaṃjñastu vahniḥ sarvārthasādhakaḥ ||126:012||
tāmrapātre śarāve vā ānayitvā hutāśanam |
astreṇa prokṣayet tattu punarbījaṃ niyojayet ||126:013||
tatastvāveṣṭayet paścāt kavacena yathāvidhiḥ |
sthāpayitvā śivā kuṇḍe yonimārgeṇa nikṣipet ||126:014||
[bhrāmayittvā tathā ka]
jayākhyena tu mantreṇa hṛdayantu punaryajet |
garbhādhānaṃ bhavatyevaṃ jātavedasya pārthiva ||126:015||
śirasābhyarcayitvā tu jayāṃ devīṃ tato yajet |
kṛtaṃ pusavanaṃ hyevaṃ sīmantonnayanaṃ śṛṇu ||126:016||
ajitāmarcayet pūrvaṃ śivābījaṃ tato yajet |
sīmantakaraṇaṃ vahneḥ kṛtaṃ bhavati vedikam ||126:017||
astreṇa tu samabhyarcya japeddevyāparājitām |
jātakarmma kṛtaṃ hyevaṃ tato nāma vinirdiśet ||126:018||
vighneśamarcayitvā tu kavacasya vinirdiśet |
tato'sya śrāvayennāma devyagnisthaḥ hutāśanaḥ ||126:019||
nādevyo devyāśca karmāṇi sādhayanti kadācana |
tena kāryeṇa rājante kāryo devāgnipāvarke ||126:020||
jananeva ca śūdrāśca abhayākhyā niyojane |
bodhena aṃkuśādyā tu vīṇākhyā sarvakarmasu ||126:021||
[śūdrāsya kha]
evaṃ vahnistu saṃskṛtya mudrāmaṃtrairyathākramam |
tato homaṃ prakurvīta śāstradṛṣṭena karmaṇā ||126:022||
hṛdvīje nāstared darbhān paridhīśca nighāpayet |
prāgaganuttarāgrāṃśca punardevān prapūjayet ||126:023||
brahmāṇaṃ śaṃkaraṃ viṣṇuṃ mantreśaṃ samanvitam |
pūrvādārabhya gāyatryā viṣṭarasthān yathākramam ||126:024||
āgneyīṃ diśamāśritya ājyabhāgantu dāpayet |
adhiśrayaṇaṃ purā kṛtvā paścādutplavanādikam ||126:025||
proddeśamātrakaṃ darbhaṃ procchinne tu nakhena tu |
aṃguṣṭhānāmike gṛhya ghṛtasyotplavanaṃ kuru ||126:026||
tataḥ saṃplavane mantrī sammukhaṃ ghṛtamutpunaḥ |
darbhacūḍikayā samyak araṇyoktaṃ jvalaṃ tayā |
||126:027a-d||
nairājanantu bāhyena udakena spṛśettataḥ ||126:027ef||
śruvasru cāṃ pratāpāgnau parigṛhya samantataḥ |
saṃspṛśya ca kuśaṃ sarvān agramadhyānalokikān ||126:028||
sthāpeddakṣiṇe pārśve ājyādīni tathottare |
hṛdayena vidhānajñaḥ sarvakarma samārabhet ||126:029||
tato'pi dhārayet vastrān devyābhistvanupūrvaśaḥ |
punarūdghāṭanaṃ kuryāt astrabījena pārthivaḥ ||126:030||
[yācakaḥ ka I do not know whether it is correct or not ]
niskṛtiṃ tu mahāstreṇa dattvā sarpi rnirūpayet |
śive some tathā vahnau tatastridhā parikalpayet ||126:031||
tarpayitvā tato vahniṃ dattvā pūrṇāhutiṃ kramāt |
tatastvāsanavinyāsaṃ prāguktaṃ parikalpayet ||126:032||
pūrvoktena vidhānena gaṃdhapuṣpairanukramāt |
pūjayitvā mahādevyā tato homaṃ samācaret ||126:033||
bahuhavye dhane śuddhe susamiddhe hutāśane |
vidhūme lelihāneca vahninā yaḥ samidhyati ||126:034||
