%%% Chapter 128
aṣṭāviṃśatyadhikaśatatamo'dhyāyaḥ |

brahmovāca |

sarvārthasādhakaṃ śārstraṃ brahmavaktrāt vinisṛtam |
tenāpi nṛpaśārdūṃla kīrttitaṃ naravāhane ||128:001||
indreṇa vidhinā prāptamagastyena tathāgatam |
daśalakṣapramāṇantu śivo brahmaṇe proktavān ||128:002||
[brahmadakṣaprajāpataye śivo brahmaṇi proktavān ka ga]
labdhaṃ śakrasya lokasya vidyā devena bhāṣitam |
ghorotpatti vadhādīni devyārādhanamuttamam |
| ||128:003a-d||
[ghorotpatti vadhārthāya ka ga]
karmayogaśca yogaśca caturvargaprasādhakam ||128:003ef||
ādyaṃ devyavatāraṃ ca vācayed yaḥ śṛṇoti vā |
sa saṃsārādvinirmuktaḥ prāpnoti paramaṃ padam ||128:004||
vidyāsiṃhāsane madhye vastrapuṣpādi śobhite |
pūjayitvā śivaṃ jñātaṃ śṛṇuyādvācayet tathā ||128:005||
śrīmaddaṃḍāsanaṃ vāpi kṛtvā hemaṃ suśobhanam |
hemapaṭṭaparicchannaṃ nānāratnavibhūṣitam ||128:006||
rājataṃ tāmra kāsyaṃ vā brahmarītyā vinirmitam |
tarusārasamudbhūtaṃ śṛṃgavaṃśādisambhavam ||128:007||
ratna hemasamāyuktaṃ śaṃkhasphaṭika moktikaiḥ |
yathāsambhava sambhūtairadhaścordhvaṃ vibhūṣitam ||128:008||
[maṇiṃ ka]
samutkīrṇaṃ vicitraṃ ca sūtracinha vibandhanam |
dviguṇe dvipramāṇeṣu pūrṇaca ndranibheṣu ca ||128:009||
[sūtracitram ka; arddhapramāṇe ka ga]
citrotkīrṇaṃ suvarṇeṣu pratipādeṣu saṃsthitam |
dukūlaṃ paṭṭadevāṃgaṃ citrapaṭṭādisambhavam ||128:010||
viddhaṃ kusumaraktaṃ vā prākāra śikharānvitam |
caturbhiścandrakairyuktaṃ paṃcavarṇaiḥ suśobhanaiḥ ||128:011||
