giriprākāraśikharaiḥ sulakṣaiḥ paṃca varṇakaiḥ ||128:012a-d||
[varakopeteḥ ka ga]
sarvavastrasamudbhūtaiḥ kandukaiśca pralamvibhiḥ ||128:012ef||
itthamāśravaṇaṃ kṛtvā vinyaset daṇḍakāsane |
tasyopari mahāśāstraṃ devyākhyaṃ sthāpya pūjayet ||128:013||
vidyādānopahāreṇa śobhāṃ kṛtvā prayatnataḥ |
gandhādivāsitakaraḥ śrīmadāsanasaṃsthitaḥ ||128:014||
[vidyādānopacāreṇa ka ga]
bhāvayitvā śivaṃ devyāḥ śāstre'smin parameśvaram |
svayaṃ tiṣṭhati deveśī patiṃ devanamaskṛtam ||128:015||
[yātāṃ ka]
svakāyena tīrtheṣu narendra-bhavaneṣu ca |
bhāvayetparamaṃ dharmaṃ gṛhagrāme pureṣu ca ||128:016||
[sukāyena ka]
śrotāraṃ ca gurudhyānaṃ śivaṃ dhyātvā yathāvidhiḥ |
gandhapuṣpaiśca sambhāraiḥ pratyahaṃ tu yuge yuge ||128:017||
[jñāne ka ga]
pūjayitvā namitvā ca kṛtāṃjalipurāḥ sthitā |
sarve nīcāsanāḥ śāntā yathāvṛddha kramānugāḥ ||128:018||
dharmataḥ śrotumicchanti kathāntaravivarjitāḥ |
jñānārambhe samāptau ca śrotṛbhirvā cakena ca ||128:019||
devyā maṃtraṃ śivākhyaṃ ca uccāryaṃ sarvasiddhaye |
ānayed dhūpapuṣpādyai ekaikaḥ śrāvakaḥ kramāt ||128:020||
sarvasādhujanārthāya jñānamantraprado'pi vā |
ācārebhyaḥ karaṃ dadyāt vācakaḥ kusumatrayam ||128:021||
[ācāntebhyaḥ ka ga]
te'pi tairādimadhyāntaiḥ kuryuḥ pūjāṃ tu mastake |
iti śaktyā ca bhaktyā ca pūjāṃ kṛtvā sadakṣiṇām ||128:022||
pravarttaṃyati yaḥ kaścit devyāḥ pustaka vācanam |
sarvasattvopakārāya ātmanaśca vimuktaye ||128:023||
tasya puṇyaphalaṃ vakṣye śrotṛṇāṃ vācakasya ca |
dhanamāyuḥ prajā kīrttiḥ prajñāṃ buddhiṃ priyaṃ sukham ||128:024||
iha samprāpya vipulaṃ dehānte śāntimāpnuyāt |
asampūjya mahājñānaṃ pradeśe cāpyasaṃsthite ||128:025||
vācayannarakaṃ yāti tasmāt saṃskṛtya vācayet |
prasampūjya tathā vākyaṃ devāgnigurusannidhau ||128:026||
[api vācyaṃ ka]
mune dharmapravāhasya upakārāya buddhimān |
yathā pravarttito dharmo adharmaṃ ca parityajet ||128:027||
lobhādbhayānna vācyedaṃ devyāḥ śāstraṃ śivātmakam |
vācanāttu jagacchāntiravadhāryaṃ dine dine ||128:028||
gaccheyuḥ kuśapuṣpārthaṃ śivomāpūjanāya ca |
tataḥ śāstraṃ samāpyaṃ tu pūjāṃ kṛtvā viśeṣataḥ ||128:029||
[śveta ka ga No FN no. in the text portion. Please check! ]
devyā vidyāguruṇāṃ ca bhaktyā ca śivayoginām |
kanyakā dvijabandhūnāmanyeṣāmapi buddhimān ||128:030||
bhojanaṃ kalpayeccaiṣāṃ dīnārthānāṃ ca sarvaśaḥ |
mitrasvakulasādhūnāmante bhṛtyajanasya ca ||128:031||
gurave dakṣiṇāṃ dadyācchivo gomithunaṃ śubham |
vastra yugmāṃgulīyakaṃ ghṛtapūrṇaṃ tu bhojanam ||128:032||
[subhājanam ka No FN no. in the text portion. Please check! ]
vācakāya pradātavyaṃ dakṣiṇā pūrvabhāṣitā |
abhāṣitasya dātavyā gurorardhena dakṣiṇā ||128:033||
śeṣāṇāṃ ca yathāśaktyā dakṣiṇāṃ śivayoginām |
dadyāt prabodhayet paścāt pradīpādeḥ śataṃ budhaḥ ||128:034||
vitānañca dhvajaṃ deyaṃ devī devasya bhojanam |
yathā mantravataḥ kāryaṃ pūjā nārcā vivarjitā ||128:035||
[ka ga pustake ślokatrayaṃ nāsti]
nivedayecchive devyai aśeṣaṃ puṣpavādinām |
jñānaṃ puṇyaṃ mahāśāntiṃ śravaṇānnātra saṃśayaḥ ||128:036||
[puṇya vāriṇā ka; tataḥ syādakṣayaphalam ka ga]
evamudyotanaṃ kṛtvā devyāḥ śāstrasya bhaktitaḥ |
śiva - dīpa - pradātā ca pranaṣṭaâtamaâsaṃcayaḥ ||128:037||
vidhūtapāpakalilo viśuddhaste na saṃśayaḥ |
bhavanti sarvalokāstu bhāvitā deva yonayaḥ ||128:038||
aśeṣapāpanirmuktaḥ śṛṇu yat phalamāpnuyāt |
kule niśaṃkamuddhṛtya bhāryā putrādibhiryutaḥ ||128:039||
bahubhi svajanaiḥ snigdhai rbhṛtyadāsaiḥ samāśritaiḥ |
ityebhiḥ sahitaiḥ sarvaiḥ śrīmacchivapure brajet ||128:040||
[marttyadāsaiḥ ka]
mahāvimānarārūḍhaḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ |
tatra bhuktvā mahābhoga yāvadācandrapāvakam ||128:041||
[icchayā śivamandire ka]
dātā harttā ca karttā ca yāvatsākṣāllaye mahat |
pralayānte tataḥ jñānaṃ prāpya yogamanutta mam ||128:042||
tato devyā prasādena mucyate nātra saṃśayaḥ |
yasmādavagataṃ kuryāt devyāḥ pustakavācanam ||128:043||
[parameśaprasādena ka]
bhogāpavargaṃphaladaṃ śivabhaktyā dine dine |
na mārī na ca durbhikṣaṃ na rakṣāṃsi na vyādhayaḥ ||128:044||
nākāle mriyate rājā hanyate na ca śaktibhiḥ |
śṛṇoti yaśca satataṃ śivadharmaṃ narādhipaḥ ||128:045||
[kha pustake padyadvayaṃ nāsti]
tatra deśe mahāpuṇye devyāḥ sannihitā nṛpa |
śrutvā sakṛnnigadato manoyogānnarādhipa ||128:046||
śivaḥ sahomayā tatra krīḍate bhaktimatāṃ pure |
dadāti sarvakāmāni manasepsitaphalāni ca ||128:047||
sakṛcchrutvā mahāpuṇyaṃ pratiṣṭhā yājñikaṃ nṛpa |
hemante brahmalokaṃ tu śiśire viṣṇunā saha ||128:048||
tasmin dine mahāpuṇye tasya candramaso bhavet |
iha bhuktvākhilān bhogān parivāreṇa sa nṛpaḥ ||128:049||
ante devyā puravare śivena vidyutā saha |
krīḍate vipulairbhogairyāvadācandratārakam ||128:050||
[ka ga pustake nāsti padyadvayam]
vasante bhūṣyate devī umā sarvasukhapradā |
nidāghe vahirlokantu sarvakāmasamanvitam ||128:051||
[brahmalokastu kha]
tasmin bhogān mahān bhuktvā devīloke mahīyate |
prāvṛṭ kāle rudralokaṃ śruṇuyād yāti pārthivaḥ ||128:052||
śarat sarvānavāpnoti kāmān rājyaṃ nṛpottama |
triḥ śrutvā bhaktimāsthāya mucyate sarvapātakaiḥ ||128:053||
viśuddhaśca bhavedvaṃśaḥ sarvakāmaphalāvahaḥ |
paṃca śrutvā mahādhyāyī svargaloke mahīyate ||128:054||
mātṛsaṃghaṃ yamo nityaṃ tuṣyate avicāraṇāt |
tasya bhogaṃ varṇayituṃ mama vāṇī na śaknuyāt ||128:055||
ihaloke śubhaṃ bhuktvā tadante śivalokataḥ |
khaṭvāvadhaṃ tathā śrutvā vināyakasya janma ca ||128:056||
[bhavate vigatāmayaḥ ka ga]
mātṛlokamavāpnoti krīḍate ca ciraṃ sukho |
devīṃ sampūjayitvā tu vidhinā nṛpasattama ||128:057||
prasādañca prakurvīta pratyakṣā ca bhavet śivā |
sadācāraḥ śubhāhāraḥ sarvasaṃgavivarjitaḥ ||128:058||
vācayan purāṇamettattu sarvakāmamavāpnuyāt |
vācayan śatamardhaṃ vā pratyakṣaṃ prāpnuyācchivam ||128:059||
etaccābhyudayapādaṃ śataistribhirnarottamaiḥ |
sahasrairdvādaśairvatsa kathitaṃ sarvasiddhidam ||128:60||
| oṃ namo durgāyai |

iti śrī devīpurāṇe vācanavidhirnāma aṣṭāviṃśatyadhikaśatatamodhyāyaḥ |
|
[ādye devyavatāre devīpurāṇaṃ samāptamiti ka ga]
|| ādye devyavatāre devīpurāṇaṃ sampūrṇam |
|
[ka ga samāptaḥ sampūrṇam]































